NK026(la)001:1: // 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi cho ga khrigs su byas
NK026(la)001:2: pa dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs las glegs bam
NK026(la)001:4: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK026(la)001:6: de nas rgyal thebs kyis gu gul dang bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags ring gis bgegs bskrad /
NK026(la)001:7: slob ma rnams las mkhan gyis sna drangs la ru
NK026(la)001:8: lu gar gyi dbyangs dang bcas pas dkyil 'khor dang
NK026(la)001:9: bla ma la bskor ba lan gsum du byas te
NK026(la)001:12: slob ma rnams dkyil 'khor du zhugs zin pa yin
NK026(la)001:13: na'ang gzhung gi dgongs pa ltar bgegs gtor slob ma
NK026(la)001:15: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK026(la)001:16: slob ma rnams 'phrang la bshar te rgyal thebs kyis
NK026(la)001:17: bgegs bskrad par gsungs kyang rdo rje slob dpon nyid
NK026(la)001:18: kyis yungs thun brdeg cing bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags
NK026(la)001:20: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK026(la)001:21: na mash+tsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK026(la)001:22: na mo badz+ra kro d+ha ya ma h+aa damsh+tmo ta ka ta bee ra w+aa ya /
NK026(la)001:23: a si mu sa la d+h+aa ra ya /
NK026(la)001:24: pa ra shu pa sha has+t+aa ya /
NK026(la)001:26: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:34: bi s+pho ta ya bi s+pho ta ya /
NK026(la)001:35: sarba big+h+n+aana bi n+aa ya ka n+aan /
NK026(la)001:36: ma h+aa g+ha na pa ti dzi w+ai te an+ta ka ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:37: zhes sogs dang khro bo'i drag sngags gzhan yang brjod de bgegs bskrad cing /
NK026(la)001:38: las mkhan gyis sna drangs la ru lu'i gar dbyangs
NK026(la)001:39: kyis bla ma dang dkyil 'khor la bskor ba lan
NK026(la)001:40: gsum byas te gral la 'khod de /
NK026(la)001:42: da ni slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK026(la)001:44: dang po bdag nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK026(la)001:45: gnyis pa slob ma khrus dang zhes gsungs pas las bum gyi chus khrus bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:46: ji ltar bltams pa zhes sogs sngags dang bcas pa brjod nas khrus bya /
NK026(la)001:47: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu byas la /
NK026(la)001:49: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad khyab
NK026(la)001:50: bdag gdod ma'i mgon po kun bzang he ru ka'i
NK026(la)001:52: de'i ched du 'dir bcom ldan 'das zhi khro tshogs
NK026(la)001:53: chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs te don nyams
NK026(la)001:54: su blangs te sems can gyi don rgya chen po
NK026(la)001:55: bgyid snyam pa'i byang chub kyi mchog tu thugs bskyed
NK026(la)001:57: gsan bya'i chos kyi ngo skal du gyur pa ni 'dir /
NK026(la)001:58: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa la //
NK026(la)001:59: rgyu dang lam dang 'bras bu'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:61: 'di la yang 'chad tshul mang yang dang por dpon
NK026(la)001:62: slob kyi rten 'brel legs par 'grig pas rdo rje
NK026(la)001:63: theg pa'i smin byed rgyu'i dbang bzhis smin par byas
NK026(la)001:64: te / de nyid lam dus su thun bzhi'am drug dang /
NK026(la)001:65: yang na thun mtshams med par dbang bzhi'i lam nyams
NK026(la)001:66: su blangs pas 'bras bu kun bzang ye shes bla
NK026(la)001:68: rgyu lam 'bras bu'i dbang yongs su rdzogs pa zhes bya ba yin la /
NK026(la)001:69: de ltar dbang bskur byed pa la yang rgyud sde
NK026(la)001:70: so so'i lugs dang spyi bka'i khog nas sgos bka'
NK026(la)001:71: tshang ba'i lugs gnyis su yod pa las phyi ma
NK026(la)001:72: yin / de la yang gang zag dbang po yang
NK026(la)001:73: rab rnams kyi don du snga gyur gter ma'i phyogs
NK026(la)001:74: su theg pa rim dgu'i smin byed cig car du
NK026(la)001:75: bskur ba'i lugs mang du yod kyang /
NK026(la)001:76: 'dir gsang sngags bka' ma 'dus pa chen po mdo'i
NK026(la)001:77: lugs kyis dang por sgo 'byed phyag na rdo rje
NK026(la)001:78: ngan song kun 'dren gyi dbang gis sgo phye ste
NK026(la)001:79: 'jig rten lha mi'i theg par drangs shing grub pa'i
NK026(la)001:80: mthas blo bsgyur te nyan thos kyi theg par bkri
NK026(la)001:81: zhing / de yang lam de dag kho na mchog ma yin zhing drang ba'i don yin te /
NK026(la)001:82: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK026(la)001:83: bslu ba'i thabs kyis gzud pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:84: so so mos pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK026(la)001:85: lta spyod rnams dang mthun 'jug tu //
NK026(la)001:86: sbyar nas brten drang thabs su gsungs //
NK026(la)001:88: de yang ji ltar la la zhig /
NK026(la)001:90: gru gzings dag la brten pas 'gro //
NK026(la)001:91: mthar son pa na 'bor ba bzhin //
NK026(la)001:92: thabs sam theg pa'i bye brag rnams //
NK026(la)001:93: brten pas drang ba'i thabs yin yang //
NK026(la)001:94: don gyi nges pa rnyed ma thag /
NK026(la)001:95: chu bo brgal ba'i gru bzhin 'dor //
NK026(la)001:97: dper na chu bo brgal bar 'dod pas gru gzings la ma brten par 'gro mi nus la /
NK026(la)001:98: skam sar thon nas gru brten kyang ngal ba don med par 'bor dgos pa'i phyir na /
NK026(la)001:99: lha mi nyan rang sogs kyi theg pa rnams 'bor
NK026(la)001:100: ba'i rgya mtsho las drang ba'i lam rten gru gzings
NK026(la)001:102: dngos don bsgrub bya'i gtso bo ni theg pa chen po'i lam yin par gsungs shing /
NK026(la)001:103: de lta bu'i theg pa chen po de la yang rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK026(la)001:104: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK026(la)001:105: dang por rdo rje theg pa'i lam rten pha rol
NK026(la)001:106: tu phyin pa'i lam byang chub sems dpa'i theg par
NK026(la)001:107: dkris te / lam de'i tshul rnams khong du chud pa dag /
NK026(la)001:110: yo ga rnal 'byor gyi rgyud rnams su rim bzhin drangs /
NK026(la)001:111: mthar gsang sngags bla na med pa yo ga gsum
NK026(la)001:112: gyi dkyil 'khor chen por 'jug pa'i skabs yin pas
NK026(la)001:113: lam srol 'di ni rmad du byung ba bstan pa
NK026(la)001:114: yongs rdzogs kyi nye lam chen por gyur pa yin
NK026(la)001:115: / de ltar yo ga gsum las 'dir a nu
NK026(la)001:116: yo ga gtso che ba'i khog nas yo ga gsum
NK026(la)001:117: gyi smin grol gyi lam tshang la ma nor ba
NK026(la)001:118: bstan pas de kho na nyid kyi don mngon du
NK026(la)001:119: / 'gyur zhing / de lta bu'i don khong du
NK026(la)001:120: chud nas lam thams cad grogs su 'gyur ba yin
NK026(la)001:122: des na de bzhin nyid shes na //
NK026(la)001:123: thams cad thams cad gang yang rung //
NK026(la)001:124: dam pa'i lam du nges pas na //
NK026(la)001:125: lam gyi nang nas nye lam yin //
NK026(la)001:127: de lta bu'i lam gyi 'jug sgo ni dbang bskur kho na ste /
NK026(la)001:128: de la yang ma thob pa'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK026(la)001:129: thob pa'i phan yon gnyis las /
NK026(la)001:132: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK026(la)001:133: dbang rnams thob pa ma byas par //
NK026(la)001:134: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:139: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK026(la)001:140: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK026(la)001:141: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK026(la)001:142: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur na //
NK026(la)001:143: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK026(la)001:144: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK026(la)001:145: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK026(la)001:146: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:148: lung sbyor rgyas par gzhan dag kyang spro'o //
NK026(la)001:149: de ltar gsang sngags nang gi dbang bskur ba'i tshul yang /
NK026(la)001:151: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang /
NK026(la)001:152: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:153: zhes gsungs pa rnams 'og tu rgyas par 'byung zhing /
NK026(la)001:154: de lta bu'i dbang bskur ba'i yon 'bul tshul yang /
NK026(la)001:156: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK026(la)001:157: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK026(la)001:158: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK026(la)001:159: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK026(la)001:161: de ltar phul ba'i phan yon yang /
NK026(la)001:163: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK026(la)001:164: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK026(la)001:165: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK026(la)001:166: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:168: de ltar dbang bskur bya yang lam srol 'di'i lugs kyi dbang gi chu bo chen po bzhi ste /
NK026(la)001:170: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK026(la)001:171: phyi rgyud dbang gi chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:172: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK026(la)001:173: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:174: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK026(la)001:175: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:176: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK026(la)001:177: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:178: zhes gsungs pa'i don phyi rgyud kyi dbang gi chu bo chen po grub nas /
NK026(la)001:179: yo ga gsum gyi dbang gi chu bo bya ba skabs su bab pa yin /
NK026(la)001:180: de lta bu'i dbang gi ngo bo ni gdul bya'i rgyud byin gyis rlob pa yin la /
NK026(la)001:181: nges tshig ni rang rang gi lta sgom spyod gsum la dbang ba ste /
NK026(la)001:182: dper na rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang
NK026(la)001:183: bskur ba des rgyal srid la dbang sgyur nus pa
NK026(la)001:185: dbye ba yang rgyas par phye na mang du yod kyang /
NK026(la)001:186: bsdu na rang lugs su yongs su 'dzin pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi dbang /
NK026(la)001:187: bka' rtags po ti glegs bam gyi dbang /
NK026(la)001:189: rig pa'i rtsal dbang dang bzhir phye ba'i lugs ltar na /
NK026(la)001:190: theg pa rim dgu dang sbyor bas /
NK026(la)001:191: byang sems man chad la dbang dang po sbyor te so sor thar pa'i skabs /
NK026(la)001:192: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshul shog bka' stsal pa //
NK026(la)001:193: skra byi snam sbyar gyon pa'i lus ldan zhing //
NK026(la)001:194: mod la dbang po rab zhi gnas gyur te //
NK026(la)001:195: sangs rgyas dgongs pas lus gzugs bkab par gyur //
NK026(la)001:196: zhes gsungs pa'i don yang sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pas
NK026(la)001:197: byin gyis brlabs te dge slong gi dngos por dbang
NK026(la)001:198: bskur ba lta bu yin la /
NK026(la)001:199: de mtshungs byang sar yang bcom ldan 'das dga' ldan
NK026(la)001:200: nas 'pho ba'i tshe byams pa rgyal tshab tu dbang
NK026(la)001:201: bskur ba dang / 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur
NK026(la)001:202: ba sogs kyang don gyi dbang yin pa'i phyir na
NK026(la)001:203: bskur ba dang / / thang yig las /
NK026(la)001:204: yongs su 'dzin pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dbang //
NK026(la)001:206: gnyis pa po ti glegs bam gyi dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:207: rgyal po dzah'am rgyal po lung bstan rdo rje'i khang
NK026(la)001:208: thog tu tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad kyi rgyud
NK026(la)001:209: sde'i chos char chen po babs pa lta bu dang
NK026(la)001:210: / bod yul gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir yang dam
NK026(la)001:211: pa'i chos kyi dbu brnyes pa'i thog mar lha tho
NK026(la)001:212: tho ri snyan shal gyi dus pho brang yum bu
NK026(la)001:213: bla mkhar du mdo sde za ma tog dang dbang
NK026(la)001:214: skong phyag rgya pa sogs babs pa la brten bsil
NK026(la)001:215: ldan gyi ljongs 'dir mdo sngags kyi bstan pa gnyis
NK026(la)001:216: ldan dar bar byed pa'i rten 'brel don gyi dbang
NK026(la)001:219: chos bka' gtad pa po ti glegs bam dbang //
NK026(la)001:222: yi dam gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs
NK026(la)001:223: brnyan gyis dbang bskur pa rang gzhung kho na'i khyad
NK026(la)001:225: rig pa'i rtsal dbang yi dam lha yi dbang //
NK026(la)001:228: rig pa'i rtsal dbang dngos a ti yo ga'i dbang bskur ba rnams yin te /
NK026(la)001:230: yongs rdzogs phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dbang //
NK026(la)001:232: khyad par gsang sngags nang pa bla na med pa'i phyogs 'dir /
NK026(la)001:236: bde ba chen po'am dbang bzhi pa ste bzhir nges la /
NK026(la)001:237: de dag la yang so sor rim pa bzhin du dbang /
NK026(la)001:242: 'bras bu ste don tshan drug las /
NK026(la)001:243: dang po bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:244: mtshon byed dpe'i dkyil 'khor du rdo rje slob ma'i dbang gi dus su rig pa'i dbang lnga /
NK026(la)001:245: brtul zhugs rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang bcas
NK026(la)001:246: pa ston par byed pa la phyi phan pa'i dbang
NK026(la)001:247: bcu dang / nang nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK026(la)001:249: phyi nang gi phung khams skye mched sbyong bar byed pa bskyed rim gyi lam /
NK026(la)001:250: gsum pa de lam du 'khyer byed kyi lta ba ni /
NK026(la)001:251: snang phyogs kyi ngo bo nyid gsum /
NK026(la)001:252: stong phyogs kyi ngo bo nyid gsum /
NK026(la)001:253: zung 'jug gi ngo bo nyid gsum ste lta ba'i ngo bo nyid gsum /
NK026(la)001:254: bzhi pa de'i grub mtha' la 'khor 'das dbyer med /
NK026(la)001:259: bgrod byed kyi thabs des lus rtsa'i dri ma mtha' dag sbyangs te /
NK026(la)001:260: drug pa 'bras bu sprul pa'i sku 'grub par byed pa yin te /
NK026(la)001:261: shes byed kyi gtan tshigs su /
NK026(la)001:262: dri med bshags rgyud de bum dbang gi bshags pa'i dus su /
NK026(la)001:263: bskyed rim dbyibs kyi lam du ma shes bshags //
NK026(la)001:265: ngo bo nyid gsum lta ba'i klong du bshags //
NK026(la)001:267: grub mtha' 'khor 'das dbyer med dang du bshags //
NK026(la)001:269: ma rtogs 'chi dus snang ba bsgyur ba dang /
NK026(la)001:270: 'od kyi gong bu sgra yis 'pho ma shes //
NK026(la)001:272: lus kyi rtsa yi gtso bo phal pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:273: ye nas sprul skur gnas pa ma shes te //
NK026(la)001:274: dbyibs kyi lha sku rang gsal sgom ma shes //
NK026(la)001:275: sprul sku rang bzhin lhun grub 'bras bur bshags //
NK026(la)001:278: rdzas gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:281: gnyis ka las thob pa sogs dngos sam thabs dang brdas bskur /
NK026(la)001:282: lam bdag byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa 'khor lo
NK026(la)001:283: la brten pa dang ma brten pa'i rdzogs rim zab
NK026(la)001:284: mo / lta ba nyon mongs rang byung /
NK026(la)001:287: gsal zhing yangs pa'i rang byung ste rang byung gi ye shes bzhi /
NK026(la)001:290: bgrod byed kyi thabs des ngag rtsa yi ge'i dri
NK026(la)001:291: ma sbyangs te 'bras bu longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK026(la)001:293: bshags rgyud kyi 'phros gsang dbang gi bshags pa'i skabs las /
NK026(la)001:294: 'khor lo brten dang ma brten man ngag gnad //
NK026(la)001:295: bde ba nyams su len pa'i lam ma bsgoms //
NK026(la)001:296: bdag la byin rlabs lam gyi ngang du bshags //
NK026(la)001:298: nyon mongs dang ni rnam rtog s+n+rel gzhi ste //
NK026(la)001:299: gsal zhing yangs pa'i rang byung ye shes gnas //
NK026(la)001:300: lta ba rang byung ye shes klong du zhes sogs lta ba dang /
NK026(la)001:301: grub mtha' ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngang du zhes sogs grub mtha' dang /
NK026(la)001:302: 'da' kha'i gdams ngag 'od gsal ngang du zhes sogs 'da' kha'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK026(la)001:303: 'bras bu longs spyod rdzogs sku'i ngang du bshags //
NK026(la)001:305: de bzhin du dbang gsum pa yang /
NK026(la)001:306: dngos sam ye shes kyi phyag rgya b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor du shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK026(la)001:307: de lam myur mgyogs pho nya'i lam ste thabs lam /
NK026(la)001:308: lta ba lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes /
NK026(la)001:309: grub mtha' bde stong rgya chung ba /
NK026(la)001:310: 'da' kha'i rnal 'byor nam 'chi ba'i tshe rdo rje sems dpa' 'byon par 'gyur ba /
NK026(la)001:311: bgrod byed kyi thabs des yid khams bdud rtsi'i dri
NK026(la)001:312: ma spyangs te 'bras bu chos kyi skur grol bar
NK026(la)001:313: byed de / bshags rgyud kyi dbang gsum pa'i bshags pa'i skabs las /
NK026(la)001:314: yum bdag 'dod pa'i byin rlabs mnyam pa la //
NK026(la)001:315: 'khor lo thabs kyi lam du zhes sogs lam dang /
NK026(la)001:316: bde bzhi lta ba lhan skyes ngang du zhes sogs lta ba dang /
NK026(la)001:317: bde stong rgya chung grub mtha' ma rtogs pa //
NK026(la)001:319: 'da' kha rdo rje sems dpa'i ngang du zhes 'da' kha'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK026(la)001:320: 'bras bu chos kyi sku yi ngang du zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:321: de ltar dbang bzhi pa yang /
NK026(la)001:322: don dam byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bzhi pa rig pa rtsal gyi dbang /
NK026(la)001:323: de'i lam ro rkyang dbu gsum gyi rdo rje rlabs /
NK026(la)001:324: lta ba chos thams cad shin tu rnam par dag pa /
NK026(la)001:325: grub mtha' bde stong rgya che ba /
NK026(la)001:326: 'da' kha'i rnal 'byor phyag rgya chen po /
NK026(la)001:327: bgrod byed kyi thabs de nyid kyis ye shes rlung gi dri ma sbyangs te /
NK026(la)001:328: 'bras bu ngo bo nyid sku thob par 'gyur ba ste /
NK026(la)001:329: bshags rgyud kyi bde ba chen po'i bshags pa'i skabs las /
NK026(la)001:330: rdo rje rba rlabs lam gsum ngang du zhes sogs lam dang /
NK026(la)001:331: lta ba chos rnams rnam dag ngang du zhes sogs lta ba dang /
NK026(la)001:332: bde stong rgya cha'i grub mtha' zhes sogs grub mtha' dang /
NK026(la)001:333: 'da' kha phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du zhes sogs 'da' kha'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK026(la)001:334: 'bras bu ngo bo nyid kyi sku ru zhes sogs kyang gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:335: de ltar dbang de rnams bskur bar byed pa'i bla ma'ang bzhir nges te /
NK026(la)001:336: sgro 'dogs gcod byed kyi bla mas bum dbang /
NK026(la)001:337: ye shes ston byed kyi bla mas gsang dbang /
NK026(la)001:338: lhan skyes ston byed kyi bla mas dbang gsum pa /
NK026(la)001:339: de nyid ston byed kyi bla mas dbang bzhi pa
NK026(la)001:340: rnams bskur bar byed dgos pa yang dri med bshags
NK026(la)001:341: rgyud kyi gleng gzhi'i skabs las /
NK026(la)001:342: lam la gnas pa'i bla ma dam pa ni bzhi zhig yod de /
NK026(la)001:343: phyi sgro 'dogs yongs su gcod par byed pa'i bla ma dam pa dang /
NK026(la)001:344: nang rang byung gi ye shes ston par byed pa'i bla ma dam pa dang /
NK026(la)001:345: gsang ba lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ston par byed pa'i bla ma dam pa dang /
NK026(la)001:346: mthar thug de kho na nyid kyi bla ma chos
NK026(la)001:347: thams cad shin tu rnam par dag pa'i de kho
NK026(la)001:348: na nyid ston par byed pa'i bla ma dam pa'o
NK026(la)001:350: de lta bu'i bla ma dam pa des gdul bya'i
NK026(la)001:351: rgyud la brtags te sdug bsngal gsum gyi mtshang bstan
NK026(la)001:352: pa ma dag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:353: lam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyi thabs bstan pa las byung ba'i nyams kyi snang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:354: lam des 'bras bu grub pa'i tshul la spro ba
NK026(la)001:355: bskyed pa dag pa'i snang ba gsum gyis rgyud sbyangs
NK026(la)001:356: / kun gzhi rgyu'i rgyud lta bas gtan la phab /
NK026(la)001:357: lus thabs kyi rgyud dbang bzhi'i lam gyis sbyangs /
NK026(la)001:358: phyag rgya chen po 'bras bu'i rgyud rang byung lhun grub tu ngo sprad /
NK026(la)001:359: de dag kyang rgyu lam 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor gsum gyi sa bsdus te /
NK026(la)001:360: mdor na de dag kyang bla ma'i snyan rgyud tshad ma gdams ngag gi sel med pa dang /
NK026(la)001:361: de nyid nyams myong tshad mas gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:362: de la nges shes bskyed phyir rtogs brjod dang lo rgyus tshad ma dang sbyar ba dang /
NK026(la)001:363: rgol ba ngan pa'i klan ka'i dri ma med pa'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:364: mdo rgyud kyi bka'i lung tshad ma ste dbang bzhi'i
NK026(la)001:365: chu bo ma nub pa'i dbang rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i
NK026(la)001:366: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ma nyams pa de nyid
NK026(la)001:367: gdams ngag gi sna kha ma log par gdul bya'i
NK026(la)001:368: mos gus kyi bsam pa tshim par byas te /
NK026(la)001:369: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi rten 'brel yang dag par bsgrigs la /
NK026(la)001:370: lta sgom spyod gsum gyi sgo nas gsang sngags kyi
NK026(la)001:371: lam bzang por 'jug pa'i tshul legs par 'chad pa
NK026(la)001:373: dri med rgyal po bshags rgyud las /
NK026(la)001:374: khyad par du yang ma dag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:376: dag pa'i snang ba rnams ma rtogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:379: phyag rgya chen po 'bras bu'i rgyud ma rtogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:382: 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor ma rtogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:383: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' yang dag pa lung gi tshad ma dang /
NK026(la)001:384: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug nyams myong rjes su dran pa'i tshad ma dang /
NK026(la)001:385: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon snyan khung brgyud pa man ngag gi tshad ma dang /
NK026(la)001:386: dngos po'i mtha' rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba lo rgyus kyi tshad ma ma rtogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:387: de dag rtogs par bya ba'i phyir 'di dag bshad de /
NK026(la)001:388: dbang gi chu bo ma nub pa dang /
NK026(la)001:389: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ma nyams pa dang /
NK026(la)001:390: gdams ngag gi sna kha ma log pa dang /
NK026(la)001:391: mos gus kyi bsam pa tshim par nus pa'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:395: mthar thug de kho na nyid kyi rten 'brel bsgrigs te /
NK026(la)001:396: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' tshad ma dang /
NK026(la)001:397: bla ma'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK026(la)001:398: rang gi rig pa tshad mas gtan la phab ste /
NK026(la)001:401: spyod pas la dor nas gsang sngags gsang ba'i lam la zhugs /
NK026(la)001:403: mdor na de dag bshad gzhi tsam ma yin par
NK026(la)001:404: mngon sum gyi spyod yul du byar rung bas bla
NK026(la)001:405: ma gdams ngag can zhig nges par bsten dgos shing
NK026(la)001:406: / khyad par 'khrul pa med pa'i lam 'di ltar 'jug rung ngam /
NK026(la)001:407: brten rung gi skal pa bzang po dang ldan pa yin /
NK026(la)001:408: de'i thabs kyi gtso bo 'dir skabs su babs pa
NK026(la)001:409: smin byed dbang gi las bya ba'i skabs yin la
NK026(la)001:410: / de la yang slob dpon gyi bya ba dang /
NK026(la)001:411: slob ma'i bya ba gnyis su yod pa las /
NK026(la)001:412: slob dpon gyi bgyi bar 'os pa mtha' dag kha
NK026(la)001:413: sang nas legs par grub pa'i tshul kun gyis nyams
NK026(la)001:414: su myong ba de bzhin lags /
NK026(la)001:416: rtsa ba'i dbang du slob ma 'jug pa'i chos bcu
NK026(la)001:417: bdun du gsungs pa'i dang po slob dpon gyi bdag
NK026(la)001:418: 'jug dang / gnyis pa khrus bya ba gnyis grub pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK026(la)001:419: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo kun tu
NK026(la)001:420: bzang po dang tha mi dad pa'i zhabs drung du
NK026(la)001:421: 'jug pa'i chos rnams zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul
NK026(la)001:422: mdzod / ces mtshams sbyar la man+dala 'bul /
NK026(la)001:424: gsum pa mig dgab pa song nas /
NK026(la)001:425: zhes 'byung bas mig dar dmar po 'ching zhing /
NK026(la)001:426: 'khrul gzhi'i don du mig dar bcings par mos mdzod /
NK026(la)001:427: tsak+shu ban+d+ha w+aa ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:429: dar sna lnga'i cod pan me tog gi phreng ba lnga brgyus pa brim zhing /
NK026(la)001:430: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dang mjal ba'i tshe phyag
NK026(la)001:431: rten mtshon pa'i me tog gi phreng ba gtad par
NK026(la)001:432: mos mdzod / +aa kham w+ai ra h+aum /
NK026(la)001:435: bzhi pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:436: zhes gsungs pa'i don bla mas bzhengs te dkyil 'khor phyogs su thal mo sbyar te /
NK026(la)001:437: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK026(la)001:438: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK026(la)001:440: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bgyi //
NK026(la)001:441: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:443: lha rnams dgyes pas chu gcig ces bka' gnang bar bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:445: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK026(la)001:446: bu khyod dad pa ci la dad //
NK026(la)001:447: khyod kyi dgos pa ji lta bu //
NK026(la)001:448: da lta nyid du 'dir smros shig /
NK026(la)001:450: slob mas de'i lan du 'di'i rjes zlos bya ste /
NK026(la)001:451: bdag ni skal ldan bde chen te //
NK026(la)001:453: byang chub sems la bdag dad do //
NK026(la)001:454: theg chen chos la bdag mos so //
NK026(la)001:459: e ma bde gshegs snying po'i don //
NK026(la)001:460: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK026(la)001:461: khyed kyi rab tu bstan du gsol //
NK026(la)001:462: ye shes rdo rje'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK026(la)001:463: rdo rje'i lam nas drangs nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:465: byin rlabs dbang mchog blang bar bgyi //
NK026(la)001:467: drug pa lus dbul ba ni /
NK026(la)001:469: lus dbul ba'i tshigs bcad tsam las ma byung yang 'di'i don ni /
NK026(la)001:471: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK026(la)001:472: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:473: zhes gsungs pa'i bde gshegs ni 'das pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK026(la)001:474: dbang phyug ni bla ma ste da ltar gyi sangs rgyas /
NK026(la)001:475: sems can ni ma 'ongs pa na sangs rgyas su 'gyur bas ma 'ongs sangs rgyas te /
NK026(la)001:476: de dag dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i phyir mkhas grub
NK026(la)001:477: se ston rin chen rgyal mtshan gyis tshig gi mtha'
NK026(la)001:479: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK026(la)001:480: dus gsum bzhugs la lus 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:483: bde gshegs la lus phul bas sku gsung thugs yon
NK026(la)001:484: tan phrin las kyi ye shes thob pa'i dgos pa
NK026(la)001:485: dang / bla ma la lus phul bas sangs rgyas
NK026(la)001:486: thams cad kyi ye shes thob pa'i snod du rung
NK026(la)001:487: dang / ba dang / sems can la lus phul
NK026(la)001:488: bas sems can gyi don mthar phyin par bya ba
NK026(la)001:492: phyogs bcu sras dang bcas pa dang //
NK026(la)001:493: dbang phyug sangs rgyas da lta bdag /
NK026(la)001:494: ma 'ongs rang bzhin sems can la //
NK026(la)001:495: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul bya //
NK026(la)001:496: mchog gi yon phyir snod du 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:498: dbang gi yon gyi mchog bdag gi lus dus gsum
NK026(la)001:499: du bzhugs pa'i rgyal ba de dag la 'bul dgos
NK026(la)001:500: pas yid rtse gcig de'i don bzhi pas thal mo
NK026(la)001:501: sbyar te rjes zlos bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:504: 'byung lus gdos pas bcings pa'i phung po 'di //
NK026(la)001:505: bdag med rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyar ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:506: lus sogs rdzas kyi mchod pa dam pa 'dis //
NK026(la)001:507: bla med sman pa'i mchod par 'bul lags na //
NK026(la)001:508: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis dgongs nas su //
NK026(la)001:509: blang dor med pa'i tshul gyis bzhes su gsol //
NK026(la)001:513: bi shwa badz+rasa bgegs bskrad la /
NK026(la)001:514: zhes gsungs pa'i don dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi thugs
NK026(la)001:515: ka nas khro bo'i tshogs spros te dbang len pa
NK026(la)001:516: la bar du gcod pa'i bgegs rigs rnams bskrad par
NK026(la)001:518: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK026(la)001:519: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK026(la)001:520: dag pa mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK026(la)001:521: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyi
NK026(la)001:522: rlabs kyis 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gnod
NK026(la)001:523: cing 'tshe bar byed pa'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir
NK026(la)001:526: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata /
NK026(la)001:527: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK026(la)001:531: slob ma'i klad pa dung khang du nyi ma'i 'od kyis lus thams cad khyab /
NK026(la)001:532: a yu h+aum dzahs tshe'i ngo bo mu tig dkar po lta bu /
NK026(la)001:533: b+h+r+aum las zla gam dmar po sgo gcig pa'i nang
NK026(la)001:534: du badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum gis h+aum
NK026(la)001:535: k+aa ra bskyed / badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa las mi g.yo bas sgo bsrung ba bsam /
NK026(la)001:536: rang dpal gyi sor mo bcur nyi zla la yig
NK026(la)001:537: 'bru bcu las rigs lnga yab yum gyi 'phro 'du
NK026(la)001:538: byas te / zhes gsungs pa'i don slob ma'i klad
NK026(la)001:539: pa dung khang du nyi ma'i 'od kyis lus thams
NK026(la)001:540: byas te / cad khyab / bla ma'i thugs ka'i
NK026(la)001:541: sa bon las yi ge b+h+r+aum re slob ma rnams
NK026(la)001:543: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes brjod pas /
NK026(la)001:544: zla gam dmar po'i khang khyams sgo gcig pa sgo khyud can zhig bsam /
NK026(la)001:545: de'i nang du a yuhh+aum dzah zhes brjod pas slob
NK026(la)001:546: ma de rnams kyi tshe'i dngos po thams cad mu
NK026(la)001:547: tig dkar po lta bur bsdus te h+aum la thim
NK026(la)001:548: / badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:549: ces brjod pas h+aum k+aa ra sngo nag zhal gcig
NK026(la)001:550: phyag gnyis g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon sdigs mdzub can
NK026(la)001:551: du bsam / zla gam gyi sgo khyud la /
NK026(la)001:552: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:553: ces brjod pas khro bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag
NK026(la)001:554: ral gri dang sdigs mdzub kyis zhags pa bsnams pas
NK026(la)001:556: slob dpon bdag nyid dpal chen por gsal ba'i sor
NK026(la)001:557: mo bcu las g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la nyi
NK026(la)001:558: ma'i gdan la / h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa ste /
NK026(la)001:559: 'bru lnga las rigs lnga yab lnga /
NK026(la)001:560: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la zla ba'i gdan la /
NK026(la)001:561: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+y+aam t+aam ste 'bru lnga las yum lnga /
NK026(la)001:563: zhes sbyar bas rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba mdzad par bsam /
NK026(la)001:567: zhes phyag rgya bsdams te bden pa brjod pa ni /
NK026(la)001:570: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK026(la)001:571: cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing
NK026(la)001:572: khams mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden
NK026(la)001:573: pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis
NK026(la)001:574: gang zag 'di dag gi rgyud la yod pa'i las
NK026(la)001:575: dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK026(la)001:576: lta ba dman zhing shes rab zhan pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK026(la)001:577: khyad par du gsang sngags zab mo'i dbang nod pa'i
NK026(la)001:578: sgrib pa gang yod pa thams cad skad cig tsam
NK026(la)001:579: la byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:581: zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing phyag rgya bkrol
NK026(la)001:582: te sprugs pas rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba mdzad
NK026(la)001:583: pa byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba'i 'od zer
NK026(la)001:584: gyis slob ma rnams kyi sgrib pa ma lus par
NK026(la)001:585: sbyangs pas shes rgyud shel ltar dag par bsam /
NK026(la)001:586: badz+ra a be sha ya +aa las khro bo h+aum
NK026(la)001:587: k+aa ra dang mi g.yo ba gnyis 'od du zhu
NK026(la)001:588: bas slob ma'i rnam shes dang gcig tu gyur te
NK026(la)001:589: / lus bkrag mdangs dang ldan par bsam zhing mthar
NK026(la)001:590: lus kyang dngula chu zhun ma lta bur gnas par
NK026(la)001:591: / gyur / de nas rang gang mos kyi lhar bskyed la go bgo lus bsrung ngo //
NK026(la)001:593: skad cig gis slob ma pad zla'i gdan la h+aum
NK026(la)001:594: las rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa yongs su gyur
NK026(la)001:595: pa las rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po g.yas rdo
NK026(la)001:596: rje thugs ka dang g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa
NK026(la)001:597: rin po che'i rgyan dang dar gyi na bza' gsol
NK026(la)001:598: ba zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs par
NK026(la)001:599: gyur / ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:600: de bzhin du thog mtha' 'dra bar /
NK026(la)001:604: kri t+y+aa nush+tha na sogs phyag rgya dang bcas te ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:605: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:606: de bzhin du w+aa ka badz+ra /
NK026(la)001:607: tsit+ta badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab bo //
NK026(la)001:608: go bgo ba ni rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK026(la)001:609: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha rak+sha /
NK026(la)001:610: zhes brjod pas lus mgo mjug thams cad rdo rje'i go khrab kyis gtams par bsam /
NK026(la)001:611: sngar ltar lag gnyis kyi mdzub mo gnyis khro bo
NK026(la)001:612: rdo rje gnod sbyin dang mi 'chi thal sbyor gyi
NK026(la)001:613: rang bzhin can gyis gnas drug tu bsrung ba'i phyag
NK026(la)001:614: rgya bcas pas gsang gnas su khro bo gnyis gshibs
NK026(la)001:615: te zhal phyir bstan bzhengs pa'i tshul du bsrung /
NK026(la)001:616: lte bar khro bo gnyis dbu sprad bcu drug mdor zhabs sprad de ske rags kyi tshul du bsrung /
NK026(la)001:617: rgyab kyi tshigs pa bdun par dbu sprad snying gar phyag sprad de stod chings kyi tshul du bsrung /
NK026(la)001:618: mgrin par khro bo gnyis gshibs te bzhengs pa'i tshul du bsrung /
NK026(la)001:619: dpral bar dbu sprad ltag khung du zhabs sprad de thod khyer gyi tshul du bsrung /
NK026(la)001:620: spyi bor bzhengs pa'i tshul gyis bsrung bar bsam la
NK026(la)001:621: gnas de dag tu phyag rgya'i mdzub mo gnyis bsnol
NK026(la)001:623: brgyad pa skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK026(la)001:624: mdun gyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i steng gi char bla
NK026(la)001:625: ma yi dam sangs rgyas byang sems dpa' bo mkha'
NK026(la)001:626: 'gro chos skyong srung mar bcas pa mngon sum lta
NK026(la)001:627: bur bzhugs pa'i drung du sems can rnams dang lhan
NK026(la)001:628: cig par skyabs su 'gro ba 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod
NK026(la)001:630: rdo rje rnal 'byor mchog gi lha //
NK026(la)001:632: rdo rje can la phyag btsal te //
NK026(la)001:633: byams mgon khyod la skyabs su mchi //
NK026(la)001:635: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK026(la)001:636: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:637: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK026(la)001:638: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK026(la)001:639: dngos 'byor yid kyi rnam sprul pa'i //
NK026(la)001:640: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK026(la)001:641: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK026(la)001:642: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK026(la)001:643: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK026(la)001:644: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK026(la)001:645: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK026(la)001:646: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK026(la)001:647: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK026(la)001:648: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:649: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK026(la)001:650: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK026(la)001:652: rtsa bar gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK026(la)001:653: sems bskyed pa'i phyir 'di'i rjes zlos kyang byar bzhug ste /
NK026(la)001:654: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK026(la)001:655: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK026(la)001:656: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK026(la)001:657: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK026(la)001:663: mthar phyin byang sems rnams bskyed phyir /
NK026(la)001:665: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK026(la)001:666: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK026(la)001:667: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK026(la)001:668: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK026(la)001:669: e ma ho ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gag pa med las thams cad 'gag /
NK026(la)001:671: e ma ho ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK026(la)001:672: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK026(la)001:673: e ma ho ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK026(la)001:674: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK026(la)001:675: e ma ho ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs 'gro 'ong med las 'gro dang 'ong //
NK026(la)001:677: ces sogs kyang tshar gsum gyi bar du rjes zlos byar gzhug /
NK026(la)001:680: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyi //
NK026(la)001:681: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK026(la)001:682: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa'i //
NK026(la)001:683: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK026(la)001:684: zhes sogs kyis gnang ba sbyin /
NK026(la)001:685: dgu pa dam tshig sbyin pa zhu ba ni /
NK026(la)001:686: slob mas rjes zlos bya ste /
NK026(la)001:689: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK026(la)001:690: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:691: a la la ste dam tshigs skongs //
NK026(la)001:692: a la la ste dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:693: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK026(la)001:694: mchod cing ji ltar mdzad pa ltar //
NK026(la)001:695: bdag cag rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK026(la)001:696: nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK026(la)001:698: bla mas ka p+aa lar bdud rtsi la chos sman btab pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:699: bdud rtsi'i nang du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK026(la)001:700: kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yig 'bru gsum
NK026(la)001:703: badz+ra a mri ta ma ti s+thi ra man+da la /
NK026(la)001:705: rdo rjes bdud rtsi lce thog tu bzhag la /
NK026(la)001:706: dam tshig gi snod dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:707: bcu pa de nas dam tshig dbog pa ni /
NK026(la)001:708: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NK026(la)001:709: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:710: deng bdag sangs rgyas sku gsung thugs 'dzin pa //
NK026(la)001:711: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sbyin //
NK026(la)001:712: bla mas phyag g.yas kyis rdo rje dang bcas srin
NK026(la)001:713: lag gis bdud rtsi blangs la slob ma'i gnas gsum
NK026(la)001:714: du bzhag cing / +aahh+aum sa ma ya dzah zhes
NK026(la)001:715: brjod pas sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig thob par
NK026(la)001:716: bsam la dam tshig dbog cing bsgugs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:718: dam tshig sdom pa chen po ni //
NK026(la)001:719: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs //
NK026(la)001:720: da lta nga yi snying la gnas //
NK026(la)001:721: da ni mched lcam rnams kyi srog /
NK026(la)001:725: dam tshig chen po bdud rtsi lnga //
NK026(la)001:726: rang bzhin 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK026(la)001:727: gzi byin ldan par byin rlabs pas //
NK026(la)001:728: dam tshig sdom pa'i mchog ces bya //
NK026(la)001:730: slar yang rdo rje snying gar bzhag la /
NK026(la)001:732: snying gar rdo rje brtan byas la //
NK026(la)001:735: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK026(la)001:736: dam nyams ma 'dres gang la ni //
NK026(la)001:737: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK026(la)001:738: theg pa chen po ston byed pa //
NK026(la)001:739: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK026(la)001:740: sku gsung thugs la brtag gnas te //
NK026(la)001:741: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK026(la)001:742: ces brjod cing don bkrol lo //
NK026(la)001:743: bcu gcig pa mna' chu ni /
NK026(la)001:744: dung chos su tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu rdo rje gnod sbyin du bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:747: tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba la //
NK026(la)001:748: rdo rje 'dzin pas rab gnas bya //
NK026(la)001:751: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpar bskyed cing
NK026(la)001:752: ye shes pa 'jug par gsungs pa 'dir cho ga'i
NK026(la)001:753: dngos bstan las rdo rje gnod sbyin 'byung ba 'thad
NK026(la)001:754: cing / cho ga gsum gyis bskyed rigs par snang bas 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:755: dung phor gyi chu stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las rdo rje'i mche ba h+aum gis mtshan pa las /
NK026(la)001:756: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin ljang nag mche ba 'dzin par gyur /
NK026(la)001:757: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hohs bstim /
NK026(la)001:758: zhu ba las dam tshig rdo rje'i chur gyur pa slob ma rnams la sbyin te /
NK026(la)001:760: dam tshig ma bsrungs pa'i nyes dmigs brjod pa'i sgo nas dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK026(la)001:761: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK026(la)001:762: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK026(la)001:763: rdo rje khro bo chen por 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:764: rdo rje'i chu ni btung bar gyis //
NK026(la)001:765: badz+ra yak+sha h+aum gis lan gsum gyi bar du sbyin
NK026(la)001:766: pa ni sgo gsum gyi dam tshig bsrung ba'i don
NK026(la)001:768: lan gsum byin nas rab bsgrags pas //
NK026(la)001:770: bsrungs pa'i yon tan nam phan yon gyi sgo nas dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK026(la)001:772: de lta bas na bu khyod kyi //
NK026(la)001:773: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK026(la)001:774: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub 'byung //
NK026(la)001:775: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thung zhig /
NK026(la)001:776: badz+ra u ta ka thahs slar yang dam chu sbyin no //
NK026(la)001:777: slar yang de dag gi don bshad pa ni /
NK026(la)001:779: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu de bzhag pa lce la bzhag kyang /
NK026(la)001:780: babs pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas gal te dam tshig ma bsrungs na /
NK026(la)001:781: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba lcags
NK026(la)001:782: kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur nas snying khrag
NK026(la)001:783: zho bzhin 'jib pas tshe thung zhing nad mang ba
NK026(la)001:784: dang / tshe phyi mar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag par 'gyur ro //
NK026(la)001:785: dam tshig bsrungs na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas /
NK026(la)001:786: des rtag tu byin gyis brlab cing tshe 'dir yang
NK026(la)001:787: dge dgu dang smon brgyad du gyur nas nad bzhi
NK026(la)001:788: brgya rtsa bzhi gdon stong phrag brgyad cus mi tshugs
NK026(la)001:789: pa dang / phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang
NK026(la)001:790: chub thob nas sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i
NK026(la)001:791: mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'i ded
NK026(la)001:793: zhes gsungs pa ltar brjod la don bshad /
NK026(la)001:796: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i ye shes gang //
NK026(la)001:797: de ring dngos grub mchog tu gsungs //
NK026(la)001:798: dam tshig che bas chen po mchog /
NK026(la)001:799: bye brag med par khyod kyis spyod //
NK026(la)001:800: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK026(la)001:801: lhag par bsnyen pa mi bya ste //
NK026(la)001:802: mnyam nyid rin chen klong bzhugs nas //
NK026(la)001:803: ci la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK026(la)001:805: rgyal ba'i rigs su gyur pa'i bu khyod rnams //
NK026(la)001:806: rdo rje slob dpon snying ltar khur //
NK026(la)001:807: rdo rje mched la mig bzhin gyis //
NK026(la)001:808: yi dam lha ni snying ltar khur //
NK026(la)001:809: gsang ba'i dam tshig rang tshang ltar //
NK026(la)001:810: nam yang de bzhin sems par gyis //
NK026(la)001:811: sems can thams cad bu ltar bzung //
NK026(la)001:812: rgyal ba'i bka' las ma 'da' zhig /
NK026(la)001:814: don rgyas par bkrol te bshad do //
NK026(la)001:816: bcu gnyis pa mna' dgag pa ni /
NK026(la)001:817: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK026(la)001:818: dam tshig sdom pa chen po'i ni //
NK026(la)001:819: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams dang //
NK026(la)001:820: sgrub pa po dang rnal 'byor pa //
NK026(la)001:821: de dag nyams na khrag chen po //
NK026(la)001:822: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung //
NK026(la)001:823: zhes brjod la slob mas bro bor ba'i don du /
NK026(la)001:824: i dam na ra kan zhes rjes zlos bya'o //
NK026(la)001:825: bcu gsum pa rin po che'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK026(la)001:826: gsang sngags gzhan ltar na 'og tu 'thad kyang yig
NK026(la)001:827: rnying thams cad du skabs 'dir bshad pas gong du
NK026(la)001:828: sbyin pa'i me tog gi phreng ba de dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:829: gyi lha rnams la phung bas las 'brel gang yod
NK026(la)001:830: la phog par shog cig snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos
NK026(la)001:832: me tog la sogs rin chen phreng //
NK026(la)001:833: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK026(la)001:834: thugs rjes bzung bar dgongs nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:835: gang yin de la 'bab gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:836: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes dkyil 'khor phyogs su gtad
NK026(la)001:837: de ras bris kyi pad+ma 'dab brgyad bris pa'i steng
NK026(la)001:838: du dor la / dbus dang phyogs mtshams kyi rigs gang la phog brtag go //
NK026(la)001:840: 'dir me tog 'dor tshul g.yung ston chen po'i sgyu
NK026(la)001:841: 'phrul dbang byang du bla ma'i sku la gtor bar
NK026(la)001:842: bshad pa yang shin du 'thad cing /
NK026(la)001:843: 'dir nges gsal ma byung yang ras bris kyi pad
NK026(la)001:844: 'dab la 'dor ba 'di phyag len bde bas phyogs
NK026(la)001:845: mtshams dbus gar babs brtags te dbus su de bzhin
NK026(la)001:846: gshegs pa'i rigs / shar du rdo rje'i rigs /
NK026(la)001:850: mtshams rnams rigs chung du bsdus te /
NK026(la)001:851: slar yang me tog gi phreng ba slob ma'i mgor 'ching zhing /
NK026(la)001:852: dbus su babs pa rnams la bud+d+ha m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:854: de bzhin du shar du badz+ra m+aa le lhor rat+na
NK026(la)001:855: m+aa le nub tu pad+ma m+aa le byang du karma
NK026(la)001:856: m+aa le shar lho sogs mtshams bzhir sngags par bkab
NK026(la)001:857: med de / de yang las rim las /
NK026(la)001:858: dkyil 'khor yid la mngon byas la //
NK026(la)001:859: 'dod pa'am yang na gzhan yang rung //
NK026(la)001:860: dor te 'brel ba legs brtag bya //
NK026(la)001:863: bcu bzhi pa lha dbab ste /
NK026(la)001:864: lha gang la phog pa de dag gi phyag rgyas snying gi dkyil du bstim /
NK026(la)001:867: rang ming dam tshig h+aum dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:868: dam tshig phyag rgya lan gsum bstan //
NK026(la)001:869: lcags kyu ha his bkug byas nas //
NK026(la)001:870: nyes legs phrin las gsal byas la //
NK026(la)001:871: phyag rgyas bstim la brtan par bya //
NK026(la)001:873: me tog gang la phog pa'i lhar bskyed de bstim par gsungs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:874: g.yung ston chen pos gong gi dam chu'i gnas skabs
NK026(la)001:875: de nyid lhar blangas te ye shes pa 'jug pa
NK026(la)001:876: sogs 'chad tshul mang bas gzhung don dang mi 'gal
NK026(la)001:877: bar gsar du bsdebs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:878: sh+au nya t+aas stong pa'i ngang las /
NK026(la)001:879: slob ma rnams pad+ma dang zla ba'i steng du h+aum
NK026(la)001:880: las rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa yongs su gyur
NK026(la)001:881: pa las rdo rje sems dpa' mthing dkar dmar ba'i
NK026(la)001:882: zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo
NK026(la)001:883: rje dang dril bu bsnams te yum la 'khyud pa
NK026(la)001:884: / bar pa gnyis kyi 'khor lo dang pad+ma /
NK026(la)001:885: tha ma gnyis kyis rin po che dang ral gri /
NK026(la)001:886: yum dbyings phyug ma sngon mo rdor dril 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa'i spyi bor /
NK026(la)001:888: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros par 'og min nas dus
NK026(la)001:889: gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad bcom ldan 'das zhi
NK026(la)001:890: khro tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par
NK026(la)001:891: nam mkha'i khams gang bar spyan drangs te khyed rang
NK026(la)001:892: rnams la thim pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK026(la)001:893: ces brjod la las slob rnams kyis spos dang rol mo'i sgra chen po bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:894: bla mas rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgyar bcas te /
NK026(la)001:895: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes lan gsum bya zhing se gol gtogs pa'i mthar /
NK026(la)001:896: badz+ra sat+wa dz+ny+aa na sat+wa e h+ye hi b+ha ga
NK026(la)001:897: wan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh
NK026(la)001:899: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:900: de rjes las rim gyi dgongs pa /
NK026(la)001:901: phyag rgyas bstim la brtan par bya //
NK026(la)001:902: zhes gsungs pa'i don du spro na dbyangs dang rol mor bcas te /
NK026(la)001:903: slob dpon gyis so so'i phyag rgya bca' ba dang bstun te /
NK026(la)001:904: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK026(la)001:905: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK026(la)001:906: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod de //
NK026(la)001:907: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK026(la)001:908: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:910: badz+ra gan+de hoh pra be sha ya phata /
NK026(la)001:911: a be sha ya as snying gi dkyil du bstim mo //
NK026(la)001:913: nyes legs phrin las gsal byas la //
NK026(la)001:914: zhes gsungs pa'i don mig dar dang bcas te dkyil
NK026(la)001:915: 'khor la bltas pas kha dog ji ltar snang dri
NK026(la)001:916: zhing dkar ser dmar ljang gis las bzhi dang /
NK026(la)001:918: mthing khas mchog thob par 'gyur bar ngo sprad do //
NK026(la)001:919: de lta bu'i ye shes de dag mi nyams shing brtan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:920: spyi bor rdo rje rgya gram du bzhag la tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:922: bco lnga pa lha mi spang ba ni lha ma sgoms na /
NK026(la)001:925: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK026(la)001:926: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:929: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyar na //
NK026(la)001:931: lha yi sku nyid gsal bsgoms na //
NK026(la)001:933: de nyid chu zla'i tshul shes na //
NK026(la)001:934: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:936: bcu drug pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK026(la)001:937: bla mas mig thur thogs te /
NK026(la)001:938: rdo rje de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK026(la)001:940: sangs rgyas gsung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK026(la)001:941: sangs rgyas dngos grub thams cad ni //
NK026(la)001:942: brten nas thob par 'gyur ba yin //
NK026(la)001:943: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha phata /
NK026(la)001:944: ces mig ras bsal bas ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal nas /
NK026(la)001:945: ye nas rang la gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor mthong bar bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:948: 'khor lo mngon pa'i nga rgyal bya //
NK026(la)001:950: de yang mtshon byed dape'am lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi
NK026(la)001:951: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di nyid la rten dang brten
NK026(la)001:952: pa gnyis las / rten gzhal yas khang phyi nas bstan /
NK026(la)001:953: brten pa lha nang nas ston dgos pas /
NK026(la)001:955: phyi rol tu rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba d+r+wa
NK026(la)001:956: ba gur bla bre ye shes kyi me rab tu
NK026(la)001:957: 'bar ba dang bcas pa'i nang du dur khrod chen
NK026(la)001:958: po brgyad / de'i nang du sna tshogs pad+ma'i 'dab
NK026(la)001:959: ma yongs su brdal ba'i lte bar nyi ma'i dkyil
NK026(la)001:960: 'khor gyi gdan la sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK026(la)001:961: phyi rin po che sna tshogs las grub cing /
NK026(la)001:962: nang dur khrod rdzas kyi rang bzhin can gyi gzhal
NK026(la)001:963: yas khang rim pa bcu gcig gi nang ma'i lte
NK026(la)001:964: bar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad ser po /
NK026(la)001:965: glo 'bur gyi gru chad phyogs mdog /
NK026(la)001:975: bcu pa dang bcu gcig pa gnyis phyogs mdog /
NK026(la)001:976: de'i steng du reg la ma 'byar ba'i rnam pas
NK026(la)001:977: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po
NK026(la)001:978: me ri rdo rje sogs bsrung ba'i 'khor lo'i nang
NK026(la)001:979: du pad ra nyi dkyil dang sna tshogs rdo rje'i
NK026(la)001:980: lte ba la gnas pa'i gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid
NK026(la)001:981: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i lte bar 'khor lo
NK026(la)001:984: khyams phyogs mdog dang bcas pa rten gzhal yas khang yin la /
NK026(la)001:986: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lte bar gzhi'i kun bzang yab yum /
NK026(la)001:987: de'i mdun du mi bskyod rdor sems yab yum /
NK026(la)001:988: rtsibs bzhir shar du rnam snang /
NK026(la)001:991: byang du don grub yab yum rnams /
NK026(la)001:992: rtsibs mchan bzhi dang glo 'bur gyi gru chad bzhir sems dpa' yab yum brgyad /
NK026(la)001:993: khyams kyi shar nub tu bya ba dang byed po yab yum /
NK026(la)001:995: sgo bzhir sgo ba yab yum brgyad rnams zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK026(la)001:996: 'og gi khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bcom
NK026(la)001:997: ldan 'das che mchog he ru ka dbu nyer gcig
NK026(la)001:999: zhabs brgyad kyis khro mo gnam zhal ma'i dbu brgyad bardzisa shing /
NK026(la)001:1000: zhal dbus mar gsang rdor 'tshir ba /
NK026(la)001:1001: yab kyi phyag na zhi ba zhe gnyis dang /
NK026(la)001:1002: yum gyi phyag bco brgyad kyis gnas yul gyi khro mo phra men rnams 'dzin pa ste /
NK026(la)001:1003: bdud rtsi khro mkhar gyi rnam par bzhugs pa /
NK026(la)001:1004: de'i mdun du dbang mchog he ru ka dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa /
NK026(la)001:1005: de'i mdun du badz+ra he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK026(la)001:1006: de'i phyi rol gyi rtsibs bzhi la phyogs bzhir rgyud kyi khro bo bzhi dang /
NK026(la)001:1007: mtshams su lung gi khro bo bzhi yab yum /
NK026(la)001:1008: glo 'bur gyi phyogs mtshams su gnas kyi khro mo brgyad /
NK026(la)001:1009: khyams dang por yul gyi phra men brgyad /
NK026(la)001:1010: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa /
NK026(la)001:1011: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa dkar khyams la sbor ma brgyad /
NK026(la)001:1013: dkyil 'khor gsum pa dmar khyams la dbang mo nyer
NK026(la)001:1014: brgyad de 'di yan khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:1015: / dkyil 'khor bzhi pa ser khyams la mkha' 'gro sum cu so gnyis /
NK026(la)001:1016: dkyil 'khor lnga pa dmar khyams la ma bdun sring bzhi /
NK026(la)001:1017: dkyil 'khor drug pa dkar khyams la rdo rje ging
NK026(la)001:1018: chen bco brgyad de bzhi pa dang drug pa gnyis
NK026(la)001:1020: dkyil 'khor bdun pa nag khyams la khro bo khro
NK026(la)001:1021: mo drug cu ste khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:1022: / dkyil 'khor brgyad pa phyogs mdog la pho nya
NK026(la)001:1023: nyis brgya bzhi bcu ste mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil
NK026(la)001:1024: / 'khor / dkyil 'khor dgu pa ljang khyams la
NK026(la)001:1025: ma mo drug cu ste dam tshig chen po'i dkyil
NK026(la)001:1026: / 'khor / 'khor / dkyil 'khor bcu pa phyogs mdog la bka' brgyad theg dgu'i lha tshogs /
NK026(la)001:1027: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa phyogs mdog can gyi khyams
NK026(la)001:1028: la yo ga gsum gyi brgyud gsum rig 'dzin bla
NK026(la)001:1029: ma ste / 'di rnams kyang mngon sum lta bur mthong ba'i mos pa dang /
NK026(la)001:1030: 'di rnams kyang khyed rang rnams kyi lha skal yin
NK026(la)001:1031: pas mchod bstod sgom bzlas la nan tan du mdzod
NK026(la)001:1033: rgyas par spro na zhi khro gnyis ka'i mngon rtogs ltar ngo sprad do //
NK026(la)001:1034: de nas lha de rnams kyi brda don bshad pa ni /
NK026(la)001:1036: bcu bdun pa dkyil 'khor lha'i don rtags bshad pa ni /
NK026(la)001:1037: chos kyi dbyings spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i rtags su lte ba zlum po /
NK026(la)001:1038: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lnga /
NK026(la)001:1039: ye nas rgyu 'bras dbyer med pas rdo rje'i ra ba /
NK026(la)001:1040: tshad med bzhi dang ldan pas gru chad bzhi /
NK026(la)001:1041: lhag pa'i ye shes phrin las bzhi dang ldan pas glo 'bur bzhi /
NK026(la)001:1042: che ba'i yon tan phyogs med rgyas pas gru bzhir ldan pa /
NK026(la)001:1043: ting nge 'dzin bzhi dang ldan pas sgo bzhi /
NK026(la)001:1044: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pas dur khrod kyi thod pa skam rlon gnam lcags gzer gyis bsdams pa /
NK026(la)001:1045: 'khor ba ma spangs gnas su dag pas zhing lpags kha sbyar gyi sgo /
NK026(la)001:1046: skar ma'i sgo rten rus sbal gyi ma them /
NK026(la)001:1051: rgyu skar nyer brgyad kyi phyam /
NK026(la)001:1053: de dag ni nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i rtags so //
NK026(la)001:1054: ye shes lnga dang ldan pas rtsig pa lnga /
NK026(la)001:1056: rin chen gdung brgyad bsnol ma /
NK026(la)001:1057: rin chen sna tshogs kyi dral phyam mo //
NK026(la)001:1058: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bas zla phyed rdo
NK026(la)001:1059: rje'i gdung mgo gzhig par mi nus pas bcu gcig
NK026(la)001:1061: che ba'i yon tan yongs su ma 'gags pas mda' yab dkar po /
NK026(la)001:1062: chos rnams lhun gyis grub cing theg pa brgyad nas bgrod pas rta babs brgyad /
NK026(la)001:1063: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing mtshan rtog dang bral
NK026(la)001:1064: bas 'khor lo gdugs 'phan dar dpyangs dpag bsam gyi
NK026(la)001:1065: shing / thams cad la dbang sgyur ba me ri'i phreng ba'o //
NK026(la)001:1067: me tog phog pa la sogs pa /
NK026(la)001:1071: sku mdog gsang mtshan rnams bstan te nges par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:1072: zhes gsungs pa'i don ltar rgyas bshad bya /
NK026(la)001:1078: sku mdog gsang mtshan rnams bstan te zhes 'byung bas
NK026(la)001:1079: 'dir gsang mtshan 'dogs pa g.yung ston chen pos kyang
NK026(la)001:1080: bshad mod / 'on kyang 'og tu phan dbang bcu'i
NK026(la)001:1081: dgu par gsang ming 'byung phyir ming btags pa ni
NK026(la)001:1082: bshad mod / der 'thad la / lha'i snying po
NK026(la)001:1083: dang sku mdog sogs 'dir ston pa 'thad pas me
NK026(la)001:1084: tog gar babs kyi lha'i ngo sprad cing /
NK026(la)001:1085: snying po so so'i rjes zlos kyang byar gzhug ste /
NK026(la)001:1086: dper na rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la me tog phog na lha de'i mngon rtogs bsgrag cing /
NK026(la)001:1089: zhes pa lta bus mtshon te zhi khro'i skabs gang 'thad kyi lha dang /
NK026(la)001:1090: de dag gi snying po rnams kyang bsgrag go //
NK026(la)001:1091: des 'jug pa'i chos rnams grub nas /
NK026(la)001:1093: skabs 'dir gtad rgya dang dngos grub blang ba 'byung zhing /
NK026(la)001:1094: de yang glan ston bsod nams mgon pos de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags dang /
NK026(la)001:1095: lha ngo shes nas de dag gi khungs smos pas
NK026(la)001:1096: yid ches par bya ba'i phyir brgyud khungs kyi gtad
NK026(la)001:1097: rgya'am / zab mo dbang gi gleng gzhi gdams pa
NK026(la)001:1098: dang bcas pa bshad pa ni las 'di ru gzigs
NK026(la)001:1099: rgya'am / shig / de nas brgyud pa'i khungs ngo
NK026(la)001:1100: shes nas grub pa'i 'bras bu thob pa'i phyir dngos
NK026(la)001:1101: grub blang ba'i rim pa zhes dang /
NK026(la)001:1102: de dag legs par tshar nas dkyil 'khor lha'i dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK026(la)001:1104: 'on kyang dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK026(la)001:1106: dngos grub blang ba'i cho ga dang lag len rnams
NK026(la)001:1107: 'di dag 'og ma gnyis 'dam kha yin pas nam
NK026(la)001:1108: zla'i dus tshod brtsi ba gal che ba yin no
NK026(la)001:1109: // zhes gsungs pas mdor na gtad rgya dang dngos
NK026(la)001:1110: grub gnyis 'dir byas kyang rgyu mtshan de dag gi
NK026(la)001:1112: deng sang bla ma'i phyag bzhes su mjug tu mdzad
NK026(la)001:1113: pa ltar rnam pa gcig tu 'thad par snang bas
NK026(la)001:1114: / 'dir dbang dngos la 'jug par bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:1116: de nas dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK026(la)001:1118: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK026(la)001:1119: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:1120: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni //
NK026(la)001:1121: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:1122: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK026(la)001:1123: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:1124: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga ni //
NK026(la)001:1125: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:1127: yo ga la sogs pa drug gi dbang tshar nas /
NK026(la)001:1128: da gsang sngags nang gi dbang bskur ba la /
NK026(la)001:1129: cho ga sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK026(la)001:1131: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba yi //
NK026(la)001:1132: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK026(la)001:1133: rnam pa gnyis kyi khyad par gyis //
NK026(la)001:1134: dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:1139: zab mo'i dbang gnyis su bstan pa la /
NK026(la)001:1140: phyi dbang nang dbang ma h+aa /
NK026(la)001:1141: sgrub dbang gsang dbang a nu gtso che yang /
NK026(la)001:1142: thun mong du dbang gang rung bskur ba la /
NK026(la)001:1143: dpon slob rnams gos bzang po dang /
NK026(la)001:1144: rgyan dang thor tshugs dbu rgyan la sogs pa brjid bag dang ldan pas khri la 'dug ste /
NK026(la)001:1145: kha g.yu kha gser la sogs pa thogs pa rgyal po ltar dbang bskur ba'o //
NK026(la)001:1146: yang thams cad khrus dang gtsang sbra byas te gos gtsang ma gyon /
NK026(la)001:1147: dpral mgrin snying khar dri bzang pos thig le dang bcas pa ni bram ze ltar dbang bskur ba'o //
NK026(la)001:1148: yang na thams cad ye shes lha'i ngang las gtsang
NK026(la)001:1149: rme'i rtog pa dang nyam nga bag tsha med par
NK026(la)001:1150: brtul zhugs chen po'i ngar dang ldan pa ni gdol
NK026(la)001:1151: ba ltar dbang bskur ba ste /
NK026(la)001:1152: de dag kyang ldog pa tha dad du snang yang ngo bo gcig pas /
NK026(la)001:1153: dbang stegs la yi dam che mchog gi nga rgyal gyis 'dug par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:1154: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni dbang stegs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:1155: pad+ma 'dab brgyad sgo rgyan rdzogs par bris pa'i steng
NK026(la)001:1156: du bla bres / g.yas su gdugs dkar po gser gyi yu ba can /
NK026(la)001:1158: mtha' skor du bkra shis pa'i rdzas dang rtags kyi
NK026(la)001:1159: khyad par brgyad sogs mchod pa'i yo byad kyis bskor
NK026(la)001:1160: ba dngos sam bsgoms pas kyang rung ste /
NK026(la)001:1161: de lta bu'i dbang stegs la slob ma rnams che
NK026(la)001:1162: mchog dbu nyer gcig phyag zhe gnyis zhabs brgyad pa
NK026(la)001:1165: rgyu'i he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i nga rgyal gyis kyang rung ste bskyed rim phog go //
NK026(la)001:1166: bla ma yang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo che mchog gi nga rgyal gsal btab ste /
NK026(la)001:1168: de nas bla mas spyi bo nas /
NK026(la)001:1169: rta'i 'dur glu phyogs bcur 'tsher zhing bsgrags pas /
NK026(la)001:1170: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar byon /
NK026(la)001:1171: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum la thim pas dbang bskur ba'i nus pa dang ldan par byas /
NK026(la)001:1172: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyang byon /
NK026(la)001:1173: rta'i rna ba dang phum phum gyi rnam pa'i 'od kyi phung por sgom /
NK026(la)001:1174: de'i 'od zer gyis slob ma rnams kyi bag chags
NK026(la)001:1175: dang snod ngan pa'i dri ma thams cad dag par
NK026(la)001:1176: bsam / de nas sems can 'di dag 'khor ba
NK026(la)001:1177: las bsgral te bla na med pa'i byang chub la
NK026(la)001:1178: 'god snyam pa'i byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems
NK026(la)001:1180: de nas slob ma rnams la thugs ma yengs par gsan mdzod /
NK026(la)001:1181: de yang dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin
NK026(la)001:1182: po che dbang gi rgyal po de dgos 'dod thams
NK026(la)001:1184: rang gi ci ltar gsol ba btab pa bzhin du 'dod pa'i don 'grub pa ltar /
NK026(la)001:1185: bla ma 'di yang dgos 'dod thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pas /
NK026(la)001:1186: mchog thun mong gi gsol ba gang btab 'grub pas /
NK026(la)001:1187: bla ma sangs rgyas su bsgom la mos gus gdung sems gyis la gsol ba thob bya /
NK026(la)001:1188: slob mas thal mo sbyar la /
NK026(la)001:1189: 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum bya ste /
NK026(la)001:1190: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK026(la)001:1191: sa mtha'i sems dpa' chen po yis //
NK026(la)001:1192: ji ltar mchod cing zhus pa ltar //
NK026(la)001:1193: de bzhin skal ldan bdag cag la //
NK026(la)001:1194: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po yis //
NK026(la)001:1195: dbang rnams rim par stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:1198: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:1199: gsang ba rdo rje rnam gsum las //
NK026(la)001:1200: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK026(la)001:1201: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK026(la)001:1203: de nas bla mas bzhengs te dkyil 'khor phyogs su btud cing /
NK026(la)001:1206: slob bu rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1207: sems can don la bdag brtson na //
NK026(la)001:1208: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:1209: badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum dzah zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK026(la)001:1210: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad mdun
NK026(la)001:1211: gyi nam mkhar sprin 'thibs pa bzhin byon nas dbang
NK026(la)001:1212: bskur zhig par bka' stsal bar bsam la /
NK026(la)001:1213: skabs 'dir glan ston gyi dgongs pa ltar du /
NK026(la)001:1214: bla mas ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs ye shes lnga'i sngags dang bcas te /
NK026(la)001:1215: dbu rgyan sogs dbang chas gyon te 'khor los sgyur
NK026(la)001:1216: ba'i cha lugs kyis dbang khrir bzang po'i 'dug stangs
NK026(la)001:1217: kyis 'dug la / na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:1218: de bzhin du w+aa ka badz+ra /
NK026(la)001:1219: tsit+ta badz+ra sogs brjod pas bdag nyid sku gsung thugs
NK026(la)001:1220: yon tan phrin las kyi gzi byin dang ldan par
NK026(la)001:1221: bsam la / bskur byed nam mkha' lha rnams la gsol ba 'debs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:1224: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
NK026(la)001:1226: dang ba'i yid kyis zhugs nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:1227: byin rlabs dbang mchog nod par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:1229: dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs par bskur te /
NK026(la)001:1230: thor mar phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu la /
NK026(la)001:1231: dang po zhi ba'i lha'i phyag rgya'i dbang /
NK026(la)001:1235: lnga pa bkra shis rdzas brgyad /
NK026(la)001:1236: drug pa rin chen sna bdun /
NK026(la)001:1241: de la dang po zhi ba'i phyag rgya'i dbang sngar yo gar song la /
NK026(la)001:1243: zhes gsungs pa gong du song bas mi dgos /
NK026(la)001:1244: de'i dod du 'dir rigs lnga'i sku lngas dbang bskur zhing /
NK026(la)001:1246: rgyal po phyag rgya mchog gi rgya //
NK026(la)001:1247: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'da' ba //
NK026(la)001:1248: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1249: dam tshig phyag rgyar rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:1251: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK026(la)001:1252: cad kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis skal ldan khyed rnams
NK026(la)001:1253: la phyag rgya lnga'i dbang bskur bas rigs lnga ye
NK026(la)001:1254: shes lnga'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1255: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aaha b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1256: gnyis pa phyag mtshan gyi dbang rdzas rdo rje sogs rim pa bzhin thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1258: me long lta bu'i ye shes nyid //
NK026(la)001:1259: 'joms byed rdo rje rang snang bas //
NK026(la)001:1260: rdo rje sems dpa' dam tshig che //
NK026(la)001:1261: mi phyed rdo rje'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1263: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK026(la)001:1265: skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyed la rdo rje'i rigs
NK026(la)001:1266: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag mtshan rdo rjes dbang bskur
NK026(la)001:1267: bas me long lta bu'i ye shes rdo rje sems
NK026(la)001:1268: dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dbang thob par gyur cig
NK026(la)001:1269: / ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:1272: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK026(la)001:1273: 'khor lo chen po rang snang bas //
NK026(la)001:1274: rnam par snang mdzad bdag nyid che //
NK026(la)001:1275: chos kyi 'khor los khyod dbang bskur //
NK026(la)001:1277: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod la de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK026(la)001:1278: rigs rnam par snang mdzad kyi phyag mtshan 'khor los
NK026(la)001:1279: dbang bskur bas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes rnam
NK026(la)001:1280: par snang mdzad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam
NK026(la)001:1281: pa ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi
NK026(la)001:1283: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes nyid //
NK026(la)001:1284: yid bzhin nor bur rang snang bas //
NK026(la)001:1285: rin chen 'byung ldan bdag nyid de //
NK026(la)001:1288: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod la rin po che'i rigs
NK026(la)001:1289: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi phyag mtshan rin po che'i
NK026(la)001:1290: dbang bskur bas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rin
NK026(la)001:1291: chen 'byung ldan gyi sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam
NK026(la)001:1292: pa ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi
NK026(la)001:1293: pad+ma thogs te / so sor rtog pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK026(la)001:1294: bag chags med par rang snang bas //
NK026(la)001:1295: snang ba mtha' yas bdag nyid de //
NK026(la)001:1296: spyod bzhin ma chags dbang thob shog na mo /
NK026(la)001:1297: phyogs bcu dus gsum skal ldan khyod la pad+ma'i rigs
NK026(la)001:1298: snang ba mtha' yas kyi phyag mtshan pad+ma'i dbang bskur
NK026(la)001:1299: bas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes snang ba mtha'
NK026(la)001:1300: yas kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam pa ma
NK026(la)001:1301: h+aa pra t+y+aa be k+sha na dz+ny+aa na a b+hi
NK026(la)001:1303: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK026(la)001:1304: ral gri'i dngos por rang snang bas //
NK026(la)001:1305: don yod pa yi ngo bo ste //
NK026(la)001:1306: sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1308: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod la las kyi rigs don
NK026(la)001:1309: yod grub pa'i phyag mtshan ral gris dbang bskur bas
NK026(la)001:1310: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes don yod grub pa'i
NK026(la)001:1311: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam pa ma h+aa kri
NK026(la)001:1312: t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na a b+hi gsum pa rig
NK026(la)001:1313: ma thogs te / shes rab gzungs kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK026(la)001:1314: rtog dang ldan par gyur pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1315: mtha' gnyis don du mi gtong ba'i //
NK026(la)001:1316: rgyal yum shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK026(la)001:1317: gzungs kyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:1318: don dam rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK026(la)001:1319: dri med rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:1320: cis kyang gos med rig ma'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1321: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:1322: gnyis med yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK026(la)001:1323: thams cad bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1324: byang chub sems dang don du 'brel //
NK026(la)001:1325: shes rab chen po rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK026(la)001:1326: ma h+aa mu dre a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1327: bzhi pa bum pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1329: skabs 'dir zhi ba'i dbang bum rnams yin te /
NK026(la)001:1330: thog mar rdo rje slob dpon gyis dbus kyi bum pa blangs te bskur zhing /
NK026(la)001:1331: rgyal thebs sogs kyi rol mo'i sgra dang spos dud chen po sbyar ro //
NK026(la)001:1332: sgom don ni bum pa'i nang na bzhugs pa'i lha
NK026(la)001:1333: tshogs de rnams kyi sbyor mtshams nas byang sems bdud
NK026(la)001:1334: rtsi'i chu rgyun byung ba des khyed rang rnams kyi
NK026(la)001:1335: lus kyi nang thams cad gang bas /
NK026(la)001:1336: sngon chad phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga dang
NK026(la)001:1337: nyon mongs pa lnga rang kha ma'i sgrib pa ma
NK026(la)001:1338: spangs gnas su dag ste bum pa'i dbang bskur ba
NK026(la)001:1339: thob pa'i yon tan gyis ye shes rnam pa lnga'i
NK026(la)001:1340: chu rgyun la longs spyod pa'i nus pa dngos su
NK026(la)001:1344: bkra shis chen po'i bum dbang 'di //
NK026(la)001:1345: bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i pho brang ste //
NK026(la)001:1346: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par gyur pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1347: dbang mchog de yang sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1349: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod la bum pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1350: dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa badz+ra k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1351: de bzhin du shar gyi bum pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1353: sngags bud+d+ha k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK026(la)001:1355: lho'i bum pa la yang tshig gong ma dang /
NK026(la)001:1356: sngags rat+na k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK026(la)001:1357: nub kyi bum par yang bskur tshig gong ma dang /
NK026(la)001:1358: sngags pad+ma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih byang gi bum par yang bskur tshig gong ma dang /
NK026(la)001:1359: sngags karma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK026(la)001:1360: phyogs bcu skal ldan rigs kyi bu la bum pa'i
NK026(la)001:1361: dbang bskur bas nang gi sgrib pa ma lus pa
NK026(la)001:1362: dag nas dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig
NK026(la)001:1363: / lnga ka'i bum chu yang blud do //
NK026(la)001:1364: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK026(la)001:1365: bum pa zlum po chos kyi gter //
NK026(la)001:1366: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //
NK026(la)001:1367: 'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:1371: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK026(la)001:1372: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1373: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog kyang //
NK026(la)001:1374: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1375: ting 'dzin d+aurbasa bsod nams kun tu 'phel //
NK026(la)001:1376: ji ltar drang srong chen po a ta kas //
NK026(la)001:1377: byin gyis brlabs pa'i r+ts+wa mchog d+aurba 'dis //
NK026(la)001:1378: reg pas nad rnams thams cad bsal gyur nas //
NK026(la)001:1379: nad kyis gdungs pa kun las thar bar shog /
NK026(la)001:1380: d+aurbasa dge ba'i rtsa ba 'gag med pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1381: dbang thob nas ni kun tu bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:1382: d+aurbasa tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK026(la)001:1383: rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe ni rab grub nas //
NK026(la)001:1384: nyon mongs skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK026(la)001:1385: bkra shis des kyang tshe ni brtan gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1387: yang dag las mtha' chags shing ral gri 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:1388: rdo rje dang ni rin chen chu skyes dang //
NK026(la)001:1389: de bzhin las kyi rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1390: kha dog bzang po mdog mdzes li khri 'dis //
NK026(la)001:1391: lha mi'i 'dod yon dbang du 'dus par shog /
NK026(la)001:1392: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK026(la)001:1393: chos rnas ma lus dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK026(la)001:1394: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:1395: li khris bkra shis mchog tu brtan gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1397: yang dag lta bas bden gnyis me long ston //
NK026(la)001:1398: de grub de thob de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK026(la)001:1399: chos rnams thams cad sgyu ma lta bu de //
NK026(la)001:1400: rang bzhin dag pas sgyu ma slar shes nas //
NK026(la)001:1401: gti mug mun pa'i bag chags bsregs sbyangs te //
NK026(la)001:1402: me long lta bu'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1403: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK026(la)001:1404: ye shes rgyal po'i bdud rtsi mchog gyur nas //
NK026(la)001:1405: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1406: bkra shis des kyang sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1408: yang dag ngag gi sgra skad tshangs pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1409: ji ltar m+aa ra ya nar lha chen gyis //
NK026(la)001:1410: dung sgra bsgrags nas rims nad bsal ba ltar //
NK026(la)001:1411: dam chos bdud rtsi dung gi sgra bsgrags pas //
NK026(la)001:1412: nad kyis gdungs pa kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK026(la)001:1413: dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrog pa'i tshul //
NK026(la)001:1414: yon tan rgya mtsho mchog tu dag gyur nas //
NK026(la)001:1415: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1416: bkra shis des ni tshe la longs spyod shog /
NK026(la)001:1418: shes bcu srog gi dbang po thob nas ni //
NK026(la)001:1419: yang dag dran pas g+hi wang nad gso mdzad //
NK026(la)001:1420: ji ltar g+hi wang khyu mchog glang po yi //
NK026(la)001:1421: srog gi dbang po gnyen du gyur nas ni //
NK026(la)001:1422: rnam par dkar ba'i dam chos 'dzin pa ltar //
NK026(la)001:1423: shes bcu srog gi dbang po thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1424: g+hi wang dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK026(la)001:1425: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur te //
NK026(la)001:1426: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1427: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK026(la)001:1429: yang dag don dam rtogs pa bilba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1430: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK026(la)001:1431: ji ltar rgyu dang sa bon nyung ngu las //
NK026(la)001:1432: 'bras bu cher smin shing mchog bilba ltar //
NK026(la)001:1433: de bzhin dge ba'i rgyu mchog chung ngu las //
NK026(la)001:1434: 'bras bu rgya che dpag med thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1435: bilba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK026(la)001:1436: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK026(la)001:1437: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1438: bkra shis des ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK026(la)001:1440: yang dag 'tsho ba rnams ni 'dod zho yi //
NK026(la)001:1441: lha dbang brgya byin bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK026(la)001:1442: byin gyis brlabs shing grub pa'i rdzas mchog gis //
NK026(la)001:1443: nad rnams ma lus 'joms pa'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK026(la)001:1444: rnam par rgyal ba'i ro mchog chen po 'dis //
NK026(la)001:1445: bsam gtan ting 'dzin bcud zas ldan par shog /
NK026(la)001:1446: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK026(la)001:1447: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK026(la)001:1448: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1449: bkra shis des kyang nad rnams sel bar shog /
NK026(la)001:1451: yang dag rtsol bas yungs kar bdud bzhi 'dzoms //
NK026(la)001:1452: bde bar gshegs pas byin gyis brlabs pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1453: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i sgrub rdzas rgyal po 'dis //
NK026(la)001:1454: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs kyi tshogs bcom nas //
NK026(la)001:1455: deng 'dis bkra shis mchog nyid thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1456: yungs kar rdo rje'i rigs te bgegs rnams 'joms //
NK026(la)001:1457: yon tan mthu stobs chen por gyur pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1458: bdud bzhi bar du gcod pa kun bcom nas //
NK026(la)001:1459: mi mthun phyogs las rab tu rgyal bar shog /
NK026(la)001:1462: dam chos rnam par 'byed pa'i 'khor lo ste //
NK026(la)001:1463: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK026(la)001:1464: 'khor lo rin chen brtan pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1465: sa bcu dag la dbang sgyur zhing //
NK026(la)001:1466: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs pa dang //
NK026(la)001:1467: chos kyi rgyal po chen por shog /
NK026(la)001:1468: 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas theg pa rnam gsum rtogs
NK026(la)001:1469: nas sa bcu la dbang sgyur ba'i chos kyi rgyal
NK026(la)001:1470: po'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1472: ting 'dzin mi 'gyur stobs kyi glang po che //
NK026(la)001:1473: de thob de grub glang po rin chen sa bcu dag la dbang sgyur zhing //
NK026(la)001:1474: theg pa rnam gsum byang chub snying por gnas par shog /
NK026(la)001:1475: glang po che yi dbang bskur bas theg pa rnam
NK026(la)001:1476: gsum rtogs nas stobs bcu la dbang sgyur ba'i dbang
NK026(la)001:1477: dam pa rta mchog thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1478: rdzu 'phrul myur mgyogs shugs 'chang rdzu 'phrul rta //
NK026(la)001:1479: de thob de grub rta mchog rin chen rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i dbang thob nas //
NK026(la)001:1480: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sgrol ba dang //
NK026(la)001:1481: thar pa'i 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1482: rta mchog gi dbang bskur bas rdzu 'phrul rkang pa
NK026(la)001:1483: bzhis 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad thar bar sgrol
NK026(la)001:1484: ba'i dbang dam pa dmag dpon thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1485: dran pa rang gi phyogs 'dzin gzhan 'joms dmag /
NK026(la)001:1486: de thob de grub dmag mi rin chen mi 'jigs bzhi yi dbang thob nas //
NK026(la)001:1487: phas kyi rgol ba tshar bcad de //
NK026(la)001:1488: go cha chen po bgos par shog /
NK026(la)001:1489: dmag mi'i dbang bskur bas mi 'jigs pa bzhis rgol
NK026(la)001:1490: ba thams cad tshar bcad nas go cha chen po'i
NK026(la)001:1491: dbang dam pa btsun mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1492: lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa btsun mo ste //
NK026(la)001:1493: de thob de grub btsun mo rin chen shes rab dbyings kyi mchog thob nas //
NK026(la)001:1494: skye 'gag med pa'i don rtogs te //
NK026(la)001:1495: byang chub snying por gnas par shog /
NK026(la)001:1496: btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas shes rab dbyings kyi skye
NK026(la)001:1497: 'gag med pa'i don rtogs shing dbang dam pa blon
NK026(la)001:1498: po thogs te / gdul dka' 'dul mkhas khyim bdag dga' ba yin //
NK026(la)001:1499: de thob de grub blon po rin chen sum cu rtsa gsum dbang phyug rje //
NK026(la)001:1500: rdzu 'phrul chen po brgya byin ltar //
NK026(la)001:1501: lha yi rgyal po chen por shog /
NK026(la)001:1502: blon po'i dbang bskur bas rdzu 'phrul chen po lha'i rgyal po'i dbang dam pa nor bu thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1503: btang snyoms yang dag don mdzad rin chen yin //
NK026(la)001:1504: de thob de grub 'jig rten dbang phyug de bzhin gshegs //
NK026(la)001:1505: dpe byad mtshan gyis brgyan pa dang //
NK026(la)001:1506: gser gyi kha dog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1507: nor bu rin po che'i dbang bskur bas mtshan dpe
NK026(la)001:1508: dang ldan zhing gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i sku
NK026(la)001:1510: dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan rin po che //
NK026(la)001:1511: 'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i snying po 'byung //
NK026(la)001:1512: dgos pa mchog sbyin nor bdun phun sum tshogs //
NK026(la)001:1513: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen spyod par shog /
NK026(la)001:1515: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyed rnams la rgyal srid sna
NK026(la)001:1516: bdun gyi dbang bskur bas 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyis
NK026(la)001:1518: mi gnas pa'i ye shes la spyod pa'i dbang dam pa bdun pa gdan khri ni /
NK026(la)001:1520: rang rig rtogs pa'i ye shes ni //
NK026(la)001:1521: cis kyang mi gos thams cad 'joms //
NK026(la)001:1522: seng ge'i gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1523: mi 'jigs bzhi yi dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1524: sems nyid rtogs pa'i rig pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1525: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK026(la)001:1526: glang chen theg pa'i dbang sangs rgyas stobs bcu'i dbang thams cad sems su rtogs gyur nas //
NK026(la)001:1527: gar ma bgrod pa kun tu phyin //
NK026(la)001:1528: myur mgyogs rta yi dbang rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i dbang nyon mongs sems su gang shes pa //
NK026(la)001:1529: spyod bzhin mi gos dbang du byed //
NK026(la)001:1530: mdzes byed rma bya'i dbang rgyal ba'i dbang bcu thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1531: shes bya rang du gang rtogs pa //
NK026(la)001:1532: bltas pa med par thams cad gsal //
NK026(la)001:1533: mkha' lding shang shang dbang shes bya thogs med dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1534: sems can chen po lnga'i gdan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK026(la)001:1535: yon tan lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa
NK026(la)001:1537: rin po che khri thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1538: sems nyid dgos 'dod lhun grub pas //
NK026(la)001:1539: rtog pas ma btsal rang la snang //
NK026(la)001:1540: rin chen khri yi dbang yon tan brtan pa'i dbang rin chen pad+ma seng ge'i khri //
NK026(la)001:1541: bla mar gyur pa'i gdan mchog ste //
NK026(la)001:1542: khyad par chen por gyur pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1543: khri chen dag la bzhugs par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:1544: rin po che'i khri'i dbang bskur bas 'gro ba lha dang bcas pa'i bla mar gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1547: dar gyi cod pan phreng la sogs //
NK026(la)001:1548: dbang mchog brjid pa'i rgyan gyis bklubs //
NK026(la)001:1549: mgul rgyan do shal se mo do //
NK026(la)001:1550: dpung rgyan lag gdub rkang gdub rnams //
NK026(la)001:1551: dbang mchog rgyal po de la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:1552: chos nyid cir yang snang ba'i longs spyod rgyan //
NK026(la)001:1553: rigs lnga'i rin chen dbu rgyan 'di bcings pas //
NK026(la)001:1554: ye shes lnga dag rigs lnga dbyer med pa //
NK026(la)001:1555: rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1556: zhe sdang chen po rang gi sems //
