NK026(la)001:1558: byang chub phyogs rnams rtogs pa'i rgyan //
NK026(la)001:1559: mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1560: 'bras bu'i chos la dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1561: sarba ta th+aa ga ta gu h+ya bud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma sat+wa swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:1563: skabs 'dir gsang mtshan 'dogs dgos pas gong du me tog phog pa'i rigs nges par byas te /
NK026(la)001:1565: dbus su bab pa pho rnams la rdo rje snying po rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1568: mo rnams la rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsal lta bu /
NK026(la)001:1569: de bzhin du shar ba rnams la rdo rje sku mchog rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1572: rdo rje bee ro tsa na rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1573: mo rnams la de bzhin dbyings phyug rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1574: lho ba rnams la rdo rje yon tan rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1577: rdo rje rin chen snying po rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1578: mo rnams la rin chen dbyings phyug rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1579: nub pa rnams la rdo rje gsung mchog rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1582: rdo rje ma chags pad+ma rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1584: mo rnams la pad+ma dbyings phyug rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1585: byang pa rnams la rdo rje las rab rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1589: mo rnams la las kyi dbyings phyug rtsal /
NK026(la)001:1590: zhes sogs kyi mtshon par gtags shing /
NK026(la)001:1593: dbang thob mdzes pa brjid pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK026(la)001:1594: dbang phyug yin pas de la kun phyag 'tshal //
NK026(la)001:1595: rdo rje dbang phyug ces pa'i mtshan nas ni //
NK026(la)001:1596: kun gyi sgra chen 'bod cing bsgrags par bya //
NK026(la)001:1597: ston pa'i thugs rjes nges par ming btags pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1598: thugs rje'i ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK026(la)001:1600: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyed rnams la rdo rje ming
NK026(la)001:1601: gi dbang bskur bas rgyal ba'i zhing khams thams cad
NK026(la)001:1602: du dbang phyug grags pa'i snyan pas khyab par gyur
NK026(la)001:1605: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong ldan pa zhig /
NK026(la)001:1606: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la sbyin byas pas //
NK026(la)001:1607: 'jig rten kun la kha lo sgyur ba yi //
NK026(la)001:1608: dbang mchog rgyal po 'di ni thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1609: yongs la dbang sgyur dbang gi mchog /
NK026(la)001:1610: gang la'ang ma chags 'dod dgur sgyur //
NK026(la)001:1611: gnyis su med pa'i pho brang du //
NK026(la)001:1612: spong len med par dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:1614: brjid pa'i don du 'bru bkod nas //
NK026(la)001:1615: gzhan don 'di la phan pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:1616: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar mdzod //
NK026(la)001:1618: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyed rnams la 'khor lo'i dbang
NK026(la)001:1619: bskur bas 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal thabs kyis 'jig
NK026(la)001:1620: rten gyi kha lo gyen du bsgyur ba'i dbang dam
NK026(la)001:1622: badz+ra tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1624: de yan chad kyis phyi dbang bcu tshar ba'o //
NK026(la)001:1625: de nas nang dbang bcu gcig la /
NK026(la)001:1626: dang po gsang ba nyan pa'i dbang /
NK026(la)001:1629: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal po /
NK026(la)001:1631: drug pa khyad par gyi rin chen bdun /
NK026(la)001:1632: bdun pa phyag rgya gzugs brnyan /
NK026(la)001:1635: bcu pa bkra shis rtags kyi /
NK026(la)001:1636: bcu gcig pa thig le ming gi dbang ngo //
NK026(la)001:1638: 'dir sgyu 'phrul sogs la spyir bsam rgyud dang /
NK026(la)001:1639: bsgrag tshig gnyis bye brag tu phye nas so sor ngo bo /
NK026(la)001:1649: yon tan sogs bcu gsum gyis ston par byed cing /
NK026(la)001:1650: de lta bu'i bsam rgyud bsgom bya la yang nyan
NK026(la)001:1651: dbang gi bskur gnas rna ba yin pas rna ba
NK026(la)001:1652: gnyis kyi 'doms rtsar gzhal yas khang gi dbus su
NK026(la)001:1653: rdor rin 'byung yab yum bco brgyad sgom dgos te
NK026(la)001:1661: zhu ba las slob ma rin 'byung du bskyed tshul gsungs pa rgyas par spro na sbyar dgos te /
NK026(la)001:1662: gsang snying gi le'u bcu par /
NK026(la)001:1663: nyan byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK026(la)001:1664: gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK026(la)001:1665: tram gi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK026(la)001:1666: rin chen dkyil 'khor gsal spro bstim //
NK026(la)001:1668: 'on kyang 'dir rtsa ba zur lugs dang khams lugs
NK026(la)001:1669: gnyis kar slob ma rin 'byung du bskyed pa tsam
NK026(la)001:1670: las ma gsungs pa de'i don 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:1671: dang po nyan pa'i dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:1672: slob ma rnams skad cig gis rin chen 'byung ldan
NK026(la)001:1673: ser po rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pa
NK026(la)001:1674: yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur pa de la bla
NK026(la)001:1675: mas glegs bam gtad de dbang bskur bas theg pa
NK026(la)001:1676: gsum gyi dam pa'i chos ma lus pa nyan pa'i
NK026(la)001:1679: mdo dgongs 'dus lta bu'i glegs bam gtad de /
NK026(la)001:1682: gsang ba'i sgo ru 'di zhugs nas //
NK026(la)001:1683: glegs bam lag tu gtad pas ni //
NK026(la)001:1684: dam chos mdzod chen theg pa gsum //
NK026(la)001:1685: ma lus nyan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1686: gsang ba gsang chen gsang ba rnams //
NK026(la)001:1687: ston pas nges par gsungs pa'i don //
NK026(la)001:1688: nyan cing yid la 'dzin pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1691: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod rnams la chos nyan pa'i
NK026(la)001:1692: dbang bskur bas gsang ba'i bka' mtha' dag nyan pa'i
NK026(la)001:1693: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:1694: sarba ta th+aa ga ta gar+b+ha sarba d+harma sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1695: de nas gnyis pa phrin las kyi dbang gi phyir
NK026(la)001:1696: slob ma rin chen 'byung ldan gnas 'gyur te don
NK026(la)001:1697: grub ljang gu rgya gram dang dril bu 'dzin pa
NK026(la)001:1698: yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur pa la sna tshogs
NK026(la)001:1699: rdo rje gtad pas phrin las bzhir dbang sgyur ba'i
NK026(la)001:1702: sna tshogs rdo rje thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1703: zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po yi //
NK026(la)001:1704: rigs su gyur pa ma lus pa //
NK026(la)001:1705: dgos pa thams cad byed par 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:1706: las rnams rgya mtsho thams cad kun //
NK026(la)001:1707: grub rtags rdo rje rgya gram rdzas //
NK026(la)001:1708: thabs mchog dbang ni sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1709: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod dag /
NK026(la)001:1710: mnan bskrad rmongs gso 'gugs pa dang //
NK026(la)001:1711: gang byed las rnams grub par shog /
NK026(la)001:1713: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod rnams la bya ba phrin
NK026(la)001:1714: las kyi dbang bskur bas 'gro don thogs pa med
NK026(la)001:1715: pa'i dbang dam pa gsum pa 'chad pa'i dbang ni
NK026(la)001:1717: slob ma'i lce la snang ba mtha' yas bskyed ces
NK026(la)001:1718: gsungs pa'i don slob ma don grub gnas 'gyur te
NK026(la)001:1719: snang ba mtha' yas dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu
NK026(la)001:1720: 'dzin pa yum dang bcas par gyur pa la 'khor
NK026(la)001:1721: lo gtad pas dam pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK026(la)001:1722: zhing 'chad pa'i dbang thob par mos mdzod /
NK026(la)001:1725: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong mu khyud ldan //
NK026(la)001:1726: 'jig rten kun la kha lo sgyur ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1727: dbang sgyur 'khor lo'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1728: gzhan gyi re ba skong ba'i bu mchog 'di //
NK026(la)001:1729: rgyal po rgyal rigs rmad du byung ba bzhin //
NK026(la)001:1730: rgya tshab chos kyi sras su byung bas na //
NK026(la)001:1731: gsung rab dam pa'i mdzod gsum sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1732: bu des slob ma'i tshogs kun skyong ba dang //
NK026(la)001:1733: bstan pa sgrog pa'i sa la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:1734: rdo rje rgyal por mnga' gsol dbang mchog 'di //
NK026(la)001:1735: theg pa dgu yi rtags bcas sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1737: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod rnams la chos 'chad pa'i
NK026(la)001:1738: dbang bskur bas bka' gsung rab mtha' dag bshad pa'i
NK026(la)001:1739: dbang dam pa d+har+m+aa tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1740: bzhi pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:1741: slob ma snang ba mtha' yas gnas 'gyur te rdo
NK026(la)001:1742: rje sems dpa' dkar po rdo rje dang dril bu
NK026(la)001:1743: 'dzin pa yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur pa la
NK026(la)001:1744: rdo rje dang dril bu glegs bam rnams gtad pas
NK026(la)001:1745: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang thob
NK026(la)001:1746: ste rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa'i nub pa dang ldan
NK026(la)001:1748: po ti rdor dril thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1749: bstan pa sgrog pa'i sa la gnas byas nas //
NK026(la)001:1750: rdo rje rgyal po dpal gyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK026(la)001:1751: theg chen dgu yi rtags dang bcas te sbyin //
NK026(la)001:1752: glegs bam 'on te rdo rje rtse dagu'o //
NK026(la)001:1753: rdo rje rgyal po 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:1754: kun la bu bzhin brtse ba'i ngang tshul can //
NK026(la)001:1755: rgyal ba'i gdung gsob bstan pa rin chen 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:1756: chos la dbang 'byor rgyal thabs sbyor bar shog /
NK026(la)001:1758: phyogs bcu skal ldan khyod rnams la rdo rje'i rgyal
NK026(la)001:1759: po'i dbang bskur bas thabs mkhas thugs rje'i rlabs kyis
NK026(la)001:1760: 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dbang dam pa nus dbang lnga
NK026(la)001:1761: pa 'di la bsam rgyud med kyang sngar bzhin che
NK026(la)001:1762: mchog gi nga rgyal la gnas pa'i dbang du byas
NK026(la)001:1763: pa yin te bsgrag tshig ni /
NK026(la)001:1765: dom dregs kyi gdan thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1766: dbang phyug la sogs dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:1767: smon lam chen po brtan byed pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1768: dregs pa bsnol ba dbang gi gdan //
NK026(la)001:1769: brten pas zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1770: mtha' gnyis mun pa sel ba yi //
NK026(la)001:1771: nyi zla gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1772: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba yi //
NK026(la)001:1773: bdag gzhan don kun rdzogs par shog /
NK026(la)001:1774: mnyam rdzogs brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK026(la)001:1775: thams cad du ni thogs med phyir //
NK026(la)001:1776: zil gnon dom gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1777: brtul zhugs gsum gyi dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1778: lha chen gdan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1779: khams gsum dregs pa zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang dam pa gdan khri thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1780: rang snang yon tan mang pos brjid //
NK026(la)001:1781: rtsol ba zil gyis gnon byed phyir //
NK026(la)001:1782: khyu mchog zung gis dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1783: thams cad zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1784: phung po khams sogs don rig pas //
NK026(la)001:1785: yon tan mang po brjid snang phyir //
NK026(la)001:1786: ma he zung gis dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1787: kun la mdzes pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1788: thabs la rol pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK026(la)001:1789: gdul bya kun la mthun 'jug phyir //
NK026(la)001:1790: gzig gi gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1791: thabs la mkhas pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1792: rgyu 'bras gnyis med sems nyid la //
NK026(la)001:1793: sa dang sa yi rim bral phyir //
NK026(la)001:1794: mkhyen pa stag gi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:1795: khyad 'phags sa dbang thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1796: sa rnams non pa'i rtags mchog gdan khri'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:1797: lha chen la sogs zhing chen nyi zlar bcas //
NK026(la)001:1798: khyu mchog ma he stag gzig dom gyi khri //
NK026(la)001:1799: yon tan rdzogs pa'i gnad du sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1800: drug pa khyad par gyi rin chen bdun ni /
NK026(la)001:1802: 'khor lo bskor zhing gcod pa'i rtags //
NK026(la)001:1803: skye ba rnams bzhi rgyun chod pa //
NK026(la)001:1804: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1805: skye bzhi grol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1806: 'khor lo'i dbang dam pa bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1807: skye ba rnam pa bzhi las grol ba'i dbang dam pa lha yum thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1808: dbyings phyug la sogs bde ba'i yum //
NK026(la)001:1809: thugs rje gzugs kyi rig ma ste //
NK026(la)001:1810: de ring khyod la byin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1811: thabs la spyod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1813: thabs kyi spyod pa la 'jug pa'i dbang dam pa rdo rje thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1814: chos rnams kun la thogs med pa'i //
NK026(la)001:1815: blo gros kun ldan rdo rje sems //
NK026(la)001:1816: de ring khyod la byin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1817: shes bya mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1819: rdo rje sems dpa'i blo gros phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa stobs po che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1820: khams gsum bdo ba kun 'dul ba //
NK026(la)001:1821: stobs chen khro bo chen po ste //
NK026(la)001:1822: de ring khyod la byin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1823: bdud dpung 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1824: stobs po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1825: bdud tshogs mtha' dag 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa glang po che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1826: theg pa'i mtha' la gnas pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:1827: zil gnon theg chen glang gi gzugs //
NK026(la)001:1828: de ring khyod la byin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1829: bdo ba zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:1830: byang chub sems dpa' spos kyi glang po'i dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1831: stobs bcus pha rol zin gyis gnon pa'i dbang dam pa rta mgrin thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1832: thams cad bdag nyid khyab chen po //
NK026(la)001:1833: dbang phyug kun 'gro rta yi gzugs //
NK026(la)001:1834: de ring khyod la byin byas pas //
NK026(la)001:1835: thogs med rdzu 'phrul thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:1836: khro bo rta mgrin gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1837: gang la yang thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phul gyi dbang dam pa rdo rje rin chen thogs te /
NK026(la)001:1838: kun rdzogs sems dpa'i rig par ldan //
NK026(la)001:1839: bsam pas 'byung ba rin po che //
NK026(la)001:1840: de ring khyod la byin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:1841: gdul bya ma lus re skong shog /
NK026(la)001:1842: rdo rje rin chen gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:1843: gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin skong ba'i dbang dam
NK026(la)001:1844: pa skye la dbang sgyur rgyal po mnyes pa'i gzugs
NK026(la)001:1845: // pha rol dpung 'joms srid thub 'dzin pa dang //
NK026(la)001:1846: bdag gzhan don grub rdzu 'phrul rkang par ldan //
NK026(la)001:1847: dgos 'dod yid bzhin skong ba'i rin po che //
NK026(la)001:1848: rgyal po de la thabs kyis byin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1849: khro bo gsang bum gyi dbang 'dir bskur nges pa zhig brgyud pa gnyis kar mi snang yang /
NK026(la)001:1850: rig pas brtags na gong gi zhi ba'i bum dbang gi rjes su bskur yang rigs par snang zhing /
NK026(la)001:1851: yang na skabs 'dir gzugs brnyan phyag rgya'i dbang gi mgor 'thad pa 'dra bas 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:1852: khro bo gsang bum rnams kyi dbang bskur ba'i tshe
NK026(la)001:1853: lha rnams kyi sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi babs pas
NK026(la)001:1854: bag chags kyi dri ma dag cing bum dbang thob
NK026(la)001:1855: pa'i dmigs pa zhi ba'i skabs ltar bsgom du bcug
NK026(la)001:1856: la / dbus kyi gsang bum la /
NK026(la)001:1857: ru lu'i mthar badz+ra he ru ka k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1858: shar gyi gsang bum la ru lu'i mthar bud+d+ha he ru ka k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK026(la)001:1859: lhor ru lu'i mthar rat+na he ru ka k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK026(la)001:1860: nub la ru lu'i mthar pad+ma he ru ka k+aa
NK026(la)001:1861: la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih byang la ru lu'i
NK026(la)001:1862: mthar karma he ru ka k+aa la sha a b+hi
NK026(la)001:1863: shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod cing mthar bdud rtsi rlon sbyor
NK026(la)001:1864: yin na blud cing skam sgrub kyi bdud rtsi ril
NK026(la)001:1866: bdun pa phyag rgya gzugs brnyan gyi dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:1867: de nas rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na /
NK026(la)001:1868: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1869: ris sam 'bur ram lugs su blug pa yi //
NK026(la)001:1870: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan de yi spyi bor bzhag /
NK026(la)001:1871: 'dir gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo la rtsa ba'i
NK026(la)001:1872: bla ma sangs rgyas yi dam du nges pas dbang
NK026(la)001:1873: zhu'i tsakli dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su sbams te gsal
NK026(la)001:1876: zhi khro'i lha tshogs de dang de dag gzugs brnyan
NK026(la)001:1877: gyi rnam pa byon te bdag la thim pa'i dmigs
NK026(la)001:1878: pa snga 'gyur spyi ltar bya dgos par snang ngo
NK026(la)001:1879: // de la 'dir thog mar yo ga ltar zhi
NK026(la)001:1880: ba rdo rje dbyings rgyas pa'i lha dbang rnams yin
NK026(la)001:1881: // te / sgrub mchod kyi tshe bsgom byar med
NK026(la)001:1882: kyang ngo bo gcig yin pas rnam par rtog pa'i
NK026(la)001:1883: spro bsdu mi bya ba gal che'o //
NK026(la)001:1887: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:1888: rdo rje'i rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:1889: 'byung ba nam mkha' rnam dag pa //
NK026(la)001:1890: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:1891: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK026(la)001:1892: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:1895: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK026(la)001:1896: sems dpa' rdo rje dbyings la blta //
NK026(la)001:1897: brtan ma rdo rje 'gyur ba med //
NK026(la)001:1898: rtags kyi phyag rgya de ring khyod la sat+wa badz+ra h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1900: rdo rje rin chen chos don gsal //
NK026(la)001:1901: rdo rje 'bar ba mtha' gnyis bsreg /
NK026(la)001:1902: rtags kyi phyag rgya de ring khyod la badz+ra rat+na h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1904: chos kyi rdo rje chos don rig /
NK026(la)001:1905: rdo rje sdud ma dabyings su sbyor //
NK026(la)001:1906: rtags kyi de ring d+harma badz+ri h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1908: las kyi rdo rje dbyings su sbyor //
NK026(la)001:1909: rdo rje bskyed ma cir mi gnas //
NK026(la)001:1910: rtags kyi de ring karma badz+ra h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1913: gtso zung 'brel ba'i phyag rgya ste //
NK026(la)001:1915: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma gri //
NK026(la)001:1917: 'bar ma nub mo sdud chu lho //
NK026(la)001:1918: rgyud dkrugs chu na m+aa ki lho //
NK026(la)001:1919: lung gcus man ngag de ltar gab //
NK026(la)001:1920: me ni gos dkar gos gtsang nub //
NK026(la)001:1923: gzugs kyi phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:1924: sangs rgyas rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:1925: 'byung ba sa ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:1926: de rgyan can du lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:1929: sems dpa' rdo rje dbyings la lta //
NK026(la)001:1930: rdo rje sgeg mo 'gyur ba med //
NK026(la)001:1931: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra sat+wa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:1933: rdo rje rgyal po mtha' bzhi 'joms //
NK026(la)001:1934: bdug pa dbyings kyi tshim par byed //
NK026(la)001:1935: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra r+aa dza dzah badz+ra d+h+au pe h+aum a /
NK026(la)001:1936: rdo rje chags pas mtha' gnyis 'joms //
NK026(la)001:1937: rdo rje lcags kyus de bzhin 'gugs //
NK026(la)001:1938: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra r+aa ga hoh badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah rdo rje legs pa gsal bar bskul //
NK026(la)001:1939: sgron ma gnyis med tshul gyis gsal //
NK026(la)001:1940: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra s+aa d+h+au du /
NK026(la)001:1943: rdo rje lcags kyu mda' gzhu rgya //
NK026(la)001:1944: me long pog phor lcags kyu phreng //
NK026(la)001:1945: rgyal mtshan se gol tog rgya gram //
NK026(la)001:1947: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:1948: rin chen rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:1949: 'byung ba chu ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:1950: rin chen dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:1951: rtags kyi de ring s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK026(la)001:1953: rdo rje rin chen mnyam nyid gsal //
NK026(la)001:1954: phreng ba ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal //
NK026(la)001:1955: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra rat+na tram /
NK026(la)001:1957: rdo rje nyi ma gsal mtha' mnon //
NK026(la)001:1958: me tog mtha' dral rang rig mdzes //
NK026(la)001:1959: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra s+aur+ya tram /
NK026(la)001:1961: rgyal mtshan mi gnon nga rgyal ldan //
NK026(la)001:1962: zhags pas ma lus sems su sdud //
NK026(la)001:1963: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra ke tu b+h+ri /
NK026(la)001:1965: bzhad pas rang rig dgyes ldan pa //
NK026(la)001:1966: rdo rje bde byed mtha' dang bral //
NK026(la)001:1967: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra ha sa ha /
NK026(la)001:1970: rin chen myu gu nyi ma dang //
NK026(la)001:1971: rgyal mtshan mo phreng rin chen dang //
NK026(la)001:1972: me tog zhags pa bsil yab bo //
NK026(la)001:1974: 'du shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:1975: pad+ma'i rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:1976: 'byung ba me ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:1977: pad+ma dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:1978: rtags kyi de ring +aamha ro li ka /
NK026(la)001:1980: chos ni rang rig cir ma chags //
NK026(la)001:1981: dbyangs ni de don gsal bar byed //
NK026(la)001:1982: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra d+har+m+aa h+r+aih badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih rdo rje gnon po mtha' rnams gcod //
NK026(la)001:1983: sgrol ma ma skyes don gsal byed //
NK026(la)001:1984: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra tik+sha na d+hi /
NK026(la)001:1985: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih 'khor lo mya ngan 'das par bskor //
NK026(la)001:1986: thams cad der 'brel lcags sgrog ma //
NK026(la)001:1987: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra tsakra h+r+aih badz+ra s+pho ta bam /
NK026(la)001:1988: smra ba rigs gsal brjod pa 'dra //
NK026(la)001:1989: gsal bkra kun la gsal bar byed //
NK026(la)001:1990: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra b+h+aa sha b+ha /
NK026(la)001:1991: badz+ra r+aa ga ra ti h+r+aih 'od rim las /
NK026(la)001:1994: pi wang mar me lcags sgrog rma bya'i mdongs //
NK026(la)001:1996: 'du byed phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:1997: las kyi rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:1998: 'byung ba rlung ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:1999: las kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:2000: rtags kyi de ring h+aa pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika t+aam badz+ra ra ti /
NK026(la)001:2001: las ni don bdun gcig par rig /
NK026(la)001:2002: gar ni gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK026(la)001:2003: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra kar+m+aa ha /
NK026(la)001:2005: rdo rje bsrung ba mtha' ma reg /
NK026(la)001:2006: byug pa de don blos rig pa'o //
NK026(la)001:2007: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra rak+sha ham /
NK026(la)001:2009: gnod sbyin mtha' rnams za bar byed //
NK026(la)001:2010: dril bu de don gsal sgrog pa'o //
NK026(la)001:2011: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra yak+sha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2012: badz+ra g+han+de hoh khu tshur gnyis med don rig pa //
NK026(la)001:2013: 'bebs pa de nyid snang bar byed //
NK026(la)001:2014: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra san+ti bam /
NK026(la)001:2015: badz+ra a be sha ya a ha /
NK026(la)001:2017: ral gri rdo rje phreng ba dang //
NK026(la)001:2018: mche ba khu tshur gar byug pa //
NK026(la)001:2020: 'di yan chod kyis sngags rnams dpe rnying phal dang
NK026(la)001:2021: gong ra'i dpe tsaka sogs phal cher la ma dag
NK026(la)001:2022: pa'i rgyun kho na 'byams pa las dpyad pa ma
NK026(la)001:2024: kho bos yo ga'i rang gzhung dang g.yung ston chen
NK026(la)001:2025: po'i sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang byang ltar dag par
NK026(la)001:2026: bcos te yid brtan du rung bar bgyis yod pas
NK026(la)001:2027: mkhas pa chos kyi spyan ldan rnams kyis dpang po
NK026(la)001:2029: lung a nu'i rigs bdag kun bzang thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2031: byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK026(la)001:2032: srid gsum dbang sdud thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:2033: bsnyems pa mi mnga' 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:2034: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:2035: e ma ho kun bzang rdo rje yid //
NK026(la)001:2036: rig pa tshul snang sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:2037: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:2038: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2041: gdod nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyi dbyings //
NK026(la)001:2042: ma skyes ma 'gags dngos por 'dzin dang bral //
NK026(la)001:2043: 'byung byed thams cad bskyed pa yum gyi tshul //
NK026(la)001:2044: bzang po bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:2045: phyi yi yul ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:2046: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK026(la)001:2047: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK026(la)001:2048: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang a a a badz+ri b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK026(la)001:2049: a b+hi rgyud ma h+aa'i gtso bo rdor sems thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2050: ma skyes rdo rje thabs la rol //
NK026(la)001:2051: don dam dbyer med rol mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:2052: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:2053: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag la dgongs //
NK026(la)001:2054: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:2055: rdo rje rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:2056: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin pas //
NK026(la)001:2057: rdo rje sems pa'i dbang 'byung ba nam mkha' sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:2058: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:2059: rdo rje rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK026(la)001:2060: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK026(la)001:2061: m+aum d+h+aa t+we shwa r+ai a b+hi rnam snang thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2062: gzugs kyi phung po gnas dag pas //
NK026(la)001:2063: de bzhin rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:2064: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yin pas //
NK026(la)001:2065: rnam par snang mdzad dbang 'byung ba sa ni sangs
NK026(la)001:2066: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang bde gshegs rigs kyi yum
NK026(la)001:2067: sangs rgyas spyan gyi dbang dz+ai na dzika /
NK026(la)001:2068: l+aam dwe sha ra ti a b+hi rin 'byung thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2069: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rin chen rigs su lhun sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan gyi //
NK026(la)001:2070: rin chen 'byung ldan dbang 'byung ba chu ni sangs
NK026(la)001:2071: rin chen dbyings kyi dbang rin chen rigs kyi yum
NK026(la)001:2072: m+aa ma k+ai yi dbang s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK026(la)001:2073: m+aam mo ha ra ti a b+hi snang mtha' thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2074: 'du shes phung po sangs pad+ma'i rigs su lhun sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yin pas //
NK026(la)001:2075: snang ba mtha' yas dbang 'byung ba me ni sangs
NK026(la)001:2076: pad+ma dbyings kyi dbang pad rigs kyi yum gos dkar
NK026(la)001:2078: p+y+aam r+aa ga ra ti a b+hi don grub thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2079: 'du byed phung po sangs las kyi rigs su lhun sangs rgyas phrin las mchog yin pas //
NK026(la)001:2081: grub pa'i dbang 'byung ba rlung ni sangs las kyi
NK026(la)001:2082: dbyings kyi dbang sna tshogs 'dul ba'i yum dam tshig
NK026(la)001:2083: sgrol ma'i dbang h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK026(la)001:2084: t+aam badz+ra ra ti a b+hi sa snying thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2085: mig gi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2086: byang chub chen po mthong ba'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:2087: bdag gi mig las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2088: sa yi snying po'i dbang gzugs su snang ba sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2089: byang chub lha mo dkar mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2090: phyi yi gzugs las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2091: lha mo l+aa s+ya dbang k+shi hi r+aa dza ya /
NK026(la)001:2092: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:2093: a b+hi nam mkha'i snying po thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2094: rna ba'i rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2095: byang chub chen po thos pa'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:2096: bdag gi rna bas bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2097: nam mkha' snying po'i dbang sgra yi yul ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2099: yul gyi sgra las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2100: lha mo m+aa le'i dbang t+r+aam +aa gar+b+ha ya /
NK026(la)001:2101: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh a b+hi spyan ras gzigs thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2102: sna yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2103: byang chub chen po snom pa'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:2104: bdag gi sna las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2105: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang tshor zhing yul rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2106: byang chub lha mo r+aa ga ti //
NK026(la)001:2107: tshor ba yul las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2108: lha mo g+ai ti'i dbang h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pad ma /
NK026(la)001:2110: a b+hi phyag rdor thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2111: lce yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2112: byang chub chen po myong ba'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:2113: bdag gi lce las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2114: phyag na rdo rje'i dbang bro ba'i yul rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2115: byang chub lha mo in+d+ra n+ai //
NK026(la)001:2116: bro ba'i yul las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2117: lha mo n+air+t+ya'i dbang dz+ri ku ru pan+na hrih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK026(la)001:2118: a b+hi byams pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2119: mthong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2120: byang chub chen po mthong bar byed //
NK026(la)001:2121: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2122: byams pa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2123: dbyar dgun ston dpyid sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2124: dus bzhi yum rnams sems ma'i sku //
NK026(la)001:2125: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2126: d+h+au pe'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2127: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2129: a b+hi sgrib sel thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2130: thos pa'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2131: byang chub chen po thos par byed //
NK026(la)001:2132: thos pa'i dbang po de bskyed pas //
NK026(la)001:2133: sgrib pa rnams sel dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2134: de bzhin nyid las sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2135: lha mo 'od ldan mdzes ma'i sku //
NK026(la)001:2136: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2137: badz+ra push+pe'i dbang th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2139: a b+hi kun bzang thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2140: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2141: byang chub chen po tshor byed pa //
NK026(la)001:2142: dbang po de las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2143: kun tu bzang po'i dbang yul dus bzhi yang sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2144: lha mo mun sel 'od kyi mchog /
NK026(la)001:2145: yul de nyid las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2146: badz+ra +aa lo ke'i dbang h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2147: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK026(la)001:2149: myong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2150: byang chub chen po myong byed pas //
NK026(la)001:2151: dbang po de las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2152: 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i dbang dus bzhi'i dus nyid sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2153: lha mo 'jam des bde ldan ma //
NK026(la)001:2154: dus de'i yul las sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2155: badz+ra gan+d+he'i dbang m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2157: a b+hi gshin rje gshed thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2158: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2159: 'joms byed khro bo reg shes te //
NK026(la)001:2160: reg shes nyid las skur bskyed pa //
NK026(la)001:2161: gshin rje gshed po'i dbang de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2162: rtag par ma yin khro bo ste //
NK026(la)001:2163: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pa //
NK026(la)001:2164: ro langs ma yi dbang h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK026(la)001:2165: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2166: a b+hi stobs po che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2167: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2168: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed de //
NK026(la)001:2169: de nyid las ni skur gzhan gyis mi thub dbang de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2170: chad par ma yin khro mo nyid //
NK026(la)001:2171: de nyid las ni skur mi pham ma yi dbang h+aum pradz+ny+aan+ta krita phata /
NK026(la)001:2172: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra a b+hi rta mgrin thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2173: phyi ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2174: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed sku //
NK026(la)001:2175: de nyid las ni skur rta mgrin dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2176: de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2177: bdag tu ma yin khro mo nyid //
NK026(la)001:2178: yul de nyid las skur khro gnyer ma yi dbang h+aum pad+m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK026(la)001:2179: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra a b+hi bdud 'khyil thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2180: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2181: 'joms byed khro bo reg bya ste //
NK026(la)001:2182: rig pa nyid las skur bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i dbang de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2183: mtshan ma ma yin khro mo'i sku //
NK026(la)001:2184: yul de nyid las skur ral gcig ma yi dbang h+aum big+h+n+aan+ta krita phata /
NK026(la)001:2185: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra a b+hi kun bzang thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2186: yid kyi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2187: byed po kun tu bzang po ste //
NK026(la)001:2188: de nyid las ni skur kun tu bzang po'i dbang h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta /
NK026(la)001:2189: a b+hi bzang mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2190: chos kyi skye mched sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2191: bya ba kun tu bzang mo byung //
NK026(la)001:2192: de nyid las ni skur kun tu bzang mo'i dbang a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK026(la)001:2193: a b+hi lha'i thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2194: nga rgyal thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2195: brgya byin lha yi dbang po byung //
NK026(la)001:2196: de nyid las ni skur lha yi thub pa'i dbang mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2197: a b+hi lha min thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2198: phrag dog thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2199: lha ma yin las thag bzang ris //
NK026(la)001:2200: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pa //
NK026(la)001:2201: lha min thub pa'i dbang mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2202: a b+hi mi'i thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2203: 'dod chags thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2204: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa ste //
NK026(la)001:2205: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pas //
NK026(la)001:2206: sh+aakya thub pa'i dbang mu ne s+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2207: a b+hi byol song thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2208: gti mug nyid las skur bskyed pa //
NK026(la)001:2209: sangs rgyas seng ge rab brtan byung //
NK026(la)001:2210: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pa //
NK026(la)001:2211: byol song thub pa'i dbang mu ne pram s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2212: a b+hi yi dwags thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2213: ser sna thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2215: ser sna nyid las bskyed byas pas //
NK026(la)001:2216: yi dwags thub pa'i dbang mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2217: a b+hi dmyal ba'i thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2218: zhe sdang ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK026(la)001:2219: ston pa chos kyi rgyal po byung //
NK026(la)001:2220: zhe sdang rgyu las skur bskyed pas //
NK026(la)001:2221: dmyal ba'i thub pa'i dbang mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2222: a b+hi de dag kyang +aahh+aum h+r+ai ha'i gnas su dang por bkod la byin no //
NK026(la)001:2223: kun gyis 'da' bar dka' ba yi //
NK026(la)001:2224: tshig btsan yul la dbang sgyur ba //
NK026(la)001:2225: rgyal po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:2226: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par gyur //
NK026(la)001:2228: phyogs bcu skal ldan rigs kyi bu la phyag rgya
NK026(la)001:2229: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas sku lnga
NK026(la)001:2230: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK026(la)001:2232: phyogs bcu skal ldan rigs kyi bu la phyag rgya
NK026(la)001:2233: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas sku lnga
NK026(la)001:2234: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK026(la)001:2236: phyogs bcu skal ldan rigs kyi bu la rgyal po
NK026(la)001:2237: bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya'i dbang bskur bas rgyud ma
NK026(la)001:2238: h+aa yo ga dang lung a nu yo ga'i lha
NK026(la)001:2239: tshogs zhi khro rab 'byams kyi sku lnga yongs su
NK026(la)001:2240: rdzogs te / chos sku longs sku sprul sku rdo
NK026(la)001:2241: rje'i sku mngon par byang chub pa'i sku thob par
NK026(la)001:2242: rdzogs te / gyur cig / ces brjod de /
NK026(la)001:2243: de yan chad zhi ba'i lha'i dbang ngo //
NK026(la)001:2244: 'di'i khro bo a ti la bsdus te bstan pa tsakli nyung bas dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:2245: don la ma h+aa yo ga la'ang zhi khro gnyis yod do //
NK026(la)001:2246: de nas khro bo'i dbang la /
NK026(la)001:2247: dang po dbang mchog gi sku thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2248: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2250: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2251: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK026(la)001:2252: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK026(la)001:2253: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK026(la)001:2254: dbu gsum bar du rngams pa ni //
NK026(la)001:2255: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK026(la)001:2256: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK026(la)001:2257: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK026(la)001:2258: dbu gsum tha mar rngams pa ni //
NK026(la)001:2259: g.yas g.yon dbus gsum mthing ba'i zhal //
NK026(la)001:2260: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK026(la)001:2261: khams gsum re ba skong ba'i zhal //
NK026(la)001:2262: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK026(la)001:2263: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK026(la)001:2264: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK026(la)001:2265: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK026(la)001:2266: b+han+d+ha zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK026(la)001:2267: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK026(la)001:2268: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK026(la)001:2269: me dang rgya mtsho ga'u g.yas //
NK026(la)001:2270: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK026(la)001:2271: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2272: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK026(la)001:2273: kro d+hi mthing nag 'khril ba'i tshul //
NK026(la)001:2275: rgyud rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2276: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:2277: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum
NK026(la)001:2278: ru lu sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+h+ai shwa
NK026(la)001:2281: phyogs bcu skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyed rnams kyis
NK026(la)001:2282: dbang mchog yab yum gyi dbang thob pa gyur cig
NK026(la)001:2283: / che mchog dbu nyer gcig pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2285: ston pa kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2286: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK026(la)001:2287: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pa //
NK026(la)001:2288: che mchog he ru ka'i dbang sbyin no //
NK026(la)001:2289: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2290: khro mo kun gyi rje btsan yum //
NK026(la)001:2291: shes rab dbyings las skur bskyed pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2292: kro d+hi shwa r+ai'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2293: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2294: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2295: a b+hi che mchog zhal gsum phyag drug pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2296: ston pa kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2297: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK026(la)001:2298: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pa //
NK026(la)001:2299: che mchog dbang bskur khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2300: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2301: khro mo kun gyi rje btsan yum //
NK026(la)001:2302: shes rab dbyings las sku bskyed pa //
NK026(la)001:2303: kro d+hi shwa r+ai'i dbang bskur sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2304: sid+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2305: sid+ha ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2307: phyogs bcu ston pa kun bzang yab yum gnas gyur
NK026(la)001:2308: pa'i che mchog he ru ka yab yum gyi dbang
NK026(la)001:2309: bskur dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:2311: kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2312: khro mo kun gyi rje btsan yum //
NK026(la)001:2313: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pas //
NK026(la)001:2314: che mchog yum gyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2315: kro d+ha kro d+hi sh+aa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2316: a b+hi che mchog khro mkhar gyi sku thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2317: e ma hoh chos kun sku la yongs su rdzogs pas chos kyi sku //
NK026(la)001:2318: rdo rje che mchog phyag 'tshal he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2319: theg pa dgu dang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK026(la)001:2320: phyag rgya gcig tu bkod nas rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK026(la)001:2321: 'khor ba dang ni thar pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK026(la)001:2322: dpa' bo chen po'i gdan du brjid cing rol //
NK026(la)001:2323: 'gran gyi zla med che btsan gcig pu nyid //
NK026(la)001:2324: gsang mchog 'bar ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:2325: na mo gzhal yas ni yum kun tu bzang mo
NK026(la)001:2326: dpal che mchog gi sku la gtsug tor rgyal mtshan
NK026(la)001:2327: rtse mo la gser gyi tog stong ni rdzogs pa
NK026(la)001:2328: chen po dang / sku dang sku'i rgyan la rdzogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:2329: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor gyi gdan gyi 'og nor bu
NK026(la)001:2330: rin po che'i gdan gyi steng na rdo rje lnga
NK026(la)001:2331: dang rtse gsum gyi brag ris gtams pa la /
NK026(la)001:2335: ri rab kyi kha mu tig cal dang /
NK026(la)001:2336: karma gar+b+ha'i 'od 'khrigs pa'i nor bu'i 'od 'bar brag la byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK026(la)001:2339: lha mi yang 'khor ba gzugs med pa'i khams dang /
NK026(la)001:2340: keng rus gyi ri rab dang /
NK026(la)001:2341: gzugs khams zhing chen gyi sa dang /
NK026(la)001:2342: 'dod khams kyi chags pa thams cad khrag gi rgya mtshor mngon par mthong zhing /
NK026(la)001:2343: phyag rgya rnam par spro ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:2344: de'ang che mchog mdo ltar na /
NK026(la)001:2346: gnam zhal phyag gnyis sku la 'khril //
NK026(la)001:2348: zhi ba sngon mo'am khro bo smug po'i yum mam /
NK026(la)001:2350: che mchog bdud rtsi la dgongs pa ltar na yab
NK026(la)001:2351: kyi rdo rje yum gyi zhal du bcug pas yum
NK026(la)001:2352: gyi mkha' nas badz+ra he ru ka phyed thon bdud
NK026(la)001:2353: rtsi 'bab pa'i sbyor ba gsungs so //
NK026(la)001:2354: badz+ra he ru ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2355: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2358: mchog cing byin rlabs gsal bsgrubs pas //
NK026(la)001:2359: badz+ra he ru ka'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2360: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2361: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal bas //
NK026(la)001:2362: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK026(la)001:2363: yab yum mchod cing gsal bsgrubs pas //
NK026(la)001:2364: badz+ra kro d+hi sh+aa r+ai'i dbang badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2365: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai sa ma ya h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2366: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h'u /
NK026(la)001:2367: a b+hi bud+d+ha he ru ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2368: rnam par snang mdzad gnas khrag 'thung gti mug 'jigs byed smug nag 'bar bar gsal //
NK026(la)001:2369: mchod cing bsgrubs te byin rlabs pas //
NK026(la)001:2370: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i dbang sangs rgyas spyan ma gnas
NK026(la)001:2371: khro mo dbang phyug skur thabs dang shes rab byang
NK026(la)001:2372: chub sems // spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrubs pa yis //
NK026(la)001:2373: kro d+hi sh+aa r+ai'i dbang bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2374: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2375: ru lu a b+hi rat+na he ru ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2376: rin chen 'byung ldan gnas khrag 'thung chen po nga rgyal 'joms //
NK026(la)001:2378: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrubs pa las //
NK026(la)001:2379: rat+na he ru ka'i dbang m+aa ma k+ai las gnas 'jigs byed khro mo'i sku byung ba //
NK026(la)001:2380: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK026(la)001:2381: spyan drangs mchod gnas bsnyen bsgrubs pas //
NK026(la)001:2382: kro d+hi shwa r+ai'i dbang rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2383: rat+na kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:2384: ru lu a b+hi pad+ma he ru ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2385: snang ba mtha' yas gnas dpal chen khrag 'thung 'dod chags 'joms //
NK026(la)001:2386: dmar nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK026(la)001:2387: bsgoms shing mchod de bsgrubs pa las //
NK026(la)001:2388: pad+ma he ru ka'i dbang na bza' dkar mo gnas 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur snang bas //
NK026(la)001:2389: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK026(la)001:2390: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrubs pas //
NK026(la)001:2391: kro d+hi shwa r+ai'i dbang pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2392: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:2393: ru lu a b+hi karma he ru ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2394: don yod grub pa gnas 'jigs byed khrag 'thung phrag dog 'joms //
NK026(la)001:2396: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod bsgrubs pas //
NK026(la)001:2397: karma he ru ka'i dbang dam tshig sgrol ma gnas 'jigs byed khro mo'i cha lugs bzhin //
NK026(la)001:2398: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK026(la)001:2399: lhag pa byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK026(la)001:2400: kro d+hi shwa r+ai'i dbang karma sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2401: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:2402: ru lu a b+hi rak+sha he ru ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2403: mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK026(la)001:2404: thod dbyug srin po sgrol la mkhas //
NK026(la)001:2405: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK026(la)001:2406: rak+ta he ru ka'i dbang lha mo ral gcig gnas khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK026(la)001:2407: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK026(la)001:2408: rak+sha kro d+hi'i dbang ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru
NK026(la)001:2409: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da
NK026(la)001:2411: ma h+aa rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2412: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2413: e sha ra si ti na ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2414: a b+hi sa nu thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2415: mkhyen rab bdag po gnas sgrol byed ma mo mkha' 'gro 'dul //
NK026(la)001:2416: ser nag mdog can 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK026(la)001:2417: gang sgrub mthu dang dbang stsol pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2418: sa nu he ru ka'i dbang 'jigs byed nag mo gnas khro mo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK026(la)001:2419: sprul pa yang sprul kun gyi ma //
NK026(la)001:2420: sa nu kro d+hi'i dbang ma h+aa sa nu sh+r+ai
NK026(la)001:2421: he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha
NK026(la)001:2422: na da ha pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2423: ma h+aa sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2424: a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2425: e sha ra si ti na mah ru lu a b+hi gu h+ya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2426: thugs rje'i bdag po gnas gsang ba'i don la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2427: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK026(la)001:2428: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK026(la)001:2429: gu h+ya he ru ka'i dbang gsang ba'i lha mo gnas khro mo chen mo gsang ba'i lha //
NK026(la)001:2430: gsang ba'i don la bskul byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2431: gu h+ya kro d+hi'i dbang gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:2432: gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2433: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2436: dpal ldan dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2437: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK026(la)001:2438: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig lha //
NK026(la)001:2439: yak+sha he ru ka'i dbang yum chen dam tshig gnas khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK026(la)001:2440: sangs rgyas sems can 'da' mi byed //
NK026(la)001:2441: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2442: yak+sha kro d+hi'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:2443: ma h+aa yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK026(la)001:2444: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ya na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK026(la)001:2445: phata / ma h+aa yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2446: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2447: e sha ri si ti na mah b+hi she tsa ni mang+ga la na sh+aa pa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2448: ru lu a b+hi goo r+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2449: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:2450: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol na //
NK026(la)001:2451: gru chad bzhi dang glo 'bur du //
NK026(la)001:2452: khro mo brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2453: sa yi snying po gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2454: srin mo chen mo keng thod btul //
NK026(la)001:2455: dkar mo mthu rtsal rku byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2456: badz+ra goo r+ai'i dbang badz+ra goo r+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2457: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2458: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2459: a b+hi tsoo r+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2460: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo nam mkha'
NK026(la)001:2461: snying po gnas srin mo chen mo mda' 'phen btul
NK026(la)001:2462: // rkun mo mthu rtsal len byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2463: badz+ra tsoo r+ai'i dbang badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2464: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2465: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2466: a b+hi pra mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2467: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo spyan ras
NK026(la)001:2468: gzigs dbang gnas srin mo chen mo 'jigs byed btul
NK026(la)001:2469: // rmongs mo mthu rtsal 'bral byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2470: badz+ra pra mo'i dbang badz+ra pra mo h+ae ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2471: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2472: e sha ra si ti na mah b+hi sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2473: a b+hi beet+ta l+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2474: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo phyag na rdo rje gnas srin mo beet+ta nag mo btul //
NK026(la)001:2475: thal byed mthu rtsal nyams byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2476: badz+ra beet+ta li yi dbang badz+ra beet+ta l+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2477: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2478: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2479: a b+hi puk+ka s+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2480: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo 'phags pa
NK026(la)001:2481: byams pa gnas srin mo nang rol 'dren ma btul
NK026(la)001:2482: // sbos mo'i mthu rtsal 'ching byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2483: puk+ka s+ai yi dbang badz+ra puk+ka s+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2484: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2485: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2486: a b+hi g+hasma r+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2487: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo sgrib pa
NK026(la)001:2488: rnam sel gnas lho nub srin mo rab 'jigs btul
NK026(la)001:2489: // sme sha'i mthu rtsal nyams byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2490: g+hasma r+ai yi dbang badz+ra g+hasma r+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2491: ru lu b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2492: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2493: a b+hi sme sha n+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2494: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2495: nub byang srin mo srog gcod btul //
NK026(la)001:2496: gtum mo'i mthu rtsal dbang byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2497: sme sha n+ai yi dbang badz+ra sme sha n+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2498: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2499: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2500: a b+hi tsan+da l+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2501: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo 'jam dpal
NK026(la)001:2502: gzhon nu gnas byang shar srin mo smyon ma btul
NK026(la)001:2503: // ma tshogs mthu rtsal smyo byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2504: tsan+da l+ai yi dbang badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha ha ha /
NK026(la)001:2505: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2506: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2508: dbang gi 'khor lo bar 'khyams phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK026(la)001:2509: phra men brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2510: badz+ra l+aa s+ya gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2511: shar phyogs srin mo seng gdong btul //
NK026(la)001:2512: phra men mthu rtsal gzi byin ma //
NK026(la)001:2513: sid+ha mu kha'i dbang badz+ra sid+ha mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2514: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2515: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2516: a b+hi b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2517: dbang gi 'khor lo bar khyams phra men badz+ra m+aa le gnas lho phyogs srin mo stag mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:2518: phra men mthu rtsal 'joms byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2519: b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha'i dbang badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2520: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2521: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2522: a b+hi sring+ga la mu kha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2523: dbang gi 'khor lo bar khyams phra men badz+ra g+ai ti gnas nub phyogs srin mo srog len btul //
NK026(la)001:2524: phra men mthu rtsal 'dzin byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2525: sring+ga la mu kha'i dbang badz+ra sring+ga la mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2526: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2527: e shwa ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2528: a b+hi shwa na mu kha thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2529: dbang gi 'khor lo bar khyams phra men badz+ra n+air+t+ya gnas byang phyogs srin mo spyang mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:2530: phra men mthu rtsal 'dri byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2531: shwa na mu kha'i dbang badz+ra shwa na mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2532: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2533: e sha ra si ti na mah b+hi sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2534: a b+hi g+r+ai d+ha mu kha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2535: dbang gi 'khor lo bar khyams phra men badz+ra d+h+au pe gnas shar lho'i srin mo khrag 'thung btul //
NK026(la)001:2536: phra men mthu rtsal mgyogs byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2537: g+r+ai d+ha mu kha'i dbang badz+ra g+r+ai d+ha mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2538: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2539: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2540: a b+hi kang+ka mu kha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2541: dbang gi 'khor lo bar khyams phra men badz+ra push+pe gnas lho nub srin po rkang za btul //
NK026(la)001:2542: phra men mthu rtsal khyab byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2543: kang+ka mu kha'i dbang badz+ra kang+ka mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2544: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2545: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2546: a b+hi k+aa ka mu kha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2547: dbang gi 'khor lo bar 'khyams phra men badz+ra +aa
NK026(la)001:2548: lo ke gnas nub byang srin mo 'joms byed btul
NK026(la)001:2549: // phra men mthu rtsal za byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2550: k+aa ka mu kha'i dbang badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2551: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2552: e shar si ti na ma b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2553: a b+hi u lu ka mu kha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2554: dbang gi 'khor lo bar khyams phra men badz+ra gan+d+he gnas byang shar srin mo rku byed btul //
NK026(la)001:2555: phra men mthu rtsal myos byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2556: u lu mu kha'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2557: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he he he /
NK026(la)001:2558: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2559: e sha ra si ti namah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2560: a b+hi ang+ku sha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2561: dbang gi gru chad bar khyams phyi rim gyi //
NK026(la)001:2562: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK026(la)001:2563: sgo ma bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2564: lha mo byams ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2565: shar gyi srin mo rta mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:2566: byams chen rnal 'byor mgon mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:2567: ang+ku sha yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2568: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahphata /
NK026(la)001:2569: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2570: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2571: a b+hi p+aa sha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2572: dbang gi gru chad rnam par sgo ma lha mo
NK026(la)001:2573: snying rje gnas lho sgo'i srin mo phag mgo btul
NK026(la)001:2574: // thugs rje gzhan la phan 'dogs ma //
NK026(la)001:2575: badz+ra p+aa sha'i dbang badz+ra a mu kha h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:2576: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2577: e sha si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2578: a b+hi lo ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2579: dbang gi gru chad rnam par sgo ma dga' ba
NK026(la)001:2580: chen mo gnas nub kyi srin mo dred mgo btul
NK026(la)001:2581: // dga' bas rnal 'byor srongs mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:2582: lo ka ma yi dbang badz+ra lo ka bam phata /
NK026(la)001:2583: ru lu a b+hi she ka ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2584: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2585: a b+hi b+hasmi pa la thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2586: dbang gi gru chad rnam par sgo ma btang snyoms
NK026(la)001:2587: chen po gnas byang sgo'i srin mo spyang mgo btul
NK026(la)001:2588: // btang snyoms chen pos don mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:2589: b+hasmi pa la'i dbang badz+ra b+hasmi pa la yab to hohphata /
NK026(la)001:2590: ru lu a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2591: e sha ra si ti na mah b+hi sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2592: a b+hi shar gyi spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2593: dbang gi rnam bzhi sgo bzhi'i sgo khyud la //
NK026(la)001:2594: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK026(la)001:2595: spor ma brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2596: nang gi dbang mo gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2597: srin mo 'bar ma nyi zhags btul //
NK026(la)001:2598: mi zad sna tshogs nyi zer zhags //
NK026(la)001:2599: shar gyi spor ma'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2600: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2601: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2602: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2603: a b+hi shar lho'i spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2604: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma yi dwags
NK026(la)001:2605: ston pa gnas 'bar ma srin mo me gdong btul
NK026(la)001:2606: // me khyer dman nag glog phreng 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:2607: shar lho spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2608: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2609: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2610: a b+hi lho'i spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2611: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma mi yi
NK026(la)001:2612: ston pa gnas srin mo 'bar ma gtum mo btul
NK026(la)001:2613: // gtum mo ser nag mdung thung 'phen //
NK026(la)001:2614: lho yi spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2615: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2616: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:2617: a b+hi lho nub spor ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2618: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma dmyal ba'i
NK026(la)001:2619: ston pa gnas srin mo 'bar ma ral gri btul
NK026(la)001:2620: // gshin rje sngo nag ral gri dgra //
NK026(la)001:2621: lho nub spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2622: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:2623: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa a b+hi nub kyi spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2624: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma phyi yi
NK026(la)001:2625: yul chos gnas srin mo 'bar ma sgra 'byin btul
NK026(la)001:2626: // rdo rje dril bu 'khrol byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2627: nub kyi spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2628: a b+hi she e shar b+he shar a b+hi nub byang gi spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2629: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma lha yi
NK026(la)001:2630: ston pa gnas 'bar ma srin mo gnod sbyin btul
NK026(la)001:2631: // gnod sbyin mthing nag khyung thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:2632: nub byang spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata //
NK026(la)001:2633: a b+hi she e sha ra b+he sha ra a b+hi byang gi spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2634: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma lha min
NK026(la)001:2635: ston pa gnas srin mo 'bar ma thogs med btul
NK026(la)001:2636: // thogs med sngo nag skar mad'i gdong /
NK026(la)001:2637: byang gi spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2638: a b+hi she e sha ra b+he sha tsa a b+hi byang shar gyi spor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2639: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma byol song
NK026(la)001:2640: thub pa gnas srin mo'i 'jig rten 'bar ma btul
NK026(la)001:2641: // 'jig rten smug nag glag sha stob //
NK026(la)001:2642: byang shar spor ma'i dbang badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:2643: a b+hi she e sha ra b+he sha tsa a b+hi gsang yum gos dkar thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2644: dbang gi gru chad bar khyams sgo bzhi yi //
NK026(la)001:2645: phyi rim snam bu sgo bzhi la //
NK026(la)001:2646: gsang yum bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2647: dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma //
NK026(la)001:2648: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:2649: mdun nas sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:2650: sku dkar phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2651: gsang ba yum gyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2652: sh+r+ai badz+ra mut+ga ra mu kha shwa ra ya na ma /
NK026(la)001:2653: a b+hi ser mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2654: ser mo las mkhan tshe 'phel ma //
NK026(la)001:2655: sku ser phyag na mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK026(la)001:2656: dpal chen sku la sbyor g.yas na sangs rgyas gzungs
NK026(la)001:2657: gsang ba yum gyi dbang sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma
NK026(la)001:2658: shwa ra ya y+aa na ma /
NK026(la)001:2659: a b+hi dmar mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2660: dmar mo za byed dbang sdud ma //
NK026(la)001:2661: sku dmar phyag na rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2662: dpal chen sku la sbyor rgyab na sangs rgyas gzugs
NK026(la)001:2663: gsang ba'i yum gyi dbang sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+wam ka
NK026(la)001:2664: pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na ma /
NK026(la)001:2665: a b+hi nag mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2666: nag mo ral gcig rmongs byed ma //
NK026(la)001:2667: ljang nag phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2668: dpal chen sku la sbyor g.yon nas sangs rgyas gzungs
NK026(la)001:2669: gsang ba'i yum gyi dbang sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa
NK026(la)001:2671: a b+hi ma nu rak+sha s+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2672: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:2673: phyi rim khyams kyi khrag mtsho la //
NK026(la)001:2674: sgo bzhi snam bu ngos bzhi la //
NK026(la)001:2675: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2676: srin mo'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2677: dbang phyug chen mo mi srin mo //
NK026(la)001:2678: sku mdog dmar nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK026(la)001:2679: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2680: dmar ser tri shul zhing chen g.yag /
NK026(la)001:2681: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK026(la)001:2682: ma nu rak+sha'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2684: a b+hi badz+ra bra h+ma n+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2686: tshangs pa'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2687: dbang phyug chen mo tshangs ma ste //
NK026(la)001:2688: sku mdog dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2689: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2690: dmar skya rtse lnga b+han dmar sprul //
NK026(la)001:2691: mthu stobs dbang phyug bsam mi khyab //
NK026(la)001:2692: badz+ra bra h+ma'i dbang bra h+ma ni b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2693: a b+hi roo tri thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2694: lha chen chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2695: dbang phyug chen mo 'khrug mo che //
NK026(la)001:2696: sku mdog dkar mo tri shu la //
NK026(la)001:2697: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2698: dmar ser zhing dbyug snying 'byin gzig /
NK026(la)001:2699: rol pa'i rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK026(la)001:2700: badz+ra roo tri'i dbang roo tri ma b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2701: a b+hi ku m+aa r+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2702: khyab 'jug chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2703: dbang phyug chen mo 'jug sred mo //
NK026(la)001:2705: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2706: ril pa 'khor lo pha wang ser //
NK026(la)001:2707: dregs pa'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2708: badz+ra ku m+aa r+ai'i dbang ku m+aa r+ai b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2709: a b+hi in+d+ra ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2710: gzhon nu'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2711: dbag phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2712: gzhon nu dmar mo mdud thung 'phen //
NK026(la)001:2713: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2714: dbang mo dmar skya bam dbyug dred //
NK026(la)001:2715: yon tan mthu rtsal bsam yas pa //
NK026(la)001:2718: a b+hi besh+na be thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2719: brgya byin chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2720: dbang phyug chen mo dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:2721: sku mdog dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs //
NK026(la)001:2722: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2723: dkar dmar byis za dung dmar sre //
NK026(la)001:2724: che ba'i yon tan bsam yas pas //
NK026(la)001:2725: besh+na be yi dbang besh+na be b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2726: a b+hi badz+ra ping+ka lam thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2727: lha mo khyo med gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2728: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2730: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2731: dmar mo dung dmar rgyu zhags dom //
NK026(la)001:2732: yid kyi 'dod pa bsam yas pa //
NK026(la)001:2733: ping+ka lam gyi dbang badz+ra ping+ka lam b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2734: a b+hi badz+ra a mri ta thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2735: nyi ma'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2736: dbang phyug chen mo bdud rtsi mo //
NK026(la)001:2737: sku mdog dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2738: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2739: bdud rtsi sngon mo chu srin bum //
NK026(la)001:2740: sman gyi mthu stobs bsam yas pas //
NK026(la)001:2743: a b+hi badz+ra soo mya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2744: zla ba'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2745: dbang phyug chen mo zhi ba mo //
NK026(la)001:2746: zhi ba dkar mo pun+d+ha ri //
NK026(la)001:2747: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2748: sngo skya bum ril khog smad sdig /
NK026(la)001:2749: bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyi mthus //
NK026(la)001:2750: badz+ra soo mya'i dbang badz+ra soo mya b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2751: a b+hi badz+ra d+ha na thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2752: be con chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2753: dbang phyug chen mo be con ma //
NK026(la)001:2754: sku mdog sngon mo dbyug to thogs //
NK026(la)001:2755: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2756: nag mo be con thod rlon khra //
NK026(la)001:2757: drag shul 'joms pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK026(la)001:2758: badz+ra d+ha na'i dbang badz+ra d+ha na dam b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2759: a b+hi badz+ra rak+ta s+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2760: srin mo khyo med gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2761: dbang phyug chen mo srin mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2762: sku mdog dmar ser thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:2763: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2764: dmar nag zhing chen rgyu 'dren wa //
NK026(la)001:2765: drag po'i mthu stobs bsam yas pas //
NK026(la)001:2766: badz+ra rak+sha'i dbang badz+ra rak+sha si b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2767: a b+hi badz+ra bak+sha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2768: nag chen chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2769: dbang phyug chen mo za ba mo //
NK026(la)001:2770: dmar nag sha dang khrag la rol //
NK026(la)001:2771: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2772: nag mo bam chen snying 'byin stag /
NK026(la)001:2773: mthu stobs gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
NK026(la)001:2774: badz+ra bak+sha'i dbang badz+ra bak+sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2775: a b+hi badz+ra ra ti thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2776: b+h+ring gi chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2777: dbang phyug chen mo dga' mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2779: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2780: dmar mo 'khor lo thod pa rgod //
NK026(la)001:2781: mthu dang longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK026(la)001:2782: ra ti tam gyi dbang badz+ra ra ti tam b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2783: a b+hi badz+ra ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2784: 'di ni khrag myos ma zhes bya ba'i don yin
NK026(la)001:2785: ces kho bo'i yongs 'dzin sman lung pa gsung ngo
NK026(la)001:2786: // stobs bzang chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2787: dbang phyug chen mo khrag 'thung myos //
NK026(la)001:2788: sku mdog dkar mo gshol 'chang ma //
NK026(la)001:2789: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2790: dmar nag rdor dbyug dung dmar rta //
NK026(la)001:2791: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul mtha' yas pas //
NK026(la)001:2792: ra mat+t+aa yi dbang badz+ra ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2793: a b+hi badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2794: rnam thos chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2795: dbang phyug chen mo gcig pu spyod //
NK026(la)001:2796: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK026(la)001:2797: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2798: dkar dmar rdo rje b+han+d+ha khyung //
NK026(la)001:2799: 'byor pa'i longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK026(la)001:2801: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2802: a b+hi badz+ra ma no ha ram thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2803: 'dod lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2804: dbang phyug chen mo yid 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:2805: sku mdog dmar mo mda' gzhu thogs //
NK026(la)001:2806: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2807: dmar ser zhing sdom byis za khyi //
NK026(la)001:2808: 'dod pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK026(la)001:2809: ma no ha ram dbang ma no ha ram b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2810: a b+hi badz+ra sid+d+ha kam thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2811: nor srung chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2812: dbang phyug chen mo grub mor byung //
NK026(la)001:2813: sku mdog dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:2814: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2815: dkar dmar pad+ma ro pu shud //
NK026(la)001:2816: lhag par nor gyi longs spyod che //
NK026(la)001:2817: sid+d+ha ka yi dbang badz+ra sid+d+hi kam b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2818: a b+hi badz+ra ba ya be thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2819: rlung lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2820: dbang phyug chen mo rlung mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2821: sku mdog sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:2822: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2823: dmar skya ro za sha ba'i mgo //
NK026(la)001:2825: ba ya be yi dbang badz+ra ba ya be b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2826: a b+hi badz+ra ma h+aa m+aa ra na thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2827: skyong ma khyo med gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2828: dbang phyug chen mo khyo med ma //
NK026(la)001:2829: sku mdog dmar nag ral gris gcod //
NK026(la)001:2830: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2831: ljang nag bam chen rnge chung spung //
NK026(la)001:2832: sgrol byed mthu stobs bsam yas pas //
NK026(la)001:2833: m+aa ra na yi dbang badz+ra ma h+aa m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2834: a b+hi badz+ra ag+na ye thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2835: me lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2836: sku mdog dmar mo gsal shing 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:2837: dbang phyug chen mo mi mor byung //
NK026(la)001:2838: de las mi zad sku sprul pas //
NK026(la)001:2839: ljang dmar mes bsreg rgyu 'dren skyin //
NK026(la)001:2840: rnam rtog bag chags kun bsreg pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2841: ag+ne ma yi dbang badz+ra ag+na ye b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2842: a b+hi skyin mgo 'di lho 'brong dang /
NK026(la)001:2844: ri bong gi skyes rabs las skyin gor zhig dang
NK026(la)001:2845: zhes pa da byid la ngos 'dzin la sogs lugs
NK026(la)001:2846: gsum snang ngo // badz+ra b+aa ra hi thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2847: sa bdag chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2848: dbang phyug chen mo phag mor byung //
NK026(la)001:2849: sku mdog dmar nag mche ba bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2850: de nyid las kyang sku sprul pa //
NK026(la)001:2851: ljang ser rtse gsum byis ro phag /
NK026(la)001:2852: 'jig rten khams kyi dpal gcig ma //
NK026(la)001:2853: b+aa ra hi'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:2855: a b+hi badz+ra tsa mun+d+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2856: gshin rje chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2857: dbang phyug chen mo rgan byed mo //
NK026(la)001:2858: dmar smug byis ro rgyu ma za //
NK026(la)001:2859: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:2861: ma mo mthu dbang kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2862: tsa mun+d+ai yi dbang badz+ra tsa mun+d+ai b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2863: a b+hi badz+ra su ta nam thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2864: bgegs kyi chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2865: dbang phyug ma mo sna chen mo //
NK026(la)001:2866: sku mdog dmar nag thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:2867: de nyid 'jigs pa'i sku sprul pa //
NK026(la)001:2868: ljang dmar bam chen longs spyod glang //
NK026(la)001:2869: bgegs chen kun 'dul mthu stobs kyis //
NK026(la)001:2870: su ta na yi dbang badz+ra su ta nam b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2871: a b+hi badz+ra wa ru na thogs te //
NK026(la)001:2872: chu lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2873: dbang phyug chen mo chu lha mo //
NK026(la)001:2874: sku mdog dkar sngo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:2876: ljang nag bdud rtsi dung dmar sprul //
NK026(la)001:2877: gter gyi longs spyod bsam yas pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2878: wa ru na yi dbang badz+ra wa ru na b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2879: a b+hi badz+ra ma h+aa li thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2880: nag mo'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2881: dbang phyug nag mo chen mo ste //
NK026(la)001:2882: sku mdog nag mo ang+ku sha /
NK026(la)001:2884: nag mo lcags kyu khu byug mgo //
NK026(la)001:2885: pu tra 'dzin byed thams cad rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2886: ma h+aa k+aa li'i dbang badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2887: a b+hi badz+ra tsa ka li thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2888: ra gdong chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2889: dbang phyug chen mo ra mgo ma //
NK026(la)001:2890: sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2892: sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren pa'i ra //
NK026(la)001:2893: 'khor bar mi gtong dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:2894: tsa ka li yi dbang badz+ra tsa ka li b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2895: a b+hi badz+ra bum pa ka la thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2896: bum sna'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2897: dbang phyug bum sna sngo nag ma //
NK026(la)001:2898: sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrog sdom //
NK026(la)001:2900: dmar mo be con lcags sgrog seng //
NK026(la)001:2901: bgegs bdud srin sdom dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:2902: bum pa ka la'i dbang badz+ra bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2903: a b+hi badz+ra lam bo d+ha ra thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2904: gsus chen chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2905: dbang phyug gsus 'dzin chen mo byung //
NK026(la)001:2906: sku mdog ljang nag dril bu 'khrol //
NK026(la)001:2908: ljang nag dril chen dung dmar skyeg /
NK026(la)001:2909: nga rgyal dregs pa zhing bcu spor //
NK026(la)001:2910: lam bo d+ha ra'i dbang badz+ra lam bo d+ha ra b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:2911: a b+hi ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2912: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:2914: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi ru //
NK026(la)001:2915: mkha' 'gro tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:2916: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2917: mkha' 'gro dga' byed rdo rje bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2918: mkha' 'gro rdo rje rigs dbang phyug /
NK026(la)001:2919: badz+ra d+ha ra'i dbang kro d+hi shwa r+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2922: rdo rje rgyal po gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2923: 'dren byed dkar skya lcags kyu ma //
NK026(la)001:2925: kro d+hi shwa ri'i dbang badz+ra ma h+aa he mi ti thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2926: rdo rje chags pa gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2927: gsod byed thabs kyi mda' 'gengs ma //
NK026(la)001:2928: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2929: ma h+aa ma ti'i dbang badz+ra ku ma r+ai thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2930: rdo rje legs par gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2931: spor byed dkar skya spu gri thogs //
NK026(la)001:2932: ku m+aa ri yi dbang ma h+aa badz+ra ma tsi ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2933: rdo rje rin chen gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2936: badz+ra mi tsa'i dbang badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra ya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2937: rdo rje nyi ma gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2939: rnam rtog mun sel mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2940: tri sh+r+ai sma ra'i dbang badz+ra tsag ne thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2941: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2942: khro gnyer mthing nag zhing dar 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:2943: bdud bzhi 'dul byed dbang ldan pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2944: badz+ra tsag ne'i dbang ma h+aa kro d+hi thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2945: rdo rje bzhad pa gnas gyur pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2946: 'joms byed zhing gi kha gdangs ma //
NK026(la)001:2947: dur khrod bgegs 'joms za byed pa'i //
NK026(la)001:2948: ma h+aa kro d+hi'i dbang ma h+aa a mri tod thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2949: rdo rje chos mchog gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2950: chags med dmar nag pad+ma bsnams //
NK026(la)001:2951: nyes pa'i skyon bral legs dbang rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2952: a mri tod pa'i dbang ma h+aa soo ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2953: rdo rje rnon po gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2954: chags bral dmar nag gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:2955: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2956: ma h+aa soo ma'i dbang ma h+aa badz+ra dan ti thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2957: rdo rje 'khor lo gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2959: mkha' 'gro gcod byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:2960: badz+ra dan ti'i dbang ma h+aa ra mi ni thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2961: rdo rje smra ba gnas gyur te //
NK026(la)001:2963: thogs med lcags kyu dbang sgyur ma //
NK026(la)001:2964: ma h+aa ra mi ni'i dbang ma h+aa smri ti ka pa la he ste ta ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2965: rdo rje phrin las gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2966: sna tshogs lus 'chang rgya gram thogs //
NK026(la)001:2967: mkha' 'gro phrin las rdzogs pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:2968: heste ta ka'i dbang badz+ra soo nya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2969: rdo rje srung ba gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2970: srung ba mo ljang go cha thogs //
NK026(la)001:2972: badz+ra soo nya'i dbang mri ta su ta na da ri thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2973: rdo rje gnod sbyin gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2974: gnod sbyin mo ljang mche ba 'byin //
NK026(la)001:2975: dam nyams gsod pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK026(la)001:2976: su ta na da ra'i dbang badz+ra bi la ki la thogs la /
NK026(la)001:2977: rdo rje khu tshur gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2979: rdul du rlog byed mkha' 'gro'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:2980: bi la ki la'i dbang bi shi ri ri thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2981: dpa' bar 'gro ba gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:2982: bya rog gdong la mig 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:2983: lag na gri dang 'khar gzhong thogs //
NK026(la)001:2985: bi shi ri ri dbang k+sha ni k+sha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2986: kun tu bzang po gnas 'jigs byed dkar sngo mche gtsigs ma //
NK026(la)001:2988: k+sha ni k+sha yi dbang sha ni ta ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2989: zla 'od gzhon nu gnas bzhad mgo dkar mo snying 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:2990: thams cad sgrol ba'i mkha' 'gro ging //
NK026(la)001:2991: sha ni ta ka'i dbang pi ta ki thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2992: byang sems bzang skyong gnas 'ug mgo dkar sngon keng rus 'cha' //
NK026(la)001:2993: las byed lhag sdud gzhi dbang kun //
NK026(la)001:2994: pi ta ka yi dbang badz+ra a na ya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:2995: byang sems d+r+wa 'od gnas khyi mgo mthing nag keng rus 'cha' //
NK026(la)001:2996: dur khrod 'joms pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:2999: rdo rje snying po gnas mthing nag m+ai sa phag gi mgo //
NK026(la)001:3000: gtsang rme med par za byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3001: pe k+ae ni'i dbang dza du la ya thog te /
NK026(la)001:3002: nam mkha' mdzod ni gnas sgo nag glo 'dren rnga mo mgo //
NK026(la)001:3004: dza du la yi dbang ta ki bi ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3005: 'od dpag med pa gnas thod dbyug dgra s+t+wa bong bu'i mgo //
NK026(la)001:3007: bi ka te yi dbang badz+ra ta ra she thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3008: mya ngan kun 'joms gnas dmar nag spu gri ra yi mgo //
NK026(la)001:3010: badz+ra ta ra she'i dbang ka li pra be sha thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3011: rgyal ba ye shes gnas dmar nag rus 'cha' byi la'i mgo //
NK026(la)001:3012: ma lus sgrol byed mkha' 'gro'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:3013: pra be sha yi dbang us ting ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3014: blo gros mi zad gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:3015: dmar ljang keng rus dkar po 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3017: us ting mang sa'i dbang ka ran tsa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3018: spobs pa brtsegs pa gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:3019: dmar ser rus phreng ce spyang mgo //
NK026(la)001:3021: ka ran tsa yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:3022: sarba ma ta ra thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3023: ngan song kun 'dren gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:3024: mkha' 'gro srin mo bum sna ma //
NK026(la)001:3025: rdo rje lcags kyu ka ta ri //
NK026(la)001:3026: ma ta ra yi dbang sa la ta ka thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3027: byams pa brtsegs pa gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:3029: zhags pa gri thogs 'dzin cir sgrol //
NK026(la)001:3030: sa la ta ka'i dbang badz+ra sarba b+han+d+ha a thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3031: spos kyi glang po gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:3032: mkha' 'gro d+ha sha gri ba ste //
NK026(la)001:3033: lcags sgrog spu gri za byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3034: b+han+d+ha a yi dbang badz+ra sa b+ha na a thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3035: sems dpa' don grub gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:3037: dril bu dgra s+t+was sgrol zhing spor //
NK026(la)001:3038: sa b+ha na a'i dbang rdo rje kun grags mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3039: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3040: phyi yi snam bu phyogs bzhi la //
