NK026(la)001:3041: ma bdun sring bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:3042: ma mo bdun gyi dbang mchog ste //
NK026(la)001:3043: rgya mtsho chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:3044: dpal ldan shugs sgrol gtso mo ste //
NK026(la)001:3045: ri rab bsnyil ba'i mthu mo che //
NK026(la)001:3046: rdo rje kun grags dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:3047: ma ma d+h+aa tu kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:3048: a b+hi kun tu bzang mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3050: nam mkha' stong gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:3051: thams cad kun la khyab mdzad cing //
NK026(la)001:3052: ma lus yongs la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3053: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang ma ma d+h+aa tu kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:3054: a b+hi rdo rje kun gsal ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3057: ma rig mun pa sel mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:3058: rdo rje kun gsal dbang ma ma sogs /
NK026(la)001:3059: rdo rje ye shes mchog thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3060: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:3061: pho nya ma ste drug cu'i gtso //
NK026(la)001:3062: sha chen khrag la longs spyod pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3063: rdo rje ye shes dbang ma ma sogs /
NK026(la)001:3064: rdo rje 'od chags ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3065: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:3066: rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i phreng thogs shing //
NK026(la)001:3068: rdo rje 'od chags dbang ma ma sogs /
NK026(la)001:3071: zhags pa stong gi bde ldan zhing //
NK026(la)001:3073: rdo rje 'od 'phro'i dbang ma ma sogs /
NK026(la)001:3074: rdo rje g.yu sgron ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3075: dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:3076: dam tshig nyams pa gcod byed cing //
NK026(la)001:3078: rdo rje g.yu sgron dbang ma ma sogs /
NK026(la)001:3080: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3081: phyi rim snam bu sgo bzhi ru //
NK026(la)001:3082: sring mo bzhi yi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:3083: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha yi sring //
NK026(la)001:3084: sku la bya rgod thul ba gsol //
NK026(la)001:3085: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK026(la)001:3086: lha yi sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:3089: gshin rje'i sring mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3091: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK026(la)001:3092: sku la stag gi thul pa gsol //
NK026(la)001:3093: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK026(la)001:3094: gshin rje'i sring mo'i badz+ra dun+tinga sogs /
NK026(la)001:3096: dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring //
NK026(la)001:3097: na bza' chu srin lpags pa gsol //
NK026(la)001:3098: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs ma //
NK026(la)001:3099: klu yi sring mo'i dbang badz+ra dun+tinga gnod sbyin sring mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3100: nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK026(la)001:3101: sku la rma bya'i thul ba gsol //
NK026(la)001:3102: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs ma //
NK026(la)001:3103: gnod sbyin sring mo'i dbang badz+ra dun+ti nga dpa' bo chen po thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3104: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3105: phyi rim snam bu phyogs bzhi ru //
NK026(la)001:3106: thugs kyi 'od zer sprul pa las //
NK026(la)001:3107: khro bo ging gi bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:3108: dpal chen las rnams kun byed pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3109: mthing nag ral gri b+han+d+ha bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3110: gang la dmigs pa sgrol ba yi //
NK026(la)001:3111: rdo rje ging gi dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:3112: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:3113: a b+hi khro mo chen mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3114: khro mo khams gsum dbang sdud ma //
NK026(la)001:3115: sngo nag thod khrag 'jam dpal thogs //
NK026(la)001:3117: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:3118: a b+hi dmar nag thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3120: ging chen rdo rje dmar nag ni //
NK026(la)001:3121: dung dmar dang ni ka tar bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3122: ma thogs myur du sgrol bar byed //
NK026(la)001:3123: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi gnod sbyin thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3124: ging chen rdo rje gnod sbyin ni //
NK026(la)001:3125: ljang nag phyag gis sdigs mdzub 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3126: dam tshig nyams rnams sgrol byed pa //
NK026(la)001:3127: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi spyang mgo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3128: rdo rje ging chen spyang ki ni //
NK026(la)001:3129: dmar nag spyang mgo spu gri thogs //
NK026(la)001:3130: gsod pa'i las la shin tu dgyes //
NK026(la)001:3131: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi gshin rje thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3132: rdo rje ging chen gshin rje ni /
NK026(la)001:3133: mthing nag be con dgra s+t+wa 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3134: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen te //
NK026(la)001:3135: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rol pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3136: rdo rje ging chen rol pa ni //
NK026(la)001:3137: dmar nag b+han+d+ha phal tshab bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3138: dgra bgegs ma lus nyam thag gcod //
NK026(la)001:3139: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi 'chi bdag thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3140: rdo rje ging chen 'chi bdag ni //
NK026(la)001:3141: ljang ser rdo rje gsor zhing brdeg /
NK026(la)001:3142: drag shul sbyor ba'i mthu stobs can //
NK026(la)001:3143: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi dus mtshams thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3144: rdo rje ging chen dus mtshams ni //
NK026(la)001:3147: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi ro langs thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3148: rdo rje ging chen ro langs ni //
NK026(la)001:3149: ser nag zhing gi dbyug pa 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3150: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'joms //
NK026(la)001:3151: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi 'joms pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3152: rdo rje ging chen 'joms pa ni //
NK026(la)001:3153: smug nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3154: bgegs kyi dpung yang yud kyis 'joms //
NK026(la)001:3155: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra kata a b+hi dbang bsdud thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3156: rdo rje ging lcam dbang sdud ni //
NK026(la)001:3157: ljang nag rdo rje lcags kyus 'dren //
NK026(la)001:3158: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis sgrol //
NK026(la)001:3159: rdo rje ging lcam dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi dbang sgyur ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3160: rdo rje ging lcam dbang sgyur ma //
NK026(la)001:3161: khams gsum zhing gi g.yab mo 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3162: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK026(la)001:3163: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi 'phrul mo che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3164: rdo rje ging lcam 'phrul mo che //
NK026(la)001:3165: gzugs med rlung ltar rgyu byed cing //
NK026(la)001:3166: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis khyab //
NK026(la)001:3167: rdo rje ging lcam dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi glog 'gyu ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3168: rdo rje ging lcam glog 'gyu ma //
NK026(la)001:3170: cir yang bsgyur ba'i 'phrul mo che //
NK026(la)001:3171: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi mthu mo che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3172: rdo rje ging lcam mthu mo che //
NK026(la)001:3173: ljang nag lcags kyi tho ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3174: rbod gtong bcol ba len byed pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3175: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rtsal mo che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3176: rdo rje ging lcam rtsal mo che //
NK026(la)001:3177: mthing nag rdo rje dgra s+t+wa thogs //
NK026(la)001:3178: phrin las rna nyan phra ma zer //
NK026(la)001:3179: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi sgrol byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3180: rdo rje ging lcam sgrol byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3181: smug nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3182: phrin las srid gsum sgrol byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3183: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi za byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3184: ging lcam za byed chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:3185: mthing nag phyag na longs spyod bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3186: phrin las tshogs kyi chag tshang byed //
NK026(la)001:3187: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje ging lcam myong byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3188: smug nag phyag na longs spyod bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3189: phrin las tshogs kyi chag tshang byed //
NK026(la)001:3190: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rnam rgyal yab yum thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3191: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3192: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og bcu //
NK026(la)001:3193: dgra gdon ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:3194: sku yi kha dog mthing nag las //
NK026(la)001:3195: khro bo khro mo drug cu sprul //
NK026(la)001:3196: rnam rgyal mdog dkar rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3197: snyems ma gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:3198: mthu rtsal yang che dri za'i gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3199: khro bo khro mo'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:3200: badz+ra kro d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h'u /
NK026(la)001:3201: a b+hi dbyug sngon thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3203: dbyug pa sngon po sdigs mdzub rin chen sngo //
NK026(la)001:3204: sder mo gtso 'khyud dung dmar yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:3205: mthu rtsal che bas drang srong gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3206: khro bo khro mo'i dbang 'di thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:3207: badz+ra a b+hi gshed po thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3208: gshin rje gshed po mthing nag dbyug to 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3209: rdo rje dur khrod dung dmar yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:3210: nga rgyal mthu chen gshin rje'i gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3211: khro bo khro mo'i dbang badz+ra a b+hi mi g.yo ba thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3212: mi g.yo mgon po khu tshur ral gri thogs //
NK026(la)001:3213: rdo rje gtun khung dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK026(la)001:3214: rdzu 'phrul stobs chen srin po'i gdon rnams 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3215: khro bo khro mo'i dbang badz+ra a b+hi rta mgrin thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3216: rta mgrin mdog dmar pad+ma mda' gzhu bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3217: rdo rje gtum mo dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK026(la)001:3218: thugs rje mthu rtsal gti mug klu 'dul ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3219: khro bo khro mo'i dbang badz+ra a b+hi gzhan gyis mi thub pa thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3220: gzhan gyis mi thub dgra s+t+wa gtun shing sngo //
NK026(la)001:3221: rdo rje mda' snyems dung khrag gtso la stob //
NK026(la)001:3222: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul klu gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3223: khro bo khro mo'i dbang badz+ra a b+hi bdud rtsi 'khyil ba thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3224: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3225: rdo rje rlung 'byin dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK026(la)001:3226: drag po'i mthu yis gnod sbyin 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3227: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi khams gsum rnam rgyal thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3228: khams gsum rnam rgyal rdo rje tho ba nag /
NK026(la)001:3229: rdo rje gsod byed dmar gyi mchod pa 'dren //
NK026(la)001:3230: drag shul mthu yis 'byung po'i gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3231: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi stobs po che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3232: stobs chen dud kha 'bud dung rnga yab thogs //
NK026(la)001:3233: rdo rje bskyod byed dung khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:3234: mthu stobs ldan pas sa bdag gdan 'dul ba'i //
NK026(la)001:3235: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi h+aum mdzad thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3236: h+aum mdzad dmar skya rdo rje mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK026(la)001:3237: rdo rje sgra 'byin dung dmar zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3238: nyi zla gza' skar yas gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3239: khro bo yab yum badz+ra a b+hi k+ai la ya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3240: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3241: sku yi 'od zer mthing nag las //
NK026(la)001:3242: khro bo yab yum drug cus bskor //
NK026(la)001:3243: dgra bgegs mang po 'dul slad du //
NK026(la)001:3244: rdo rje phur pa mthing nag phur bu 'dril //
NK026(la)001:3245: khro mo rgyas 'debs b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang //
NK026(la)001:3246: mthu dbang che bas dgra dang lha gdon 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3247: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi rme brtsegs thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3248: khro bo rme brtsegs mthing nag rdo rje thogs //
NK026(la)001:3249: khra mo 'dam 'byin dung chen dam rdzas bkang //
NK026(la)001:3250: mi gtsang rtog 'joms bdud dang ru tra 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3251: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra yak+sha thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3252: yak+sha ljang nag phur pa sdigs mdzub sgreng //
NK026(la)001:3253: khro mo yag mo dung chen snying khrag bcas //
NK026(la)001:3254: dam tshig nyams dang dam sri 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3255: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi /
NK026(la)001:3257: khro bo dmar nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3258: khro bo dbang sgyur mgo bcad rak+tasa bkang //
NK026(la)001:3259: mthu rtsal che bas ma gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3260: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi za 'og thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3261: khro bo za 'og thod sbrul sna tshogs mdog /
NK026(la)001:3262: khro mo za mo rdo rje thod khrag stob //
NK026(la)001:3263: rdzu 'phrul mthu yis rmu gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:3264: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi rab grub thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3265: khro bo rab grub sngo nag ral gri 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3266: khro mo rab 'jigs thod khrag zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3267: mthu rtsal che bas ya bdud 'dul mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:3268: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi ma h+aa k+aa la thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3269: khro chen ma h+aa k+aa la dmar nag zhags //
NK026(la)001:3270: khro mo ral pa sgreng ma thod khrag stob //
NK026(la)001:3271: mthu rtsal che bas ma bdud 'dul mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:3272: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi thal sbyor
NK026(la)001:3273: thogs te mi 'chi thal sbyor sngo nag thal mo
NK026(la)001:3274: sdeb // khro mo 'joms chen dung khrag zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3275: mthu rtsal che bas srog chags 'dul mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:3276: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi gu lang thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3277: khro chen gu lang smug nag gtun shing sdeb //
NK026(la)001:3278: khro mo las kun b+han+d+ha dmar gyis bkang //
NK026(la)001:3279: mthu rtsal che bas khams gsum bsad gso mdzad //
NK026(la)001:3280: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi rab rngam thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3281: rab rngam ljang nag rdo rje dkrug cing gsol //
NK026(la)001:3282: gtum chen thod khrag tsit+ta gtso la stob //
NK026(la)001:3283: mthu rtsal che bas brjed byed gdon rnams 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3284: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi gsum snang thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3285: 'jig rten gsum snang be con sdigs mdzub thogs //
NK026(la)001:3286: khro mo mi pham de bzhin dung chen stob //
NK026(la)001:3287: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung shar gdon 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3288: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi gsum 'dul thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3289: 'jig rten gsum 'dul dmar nag tho ba 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3290: khro mo lcags kyu de bzhin lcags kyu dang //
NK026(la)001:3291: shar sgo srung zhing shar gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK026(la)001:3292: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi gsum 'jigs thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3293: 'jig rten gsum 'jigs dmar nag tho ba 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3294: khro gnyer thod khrag de bzhin zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3295: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung lho gdon 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3296: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi gsum 'ching thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3297: 'jig rten gsum 'ching sngo nag dbyug to 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3298: khro mo zhags pa dung dmar zhags pa thogs //
NK026(la)001:3299: lho sgo srung zhing lho gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK026(la)001:3300: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi pad rgyal thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3301: pad rgyal dmar nag de bzhin ral gri 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3302: ro langs de bzhin thod khrag zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3303: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung nub gdon 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3304: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:3305: badz+ra a b+hi be con thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3306: be con sngon po rin chen be con 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3307: khro mo lcags sgrog de bzhin dung chen 'bud //
NK026(la)001:3308: nub phyogs sgo srung nub gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK026(la)001:3309: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi ka ti thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3310: ka ti badz+ra dmar nag gri sdigs mdzub //
NK026(la)001:3311: ral gcig dung khrag gtso bo'i zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3312: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung byang gdon 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3313: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi rdo rje go cha thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3314: rdo rje go cha mthing nag go cha bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3315: khro mo dril 'khror thod khrag dril bu bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3316: byang phyogs sgo srung byang gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK026(la)001:3317: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi rngam chen thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3318: khro bo rngam chen smug nag be con mdzub //
NK026(la)001:3319: khro mo dbang sdud thod khrag zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3320: mthu rtsal che bas bdud dang srin po 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3321: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi tho ba thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3322: rdo rje tho ba dud kha tho ba bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3323: khro mo za byed dung khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:3324: mthu rtsal che bas ma mo gshin rje 'dul //
NK026(la)001:3325: khro bo yab yum dbang badz+ra a b+hi mthong byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3326: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3328: sum brgya drug cu'i gdon bsgral phyir //
NK026(la)001:3329: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:3330: dri za'i dgra gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:3331: 'jigs byed pho nyar sku sprul pa //
NK026(la)001:3332: shar phyogs 'od zer dkar po las //
NK026(la)001:3333: dung gi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK026(la)001:3334: rdo rje 'bar ba'i pho nya mo //
NK026(la)001:3335: dkar mo mthong byed lcags kyu ma //
NK026(la)001:3336: yid kyis phyin cing bsam pas 'grub //
NK026(la)001:3337: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK026(la)001:3338: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah a b+hi sder mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3339: rdo rje sder mo pho nya mo //
NK026(la)001:3341: gar yang thogs med glog 'gyu bas //
NK026(la)001:3342: dbang 'di bu la bskur b+ha na a b+hi k+ai la ya thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3343: pho nya rdo rje k+ai la ya //
NK026(la)001:3344: dkar mo thogs med dmigs gsal ma //
NK026(la)001:3346: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'bigs ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3347: pho nya rdo rje 'bigs pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3348: dkar mo shel gyi mda' 'phel ma //
NK026(la)001:3349: gang la dmigs pa grub byed pa //
NK026(la)001:3350: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi ro langs ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3351: pho nya rdo rje ro langs ma //
NK026(la)001:3352: dkar mo lag na gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3353: mgyogs byed dur khrod mkha' 'gro ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3354: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi drag mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3355: rdo rje pho nya drag mo ma //
NK026(la)001:3356: dkar mo lag na mdung thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3357: gang la basngagasa pa grub byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3358: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi mgyogs byed thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3359: rdo rje pho nya mgyogs pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3360: dkar mo ming sring g.yab mos 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3361: ting 'dzin yid kyi pho nya yi //
NK026(la)001:3362: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gtum mo thogs te pho nya rdo rje gtum mo ni //
NK026(la)001:3364: sgrol byed pho nya tsit+ta yi //
NK026(la)001:3365: dbang 'di dbu la b+ha na a b+hi 'bebs ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3366: rdo rje pho nya 'bebs ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3367: dkar mo gar byed glu len mkhan //
NK026(la)001:3368: las la 'brid pa pho nya yi //
NK026(la)001:3369: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gsal ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3370: rdo rje pho nya gsal ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3371: dkar mo dung phreng klad la bskor //
NK026(la)001:3372: sa ma ya yi khus 'debs ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3373: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi bstod ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3374: rdo rje pho nya bstod ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3375: dkar skya dar dkar g.yab 'dor ma //
NK026(la)001:3376: rgyal bas yon tan cher ston ma //
NK026(la)001:3377: rdo rje pho nya chen mo yi //
NK026(la)001:3378: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'gugs ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3379: rdo rje pho nya 'gugs pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3380: dkar mo bdud kyi snying 'gugs ma //
NK026(la)001:3381: grub par mi 'gyur gang yang med //
NK026(la)001:3382: rdo rje pho nya sku dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:3383: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi thogs med thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3384: rdo rje pho nya thogs pa med //
NK026(la)001:3385: dkar dmar lag na zangs gri 'chang //
NK026(la)001:3386: dpa' bo chen po thogs pa med //
NK026(la)001:3387: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi bskyod ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3388: rdo rje pho nya bskyod ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3389: dkar dmar rlung gi zhags thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3390: rnal 'byor phrin las bskyod byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3391: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'chang bdag mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3392: pho nya rdo rje 'chang bdag mo //
NK026(la)001:3393: dkar dmar 'dzin byed zhags pa ma //
NK026(la)001:3395: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi phra men ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3396: rdo rje pho nya phra men ma //
NK026(la)001:3397: dkar dmar me yi sgron ma khyer //
NK026(la)001:3398: don dang rtags su bcas te 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3399: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi myur byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3400: rdo rje pho nya myur byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3401: dkar dmar glog gi zhags thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3402: gang bzung yid kyis 'debs par byed //
NK026(la)001:3403: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi bskul byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3404: rdo rje pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3406: thugs dam bskul zhing phrin las byed //
NK026(la)001:3407: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gsal bkra mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3408: rdo rje pho nya gsal bkra mo //
NK026(la)001:3409: dkar mo rdo rje zhags 'phen ma //
NK026(la)001:3410: sus kyang mo bzlog thub par dka' //
NK026(la)001:3411: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi yang dag mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3412: rdo rje pho nya yang dag mo //
NK026(la)001:3413: dkar dang dmar gyi lan phran 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3414: khams gsum sa dgu yud kyis khyab //
NK026(la)001:3415: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi chen mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3416: rdo rje pho nya chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:3417: dkar ser rdo rje rtse gcig 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3418: thugs dam dbang gi rtags ston ma //
NK026(la)001:3419: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya mo'i //
NK026(la)001:3420: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gnon mdzad ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3421: rdo rje pho nya gnon mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:3422: dkar ser rdo rje brag 'phen ma //
NK026(la)001:3423: ri rab rtse yang gnon byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3424: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gnon mdzad ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3425: rdo rje pho nya gnon mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:3426: dkar ser rdo rje brag 'phen ma //
NK026(la)001:3427: ri rab rtse yang gnon byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3428: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi dbang phyug ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3429: rdo rje pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:3430: dmar ser tri sh+aul gze mo 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3431: dug gsum nad rnams 'joms byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3432: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi sred mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3433: rdo rje pho nya sred mo ni //
NK026(la)001:3434: dkar ser lcags kyu dmar po thogs //
NK026(la)001:3435: bsdabs pa tsam gyis gang yang khug /
NK026(la)001:3436: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi kha 'bar ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3437: rdo rje pho nya kha 'bar ma //
NK026(la)001:3438: dmar ser sprin gyi go zu can //
NK026(la)001:3439: kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skem //
NK026(la)001:3440: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gsal byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3441: rdo rje pho nya gsal byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3443: gang la bya ba sa ler gsal //
NK026(la)001:3444: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi khro mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3445: rdo rje pho nya khro mo ni //
NK026(la)001:3446: dkar ser khro mo'i gzugs 'chang bas //
NK026(la)001:3447: de bzhin lag na g.yang bzhi bsdeb //
NK026(la)001:3448: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'chang ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3449: rdo rje pho nya 'chang ba ni //
NK026(la)001:3450: dkar ser rdo rje phur bu 'chang //
NK026(la)001:3451: gang la bya ba'i snying la 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3452: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gtum ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3453: rdo rje pho nya gtum pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3454: dmar ser rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3455: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'joms //
NK026(la)001:3456: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi khros ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3457: rdo rje pho nya khros ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3458: dmar ser rdo rje be con 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3459: khro zhing gdod pa dpa' brtul che'i //
NK026(la)001:3460: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi las byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3461: rdo rje pho nya las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3462: dmar ser gcod pa'i ral gri 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3463: sems can skye shi rtsad gcod ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3464: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi dus mtshan ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3465: rdo rje pho nya dus mtshan ma //
NK026(la)001:3466: dmar ser lag na shak+ti thogs //
NK026(la)001:3467: ma lus 'joms pa'i las mdzad ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3468: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi thar pa mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3469: rdo rje pho nya thar pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3470: dmar ser lag na gtun shing thogs //
NK026(la)001:3471: rdul du rlog pa'i las mdzad ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3472: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi rkul ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3473: rdo rje pho nya rkul ma //
NK026(la)001:3474: dmar ser lag na lcags kyu 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3475: ma lus 'dzin pa'i ging chen ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3476: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi dpal 'bar ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3477: rdo rje pho nya dpal 'bar ma //
NK026(la)001:3478: dmar ser ras kyi zhags pa 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3479: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3480: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi bskyod chen ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3481: rdo rje pho nya bskyod chen ma //
NK026(la)001:3482: dmar ser rlung gi rkyal ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3483: bskal pa'i me chen gtong ba yi //
NK026(la)001:3484: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi lus khros ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3485: rdo rje pho nya lus khros ma //
NK026(la)001:3486: dkar ser lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK026(la)001:3487: ba spu sra mkhregs rdo rje'i sku //
NK026(la)001:3488: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi ngag 'phrog ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3489: rdo rje pho nya ngag 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:3490: dmar ser lkugs byed lcags kyu can //
NK026(la)001:3491: smra ba ngag gi lce 'phrog ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3492: dbang 'di pu la b+ha na a b+hi yid gtum ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3493: rdo rje pho nya yid gtum ma //
NK026(la)001:3494: dkar ser sen mos snying 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:3495: thugs rjes bdud srin myos shing rlam //
NK026(la)001:3496: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi sde chen mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3497: rdo rje pho nya sde chen mo //
NK026(la)001:3498: dmar ser ral ba'i g.yab mos 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3499: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing bcu sgrol //
NK026(la)001:3500: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gsod byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3501: rdo rje pho nya gsod byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3502: dkar sngo dung gi zhags pa can //
NK026(la)001:3503: thugs rjes zhing bcu sgrol la brtson //
NK026(la)001:3504: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi rlang pa mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3505: rdo rje pho nya rlangs pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3506: dkar sngo rlung gi zhags pa bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3507: thugs rjes bdud dang srin po sgrol //
NK026(la)001:3508: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gsod ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3509: rdo rje pho na gsod pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3510: dkar sngo shel gyi gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3511: gsod pa'i las la 'ba' zhig dgyes //
NK026(la)001:3512: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi za ba mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3513: rdo rje pho nya za ba mo //
NK026(la)001:3514: dkar sngon m+aam sa zas su za //
NK026(la)001:3515: gti mug gtan nas zad mdzad ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3516: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi khrag 'thung ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3517: rdo rje pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK026(la)001:3519: 'dod chags gtan nas zad mdzad ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3520: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'cha' ba mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3521: rdo rje pho nya 'cha' ba mo //
NK026(la)001:3522: dkar sngo keng rus khral khrol 'cha' //
NK026(la)001:3523: zhe sdang gtan nas zad mdzad ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3524: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi tshe len ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3525: rdo rje pho nya tshe len ma //
NK026(la)001:3526: dkar sngo dar gyis g.yab 'dor bas //
NK026(la)001:3527: sdang ba dgra yi tshe 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:3528: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:3529: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi mdangs len ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3530: rdo rje pho nya mdangs thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3531: rdo rje pho nya mdangs len ma //
NK026(la)001:3532: dkar mo dung gi par bu bsnams //
NK026(la)001:3533: gang la dmigs pa'i mdangs 'phrog ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3534: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi srog 'phrog ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3535: rdo rje pho nya srog 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:3537: skad cig yud la nyams pa len //
NK026(la)001:3538: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi snying 'byin ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3539: rdo rje pho nya snying 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:3540: dkar sngo snying gi phreng ba bgrang //
NK026(la)001:3541: rnam shes phung po gtan stob ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3542: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi gcod byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3543: rdo rje pho nya gcod byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3544: dkar ljang shel gyi dgra s+t+wa 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:3545: rgyud drug 'khor ba brtsad nas bcad //
NK026(la)001:3546: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi bskul byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3547: rdo rje pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3548: dkar mo phyag na lcags kyu can //
NK026(la)001:3549: zhing bcu bsgral nas thugs dam bskul //
NK026(la)001:3550: dbang 'di pu la b+ha na a b+hi sna tshogs gzugs thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3551: rdo rje pho nya sna tshogs gzugs //
NK026(la)001:3552: bse yi ldan dkar zab slog gsol //
NK026(la)001:3553: ma lus sgrol ba'i bya ra ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3554: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi smyon ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3555: rdo rje pho nya smyon ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3556: dkar ljang shel gyi rdo rje 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3557: gzhan gyis mi thub drag shul che //
NK026(la)001:3558: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'jug byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3559: rdo rje pho nya 'jug byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3560: dkar ljang phyag na khra thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3562: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi yid 'phrog ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3563: rdo rje pho nya yid 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:3564: dkar ljang tshon gyi gru gu thags //
NK026(la)001:3566: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi ro rkun ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3567: rdo rje pho nya ro rkun ma //
NK026(la)001:3568: dkar ljang zhing gi ro khur ma //
NK026(la)001:3569: dur khrod bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3570: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi rdzu byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3571: rdo rje pho nya rdzu byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3572: dkar ljang rlung gi zhags pa 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3573: cir yang sprul pa'i sku gcig ma //
NK026(la)001:3574: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi 'jigs byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3575: rdo rje pho nya 'jigs byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3576: dkar ljang dung gi mche ba 'byin //
NK026(la)001:3578: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi bcud len ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3579: rdo rje pho nya bcud len ma //
NK026(la)001:3580: dkar ljang g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK026(la)001:3581: khams gsum tshe sdud pho nya ma //
NK026(la)001:3582: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na a b+hi dbyings phyug ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3583: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:3585: sum brgya drug cu'i gdon bsgral phyir //
NK026(la)001:3586: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:3587: dgra dang gshin rje'i gdon 'dul phyir //
NK026(la)001:3588: 'jigs byed pho nyar sku sprul pa //
NK026(la)001:3589: lho phyogs 'od zer ser po las //
NK026(la)001:3590: gser gyi mi mo drug cu byung //
NK026(la)001:3591: yon tan pho nya dbyings phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:3592: ser nag me yi zhags pa thogs //
NK026(la)001:3593: ci bgyi zhes kyang thogs pa med //
NK026(la)001:3594: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK026(la)001:3595: ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:3598: yon tan pho nya mkha' 'gro ma //
NK026(la)001:3599: ser nag sdigs mdzub gyad dor can //
NK026(la)001:3600: lhag ma len cing sgrub la 'go //
NK026(la)001:3601: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mthu 'bebs ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3602: yon tan pho nya mthu 'bebs ma //
NK026(la)001:3603: dmar ser pa dan g.yab 'dor ma //
NK026(la)001:3604: sgrub pa po la mthu byin 'bebs //
NK026(la)001:3605: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi sra ba mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3606: yon tan pho nya sra ba mo //
NK026(la)001:3607: ser nag rdo rje go gyon pas //
NK026(la)001:3608: cis kyang mi tshugs rdo rje'i sku //
NK026(la)001:3609: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mchongs mo che thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3610: yon tan pho nya mchongs mo che //
NK026(la)001:3611: ser nag mchongs stabs byan lag thogs //
NK026(la)001:3612: ri klungs kun sleb mchongs byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3613: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi khro gtum can thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3614: yon tan pho nya khro gtum can //
NK026(la)001:3615: ser nag sdang mig stag la zhon //
NK026(la)001:3616: dgra bgegs ma lus 'joms byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3617: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi brtson byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3618: yon tan pho nya brtson byed ma /
NK026(la)001:3619: ser nag rlung gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3620: gyen thur med par rgyug cing 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3621: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'jigs gdong ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3622: yon tan pho nya 'jigs gdong ma //
NK026(la)001:3623: kha bgrad mche gtsigs lag gnyis gdengs //
NK026(la)001:3624: stobs chen mthu yang 'joms byed ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3625: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi sha za mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3626: yon tan pho nya sha za mo //
NK026(la)001:3627: mi khog dbyug pa klad la bskor //
NK026(la)001:3628: m+aam sa za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK026(la)001:3629: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi khrag 'thor ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3630: yon tan pho nya khrag 'thor ma //
NK026(la)001:3631: mi mgo'i phor pa rlon pa ru //
NK026(la)001:3632: mi snying khrag zhag blug cing 'thor //
NK026(la)001:3633: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi so gcig thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3634: yon tan pho nya so gcig ma //
NK026(la)001:3635: ser mo kha mig so gcig ma //
NK026(la)001:3636: rdo rje rtse gcig mda' 'phen ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3637: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi ral gsig ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3638: yon tan pho nya ral gsig ma //
NK026(la)001:3639: ser mo ral pa'i go zu can //
NK026(la)001:3640: g.yon sdigs g.yas pa lcags kyu 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3641: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'khril byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3642: yon tan pho nya 'khril byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3643: ser mo sngo dmar zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3644: rdzu ni gnyen dang grung por bardzu //
NK026(la)001:3645: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'dzul byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3646: yon tan pho nya 'dzul byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3647: ser mo gser gyi zangs gri thogs //
NK026(la)001:3648: rdzu ni sbrul dang sre mor bardzu //
NK026(la)001:3649: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi myur byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3650: yon tan pho nya myur byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3651: ser mo tshon gyi gru gu thogs //
NK026(la)001:3652: rdzu ni 'ug pa srin byar bardzu //
NK026(la)001:3653: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mthu chen ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3654: yon tan pho nya mthu chen mo //
NK026(la)001:3655: ser mo thog gi char 'bebs ma //
NK026(la)001:3656: gnam sa ri klung kun tu khyab //
NK026(la)001:3657: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi nag mo thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3658: yon tan pho nya nag mo ni //
NK026(la)001:3659: nag mo ral pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3660: khams gsum b+h+yo dang khus 'debs ma //
NK026(la)001:3661: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi rtog 'joms ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3662: yon tan pho nya rtog 'joms ma //
NK026(la)001:3663: ser mo b+han+d+ha rlon pa ru //
NK026(la)001:3664: dam rdzas rnam lnga za zhing spyod //
NK026(la)001:3665: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi rtog med ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3666: yon tan pho nya rtog med ma //
NK026(la)001:3667: ser mo dung gi gzhong thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3668: gang la bcol yang tshig cing khro //
NK026(la)001:3669: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi yangs ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3670: yon tan pho nya yangs pa ma //
NK026(la)001:3671: ser mo sprin gyis ga sha can //
NK026(la)001:3672: glog gi phreng ba klad la bskor //
NK026(la)001:3673: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi sna tshogs lus thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3674: yon tan pho nya sna tshogs lus //
NK026(la)001:3675: dmar skya za 'og stod g.yogs can //
NK026(la)001:3676: rnga mo gwa par rdzu byed pa //
NK026(la)001:3677: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi sdang mig ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3678: yon tan pho nya sdang mig gam //
NK026(la)001:3679: dmar skya lcags kyi khra thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3680: dgra dang bgegs la glag ltar 'jums //
NK026(la)001:3681: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi dur khrod ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3682: yon tan pho nya dur khrod ma //
NK026(la)001:3683: dmar skya zhing gi g.yang gzhi bsdeb //
NK026(la)001:3684: mkhas pas dgra bgegs sgrol byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3685: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mig 'gro ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3686: yon tan pho nya mig 'gro ma //
NK026(la)001:3687: khyung la zhon cing glog zhags 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3688: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'grub //
NK026(la)001:3689: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi bde 'gro ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3690: yon tan pho nya bde 'gro ma //
NK026(la)001:3691: 'phyong gi bya glag dmar mo zhon //
NK026(la)001:3692: ser mo g.yu yi zor ba 'debs //
NK026(la)001:3693: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi rgyas byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3694: yon tan pho nya rgyas byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3696: tshe dang phung por bcas pa 'joms //
NK026(la)001:3697: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'dzum byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3698: yon tan pho nya 'dzum byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3699: ser skya tshon gyi gru gu brdog /
NK026(la)001:3700: rdzu ni bu chung spre'ura bardzu //
NK026(la)001:3701: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi khrag myos ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3702: yon tan pho nya khrag myos ma //
NK026(la)001:3703: dmar mo mchu ring dur bya'i gdong //
NK026(la)001:3704: rtsa la rgyu zhing snying khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:3705: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi rngam tshig ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3706: yon tan pho nya rngam tshig ma //
NK026(la)001:3707: mngags shing bcol ba'i las mchis na //
NK026(la)001:3708: rang la rang yang tshig cing khro //
NK026(la)001:3709: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mgyogs byed ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:3710: yon tan pho nya mgyogs byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3711: ser skya mgyogs byed rlung la zhon //
NK026(la)001:3712: gar yang mi gtong mthu mi che'o //
NK026(la)001:3713: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi gtum pa mo thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3714: yon tan pho nya gtum pa mo //
NK026(la)001:3715: dmar ser spu gris snying 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:3716: nyams pa'i dgra bgegs nyal thag gcod //
NK026(la)001:3717: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mdung thung ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3718: yon tan pho nya mdung thung 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3719: dkar ser g.yon sder g.yas mdung 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3720: bdud dang srin po tshar gcod ma //
NK026(la)001:3721: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi glog 'gyu ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3722: yon tan pho nya glog 'gyu ma //
NK026(la)001:3723: dmar ser glog gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3724: nam mkha'i mthongs nas 'grim ste rgyug /
NK026(la)001:3725: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi thog 'bebs ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3726: yon tan pho nya thog 'bebs ma //
NK026(la)001:3727: dmar ser thog gi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK026(la)001:3728: rgya mtsho gting yang skem par byed //
NK026(la)001:3729: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi spor byed ma thogs la //
NK026(la)001:3730: yon tan pho nya spor byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3731: dmar ser zhing chen zhal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:3732: zhing chung gtan nas len byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3733: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'khrug byed ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3734: yon tan pho nya 'khrug byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3735: ri rab rtse nas 'joms byed cing //
NK026(la)001:3737: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi dbang phyug ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3738: yon tan pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:3739: smug nag dur khrod khrag 'thung ma //
NK026(la)001:3740: sgrol byed snying 'byin gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:3741: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi k+aa ma la thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3742: yon tan pho nya k+aa ma la //
NK026(la)001:3743: mdzub mos ri rab rtse la g.yeng //
NK026(la)001:3744: rkang pas rgya mtsho'i gting nas 'khrug /
NK026(la)001:3745: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi gsal bkra ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3746: yon tan pho nya gsal bkra ma //
NK026(la)001:3747: dmar ser nyi zla zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3748: gang ltar song yang mi gtong zhing //
NK026(la)001:3749: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi kha bsgyur ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3750: yon tan pho nya kha bsgyur ma //
NK026(la)001:3751: dmar ser dung gi rgo ba zhon //
NK026(la)001:3752: ri klungs med par rjes kyis 'geng //
NK026(la)001:3753: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi kun sgrol ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3754: yon tan pho nya kun sgrol ma //
NK026(la)001:3755: dmar ljang ral gri klad la bskor //
NK026(la)001:3756: so bya sram dang chu byar sprul //
NK026(la)001:3757: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi myos byed ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3758: yon tan pho nya myos byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3759: dmar ljang ra ro smyo rdzu can //
NK026(la)001:3760: dkar dmar snying gi mtshams nas 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3761: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi khrag 'thung ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3762: yon tan pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK026(la)001:3763: dmar ljang thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:3765: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'bar ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3766: yon tan pho nya 'bar ma ni //
NK026(la)001:3767: dmar ljang rin chen 'bar ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:3769: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi mi zad ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3770: yon tan pho nya mi zad ma //
NK026(la)001:3771: gnam sa gnyis kyang thags su 'thag /
NK026(la)001:3772: skye 'chi gnyis kyang rtsa ba gcod //
NK026(la)001:3773: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi 'phrog byed ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3774: yon tan pho nya 'phrog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3777: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi sgrol byed ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3778: rin chen pho nya sgrol byed ma //
NK026(la)001:3780: ma lus sgrol ba'i mthu mo che //
NK026(la)001:3781: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi sna tshogs stob ma thogs la //
NK026(la)001:3782: yon tan pho nya sna tshogs stob //
NK026(la)001:3783: ser ljang zhing gi rkang lag 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:3784: dug gsum ma lus zhal du stob //
NK026(la)001:3785: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi yid 'phrog ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3786: yon tan pho nya yid 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:3787: ser ljang na chung tshul du bardzu //
NK026(la)001:3789: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi srog len ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3790: yon tan pho nya srog len ma //
NK026(la)001:3791: mi snying brgyus pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3792: zhing bcu gtan nas len par byed //
NK026(la)001:3793: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi bcud len ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3794: yon tan pho nya bcud len ma //
NK026(la)001:3795: ser smug zangs kyi mchu rings ma //
NK026(la)001:3797: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi tshe 'dzin ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3798: yon tan pho nya tshe rkun ma //
NK026(la)001:3799: bse yi ga'u dmar po nas //
NK026(la)001:3800: dzahdamara pho nyas tshe rkun ma'i //
NK026(la)001:3801: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi dbang mo che thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3802: yon tan pho nya dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:3803: ser smug seng ge dkar mo zon //
NK026(la)001:3804: nyi zla brgyus pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:3805: dbang 'di bu la ha la a b+hi dregs 'joms ma thogs la /
NK026(la)001:3806: yon tan pho nya dregs 'joms ma //
NK026(la)001:3808: myur ba'i shugs 'chang thugs rje che //

NK026(la)001:4102: ljang ser khrag gi phor pa thogs //
NK026(la)001:4103: ma thogs las la myur byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4104: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya phag mgo ma //
NK026(la)001:4105: ljang ser phag mgo tho ba 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:4106: che chung med par rdul du rlog /
NK026(la)001:4107: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya spyan brgya ma //
NK026(la)001:4108: mgo lus med par mig gis gang //
NK026(la)001:4109: stong khams ma lus gsal zhing bkra //
NK026(la)001:4110: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya mig stong ldan //
NK026(la)001:4111: dbu stong phyag stong spyan yang stong //
NK026(la)001:4112: stong gsum stong pa dbang cher grags //
NK026(la)001:4113: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya 'od mgyogs ma //
NK026(la)001:4115: bltas pas mi mngon gang yang med //
NK026(la)001:4116: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rlung zhon ma //
NK026(la)001:4117: lag na lcags kyi dgra s+t+wa ljang //
NK026(la)001:4118: rlung nag 'tshubs ma chibs su chibs //
NK026(la)001:4119: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rdzu 'phrul can //
NK026(la)001:4120: sbrul nag stong gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK026(la)001:4121: ltas ngan rnga mong gwa pa zhon //
NK026(la)001:4122: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rgyu ba mo //
NK026(la)001:4123: cir yang ma nges gzugs su ston //
NK026(la)001:4124: ched 'ga' chu srin sbrul gyi lus //
NK026(la)001:4125: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya dbang phyug rgyal //
NK026(la)001:4126: ljang ser mdung rtse gsum pa 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:4127: dug gsum rtsad nas len byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4128: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya grags rgyal ma //
NK026(la)001:4129: ljang nag stag zhon dred kyi mgo //
NK026(la)001:4131: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya dpal sham ma //

NK026(la)001:4133: khrag gi gtor ma zhags par 'phen //
NK026(la)001:4134: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi las kyi pho nya yak+sha mo //
NK026(la)001:4135: ljang nag gnod sbyin mgo bo thogs //
NK026(la)001:4136: gang la bya bar thod zor 'phen //
NK026(la)001:4137: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya khro bag can //
NK026(la)001:4138: bud med gzugs la skyes pa'i mgo //
NK026(la)001:4140: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya che ba mo //
NK026(la)001:4141: lag gnyis rdo rje mche ba 'debs //
NK026(la)001:4142: bzung bas mi zin gang yang med //
NK026(la)001:4143: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya dbang bskur ma //
NK026(la)001:4144: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya can //
NK026(la)001:4145: kun gyi mnga' bdag dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:4146: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya dngos grub bdag /
NK026(la)001:4147: ljang nag 'dod spyod lnga la rol //
NK026(la)001:4148: dngos grub rnam gsum dus 'dir rtsol //
NK026(la)001:4149: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya sgrol byed che //
NK026(la)001:4150: ljang nag gcod pa'i phal tshab bsnams //
NK026(la)001:4151: gang yang gson par mi byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4152: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya mnga' bdag mo //
NK026(la)001:4153: srid gsum grags pa'i rnge'u chung brdung //
NK026(la)001:4154: ma lus gdug pa zil gyis gnon //
NK026(la)001:4155: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya 'od 'phro ma //
NK026(la)001:4156: ljang nag gcod pa'i shak+ti thogs //
NK026(la)001:4157: srid gsum gsal ba'i 'od mnga' ma //
NK026(la)001:4158: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya drag mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4159: ljang smug gru gsum mthing nag thogs //
NK026(la)001:4160: drag po las kyi pho nya mo //
NK026(la)001:4161: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya khro rkyen ma //
NK026(la)001:4162: ljang smug ral pa sa la sdeb //
NK026(la)001:4163: rang la rang yang tshig cing khro //
NK026(la)001:4164: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya myur grub ma //
NK026(la)001:4165: 'jam dpal rnon po lag na thogs //
NK026(la)001:4166: ha ha ru lu'i sgra sgrog ma'i //
NK026(la)001:4167: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya chud mi za //
NK026(la)001:4168: ljang smug rin chen sgron ma thogs //
NK026(la)001:4169: gdung bas brtse zhing phan 'dogs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:4170: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi las kyi pho nya 'dul byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4171: ljang smug srin po'i thod pa thogs //
NK026(la)001:4172: khyod kyis mi 'dul gang yang med //
NK026(la)001:4173: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rgya mtsho ma //
NK026(la)001:4174: sna tshogs lus can rgya mtsho rlog /

NK026(la)001:4176: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi las kyi pho nya ltung 'dzin ma //
NK026(la)001:4177: sems can zhing bcu bsgral ba la //
NK026(la)001:4178: dmyal bar ltung nges lcags kyus 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4179: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya sgrol byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4181: rdul du rlog pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:4182: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rang dbang mo //
NK026(la)001:4183: ljang nag g.yu yi zhags pa 'debs //
NK026(la)001:4184: 'jig rten las kyi gnyen cig ma //
NK026(la)001:4185: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya 'dul mkhan ma //
NK026(la)001:4186: skyes bu na chung gzugs 'chang ma //
NK026(la)001:4187: ji lta dmigs pa bzhin du 'dul //
NK026(la)001:4188: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi las kyi pho nya goms pa mo //
NK026(la)001:4189: ljang gu yungs kar mda' 'phen ma //
NK026(la)001:4190: dkar nag snying gi mtshams su brdeg /
NK026(la)001:4191: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya las mkhan ma //
NK026(la)001:4192: ljang skya mtshe yi zor 'phen ma //
NK026(la)001:4193: log pa'i phyogs rnams bzlog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4194: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya dbang sgyur ma //
NK026(la)001:4195: nyi zla gza' skar slog par gyon //
NK026(la)001:4196: 'dzam bu gling bzhi lag par thogs //
NK026(la)001:4197: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya mchog sgrol ma //
NK026(la)001:4199: skye shi gnyis kyi rtsad gcod ma //
NK026(la)001:4200: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rgyug 'dzin ma //
NK026(la)001:4201: thugs dam gnyan po rgyud bskul phyir //
NK026(la)001:4202: shel dang lung thang yu bu bsnams //
NK026(la)001:4203: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya rngam pa mo //
NK026(la)001:4204: ljang skya sha khrag rlon par za //
NK026(la)001:4205: gsod pa'i las la shin tu rngams //
NK026(la)001:4206: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi las kyi phyag rgya spro rkyen ma //
NK026(la)001:4207: ljang skya 'debs pa'i las la myur //
NK026(la)001:4208: dza dza ho ho'i sgra 'debs ma //
NK026(la)001:4209: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya gtum chen ma //
NK026(la)001:4211: gtum pas 'dod khams lha mi btsan //
NK026(la)001:4212: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi las kyi pho nya mig dmar ma //
NK026(la)001:4213: khrag gi chang gis myos par byed //
NK026(la)001:4214: mig rtsa dmar la ra gdong che /
NK026(la)001:4215: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi phrin las pho nya sen mo can //
NK026(la)001:4216: dmar smug sen mo lcags kyus gtams //
NK026(la)001:4217: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'dzin byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4218: dbang 'di bu la pa tsa a b+hi dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK026(la)001:4220: sum brgya drug cu'i gdon bsgral phyir //
NK026(la)001:4221: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:4222: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kyi //
NK026(la)001:4223: dgra dang 'byung po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4224: sku yi 'od zer smug nag las //
NK026(la)001:4225: las byed ma mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:4226: ral pa gcig ma mthing kha 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK026(la)001:4227: tri shu ral gri dril bu nad rkyal thogs //
NK026(la)001:4228: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK026(la)001:4230: a b+hi sbas pa'i ma mo thal mdog thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:4231: g.yang gzhi dur khrod rgyan gyis mdzes par klubs //
NK026(la)001:4232: srid pa gsum na mthu chen rtsal drag pa //
NK026(la)001:4233: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma ma a b+hi dur khrod tshogs kyi ma mo ral pa can //
NK026(la)001:4234: mi thod phreng bas sku brgyan rab tu brjid //
NK026(la)001:4235: khams gsum 'di na mthu chen 'gran zla med //
NK026(la)001:4236: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma ma a b+hi za byed rngam pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4237: mthing skya khrag gi ral pa gos su byon //
NK026(la)001:4238: phyag gis skye 'gro yongs kyi tsit+ta bzung //
NK026(la)001:4239: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma ma a b+hi khams gsum sdud pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4240: dmar mo thod khrag skom du 'thung byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4241: nga rgyal dregs pa'i 'khor yang 'joms byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4242: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma ma a b+hi rgyud drug sgrol ba'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4243: smug nag me 'bar g.yang gzhi gos su gyon //
NK026(la)001:4244: mi snying brgyas pa'i phreng ba klad la bskor //
NK026(la)001:4245: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma ma a b+hi srid gsum za bar byed pa'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4246: dmar nag gnam sa gnyis kyang gos su gyon //
NK026(la)001:4247: bdud dang srin po'i tshogs rnams 'dar zhing 'dud //
NK026(la)001:4248: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma ma a b+hi srid gsum yongs la dbang sgyur ma //
NK026(la)001:4249: ser nag nyi zla thod du bcings //
NK026(la)001:4250: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4251: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:4252: ma ma a b+hi mthu rtsal bsnyems pa'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4253: ljang nag zhing gi go zu gyon //
NK026(la)001:4254: lag pa g.yas pas nam mkha' 'degs //
NK026(la)001:4255: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang ma ma a b+hi khros ma khrag 'thung gsur la dga' //
NK026(la)001:4256: mi sha rta sha zas su za //
NK026(la)001:4257: mi khrag rta khrag skom du 'thung //
NK026(la)001:4258: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang ma ma a b+hi sgrol byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4259: mthing nag nang rol glo snying 'byin //
NK026(la)001:4260: phrin las dam nyams sgrol la brtson //
NK026(la)001:4261: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang ma ma a b+hi za byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4262: tshe srog 'phrog pa'i ma mo ste //
NK026(la)001:4263: sngo nag g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK026(la)001:4264: nyams pa len cing sgrub pa ston //
NK026(la)001:4265: ma mo'i dbang 'di bu la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4266: ma ma a b+hi rngam byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4267: 'phyo la dga' ba'i ma mo ste //
NK026(la)001:4268: nam mkha' 'brug sngon chibs su chibs //
NK026(la)001:4269: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:4271: a b+hi 'dzin byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4272: 'jigs byed zhal du btab pa'i ma //
NK026(la)001:4273: ser nag thod khrag lcags kyu thogs //
NK026(la)001:4274: ma lus sgrol ba'i zhing chen mo //
NK026(la)001:4275: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi bgegs chen 'joms pa'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4276: snying la 'debs pa'i ma mo ste //
NK026(la)001:4277: sngo nag spu gri tho ba thogs //
NK026(la)001:4278: bgegs kyi rgyal po'i snying la 'debs //
NK026(la)001:4279: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi zhing bcu bsgral ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4280: ljang nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:4281: 'jig rten khams kyi dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:4282: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi chad pas gcod pa'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4283: sngo nag zhing gi g.yang gzhi sdeb //
NK026(la)001:4284: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK026(la)001:4285: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi 'byung po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4287: shar gyi phyogs kyi las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4288: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi gshin rje sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4289: b+han+d+ha gri thogs gshin rje sgrol //
NK026(la)001:4290: lho yi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4291: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi nub phyogs klu sgrol chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4292: b+han+d+ha gri thogs klu chen sgrol //
NK026(la)001:4293: nub kyi phyogs kyi las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4294: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi gnod sbyin sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4295: ljang nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:4296: byang gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4297: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi srin mo sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4298: sngo nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:4299: steng gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4300: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi srin mo sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4301: smug nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK026(la)001:4302: 'og gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4303: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi gzugs la mnga' mdzad dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:4304: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa bsnams //
NK026(la)001:4305: dgra bo'i gzugs rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4306: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi khrag la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4307: sngon mo thod khrag dkrug cing gsol //
NK026(la)001:4308: dgra bo'i khrag rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4309: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi drod la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4310: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta thogs //
NK026(la)001:4311: sdang ba dgra yi drod 'phrog ma //
NK026(la)001:4312: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi dbugs la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4313: ljang nag thod khrag zhags pa thogs //
NK026(la)001:4314: dgra yi dbugs rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4315: ma mo'i dbang ma ma a b+hi bkrag la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4316: ser na ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:4317: dgra yi mdangs rnams 'jib byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4318: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi srog la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4319: smug nag gri dang thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:4320: dgra yi srog rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4321: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo khrag 'thung bya rgod mgo //
NK026(la)001:4322: ser ljang ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:4323: 'jig rten khyab pa'i mthu mo che //
NK026(la)001:4324: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo za byed stag gi mgo //
NK026(la)001:4325: dmar ser thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:4327: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo 'jigs byed chu srin mgo //
NK026(la)001:4328: sha khrag gsur la dga' byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4330: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo chen mo dur khrod rgyan //
NK026(la)001:4331: mi lpags rlon pa na bzar gsol //
NK026(la)001:4332: dur khrod bgegs chen 'dul mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:4333: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi rdo rje gar gyi dbang mo che //
NK026(la)001:4334: dbu brgya spyan stong kun la khyab //
NK026(la)001:4335: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen ma //
NK026(la)001:4336: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK026(la)001:4337: lag na mi mgo'i phor pa ru //
NK026(la)001:4338: mi snying tshil bus bkang zhing gsol //
NK026(la)001:4339: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi sa bdag chen mo pad+ma phreng //
NK026(la)001:4340: dmar nag b+han+d+ha khrag gis bkang //
NK026(la)001:4341: mig rtsa dmar zhing rngam pa che //
NK026(la)001:4342: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi srid pa gsum gyi mnga' bdag mo //
NK026(la)001:4343: ri rab rtse nas bsnyil byed cing //
NK026(la)001:4344: rgya mtsho gting nas rnyog byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4345: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi rgya mtsho gting gi dbang mo che //

NK026(la)001:4347: sbrul nag stong gi gdengs ka can //
NK026(la)001:4348: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo
NK026(la)001:4349: rdo rje tho ba ma sngo nag mi bsrun tho
NK026(la)001:4350: ba thogs // srin mo'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhing g.yo //
NK026(la)001:4351: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NK026(la)001:4352: mthing nag dgra bo gtun du brdung //

NK026(la)001:4356: gdug pa'i tshogs kyang 'joms par byed //
NK026(la)001:4357: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo rdo rje gdengs pa mo //
NK026(la)001:4358: sngo nag rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK026(la)001:4359: gdug cing gtum pa'i drag shul che //
NK026(la)001:4360: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo rdo rje gsal bkra ma //
NK026(la)001:4361: dmar nag mi yi rgyu zhags 'phen //
NK026(la)001:4363: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo rdo rje khrag 'thung ma //
NK026(la)001:4366: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo nag mo dred zhon ma //
NK026(la)001:4367: nad kyi rkyal pa gong du btags //
NK026(la)001:4368: tshon gyi gru gu klad la bskor //
NK026(la)001:4369: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi dus bzhi'i rgyal mo mthu mo che //
NK026(la)001:4370: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing //
NK026(la)001:4371: cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK026(la)001:4372: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo gnas yul spyang ki'i mgo //
NK026(la)001:4373: mi sha za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK026(la)001:4374: bltas pas bdud rnams rlag byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4375: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo rdzu byed stag dang dom //
NK026(la)001:4376: gcan gzan gdug pa'i gzugs su sprul //
NK026(la)001:4377: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK026(la)001:4378: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo 'joms byed pho nya ma //
NK026(la)001:4379: khra ltar 'jums shing khyi ltar zug /
NK026(la)001:4380: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis len //
NK026(la)001:4381: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo gnam sa phyed kyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:4382: ri klungs med pa gzugs kyis khebs //
NK026(la)001:4383: che chung med par 'joms par byed //
NK026(la)001:4384: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo pho nya rgyug byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4385: bud med lus la 'ja' tshon gos //
NK026(la)001:4386: bang ni ri klungs med par rgyug /
NK026(la)001:4387: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi ma mo pho nya za byed ma //
NK026(la)001:4388: bud med lus la stag gi mgo //
NK026(la)001:4389: zas su gtsang rme med par za //
NK026(la)001:4390: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi rdo rje ya byin pho nya mo //
NK026(la)001:4391: dkar khra lcags kyu phur bu 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4392: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK026(la)001:4393: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi rdo rje bse byin rtsal mo che //
NK026(la)001:4394: sngo nag zhags pa phur bu thogs //
NK026(la)001:4395: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK026(la)001:4396: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi rdo rje phag byin thogs pa med //
NK026(la)001:4397: dmar nag lcags sgrog phur bu thogs //
NK026(la)001:4398: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK026(la)001:4399: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi rdo rje de byin dbang grub ma //
NK026(la)001:4400: ljang nag dril bu phur bu 'phen //
NK026(la)001:4401: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK026(la)001:4402: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi sa bdag rgyal mo chen mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4403: ser nag gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK026(la)001:4404: tshe srog kun la dbang sgyur ma //
NK026(la)001:4405: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi phyi 'khor skyong ba'i mnga' bdag mo //
NK026(la)001:4406: rgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK026(la)001:4407: gnas ni g.ya' ri gangs la gnas //
NK026(la)001:4408: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi 'phrog sring rnams kyi rje mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4409: bud med bzang sdug 'od chags ma /
NK026(la)001:4410: skra bshis ral pa gyen du mdzes /
NK026(la)001:4411: ma mo'i dbang 'di ma ma a b+hi khro tshig myur ba'i ma mo ni //
NK026(la)001:4412: bud med khrag gi ral pa can //
NK026(la)001:4413: nag mo lag na thod pa thogs //
NK026(la)001:4414: ma mo'i 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:4416: a b+hi h+aum chen mthing skya 'khor lo thod dbyug thogs //
NK026(la)001:4417: sgra 'byin gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4418: phrin las nyi zla'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4419: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la bskur bar bya //
NK026(la)001:4420: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4422: kro d+hi shwa r+ai sha ya bya h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:4424: rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje rtse lnga zhing dbyug 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:4425: mda' snyems gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4426: phrin las dri za'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4427: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4428: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:4429: kri b+ai shwa r+aa l+aa s+ya ke h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4430: a b+hi dbyug sngon sngo skya me dbal drang srong 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4431: sder mo gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4432: phrin las drang srong gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4433: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4434: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:4435: kro d+hi shwa r+ai pra ti dza h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4436: a b+hi gshed po ser nag be con gshin rje 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4437: dur khrod gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4438: phrin las gshin rje'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4439: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4440: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:4441: kro d+hi shwa r+ai ta na ba ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4442: a b+hi mi g.yo ljang sngon ral gri srin po 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4443: gtun khung gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4444: phrin las srin po'igadona tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4445: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4447: kro d+hi shwa r+ai mu ha la h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4448: a b+hi rta mgrin dmar nag zhing dbyug khyung gshog 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4449: gtum mo gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4450: phrin las klu yi gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4451: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4452: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:4453: kro d+hi shwa r+ai tsan+da d+ha ri pa ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4454: a b+hi dpal ldan dmar ljang ba dan rlung lha 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4455: mda' snyems gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4456: phrin las rlung lha'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4457: skal ldan badz+ra a pa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4459: kro d+hi shwa r+ai sha ya bya h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4460: a b+hi bdud rtsi ljang nag n+rir mgo dbyug to 'phyar //
NK026(la)001:4461: rlung 'byin gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4462: phrin las gnod sbyin gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4463: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4465: kro d+hi shwa r+ai ya ba ti h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4466: a b+hi rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje 'byung po 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:4467: gsod ma gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4468: phrin las 'byung po'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4469: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dza ya h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4471: kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma h+aa m+aa ra na h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4472: a b+hi stobs chen dud kha thong gshol tir dbyug thogs //
NK026(la)001:4473: bskyod ma gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK026(la)001:4474: phrin las sa bdag gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4475: skal ldan badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4476: s+pho ta s+pho ta ya h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:4477: kro d+hi shwa r+ai k+shi b+hi na h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4479: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi byin gyis rlabs kyis /
NK026(la)001:4480: rigs kyi bu la phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog 'di bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4481: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK026(la)001:4482: lung a nu yo ga dang /
NK026(la)001:4483: man ngag a ti yo ga'i zhi khro rab 'byams
NK026(la)001:4484: kyi sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK026(la)001:4486: brgyad pa ye shes lnga'i dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:4487: thod pa'i dbu rgyan mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtugs /
NK026(la)001:4488: bum chu dang sh+au nya t+aa brjod cing /
NK026(la)001:4489: ye shes chen po'i don dang de ldan pas //
NK026(la)001:4490: ye shes lnga yi rtags mchog phyag rgya yis //
NK026(la)001:4491: gnas lnga rab tu gtugs te thugs kyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4492: sh+au nya t+aa dang a b+hi zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK026(la)001:4493: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:4497: kri t+y+aa nu sh+tha na sogs kyi mthar /
NK026(la)001:4499: brjod cing bum chus kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:4501: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4502: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad gnas su dag nas
NK026(la)001:4503: ye shes lnga'i don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa dgu
NK026(la)001:4504: pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:4506: sku gsung thugs dang rdo rje yi //
NK026(la)001:4507: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK026(la)001:4508: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las dbang //
NK026(la)001:4509: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4510: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta gu na karma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4512: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4513: rigs lnga'i yon tan mtha' dag thob pa'i dbang dam pa rigs gsum gyi sku thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4515: sku gsung thugs dang rdo rje yi //
NK026(la)001:4516: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK026(la)001:4517: bde gshegs rnams kyi sku yi dbang //
NK026(la)001:4518: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4519: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:4521: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la bde bar gshegs pa'i sku yis byin gyis rlabs pas /
NK026(la)001:4522: rdo rje'i sku'i dbang dam pa +aahh+aum /
NK026(la)001:4523: sku gsung thugs rnal 'byor bde mchog bde gshegs rnams kyi gsung gi dbang //
NK026(la)001:4524: rdo rje can la sbyin sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra na mo /
NK026(la)001:4525: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung gis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK026(la)001:4526: rdo rje gsung gi dbang dam pa +aahh+aum /
NK026(la)001:4527: sku gsung thugs dang rnal 'byor bde mchog bde gshegs rnams kyi thugs kyi dbang //
NK026(la)001:4528: rdo rje can la sbyin sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK026(la)001:4529: ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK026(la)001:4531: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK026(la)001:4532: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang dam pa de dag gis
NK026(la)001:4533: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dang sku
NK026(la)001:4534: gsung thugs kyi dbang thob pas /
NK026(la)001:4535: dug lnga ye shes lnga sgo gsum sku gsung thugs su gyur par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:4536: bcu pa bkra shis rtags kyi dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:4537: dbang mchog thob pa'i bu de yis //
NK026(la)001:4538: don rnams grub pa'i bkra shis phyir //
NK026(la)001:4539: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK026(la)001:4540: rtags kyis brgyan te sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4541: dpal chen thugs kyi sa bon ni //
NK026(la)001:4542: 'dren pa rnams kyi thugs lags pas //
NK026(la)001:4543: bla med thar lam drang ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4544: thugs dpal be'u'i bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:4545: ston la bdud kyis bsdoms pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:4546: thugs dpal be'ura bkra shis gyur //
NK026(la)001:4547: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yis //
NK026(la)001:4548: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4549: dpal gyi be'u thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4550: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:4551: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK026(la)001:4552: thugs ka nyid las mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK026(la)001:4553: 'khor lo bkra shis phyag zhabs mtha' //
NK026(la)001:4554: skyob pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK026(la)001:4555: nyon mongs sems can dman pa'i gsos //
NK026(la)001:4556: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i bkra ston pa bdud dmag drangs pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:4557: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i de ring khyod la chos 'khor
NK026(la)001:4558: bskor ba'i gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i
NK026(la)001:4559: phyogs rnams kun las phyag zhabs mthing las mngon par
NK026(la)001:4560: gsung mchog pad+ma chos kyi rgyal //
NK026(la)001:4561: nyon mongs ma gos pad+ma'i sku //
NK026(la)001:4562: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsung lags te //
NK026(la)001:4563: ljags mchog pad+ma'i ston la bdud dmag ljags nyid pad+ma'i
NK026(la)001:4564: de ring khyod la cis kyang dgos med dbang ljags
NK026(la)001:4565: nyid pad+ma dgos pa med pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4566: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams
NK026(la)001:4567: kun las ljags kyi mchog las mngon par mi nub
NK026(la)001:4569: thams cad bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK026(la)001:4570: dpung bcoms sangs rgyas sku bstod de //
NK026(la)001:4571: sku mchog rgyal mtshan ston la bdud kyis sku ni
NK026(la)001:4572: rgyal mtshan de ring khyod la bdud las rgyal ba'i
NK026(la)001:4573: / rgyal mtshan gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags //
NK026(la)001:4574: bsngo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las sku yi mchog las
NK026(la)001:4575: mngon par bkra shis bum pa pad+ma'i dbang bcom ldan
NK026(la)001:4577: mgur mchog bkra shis 'di byin pas //
NK026(la)001:4578: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:4579: ston la bdud kyis mgur nyid bum par de ring
NK026(la)001:4580: khyod la snying rjes 'dzin pa'i dbang mgur chu thugs
NK026(la)001:4582: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams
NK026(la)001:4583: kun las mgur gyi mchog las mngon par gdugs kyis
NK026(la)001:4584: bdud kyis dbu skra gdugs su de ring khyod la
NK026(la)001:4585: gdung ba bsal ba'i dbang dbu skra gdung ba sel
NK026(la)001:4587: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i phyogs kun
NK026(la)001:4588: rnams kun las dbu skra'i mchog la mngon par snyan
NK026(la)001:4589: pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrog pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4590: mu stegs log pa'i phyogs rnams skrag pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4591: sems can kun gyi shes pa'i rgyud gsal phyir //
NK026(la)001:4592: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal po'i bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:4593: ston la bdud kyis gsung ni dung du de ring
NK026(la)001:4594: khyod la rgol ba dpa' bkong dbang dung gis rgol
NK026(la)001:4596: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams
NK026(la)001:4597: kun las gsung gi mchog las mngon par phyag zhabs
NK026(la)001:4599: mdzes snyoms yid 'ong kun gyi dpal //
NK026(la)001:4600: nywa sha bkra shis gser nyar shog /
NK026(la)001:4601: ston la bdud kyis phyag zhabs nywa bzhi gser de
NK026(la)001:4602: ring khyod la 'khor ba'i nyam nga med par shog
NK026(la)001:4603: / phyag zhabs nywa bzhis don mdzad dbang //
NK026(la)001:4604: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams
NK026(la)001:4605: kun nywa sha bzhi las mngon par 'di ni gser
NK026(la)001:4606: nya dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK026(la)001:4607: bcu gcig pa thig le ming gi dbang gi /
NK026(la)001:4608: rnam snang gi sku thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4609: don rnams grub pa'i bu mchog ste //
NK026(la)001:4610: rdo rje dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:4611: zhing khams kun tu bsgrags pa yi //
NK026(la)001:4612: rtsal gyi thig le rdo rje sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4613: zhes thig le rtsal gyi ming gdags so //
NK026(la)001:4614: skabs 'dir khro bo dang mthun pa'i ming yang rigs lnga'i 'gres sbyar te gdams pa'am /
NK026(la)001:4615: yang na thig le rdzogs pa rtsal /
NK026(la)001:4617: de bzhin du thig le kun 'byung rtsal /
NK026(la)001:4623: de bzhin du thogs mar thig le dang /
NK026(la)001:4646: thig le yon tan rtsal sogs gdags so //
NK026(la)001:4648: phyogs bcu skal ldan rigs kyi bu la don dang mi 'gal ba'i ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4649: thams cad 'dus pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4651: des nang dbang bcu gcig rdzogs so //
NK026(la)001:4652: de nas sgrub dbang bcu gsum la /
NK026(la)001:4653: dang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang /
NK026(la)001:4654: gnyis pa khams gsum byang chub sems kyi /
NK026(la)001:4656: bzhi pa 'gro don rdzogs byed thong gshol gyi /
NK026(la)001:4657: lnga pa dug gsum gtan nas sprul pa thod pa tshar gsum gyi /
NK026(la)001:4658: drug pa nyon mongs gcod pa mtshon cha'i /
NK026(la)001:4659: bdun pa spyod bzhin ma chags pa pad+ma'i /
NK026(la)001:4660: brgyad pa rnam bzhi las rdzogs ti ra dbyug pa'i /
NK026(la)001:4661: dgu pa don dam dbyer med sbrul nag chun po'i /
NK026(la)001:4662: bcu pa gnyis med mdo sbyor rtags lha mo yum gyi /
NK026(la)001:4663: bcu gcig pa bdag nyid chen po longs spyod sna tshogs kyi /
NK026(la)001:4664: bcu gnyis pa mnga' bdag chen po sgrub rdzas kyi /
NK026(la)001:4665: bcu gsum pa grags pa rdo rje ming gi dbang ngo //
NK026(la)001:4666: de la dang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:4668: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK026(la)001:4669: blo yis dbang bskur thob pa yis //
NK026(la)001:4670: shes rab chen po rig pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4671: sems lon don gyi gtan tshigs ni //
NK026(la)001:4672: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4673: pradz+ny+aa bid+y+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4675: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la rig pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4676: lta ba gtan tshigs shes rab gsum dang /
NK026(la)001:4677: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4680: bya ba'i bsam pa kun bral zhing //
NK026(la)001:4681: rtsol med gnas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:4682: snying rje chen po'i bden mchog gis //
NK026(la)001:4683: khams gsum kun la dbang sgyur ba'i //
NK026(la)001:4684: dbang mchog khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4685: a ma na si tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4687: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la 'khor lo sbyin pas byang chub kyi sems khams gsum ting 'dzin dang /
NK026(la)001:4688: snying rje sgyu ma tshad med dang /
NK026(la)001:4689: kun tu snang gi ting 'dzin mthar phyin par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4691: nyon mongs lnga po gnas gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:4692: ye shes lnga po thob bya'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4694: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4695: purna tsakra a b+hi na mo /
NK026(la)001:4696: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la yi ge 'khor lo sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4697: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med dang /
NK026(la)001:4698: sems nyid stong pa snang ba med pa'i rig pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4699: bzhi pa thong gshol thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4700: srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rnams kun //
NK026(la)001:4701: thams cad rdzogs par nus pa yi //
NK026(la)001:4702: rtags kyi dbang mchog dam pa ni //
NK026(la)001:4703: thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:4704: a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a b+hi na mo /
NK026(la)001:4705: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la thong gshol sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4706: yi ge dang lha du mas rtog 'joms phyag rgya
NK026(la)001:4707: spros bcas bdag gzhan don byed kyi dbang thob par
NK026(la)001:4708: gyur cig / lnga pa thod pa tshar gsum thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4709: dug gsum gting nas sprugs pa yi //
NK026(la)001:4710: rtags chen ga'u rnam pa gsum //
NK026(la)001:4711: dmar chen khrag gis bkang nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:4712: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4713: dug gsum gtan sprugs thod pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4714: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK026(la)001:4715: dug gsum gtan nas zad byed pa //
NK026(la)001:4716: ga'u gsum gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4717: sangs rgyas sku gsum thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:4718: t+r+ai sud+d+ha ka p+aa li a b+hi na mo /
NK026(la)001:4719: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la dug gsum sprug pa'i ga'u rnam gsum sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4720: bar du gcod pa thams cad kyi dbang du mi 'gyur bar /
NK026(la)001:4721: bus dam bcas 'tshams pa ji srid du dug gsum
NK026(la)001:4722: sku gsung thugs su sgrub pa'i tshom bu tshogs chen
NK026(la)001:4724: tshogs chen tshig sgrub kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4725: drug pa mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4726: thogs pa med pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK026(la)001:4727: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4728: ral gri la sogs mtshon cha yis //
NK026(la)001:4729: dbang mchog dam pa khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4731: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la srid pa gsum sgrol ba'i ka tar mtshon cha sbyin par /
NK026(la)001:4732: don dam bden pa mthong ba'i lam bsnyen pa mthar
NK026(la)001:4733: phyin nas zag ldog med pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur
NK026(la)001:4734: cig / bdun pa pad+ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4735: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i chos rnams la //
NK026(la)001:4736: spyad kyang gos par mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK026(la)001:4737: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK026(la)001:4738: pad+ma'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4740: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la skyon gyis ma gos rnam dag pad+ma sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4741: kun rdzob bden pa mthong ba'i lam nye bar bsnyen pa mthar phyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4742: zag pa nyon mongs phyir zlog pa med pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4743: brgyad pa bam dbyug thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4744: las rnams rdzogs par byed pa yi //
NK026(la)001:4745: dbang mchog dam pa'i rtags chen 'di //
NK026(la)001:4746: ti ra'i dbyug pa chen po dag /
NK026(la)001:4747: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4748: zhing dbyug dgra s+t+wa tri shu la //
NK026(la)001:4749: rnam bzhi las kyis 'dul ba yi //
NK026(la)001:4750: phyag rgya chen por bstan pa ni //
