NK026(la)001:4751: ti ra chen po dbyug pa'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4752: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4753: ti ra dan+da a b+hi na mo /
NK026(la)001:4754: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la las rnams rdzogs pa ti ra'i dbyug pa sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4755: dbyer med bden pa mthong ba'i las sgrub pa mthar
NK026(la)001:4756: phyin pas zag ldog med pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur
NK026(la)001:4757: cig / dgu pa sbrul nag chun po thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4758: yum dang gnyis med 'khril ba yis //
NK026(la)001:4759: chos nyid don dang gnyis med rtags //
NK026(la)001:4761: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4762: dpal chen he ru ka la ni //
NK026(la)001:4763: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4764: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4765: thugs rje zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK026(la)001:4766: de bzhin rigs kyi bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4767: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4768: bdud dang srin po kun bcom nas //
NK026(la)001:4769: 'jigs byed chen po'i mthu ldan shog /
NK026(la)001:4770: a dwa ya a b+hi na mo /
NK026(la)001:4771: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4772: don dam dang kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4773: bcu pa rig ma thogs te /
NK026(la)001:4774: gsang ba sbyor ba shes rab ma //
NK026(la)001:4775: dri med rnam dag lha mo zhig /
NK026(la)001:4776: mtshan ldan shan tu brgyan byas la //
NK026(la)001:4777: dbang thob de la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4778: don dam rang bzhin spros bral ba //
NK026(la)001:4779: dri med rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:4780: zhi byed gzungs ma'i rgyal mo'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:4781: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK026(la)001:4782: d+ha ri a b+hi na mo /
NK026(la)001:4783: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la gsang ba spyod pa'i shes rab lha mo sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:4784: bsnyen sgrub bzhi sbyor sgrol lam mchog rdzogs shing /
NK026(la)001:4785: sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin mthar phyin pas rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK026(la)001:4786: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin du gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4787: bcu gcig pa longs spyod sna tshogs la /
NK026(la)001:4788: bza' btung dngos 'byor du ma bshams te dbang bskur zhing /
NK026(la)001:4789: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK026(la)001:4790: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad kun //
NK026(la)001:4791: spyod cing ma chags rol pa yi //
NK026(la)001:4792: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:4793: dza gad la sogs bdud rtsi yis //
NK026(la)001:4794: 'khor ba'i rtog pa gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4795: dad ldan bu kun tshim par gyis //
NK026(la)001:4796: bdud rtsi rnam lnga'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4797: dbang thob rgyal po chen po dang //
NK026(la)001:4798: kun gyi bdag po yin pas na //
NK026(la)001:4799: rol mo dri dang zhal zas dang //
NK026(la)001:4800: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4801: nye ba'i longs spyod rgyan rnams kun //
NK026(la)001:4802: thams cad kun nas sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4804: / bza' dang bca' dang btung la sogs //
NK026(la)001:4805: rang sems rnam dag rgyan gyi phyir //
NK026(la)001:4806: gnyis med rol pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4807: bdud rtsi yid bzhin sku grub shog /
NK026(la)001:4808: tsa tu a b+hi dkar rtsi dmar rtsi sha dri chen //
NK026(la)001:4809: longs spyod thun mong dbang bcu dang //
NK026(la)001:4810: bdag gzhan bya ba yongs rdzogs dang //
NK026(la)001:4811: snang srid kun gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4812: sbyin pa dang tshul khrims dang bzod pa dang brtson 'grus dang /
NK026(la)001:4813: bsam gtan dang shes rab dang thabs la mkhas pa
NK026(la)001:4814: mthar phyin nas zag pa dang ldog pa med pa'i
NK026(la)001:4815: sgom lam phyag rgya chen por gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4817: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la zhal zas bza' btung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK026(la)001:4818: 'dod yon lnga la longs spyod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4819: ces bza' btung rnams slob ma la brims shing rol lo //
NK026(la)001:4820: bcu gnyis pa sgrub rdzas la /
NK026(la)001:4821: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK026(la)001:4822: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4823: stag gi sham thabs dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4824: bdud dang srin po kun bsgral nas //
NK026(la)001:4825: ma tshogs mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdus //
NK026(la)001:4826: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4827: stag gi sham thabs gsol ba yis //
NK026(la)001:4828: dpa' bo bdud las rgyal ba dang //
NK026(la)001:4829: rnam rtog 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4830: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK026(la)001:4831: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4832: glang chen ko rlon dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4833: gti mug gnas su dag pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4834: khams gsum bdag por gyur pa ltar //
NK026(la)001:4835: de ring rnal 'byor bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4836: glang chen ko rlon dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4837: gti mug gnas su dag gyur nas //
NK026(la)001:4838: bdud dpung chen po 'joms par shog /
NK026(la)001:4839: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK026(la)001:4840: bdud dang srin po la sogs pas //
NK026(la)001:4841: bcom ldan sku la bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:4842: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4843: zhing gi g.yang gzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4844: bdud dang srin po btul ba ltar //
NK026(la)001:4845: 'khor ba rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4846: de ring rdo rje bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4847: zhing gi g.yang gzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4848: bdud dang srin po la sogs pa //
NK026(la)001:4849: thams cad 'joms pa dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4850: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK026(la)001:4851: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4852: thod pa skam rlon ra ri yi //
NK026(la)001:4853: thod phreng tshar gsum mnga' gsol bas //
NK026(la)001:4854: sa gsum non nas sku gsum 'grub //
NK026(la)001:4855: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4856: thod phreng tshar gsum dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4857: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4858: dug gsum gnas su dag nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:4859: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4860: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru la //
NK026(la)001:4861: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4862: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4863: thugs rje zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK026(la)001:4864: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4865: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4866: klu bdud srin po kun bcom nas //
NK026(la)001:4867: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4868: dpal chen he ru ka la ni //
NK026(la)001:4869: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:4870: khyung gi gshog pas dbang bskur pas //
NK026(la)001:4871: bdud dang srin po zil gyis gnon //
NK026(la)001:4872: de bzhin rnal 'byor bu khyod la //
NK026(la)001:4873: khyung gi gshog pas dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4874: rdo rje khyung ltar thogs med par //
NK026(la)001:4875: mkha' ltar yongs la khyab par shog /
NK026(la)001:4876: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar shog /
NK026(la)001:4878: 'bar ba 'phro ba ye shes thugs rjer ldan //
NK026(la)001:4879: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur mun nag sel //
NK026(la)001:4880: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang //
NK026(la)001:4881: dmar nag ljang nag 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK026(la)001:4882: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4883: mtshan ma'i 'dzin rtog bsreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4884: dz+wa la ram dz+ny+aa na h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4885: a b+hi rtags gsum po yang dngos su btab ste /
NK026(la)001:4886: khrag zhag thal ba'i mtshan ma bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:4888: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK026(la)001:4889: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK026(la)001:4890: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK026(la)001:4892: khrag gi tshom bus mtshan pa ni //
NK026(la)001:4893: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK026(la)001:4894: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK026(la)001:4895: 'dod chags gnas su dag pa yi //
NK026(la)001:4896: khrag gi thig les rtags mtshan nas //
NK026(la)001:4897: khrag gi thig les dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4898: gtum pa drag po 'joms pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4899: nga rgyal dregs pa 'dul mdzad cing //
NK026(la)001:4900: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:4901: ma h+aa rak+ta t+ai la ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4902: he ru dur khrod zhing chen dmar gyi zhag gi
NK026(la)001:4903: tshom bus 'di yang sngon gyi 'di yang rtags kyi
NK026(la)001:4904: chos nyid zhags kyis brgyan pa ni //
NK026(la)001:4905: zhag gi tshom bus dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4906: chos nyid dbyings su rgyal ba dang //
NK026(la)001:4907: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba dang //
NK026(la)001:4908: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4909: chos nyid zhag gi dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:4910: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a la la hoh he
NK026(la)001:4911: ru dur khrod zhing chen thal ba'i tshom bus 'di
NK026(la)001:4912: yang sngon gyi 'di yang rtags kyi thal ba'i mtshan
NK026(la)001:4914: gdug pa ma lus rab 'dul ba //
NK026(la)001:4915: che ba'i rgyal po kun gyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:4916: thams cad kun tu dpa' bo'i mtshan //
NK026(la)001:4917: gdug pa zil gnon thal ba'i mtshan //
NK026(la)001:4918: dbang mchog 'di yis dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:4919: khams gsum gdug pa thal bar rlog /
NK026(la)001:4920: de 'dra'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:4922: bcu gnyis pa sgrub rdzas kyi dbang la /
NK026(la)001:4936: sgrub pa'i rgyal po khyod la ni //
NK026(la)001:4937: sgrub pa'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK026(la)001:4938: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:4939: rgyal ba thams cad sgrub pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4940: tshe dang sman la sogs pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:4941: sgrub pa ma lus bsgrub par gyis //
NK026(la)001:4942: sarba sid+d+hi a b+hi bcu gsum pa ming gi dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:4944: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK026(la)001:4945: dbang thob de nyid gcig pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:4946: rig 'dzin rdo rje rtsal gyi dbang //
NK026(la)001:4947: rdo rje'i ming ni sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:4949: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la ming gi dbang bskur bas lha dang gnyis su med par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:4950: de ba a wa d+hu ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:4953: de bzhin du thog mar rdo rje dang /
NK026(la)001:4986: mgon byed myu gu zhes sogs gdags so //
NK026(la)001:4988: de yan chad kyis sgrub dbang bcu gsum rdzogs so //
NK026(la)001:4989: des sgrub dbang bcu gsum song nas //
NK026(la)001:4990: dbang gong ma gsum rgyas pa logs na yod pas 'og tu 'byung yang /
NK026(la)001:4991: 'dir thun mong tsam zhig sbyin pa ni /
NK026(la)001:4994: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK026(la)001:4995: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK026(la)001:4997: sgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang //
NK026(la)001:4998: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas na //
NK026(la)001:4999: gsang ba'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:5000: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK026(la)001:5001: kun tu tshim par byed pa'i ro //
NK026(la)001:5002: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:5003: dbang thob de yi lce la bzhag /
NK026(la)001:5004: dbang mchog gsang dbang thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:5005: a ho ma h+aa su ka hoh zhes gong gi
NK026(la)001:5006: bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor bshams te bsgrubs pa'i gsang rdzas
NK026(la)001:5008: 'di tsakli gsang ba'i brda' dbang ste /
NK026(la)001:5009: gru gsum mthing nag gi dbus su pad ma 'dab brgyad lte bar rdo rjes mtshan pa'o //
NK026(la)001:5010: zhes gsungs pa'i tsakli dang rdo rje dril bu yab yum gyi rten dang rig ma sbyin la /
NK026(la)001:5011: gnyis med don med byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:5012: bu mchog de yi snying la bzhag /
NK026(la)001:5013: don dam kun rdzob lhan cig skyes //
NK026(la)001:5014: rang byung ye shes chen por shog /
NK026(la)001:5015: a ho ma h+aa su ka hoh rdo rje'i sked pa dar dpyangs sngon po can byin te /
NK026(la)001:5016: gsang dang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK026(la)001:5017: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:5018: rtsol med byang chub sems chen po //
NK026(la)001:5019: shes rab chen po rtsal gyi dbang //
NK026(la)001:5020: chos kun du mar dbang sgyur nas //
NK026(la)001:5021: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK026(la)001:5022: rdzas kyi tshig dang gang zag dang //
NK026(la)001:5023: kun rdzob dbang de ma thob kyang //
NK026(la)001:5024: chos la sems kyi dbang thob nas //
NK026(la)001:5025: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK026(la)001:5026: srid gsum dbang can thams cad kun //
NK026(la)001:5027: de la dbang mchog sgyur bar 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:5028: de yang dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:5029: a ho ma h+aa su ka hoh de nas gsang
NK026(la)001:5030: ba shes rab bde ba chen po'i brda' dbang bskur
NK026(la)001:5031: ba ste / zab pa'i dbang gsum dngos su bskur ba logs na yod do //
NK026(la)001:5032: zhes gsungs pa skabs 'dir gsang ba dang shes rab
NK026(la)001:5033: ye shes gnyis kyi brda' dbang tsam bum dbang gi
NK026(la)001:5034: mtha' rten du sbyin pa yin no //
NK026(la)001:5036: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK026(la)001:5037: gsang dbang ni skabs 'dir mi bskur bar las 'di'i
NK026(la)001:5038: man ngag gi dbang deng gi skabs su phal gyi
NK026(la)001:5039: spyod yul ma yin par slob bu snod dang ldan
NK026(la)001:5040: pa la bla ma'i gdams ngag gis shes par byos
NK026(la)001:5041: shig / ces gsungs pa thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK026(la)001:5042: dbang gong ma rnams phal gyi spyod yul ma yin
NK026(la)001:5043: pas 'dir thun mong tsam bstan nas slob ma snod
NK026(la)001:5044: dang ldan nges la logs su thun mong ma yin
NK026(la)001:5045: pa'i dbang gong ma bskur ba la dgongs pa yin
NK026(la)001:5046: pas shes pa gnad du che'o //
NK026(la)001:5050: zhes gsungs pa da lta'i phyag bzhes su phyi nang
NK026(la)001:5051: gi sgo byang gnyis bkrol te dbang bskur ba'i phyag
NK026(la)001:5052: srol 'dug cing / bskur tshig la brtags na gshin
NK026(la)001:5053: rje'i sgo byang gcig pus chog pa 'dra zhig snang
NK026(la)001:5054: srol 'dug cing / yang / bsdoms tshig tu /
NK026(la)001:5055: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs skrod //
NK026(la)001:5056: zhes gsungs pas gnyis ka dgos pa la the tshom mi bya'o //
NK026(la)001:5058: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK026(la)001:5059: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:5060: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed po yi //
NK026(la)001:5061: dgra bgegs sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK026(la)001:5063: rgya gar dur khrod 'jigs byed tshal chen du //
NK026(la)001:5064: slob dpon 'jam dpa' bshes gnyen gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5065: rdo rje grub pa rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5066: 'jal dpal sku yi dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK026(la)001:5067: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu bskyang du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5068: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:5069: rgya gar gnas dang sgrags kyi yang rdzong du //
NK026(la)001:5070: yi dam dpal chen dkyil 'khor zhal phye'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5071: yi dam ya m+aan+ta ka'i zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5072: bee ro tsa na rak+shi ta dang ni //
NK026(la)001:5073: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes gsang rdo rje drag po rtsal te sku snang bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5074: 'jam dpal sku yi dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:5075: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu skal ldan byin rlabs
NK026(la)001:5076: dbang bskur rgya gar pad+ma brtsegs pa'i dur khrod nas
NK026(la)001:5077: // slob dpon klu sgrub snying po'i gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5078: grub pa rtsal te rig 'dzin pad+ma gsung gi dngos
NK026(la)001:5079: grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan bsam yas mchims phu'i yang
NK026(la)001:5080: // dben du // zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhal phye'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5081: pad+ma dbang chen 'khor bcas zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5082: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs gsang rdo rje pad+ma rtsal te gsung drag brnyes //
NK026(la)001:5083: pad+ma gsang gi dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:5084: 'dir gshegs skal ldan sgo byang mgor bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:5085: rig 'dzin de rnams gshin rje gshed sogs la grub pa brnyes phyir bskur tshig de ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:5086: shar lho'i mar me thogs la /
NK026(la)001:5089: mnga' gzhug pho nya'i rgyal ba rgyal sras rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:5090: zhi khro'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5092: rgya gar h+aum grags dur khrod du //
NK026(la)001:5093: slob dpon h+aum k+aa ra yi gsang rdo rje dngos
NK026(la)001:5094: grub rtsal te rig 'dzin yang dag thugs kyi dngos
NK026(la)001:5096: lho brag mkhar chu dpal gyi phug ring du //
NK026(la)001:5097: mar me dgu yi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK026(la)001:5098: yi dam dpal chen 'khor bcas zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5099: slob dpon nam mkha'i snying po'i gsang rdo rje thog 'bebs rtsal te thugs dran brnyes //
NK026(la)001:5100: yang dag thugs kyi dngos grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan mar me spyi bor bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:5101: rgya bod kyi pan grub de gnyis yang dag la
NK026(la)001:5102: grub pa brnyes shing de nyid kyi sgrub rdzas mar
NK026(la)001:5106: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngag gzhug kun bzang che mchog bdud rtsi yis //
NK026(la)001:5107: nad sel sman gyi dngos grub gsol //
NK026(la)001:5109: bdud rtsi rol pa'i dur khrod rtsal chen na //
NK026(la)001:5110: slob dpon dri med bshes gnyen gsang rdo rje mi
NK026(la)001:5111: 'gyur rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas bdud rtsi yon tan
NK026(la)001:5112: dngos grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum /
NK026(la)001:5113: yar klungs ra mo sman sgang shel brag tu //
NK026(la)001:5114: bdud rtsi sman sgrub dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK026(la)001:5115: sman gyi lha srung rig 'dzin zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5116: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra yi gsang dri med zla shar rtsal te 'dod yon bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5117: bdud rtsi yon tan dngos grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5118: bdud rtsi mgor gtug cing lce thog tu yang sbyin
NK026(la)001:5119: no // rgya gar gyi pan chen bi ma la dang /
NK026(la)001:5120: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra gnyis bdud rtsi'i sgo
NK026(la)001:5121: nas grub pa brnyes shing de'i sgrub rdzas bdud rtsi
NK026(la)001:5123: byang gi phur pa thogs la /
NK026(la)001:5125: dus gsum mngag gzhug rdo rje gzhon nu zhi khro yis //
NK026(la)001:5126: dam sri phung sbyor rgyun chod cig /
NK026(la)001:5128: dregs 'dul dur khrod rtsal chen du //
NK026(la)001:5129: 'jigs byed pra b+ha hasti'i gsang rdo rje drag po
NK026(la)001:5130: rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas phur pa phrin las dngos
NK026(la)001:5132: brag dkar seng ge rdzong gi phug pa ru //
NK026(la)001:5133: gru gsum shel gyi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK026(la)001:5134: jo mo mkhar chen mtsho rgyal gsang rdo rje lcam gcig phrin las ci snyed bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5135: phur pa grub nas brag la phur pa btab //
NK026(la)001:5136: mkhar mi tsam la mdze gdon med par mdzad //
NK026(la)001:5137: ming po mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug kyang //
NK026(la)001:5138: rdo rje drag po rtsal te dngos grub thob //
NK026(la)001:5139: phur pa phrin las dngos grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5140: phur pa mgor gtug cing lag tu gtad la bsgril
NK026(la)001:5141: lo // pan grub 'di rnams kyang phur pa la grub pa brnyes shing /
NK026(la)001:5142: de'i sgrub rdzas phur bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:5143: byang shar gyi mdos rag ste mdos dang rak+ta thogs la /
NK026(la)001:5145: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngag gzhug mngon rdzogs rgyal po yab yum gyis //
NK026(la)001:5146: chag nyams bgegs bsal dngos grub gsol /
NK026(la)001:5148: dur khrod sna tshogs pad+ma'i gling //
NK026(la)001:5149: d+ha na samskri ta yi gsang rdo rje dbang phug
NK026(la)001:5150: rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas ma mo rbod gtong dngos
NK026(la)001:5151: grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan yar klungs sham po gangs
NK026(la)001:5153: ma mo rgyud lung dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK026(la)001:5154: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams kyis zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5155: 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu'i gsung rdo rje 'phrul rgod rtsal te bde stong tshang //
NK026(la)001:5156: mkha' dbyings ma mo'i dngos grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan mdos raka lag tu gtad do //
NK026(la)001:5157: rig 'dzin de rnams kyang ma mo'i dngos grub brnyes te /
NK026(la)001:5158: sgrub rdzas mdos dang dmar chen gyi rak+ta yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:5159: lho nub chos skyong gi gtor ma la /
NK026(la)001:5160: zhes gsungs pa legs ldan ma yin pa'i chos skyong spyi gtor zhig thogs la /
NK026(la)001:5162: dus gsum mngag gzhug gsang ba'i bdag po zhi khro yi //
NK026(la)001:5163: chos srung ma g.yel stong grogs mdzod //
NK026(la)001:5165: dur khrod 'dam bu'i tshal chen nub //
NK026(la)001:5166: ram bu gu h+ya de ba tsan+d+ra'i gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5167: gshog rgod rtsal te 'jin gnas 'jig rten mchod bstod
NK026(la)001:5168: dngos grub 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum /
NK026(la)001:5169: spa gro stag tshang seng ge'i phug /
NK026(la)001:5170: dregs pa kun 'dul zhal phye tshe //
NK026(la)001:5171: dpal chen dregs pa'i zhal gzigs pa //
NK026(la)001:5172: sh+r+ai sid+ha'i gsang rdo rje drag po rtsal te mchod pa sku la tshang //
NK026(la)001:5173: gsang bdag 'jig rten mchod bstod brnyes pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:5174: 'dir gshegs skal ldan chos skyong spyi gtor mgo bor gtug /
NK026(la)001:5175: pan grub 'di rnams dregs pa bran du 'khol bas /
NK026(la)001:5176: sgrub rdzas gtor ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:5177: shar du las bzhi'i rdzas dang zor gtor la /
NK026(la)001:5178: zhes gsungs pas gong du sta gon byas pa'i las
NK026(la)001:5179: bzhi'i 'brang rgyas dang gtor zor dang kong zor thogs
NK026(la)001:5181: dus gsum mngag gzhug stobs ldan sgrol ging zhi khro yi //
NK026(la)001:5182: phrin las mthar phyin kun 'grub mdzod //
NK026(la)001:5184: dur khrod ro yi tshal chen du //
NK026(la)001:5186: rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas bod yul mkha' gshegs snang srid chos skur mdzad //
NK026(la)001:5187: smod pa drag sngags dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK026(la)001:5189: brag dmar g.ya' ma lung gi gnas //
NK026(la)001:5190: stobs ldan dregs pa'i dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK026(la)001:5191: stobs ldan nag po zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5192: bee ro tsa na'i gsang rdo rje grub pa rtsal te stobs rtsal 'chang //
NK026(la)001:5193: dmod pa drag sngags dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:5194: 'dir gshegs skal ldan de dag lag tu gtad do //
NK026(la)001:5195: pan grub rig 'dzin 'di dag drag sngags kyi grub pa brnyes pa yin pas /
NK026(la)001:5196: phrin las bzhi'i rdzas dang zor gtor phrin las kyi sgrub rdzas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:5197: tshe rdzas blangs pa'i drung la /
NK026(la)001:5198: zhes gsungs pa yig rgyun ma dag pa 'dra ste /
NK026(la)001:5199: tshe rdzas blangs te btugs la zhes pa yin nam snyam zhing /
NK026(la)001:5200: don gong du dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i tshe bum
NK026(la)001:5201: de nyid tshe dpag med kyi rang bzhin du gsal
NK026(la)001:5202: bas dbang bskur zhing 'di skad do //
NK026(la)001:5204: bcom ldan mgon po ye shes tshe dpag med //
NK026(la)001:5205: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:5206: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku gsung thugs mnga' ba //
NK026(la)001:5207: rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:5208: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:5210: rgya gar a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:5211: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dzas tshe dbang grub //
NK026(la)001:5212: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs //
NK026(la)001:5213: tshom bu 'bum phrag dngos grub brnyes //
NK026(la)001:5214: 'dir gshegs skal ldan lhun grub phyag rgya chen po che //
NK026(la)001:5215: rnam smin grub pa'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK026(la)001:5216: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mthar phyin lam //
NK026(la)001:5217: rtsa ba brgyud pa'i bla ma grub thob rnams //
NK026(la)001:5218: 'dir gshegs skal ldan tshe bum spyi bor gtug go //
NK026(la)001:5219: rig 'dzin 'di rnams 'chi med grub pas de'i sgrub rdzas tshe bum yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:5220: tshe ril tshe chang yang sbyin no //
NK026(la)001:5223: gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5224: rdo rje thod phreng rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5225: rgyal ba'i rgyal tshab srid gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK026(la)001:5226: khams gsum gdul bya dbang sdud spyi dpal rje //
NK026(la)001:5227: 'dir gshegs skal ldan mnga' bdag rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan yang //
NK026(la)001:5228: gsang mtshan dbang chen 'jam dpal rtsal zhes grags //
NK026(la)001:5229: dkar chung sad na legs ni khri ral pa //
NK026(la)001:5230: rgyal sras sprul pa gdung rabs 'khor dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:5231: bzhugs ni longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5232: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon bo d+hi sa t+wa'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5233: rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas gsang sngags phyi rgyud thub pa'i brgyud 'dzin rnams //
NK026(la)001:5234: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon dzi na mi tra'i
NK026(la)001:5235: gsang rdo rje sems dpa' rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas
NK026(la)001:5236: mtshan nyid theg pa che chung lhar bcas rnams //
NK026(la)001:5237: 'dir gshegs skal ldan tsha ba rong gi rgyal po'i sgrub khang du //
NK026(la)001:5238: rgya bod mkhas grub kun gyi thugs bcud phyung //
NK026(la)001:5239: yi dam tshogs chen rnams kyi zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:5240: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po'i gsang rdo rje bde
NK026(la)001:5241: rgod rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas bka' brgyad bskyed rdzogs
NK026(la)001:5243: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa
NK026(la)001:5244: ra'i gsang thig le rtsal rgod rtsal te rig 'dzin
NK026(la)001:5245: gnas 'dir gshegs skal ldan sog po dpal gyi ye
NK026(la)001:5246: shes gsang rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter te rig 'dzin
NK026(la)001:5247: zhi khro gnas tshogs phrin las shar bar rnams //
NK026(la)001:5248: 'dir gshegs zhang stobs rgyal ba'i yon tan gsang dam
NK026(la)001:5249: tshig mthar phyin rtsal te rig 'dzin man ngag bka'
NK026(la)001:5250: srol phyag bzhes tshar ba rnams //
NK026(la)001:5251: 'dir gshegs skal ldan dar rje dpal gyi grags pa'i
NK026(la)001:5252: gsang yang dag grub pa rtsal te rig 'dzin bshad
NK026(la)001:5253: sgrub yongs grags dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams //
NK026(la)001:5254: 'dir gshegs skal ldan bka' lung ma nor rnal 'byor dbang phyug ni //
NK026(la)001:5255: rig 'dzin brgya dang rtsa brgyad dbang bskur 'dis //
NK026(la)001:5256: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang bsgrub bshad lung rnams //
NK026(la)001:5257: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu bskyang du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5258: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub gsol //
NK026(la)001:5259: de rnams kyis sgrub rten dbang rdzogs so //
NK026(la)001:5260: de yang slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes kyis /
NK026(la)001:5261: tshe ni spyi yi kha skong yin //
NK026(la)001:5262: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs skrod //
NK026(la)001:5263: rdzas skongs mar me bdud rtsi sman //
NK026(la)001:5264: mtshams phur gdab kha bsnyen phur rten //
NK026(la)001:5265: dmar chen rak+tasa thugs dam skong //
NK026(la)001:5266: 'jig rten mchod rten drag zor gtor //
NK026(la)001:5267: rig 'dzin gtor phud tshe zan rdzas //
NK026(la)001:5268: zhes gsungs pa ltar sgrub rdzas 'di rnams kyis dbang
NK026(la)001:5269: bskur bas rig 'dzin brgyud pa de rnams kyi thugs
NK026(la)001:5270: dam bskul te bsnyen sgrub las gsum gang la yang
NK026(la)001:5271: bar gcod mi 'byung zhing byin rlabs bsam gyis mi
NK026(la)001:5272: khyab pa 'byung ba'i dgos pa yod pas yid ches
NK026(la)001:5274: de nas yo ga gsum gyi rig 'dzin brgyud pa rnams kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK026(la)001:5277: ston pa kun bzang nas rim pa bzhin tsakli thogs te /
NK026(la)001:5278: rig 'dzin bla ma de rnams kyang rang la thim par mos te /
NK026(la)001:5279: yid kyi sems dpa' gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:5280: ston pa kun tu bzang po yis //
NK026(la)001:5281: skal ldan dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs //
NK026(la)001:5282: rnam shes phung po gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:5283: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK026(la)001:5284: skal ldan dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs //
NK026(la)001:5285: ston pa kun bzang longs sku rdo rje sems //
NK026(la)001:5286: 'jam dpal phyag rdor la sogs bka' sdud rnams //
NK026(la)001:5287: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu bskyang du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5288: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:5289: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5290: rdo rje bde byed rtsal te 'og min gnas na zhugs //
NK026(la)001:5291: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5292: rdo rje gzhon nu rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs rgyal po d+ha na ta lo'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5293: rdo rje dga' byed rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5294: skal ldan thu bo r+aa dza ha sti'i gsang rdo
NK026(la)001:5295: rje gsal ba rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal
NK026(la)001:5296: ldan sras mo wa ra ni yi gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5297: mdzes ma rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5298: klu yi rgyal po 'jog po'i gsang rdo rje rdzu
NK026(la)001:5299: 'phrul rtsal te rgya mtsho'i gting na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5300: 'dir gshigs skal ldan sras mo gnod sbyin byang chub
NK026(la)001:5301: gsang rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal te 'og min 'dir
NK026(la)001:5302: gshegs skal ldan gzungs ma a ra li yi gsang
NK026(la)001:5303: mtshan ni // rdo rje dbyings ma rtsal te 'og
NK026(la)001:5304: min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon ak+sha shi b+h+ai
NK026(la)001:5305: gsang rdo rje dngos grub rtsal te 'og min 'dir
NK026(la)001:5306: gshegs skal ldan mkhan po ku ku r+aa dza'i gsang
NK026(la)001:5307: rdo rje drag po rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5308: skal ldan smad 'tshong bud+d+ha sa ma ya'i gsang rdo
NK026(la)001:5309: rje yang dag rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal
NK026(la)001:5310: ldan smad 'tshong bud+d+ha sa ma ti'i gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5311: nyi 'od rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5312: o rgyan ma h+aa r+aa dza'i rdo rje 'phrul rtsal
NK026(la)001:5313: te 'dir gshegs skal ldan sras mo go ma de
NK026(la)001:5314: wi'i rdo rje nges grub rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal
NK026(la)001:5315: ldan slob dpon +aa lo ke yi gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5316: g.yung drung rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan khyi yi
NK026(la)001:5317: mkhan po phyi ma'i rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal te
NK026(la)001:5318: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon ma h+aa r+aa dza'i
NK026(la)001:5319: rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5320: drang srong b+ha shi ta yi rdo rje lhun grub
NK026(la)001:5321: rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan gzungs ma bdag nyid
NK026(la)001:5322: ma yi rdo rje 'od mchog rtsal te 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5323: skal ldan slob dpon n+aa gardzu na'i rdo rje thogs
NK026(la)001:5324: med rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon de
NK026(la)001:5325: ba r+aa dza'i rdo rje gsang ba rtsal te 'dir
NK026(la)001:5326: gshegs skal ldan 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma'i rdo
NK026(la)001:5327: rje nges pa rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan /
NK026(la)001:5328: rig 'dzin dge bsnyen legs pa'i rdo rje mchog rab
NK026(la)001:5329: rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon bud+d+ha gu
NK026(la)001:5330: h+ya'i gsang rdo rje gsang rdzogs rtsal te 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5331: skal ldan slob dpon sh+r+ai sid+ha'i rdo rje bzhad pa
NK026(la)001:5332: rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan dge slong kun dga'
NK026(la)001:5333: mo yi rdo rje shes rab rtsal te 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5334: skal ldan slob dpon bi ma la mi tra'i rdo
NK026(la)001:5335: rje gro bo lod rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5336: slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i rdo rje khyung gshog
NK026(la)001:5337: rtsal te 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon g.yu sgra
NK026(la)001:5338: snying po'i rdo rje bde 'byams rtsal te 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5339: skal ldan dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra yi dri med
NK026(la)001:5340: zla shar rtsal te rdo rje bzhad pa gter /
NK026(la)001:5342: thig le gshog rgod rtsal yang zer ro //
NK026(la)001:5343: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu bskyang du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5344: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub rtsol //
NK026(la)001:5347: kun bzang rdor sems sogs rim pas byin la /
NK026(la)001:5348: dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs chos kyi sku skye
NK026(la)001:5349: 'gag med pa spros pa dang bral ba'i mtha' las
NK026(la)001:5350: grol ba / rang bzhin lhun grub rgya chad phyogs
NK026(la)001:5351: lhung med pa rang rig pa'i ngo bo thig le
NK026(la)001:5352: chen po grwa zur med pa'i dpal kun tu bzang
NK026(la)001:5353: po 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang yum
NK026(la)001:5354: gyi mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i gnas su 'khor
NK026(la)001:5355: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas la thugs ye shes rnam pa
NK026(la)001:5357: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur byin gyis brlabs /
NK026(la)001:5358: de bzhin du gnas lugs rtogs nas ye shes lnga'i dbang thob ste /
NK026(la)001:5359: chos sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob pa gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:5360: de nas rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las khrag 'thung rigs lnga dang /
NK026(la)001:5361: che mchog he ru kar snang bar mdzad nas /
NK026(la)001:5362: rigs gsum mkhyen rab dang thugs rje dang mthu stobs kyis bdag por dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:5363: gdug pa can thams cad btul nas sum cu rtsa
NK026(la)001:5364: gsum lha'i gnas rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang du
NK026(la)001:5365: zhi ba rigs lngar snang bar byas te /
NK026(la)001:5366: lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar po la 'gro ba
NK026(la)001:5367: rigs drug gi sems can thams cad thugs rjes smin
NK026(la)001:5368: par byed pa'i dbang bskur te /
NK026(la)001:5369: sprul sku thub pa drug tu byin gyis brlabs /
NK026(la)001:5370: de bzhin du skal ldan rigs kyi bu 'di rnams kyi thugs rjes 'gro ba 'dren pa dang /
NK026(la)001:5371: phrin las kyis gdug pa can 'dul ba dang /
NK026(la)001:5372: 'bras bu thams cad la dbang sgyur ba'i dbang da ma pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:5373: 'jam dbyangs dang spyan ras gzigs la /
NK026(la)001:5374: mkhyen rab mnga' bdag 'phags pa 'jam dpal ni //
NK026(la)001:5375: mdzes pa'i sku ldan skye 'chi med pa yis //
NK026(la)001:5376: yid 'ong lha yi gnas su dbang bskur ni //
NK026(la)001:5377: grags ldan mchog skyong rin chen 'od 'bar dang //
NK026(la)001:5378: tshangs pa skye rgu'i bdag dang kun grol dang //
NK026(la)001:5379: gtsug phud 'dzin dang lha dbang brgya byin dang //
NK026(la)001:5380: lha yi rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la //
NK026(la)001:5381: bde gshegs rgyal tshab sras su dbang bskur nas //
NK026(la)001:5382: gnas skabs byang chub sems dpa'i rigs 'dzin cing //
NK026(la)001:5383: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i gdung gsob bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:5384: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag spyan ras gzigs dbang ni //
NK026(la)001:5385: 'khor ba ma stongs bar du 'gro ba 'dren //
NK026(la)001:5386: sman gyi sku ldan klu la dbang bskur ba //
NK026(la)001:5387: mgrin pa nag po klu mo kha 'dul ma //
NK026(la)001:5388: klu mo 'dul tshang yid 'ong dga' ma dang //
NK026(la)001:5389: klu yi rgyal po 'jog po la sogs pa //
NK026(la)001:5390: klu yi rig 'dzin bde gshegs gnas skabs rgyal ba mthu stobs mnga' bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK026(la)001:5391: 'jig rten dregs pa'i tshogs btul bsgral byas nas //
NK026(la)001:5392: 'jigs tshul sdigs pas gnod sbyin dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:5393: gnod sbyin kun bzang lag na rdo rje dang //
NK026(la)001:5394: grags ldan mchog skyong skar mda' ltung la sogs //
NK026(la)001:5395: gnod sbyin rig 'dzin bde gshegs gnas skabs rgyal ba gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK026(la)001:5396: grags ldan mchog skyong thig le chags med rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5397: klu rgyal 'jog po dbang phyug lhun grub rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5398: gnod sbyin skar mda' rdo rje glog 'byin rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5399: lang+ka mgrin bcu blo gros thabs ldan rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5400: li tsa b+ai ni dri med grags pa rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5401: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgyu bskyang du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5402: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:5403: rgyal bas lung bstan skal ldan rgyal po la //
NK026(la)001:5404: gsang mdzod gter 'dzin sku gsung thim rtags dang //
NK026(la)001:5405: chos kyi bgro mdzad rin chen 'char 'bab dang //
NK026(la)001:5406: kun gyi basngagasa zhes glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK026(la)001:5407: mchod cing sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan cing //
NK026(la)001:5408: gus byas rtse gcig gsol btab bsgrubs pa yis //
NK026(la)001:5409: sgrib byang chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur zhing //
NK026(la)001:5410: chos kyi char phab rnal 'byor gral du bzhag /
NK026(la)001:5411: chos la dbang thob gsang ba rgya cher brjod //
NK026(la)001:5412: tan+t+ra bco brgyad dbang thob skal ldan la //
NK026(la)001:5413: 'dren pa'i las byang byin brlabs dbang bskur zhing //
NK026(la)001:5414: rgyud sde'i mnga' bdag chos rgyal dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:5415: skal ldan rgyal po dzahyi gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5416: rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal te 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5417: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon u pa r+aa dza'i
NK026(la)001:5418: gsang rdo rje yang dag rtsal te 'og min 'dir
NK026(la)001:5419: gshegs skal ldan slob dpon in+d+ra bo d+hi'i gsang rdo
NK026(la)001:5420: rje gsal mdzes rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal
NK026(la)001:5421: ldan klu rgyal n+aa ga pu tra'i gsang thig le
NK026(la)001:5422: bskyed med rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5423: rgyal po gu h+ya tri'i gsang rdo rje gsal 'phro
NK026(la)001:5424: rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgyal po
NK026(la)001:5425: sid+ha pu tra'i gsang rdo rje 'od zer rtsal te
NK026(la)001:5426: 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5427: bzhad pa'i gsang rdo rje bde byed rtsal te 'og
NK026(la)001:5428: min 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgyal po sing+ha pu tra'i
NK026(la)001:5429: gsang rdo rje 'od zer rtsal te 'og min 'dir
NK026(la)001:5430: gshegs skal ldan ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma'i gsang
NK026(la)001:5431: rdo rje bde mchog rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5432: skal ldan ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub gsang bdud
NK026(la)001:5433: 'dul drag po rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal
NK026(la)001:5434: ldan slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5435: bde byed rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5436: za hor rgyal po pra hasti yi gsang thig le
NK026(la)001:5437: bde byed rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5438: d+ha na rak+shi ta yi gsang seng ge sgra sgrog
NK026(la)001:5439: rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon
NK026(la)001:5440: h+aum mdzad rdo rje gsang rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal
NK026(la)001:5441: te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan gu ru s+thi
NK026(la)001:5442: ra ma ti yi gsang yang dag rdzogs pa rtsal
NK026(la)001:5443: te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan +aa tsar+ya bde
NK026(la)001:5444: ba gsal byed gsang dbang phyug 'jigs med rtsal te
NK026(la)001:5445: 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon d+harma bo
NK026(la)001:5446: d+hi'i gsang shes rab mthar phyin rtsal te 'og min
NK026(la)001:5447: 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgya gar chos rgyal skyong gi
NK026(la)001:5448: gsang rdo rje bde byed rtsal te 'og min 'dir
NK026(la)001:5449: gshegs skal ldan bal po ba su d+ha ra'i gsang
NK026(la)001:5450: rdo rje thugs mchog rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5451: skal ldan rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge'i gsang rdo
NK026(la)001:5452: rje gtsug tor rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal
NK026(la)001:5453: ldan bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes kyi gsang
NK026(la)001:5454: rdo rje legs thob rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5455: skal ldan slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5456: yang dbang gter te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5457: byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:5458: de yan chad kyis a nu rdzogs pa'o //
NK026(la)001:5459: de nas ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud khungs la /
NK026(la)001:5460: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku r+aa dzas rnam dag mchod
NK026(la)001:5461: rten tu bsgrubs pas kun tu bzang po'i sprul pa
NK026(la)001:5462: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mngon sum du mthong ste
NK026(la)001:5463: / rdo rje sems dpas rdo rje chos la gsang sngags rgyud sde'i rgyal por dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:5464: rdo rje chos kyis ku ku r+aa dza la dbang
NK026(la)001:5465: bskur bas tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad la dgongs pa mthar
NK026(la)001:5467: de bzhin du rgyud lung man ngag rnams la dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:5468: slob dpon ku ku ra'i dza'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:5469: rdo rje che mchog rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5470: skal ldan skal ldan rgyal po dzahyi gsang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5471: nyi 'od rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK026(la)001:5472: rgyal po sha tra pu tri'i gsang rdo rje rab
NK026(la)001:5473: mdzes rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgyal
NK026(la)001:5474: po sid+ha r+aa dza'i gsang rdo rje grags pa rtsal
NK026(la)001:5475: te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan o rgyan rgyal
NK026(la)001:5476: po u pa r+aa dza'i gsang yang dag grub pa
NK026(la)001:5477: rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan sras mo
NK026(la)001:5478: go ma de w+ai'i gsang rdo rje zla mdzes rtsal
NK026(la)001:5479: te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan mee tri k+aa
NK026(la)001:5480: ma la yi gsang rdo rdo khyung chen rtsal te
NK026(la)001:5481: 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan +aa tsar+ya dzi na
NK026(la)001:5482: mi tra'i gsang rdo rje nges pa rtsal te 'og
NK026(la)001:5483: min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon rdo rje bzhad
NK026(la)001:5484: pa'i gsang rdo rje bde byed rtsal te 'og min
NK026(la)001:5485: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon nyin byed seng ge'i
NK026(la)001:5486: gsang rdo rje rtsal chen rtsal te 'og min 'dir
NK026(la)001:5487: gshegs skal ldan slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad gsang
NK026(la)001:5488: rdo rje 'gyur med rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs
NK026(la)001:5489: skal ldan slob dpon sh+aakya bod+d+hi gsang rdo rje grub
NK026(la)001:5490: mchog rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob
NK026(la)001:5491: dpon so kya de ba'i gsang rdo rje dad pa
NK026(la)001:5492: rtsal te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon
NK026(la)001:5493: sgeg pa rdo rje'i gsang rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal
NK026(la)001:5494: te 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon chos
NK026(la)001:5495: blon de ba'i gsang rdo rje nges chen rtsal te
NK026(la)001:5496: 'og min 'dir gshegs skal ldan mkhan po chos rgyal
NK026(la)001:5497: skyong gi gsang rdo rje bde byed rtsal te 'og
NK026(la)001:5498: min 'dir gshegs skal ldan de la gnubs sangs rgyas
NK026(la)001:5500: de yan chod ma h+aa ste rgya gar gyi bla ma rnams so //
NK026(la)001:5501: de nas bod kyi bla ma'i rim pa ni /
NK026(la)001:5502: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che //
NK026(la)001:5503: g.yung drung rin chen gter gnas su //
NK026(la)001:5504: yi dam gsal bar bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5505: stobs po che yi rdzas mchog 'di //
NK026(la)001:5506: nam mkha'i mthongs nas yas mar babs //
NK026(la)001:5507: bdag gi lag pa g.yas pas zin //
NK026(la)001:5508: ye shes rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob //
NK026(la)001:5509: 'ol mo tshal du bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5510: mngon sum dri za phrug gu byung //
NK026(la)001:5511: sangs rgyas khyod yin mtshan brtags te //
NK026(la)001:5512: dam brdar don la dam tshig bsres //
NK026(la)001:5513: rdo rje ming gi dbang yang thob //
NK026(la)001:5514: gang bzang gnas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5515: gnon sbyin phrug gu mngon byung nas //
NK026(la)001:5516: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod yon stob //
NK026(la)001:5517: slob dpon 'khor du dam du bcas //
NK026(la)001:5518: che ba'i yon tan dbang yang thob //
NK026(la)001:5519: gling dgu'i mtsho 'gram bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5520: klu phrug spun gsum mngon byung nas //
NK026(la)001:5521: ro brgya ldan pa'i mchod pa drangs //
NK026(la)001:5522: yang dag slob mar dam tshig nos //
NK026(la)001:5523: gdug pa sel ba'i dbang yang thob //
NK026(la)001:5524: dur khrod lhas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:5525: yi dwags phru gu mngon sum byung //
NK026(la)001:5526: zhabs la gtugs te mchi ma phyungs //
NK026(la)001:5527: ci bsgo nyan pa'i dbang yang nos //
NK026(la)001:5528: mthu rtsal bsnyems pa'i dbang yang thob //
NK026(la)001:5529: phyi rabs slob ma gang yin rnams //
NK026(la)001:5531: phan pa lha yi dbang nos la //
NK026(la)001:5532: bskur thabs dbang bskur rgyal po bzhin //
NK026(la)001:5533: dbang bskur 'di rnams thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:5534: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes ni //
NK026(la)001:5535: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dbang gter //
NK026(la)001:5536: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5537: 'dir gshegs skal ldan gnubs kyi bu bzhi dge mched bco lnga dang //
NK026(la)001:5538: rin chen gsum dang 'khor brgyad drug cu 'jig rten sogs //
NK026(la)001:5539: bu bzhi 'bre ston khro chung nyang sher mchog /
NK026(la)001:5540: nyang ston ye 'byung zur chen sh+aaka 'byung bzhi //
NK026(la)001:5541: dge mched dang po thugs kyi sras bzhi ni //
NK026(la)001:5542: so pa ye dbang rdo rje dbyings phyug gter //
NK026(la)001:5543: sru legs sgron ma ut+pala dbang chen rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5544: spa gor blon rje rdo rje gnam lcags rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5545: dan ston yon mchog rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5546: 'dir gshegs skal ldan gnyis pa thugs sras gnubs ban khu lung pa //
NK026(la)001:5547: yon tan rgya mtsho rdo rje rig 'dzin gter //
NK026(la)001:5548: gsum pa sru yi slob ma mchog bzhi ni //
NK026(la)001:5549: dbyar ston gsal byang rdo rje mtshams byed rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5550: rgya ston blo gros gzhon nu dbang rdzogs rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5551: rgya ston sh+aakya mchog rab gzi 'bar rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5552: zhu ston bsod sh+aaka phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5553: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skal ldan byin rlabs bzhi pa spa gor beg ston ye shes dang //
NK026(la)001:5554: lnga pa lnga ni rgya ston gzhon nu snying //
NK026(la)001:5555: skyo ston dar ma byang chub skyes mchog rab //
NK026(la)001:5556: skye ston dar rgyal lho ston snying po'o //
NK026(la)001:5557: 'dir gshegs skal ldan yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho sras //
NK026(la)001:5558: rdo rje dbang grub rtsal la brgyud pa btad //
NK026(la)001:5559: 'dir gshegs skal ldan de yi slob ma byang chub rnam gsum ni //
NK026(la)001:5560: rgya ston ba blo gros byang chub las grub rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5561: mar pa yon tan byang chub lhun grub rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5562: sna nam tshul khrims byang chub grub mchog rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5563: rgya yi slob ma brgyud 'dzin rnam gnyis ni //
NK026(la)001:5564: tho dkar gnam lde rdo rje dngos grub gter //
NK026(la)001:5565: zhu dan bsod sh+aaka phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5566: 'dir gshegs skal ldan zur chen sh+aaka 'byung rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5567: tho dkar gyis brtags zhu yis zhi ba rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5568: stong tshab byang chub rgya ston blo gros dang //
NK026(la)001:5569: bka' bstod ye shes snying po rnams la ni //
NK026(la)001:5570: mdo lung dbang sgrub rgyud 'brel phrin las gsan //
NK026(la)001:5571: khyad par bla ma brgya rtsa mnyes par bsten //
NK026(la)001:5572: thub dang pad+mas lung bstan spyan ras gzigs //
NK026(la)001:5573: thugs dam zhal gzigs dam can ci bcol nyan //
NK026(la)001:5574: mkha' 'gros lung bstan phyi nang gtsug lag bzhengs //
NK026(la)001:5575: grub rtags zhabs rjes spyi dpal dpal chen bzhengs //
NK026(la)001:5576: 'dir gshegs skal ldan zur chen slob ma rtse mo grub chen bzhi //
NK026(la)001:5577: zur chung shes grags rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5578: zur chen zhabs drung dbu yi rjes kyang bzhag //
NK026(la)001:5579: bshos lhag tsan+dana sdong por sangs rgyas 'khrungs //
NK026(la)001:5580: 'dir gshegs skal ldan mtsho nya'i bzang sgom shes rab rgyal po ni //
NK026(la)001:5581: rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal te la stod ra sa yi //
NK026(la)001:5582: zhang ston 'gos chung rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5583: bres phu'i mi nyag 'byung grags bde ba rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5584: bram gyi btsag ston la sogs rtse lkog brgyad //
NK026(la)001:5585: drag po rtsal te zur chung dngos slob bzhi //
NK026(la)001:5586: 'dir gshegs skal ldan gdung brgyad gong bu'i skyo ston sh+aaka ye ni //
NK026(la)001:5587: snying po rtsal te rdzogs chen ka ba yin //
NK026(la)001:5588: mda' phu'i mda' tig jo sh+aaka dngos grub rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5589: phrin las ka ba chu bar klan sh+aaka bzang //
NK026(la)001:5590: myu gu rtsal te sgyu 'phrul ka ba yin //
NK026(la)001:5591: shab kyi dgongs lung yang khyed bla ma ni //
NK026(la)001:5592: 'gyur med rtsal te mdo lung ka ba'o //
NK026(la)001:5593: nya tshal sh+aaka byang ma thog na ser gyi //
NK026(la)001:5594: jo sing la sogs rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5595: 'dir gshegs skal ldan gsang bdag sh+aaka seng dbang phyug rdzogs pa rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5596: 'dir gshegs skal ldan mgar ston zung nge mkha' la bskor ba mdzad //
NK026(la)001:5597: brag la phur btab rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5598: 'dir gshegs skal ldan sreg ston rdor rgyal rdo rje 'jigs med rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5599: glan ban rdor 'od rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK026(la)001:5600: 'dir gshegs skal ldan sprul sku brtson seng rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5601: glan ston bsod rgyal phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5602: glan ston sangs rgyas dpal gyi bde byed rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5603: 'dir gshegs skal ldan sprul sku rtsal 'bum de sras glan ston ni //
NK026(la)001:5604: bsod nams mgon po nyang chen shes rab dpal //
NK026(la)001:5605: gyeng khang gzi ston sh+aakya bzang po rnams //
NK026(la)001:5606: drag po rtsal te 'bro ston rdo rje ni //
NK026(la)001:5607: rdo rje bde chen rtsal te rig 'dzin gnas //
NK026(la)001:5608: 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgyud lung man ngag dbang sgrub kun gyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:5609: rgyal tshab bstan 'dzin gdul bya skyong ba'i dpal //
NK026(la)001:5610: mang thos kun mkhyen rtogs pa mngon du gyur //
NK026(la)001:5611: sh+aakya 'byung gnas rdo rje thod phreng rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5612: 'dir gshegs skal ldan lha dang rtogs pa dbyer med 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK026(la)001:5613: gdul bya smin grol mkha' spyod gnas su gshegs //
NK026(la)001:5614: sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal te rdo rje thogs med rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5615: 'dir gshegs skal ldan bshad sgrub mthar phyin tshe yi rig 'dzin thob //
NK026(la)001:5616: chu bo bzhi rdzogs dbang chen dngos su byon //
NK026(la)001:5617: legs pa dpal bzang rdo rje dbang sdud rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5618: 'dir gshegs skal ldan 'di man chod kyi bla ma'i
NK026(la)001:5619: bskur tshig rnams khyab bdag sman lung pa chen po'i
NK026(la)001:5621: ri sbug bde chen yang rtse ru //
NK026(la)001:5622: sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal po des //
NK026(la)001:5623: zung dbang chos rje'i zhabs pad bsnyen //
NK026(la)001:5624: ye shes bla ma'i sar gshegs nas //
NK026(la)001:5625: smin grol bdud rtsi'i char rgyun phab //
NK026(la)001:5626: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5627: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu bskyang du gsol /
NK026(la)001:5628: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:5629: shangs kyi chu dbar nyi phug tu //
NK026(la)001:5630: mdo sgyu sems gsum bstan pa spel //
NK026(la)001:5631: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug dngos grub brnyes //
NK026(la)001:5632: brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang zhes //
NK026(la)001:5633: grags snyan srid gsum pha mthar brgal //
NK026(la)001:5634: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin 'dir gshegs skal ldan mdo dbang bdud rtsis thugs rgyud bkrus //
NK026(la)001:5635: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed zhal gzigs //
NK026(la)001:5636: legs ldan mgon pos sras su sprul //
NK026(la)001:5637: snying rjes ma rung dbyings su bsgral //
NK026(la)001:5638: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan de //
NK026(la)001:5639: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin 'dir gshegs skal ldan chu bo ri sogs gar bzhugs su //
NK026(la)001:5641: bya ba gzhan gyis thugs mi g.yeng //
NK026(la)001:5642: dam chos 'khor ba dbyings sgrol sogs //
NK026(la)001:5643: zab gter du ma'i sgo 'byed mdzad //
NK026(la)001:5644: mtshan ni legs ldan bdud kun 'joms //
NK026(la)001:5645: gsang mtshan rdo rje gro lod rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5646: rdo rje 'chang dngos rgyal ba de //
NK026(la)001:5647: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin 'dir gshegs skal ldan pad+ma 'byung gnas dngos nyid las //
NK026(la)001:5648: ming gzhan lang gro lo tsa che'i //
NK026(la)001:5649: skyes rabs tshar du dngar ba'i rgyan //
NK026(la)001:5651: rdo rje 'chang chen sgo rum pa //
NK026(la)001:5652: kun dga' legs pa'i zhabs pad dang //
NK026(la)001:5653: mtshar chen chos kyi rgyal po sogs //
NK026(la)001:5654: rgyal rnams dgyes pa'i rgyal tshab mchog /
NK026(la)001:5655: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug des //
NK026(la)001:5657: 'dus pa chen po'i smin byed gsan //
NK026(la)001:5658: grol byed dgongs nyams klong du gyur //
NK026(la)001:5659: lcang lo can du rab gshegs nas //
NK026(la)001:5660: da lta zangs mdog dpal rir bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5661: 'dir gshegs skal ldan mkhyen brtse'i thugs sras rdo rje 'chang //
NK026(la)001:5662: yang srid len pa'i las nyon dang //
NK026(la)001:5663: bral yang dpyal pa kun mkhyen che //
NK026(la)001:5664: de nas tshul khrims rgyal mtshan zhabs //
NK026(la)001:5665: rgyal yum tshul khrims bzang mo sogs //
NK026(la)001:5666: dam pa du ma'i tshul bstan nas //
NK026(la)001:5667: rtsod dus rgyal bstan srog shing mchog /
NK026(la)001:5668: dbang phyug rab brtan bka' drin can //
NK026(la)001:5669: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin 'dir gshegs skal ldan 'jam mgon
NK026(la)001:5670: mkhyen brtse yab sras gnyis tshig brgyud la ma drangs
NK026(la)001:5672: 'on kyang deng sang mdo dbang ni rgyun ma chad
NK026(la)001:5673: tsam 'di dam pa 'di gnyis kyi bka' drin yin
NK026(la)001:5674: cing / dgongs pa rgyud kyi dbang du byas na nges par dgos sam snyam pa lags /
NK026(la)001:5675: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i bka' drin las //
NK026(la)001:5676: legs ldan bdud 'joms rdo rje mjal //
NK026(la)001:5677: mdo dbang smin grol gdams rdzogs nas //
NK026(la)001:5678: rgyab rten mdo lung dgongs 'dus gsan //
NK026(la)001:5679: dbang phyug rab brtan rgyal ba yi //
NK026(la)001:5680: dgongs pas byin rlabs mdo dbang rgyun //
NK026(la)001:5681: khyod kyis spel zhes gnang ba thob //
NK026(la)001:5682: pho brang bsam rtse'i spel dkar du //
NK026(la)001:5683: mdo dbang gtad rgyar bcas pa mdzad //
NK026(la)001:5684: skyi ston tshe ring dbang por grags //
NK026(la)001:5685: gsang mtshan rol pa'i rdo rje ste //
NK026(la)001:5686: da lta rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5687: 'dir gshegs skal ldan dam pa du ma'i zhabs pad bsnyen //
NK026(la)001:5688: rtsa rlung dgongs pa mngon du gyur //
NK026(la)001:5689: char yang spyi bo'i gtsug tu bcings //
NK026(la)001:5690: tshangs par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK026(la)001:5691: chos kyi rgyal po rdo rje'i mtshan //
NK026(la)001:5692: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin 'dir gshegs skal ldan 'di yan bla ma'i gsung /
NK026(la)001:5693: kho bo'i yongs 'dzin mchog gi tsakli'i rgyab byang ni 'dir ltar /
NK026(la)001:5694: sman lung dam pa'i rig 'khrungs nas //
NK026(la)001:5695: bstan 'gro'i don la brtser dgongs te //
NK026(la)001:5696: rgyal bstan mdo sngags bka' gter gyi //
NK026(la)001:5697: sgom sgrub 'chad nyan phyogs brgyar spel //
NK026(la)001:5698: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi //
NK026(la)001:5699: bstan pa'i me ro slar gsol phyir //
NK026(la)001:5701: bkas bskul bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan btsugs //
NK026(la)001:5702: lhag par bdag la thugs brtse bas //
NK026(la)001:5703: smin grol bdud rtsi'i rgyun bzang po //
NK026(la)001:5704: ci yang stsol ba'i thugs rje can //
NK026(la)001:5705: bka' drin bskal par gzhal dka' ba'i //
NK026(la)001:5706: drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma mchog /
NK026(la)001:5707: 'khor lo'i dbang phyug sman lung pa //
NK026(la)001:5708: rab mthong blo gros mchog gi sde //
NK026(la)001:5709: gsang mtshan rig pa'i rdo rje rtsal /
NK026(la)001:5710: da lta 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:5711: nges shes mos gus rtse gcig gis //
NK026(la)001:5712: snying nas gsol ba 'debs lags na //
NK026(la)001:5713: brtse ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK026(la)001:5714: mgon khyod rig 'dzin brgyud par bcas //
NK026(la)001:5715: thugs kyi bzhed pa bskang slad du //
NK026(la)001:5716: 'chad nyan bgyi bar rtsol lags na //
NK026(la)001:5717: 'dir gshegs skal ldan srin bu me khyer nyi zla'i 'od la snyeg pa'i dper snang yang /
NK026(la)001:5718: tshig brgyud mi chad pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK026(la)001:5719: skal pa bzang po'i smon lam gyi mtshams sbyor ba'i
NK026(la)001:5720: phyir rtsom pa po rang nyid kyi mtshang bstan pa
NK026(la)001:5721: ni 'di ltar / thub bstan e wam chos grwa ru //
NK026(la)001:5722: lha btsun pad+ma phrin las zhes //
NK026(la)001:5723: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'joms rtsal //
NK026(la)001:5724: tshangs par spyod pa'i rdo rje 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:5725: dam pa du ma'i bka' drin las //
NK026(la)001:5726: yongs rdzogs bstan la rab zhugs te //
NK026(la)001:5727: sdom pa gsum gyi bka' drin nos //
NK026(la)001:5728: mdo sngags smin grol gdams pas phyug /
NK026(la)001:5729: rgyal dbang pad+ma'i phrin las spel //
NK026(la)001:5730: phyi ma zangs mdog dpal rir smin //
NK026(la)001:5731: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye rgu bskyang du gsol //
NK026(la)001:5732: skal ldan byin rlabs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:5733: de yang rig 'dzin bla ma 'di rnams 'og min
NK026(la)001:5734: du 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor gyi khyams la bzhugs
NK026(la)001:5735: nges pas slob ma la byin gyis brlabs pa'i dgos
NK026(la)001:5737: mdor na mdo dbang bskur ba po'i bla ma de
NK026(la)001:5738: so so skye bo zhig yin yang dam tshig dang
NK026(la)001:5739: ldan na phyi ma 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor rig
NK026(la)001:5740: 'dzin gyi gral du chud par lung las gsungs shing
NK026(la)001:5741: 'di ltar 'gyur nges par rgya bod kyi rig 'dzin
NK026(la)001:5742: gong mas dbu snyung bzhes pa yin pas the tshom
NK026(la)001:5743: mi bya'o // zhes yig rnying dag las 'byung bas
NK026(la)001:5744: de'i phyir na yid ches bskyed la mos gus drag
NK026(la)001:5745: po dang ldan pa mchog tu gces so //
NK026(la)001:5746: 'di yan cho ga la zhag ji tsam thogs kyang
NK026(la)001:5747: nang re bzhin rgyud lung spel ba'i phrin las 'dzab
NK026(la)001:5749: nub re bzhin chos srung mchod skang zhi khro'i tshogs kyi phrin las /
NK026(la)001:5750: skong bshags sogs bya ba shin tu gces shing /
NK026(la)001:5751: dbang zhag gi bar du gcod dgos pa'i mtshams der gtang rag man+dala dang dge ba bsngo /
NK026(la)001:5752: 'dzugs khar khrus bgegs skrod dang mtshams sbyor gyi bshad pas spros te man+dala dang /
NK026(la)001:5753: byang chub rdo rje sogs ji ltar rigs pas gsol ba gdab pa kun la 'agre'o //
NK026(la)001:5755: de nas dbang rdzogs nas lha dbang de dag brtan
NK026(la)001:5756: par byed pa'i yan lag tu ngang sgom gyi khrid
NK026(la)001:5758: de la yang lha sgom pa dang /
NK026(la)001:5759: man ngag sgom pa gnyis las /
NK026(la)001:5760: dang po lha sgom pa ni gnyis te /
NK026(la)001:5763: dang po ni me tog phog pa'i lha gang yin bstan la sku ngo sprad //
NK026(la)001:5764: snying po bzlas lung phog la gsung ngo sprad /
NK026(la)001:5765: chos thams cad mnyam nyid thugs su ngo sprad /
NK026(la)001:5766: nus pa phun sum tshogs pas yon tan ngo sprad /
NK026(la)001:5767: rdzas dbang bskur bas phrin las ngo sprad /
NK026(la)001:5768: ces gsungs pa'i don ni zhi khro'i lha me tog
NK026(la)001:5769: gang la phog pa de'i sku bstan cing bskyed rim
NK026(la)001:5770: dang snying po'i bzlas lung phog la /
NK026(la)001:5771: de thams cad zung 'jug gi lam du 'khyer bas /
NK026(la)001:5772: de'i yon tan dang rdzas dbang thob pas las bzhi
NK026(la)001:5773: gang brtsams 'grub pa phrin las yin par ngo sprad
NK026(la)001:5774: cing / khyad par spyi 'dzab gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK026(la)001:5775: ru lu 'di tsam bzla ba'i dam bca' blang ba ni lha dang snying po lam 'khyer /
NK026(la)001:5776: rgyud lung gi las byang rnam grangs mang yang /
NK026(la)001:5777: chog khrigs 'di'i khongs su zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba dang /
NK026(la)001:5778: khro bo dam pa rgyan te rgyud kyi las byang /
NK026(la)001:5779: de'i gsal 'debs lung gi las byang zhi thung khro
NK026(la)001:5780: thung sogs thams cad tshang bar yod pas rgyas bsdus
NK026(la)001:5781: gang 'thad ci lcogs kyi nyams len byed pa'i dam
NK026(la)001:5783: de ni bum dbang gi lam 'khyer ma h+aa yo
NK026(la)001:5784: ga dang rjes su mthun pa'i bskyed rim gyi rnal
NK026(la)001:5785: 'byor ro // rdzogs rim ni rtsa bar /
NK026(la)001:5786: de dag kyang thog ma nas rang la yod cing de ltar yin pas ngo sprad do //
NK026(la)001:5787: des mtshon nas snang srid thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du longs spyod cing lam du 'khyer la /
NK026(la)001:5788: thams cad lhar gsal ba lta ba /
NK026(la)001:5789: de'i ngang la gnas pa sgom pa /
NK026(la)001:5790: lha la lha rol pa spyod pa /
NK026(la)001:5791: de las mi 'da' ba dam tshig /
NK026(la)001:5793: zhes gsungs pa bzhin ngo sprad /
NK026(la)001:5796: glang po che chang gis myos pa lta bu ste /
NK026(la)001:5797: ngang sgom chung ngu'i thad du slob pa'o //
NK026(la)001:5798: de nas bdag che mchog lta bu yi dam gyi
NK026(la)001:5799: lhar gsal ba'i spyi bor thig le dmar po sran
NK026(la)001:5801: de bas khru gang gis mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam zhig bsgom /
NK026(la)001:5802: de nas sna bug g.yon nas 'od dmar po sran
NK026(la)001:5803: ma tsam zhig byung nas spyi bo'i thig le dmar
NK026(la)001:5804: po la phog / des bdag rkyen byas nas thig le las 'od 'phros /
NK026(la)001:5807: de bzhin gshegs pa la phog /
NK026(la)001:5808: thugs mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK026(la)001:5810: thig le dmar po 'od du zhu /
NK026(la)001:5811: yang sna bug g.yas nas 'od dkar po byung gong gi thig le dkar po la phog 'od 'phros /
NK026(la)001:5812: sems can gyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK026(la)001:5813: de bzhin gshegs pa la mchod pa phul /
NK026(la)001:5815: thig le dkar po dmar po la thim ste tshangs bug nas snying gi dkyil du thim nas /
NK026(la)001:5816: bde stong gnyis med kyi ngang la bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:5817: de ni lha sgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK026(la)001:5818: gnyis pa man ngag sgom pa la gnyis te /
NK026(la)001:5821: dang po steng sgo sgom pa ni /
NK026(la)001:5822: ngang sgom 'bring po ste rang gi lus phru ma
NK026(la)001:5823: lta bu'i nang du a wa d+h+au ti sbom phra
NK026(la)001:5824: mda' smyug 'bring po tsam phyi dmar la nang dkar
NK026(la)001:5826: mar sna srog shing gter po che /
NK026(la)001:5832: klad pa chos 'khor dang gdugs te lus mchod rten du sgom /
NK026(la)001:5833: de'i rtser srog mi shigs pa'i ngo bo thig le
NK026(la)001:5834: ham gi rang bzhin sran ma tsam zhig gnas pa
NK026(la)001:5838: 'od tshur 'dus ham gi thig le la phog 'od
NK026(la)001:5839: du zhu bla ma tog gi tshul du bzhugs pa
NK026(la)001:5840: la thim / de la shes pa gtad pas de yang 'od du tshangs bug nas zhugs /
NK026(la)001:5841: snying gi dkyil du thim pas /
NK026(la)001:5842: rang gi sems dang dbyer med du 'dres pa'i ngang la ma bcos par bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:5843: gnyis pa 'og sgo sgom pa ni /
NK026(la)001:5844: spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam /
NK026(la)001:5845: de'i steng mda' gang du dkar po sran ma tsam zhig bsam /
NK026(la)001:5846: de nas dmar po la shes pa gtad pas de
NK026(la)001:5847: chags pa'i rang bzhin 'dar bas rkyen byas nas dkar
NK026(la)001:5848: po'ang 'dar nas dmar po la thim gcig tu 'dres
NK026(la)001:5850: snying gi dkyil du thim ste bde stong dbyer med kyi ngang la bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:5851: de ni ma h+aa yo ga'i ngang sgom gyi man ngag go //
NK026(la)001:5852: zhes gsungs pa'i don de dag kyang zhib tu bkrol
NK026(la)001:5853: te bshad la gdams ngag thebs nges par bya ba
NK026(la)001:5854: ni ma h+aa yo ga'i ngang sgom gdams ngag lam
NK026(la)001:5855: khyer ro // gnyis pa ni rtsa bar /
NK026(la)001:5856: lung a nu yo ga'i man ngag ni theg pa a nu yo ga /
NK026(la)001:5857: lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer med /
NK026(la)001:5858: de'i ngang la gnas pa bsgom pa /
NK026(la)001:5859: spyod lam bzhir de dang mi 'bral ba spyod pa /
NK026(la)001:5860: de las mi 'da' ba dam tshig /
NK026(la)001:5863: chu bo bzhin du rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK026(la)001:5866: de'ang snying gi dkyil du thig le dkar po phug ron gyi sgo nga tsam zhig bsam /
NK026(la)001:5867: de las 'od spyi gtsug na yar skam mda' 'phangs pa bzhin thon /
NK026(la)001:5868: de las thig phran bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros
NK026(la)001:5869: nas je che je che la stong gsum gyi stong
NK026(la)001:5870: chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams gang bar bsam /
NK026(la)001:5871: thig phran rnams tshur 'dus thig le la thim pas ro gcig tu 'dres /
NK026(la)001:5872: dbyings rig pa dbyer med bde ba chen po'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:5873: de dag kyang dmigs pas rten bcas pa de rjes
NK026(la)001:5874: ka dag gi ngang du ci gnas su mnyam pa
NK026(la)001:5875: bzhag pa kho na gnas su che'o //
NK026(la)001:5876: de ltar bum dbang 'khor bcas sam phyi dbang bcu /
NK026(la)001:5878: sgrub dbang bcu gsum rnams thob pa'i rtogs pa bskyed pa ni rtsa bar /
NK026(la)001:5880: gang gi gang la gang bstan pa //
NK026(la)001:5881: ci phyir dgos pa ye gnas pa //
NK026(la)001:5884: gang du gsungs pa'i gnas pad+ma me tog 'ja' tshon gyi tshal du'o //
NK026(la)001:5885: gang gis bskur ba'i slob dpon ni ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub bo //
NK026(la)001:5886: gang la bskur ba'i slob ma ni h+aum mdzad rdo rje dang 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs pa'o //
NK026(la)001:5887: skabs 'dir glan ston gyi bzhed par /
NK026(la)001:5888: bskyed rdzogs gnyis sam rgyud lung ste yo ga gnyis
NK026(la)001:5889: thun mong du gnas ni ri ma la ya'i rtse'am
NK026(la)001:5890: rgyal po dzah'i khab tu dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK026(la)001:5891: dang gsang ba'i bdag por rgyal po dzahl dbang bskur
NK026(la)001:5892: zhing rgyud don thams cad bshad /
NK026(la)001:5893: de nas lo brgya lhag nas byu ru dmar po chu mig dgu sgril gyi tshal /
NK026(la)001:5894: d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu yang rdo rje
NK026(la)001:5895: sems dpa' dang gsang bdag gis slob dpon chen po
NK026(la)001:5896: dga' rab rdo rje la bshad /
NK026(la)001:5897: de nas slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje zhes sam
NK026(la)001:5898: slob dpon ro langs bde ba zhes bya ba des
NK026(la)001:5899: / o rgyan yul ma ga d+ha'i brag phug tu o rgyan gyi rgyal po d+har+m+aa ka ya dang /
NK026(la)001:5900: za hor gyi rgyal po pra hasti dang /
NK026(la)001:5901: slob dpon chen po h+aum mdzad rdo rje dang /
NK026(la)001:5902: sing nga la'i r+aa dza 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la
NK026(la)001:5903: sogs pa mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa
NK026(la)001:5904: rnams la bskur zhes gsungs pa khungs dang 'brel bar
NK026(la)001:5906: gang bskur ba'i dbang ni dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK026(la)001:5911: rgyu mtshan mi lus bsgrub pa'i phyir ro //
NK026(la)001:5912: dgos pa'am 'bras bu yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa'o //
NK026(la)001:5913: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni lugs 'di'i dbu zhabs thams cad du /
NK026(la)001:5915: zhes don drug tu bstan pa'i tshul gyis 'chad par
NK026(la)001:5916: snang bas ma h+aa dang a nu'i 'gag drug gi
NK026(la)001:5917: dgongs pa bstan pa yin no //
NK026(la)001:5919: de nas chu brgyad gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'dzab mang du bzlas la /
NK026(la)001:5920: zhes gsungs pas gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi dmigs khrid
NK026(la)001:5921: tshar nas chu brgyad ces pa yig nor 'dra bas
NK026(la)001:5922: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum zhes ru lu
NK026(la)001:5923: 'bru brgyad dang gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta
NK026(la)001:5924: ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes 'dzab dbyangs
NK026(la)001:5925: dang bcas te mang du bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK026(la)001:5927: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral gyis bsnyen pa dang /
NK026(la)001:5930: sgrub pa chen po'i sgo nas bzlas brjod kyi bsnyen
NK026(la)001:5931: pa 'di dag 'bul zhing mchis na thugs rje chen
NK026(la)001:5932: pos dgongs shing bzhes nas bdag cag la sku gsung
NK026(la)001:5933: thugs kyi dngos grub da lta nyid stsal du gsol
NK026(la)001:5934: / zhes rjes zlos dang bcas te brjod /
NK026(la)001:5935: 'dir mar me smon lam chung ba zhig yod kyang
NK026(la)001:5936: phyag bzhes su 'og tu mar me smon lam dngos
NK026(la)001:5937: dang sbrel nas mdzad pa yin /
NK026(la)001:5939: de nas zhag bcur 'gro ba'i nyin mo rdzogs chen
NK026(la)001:5940: gyi dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab ma bcu drug pa mu
NK026(la)001:5941: khyud dang bcas pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la lte
NK026(la)001:5943: 'dab mar a bcu drug rnams dkar po /
NK026(la)001:5944: pad skor gyi mthar snying dkar dmar gyi shun pa rtsa ba shar /
NK026(la)001:5945: rtse mo nub tu bstan pa bri /
NK026(la)001:5946: gting du rtsa ris rtse mo pad gdan la reg pa bya /
NK026(la)001:5947: glo 'bur gru chad 'ja' ris phyi 'od skor zhing khams rta babs sgo pad+ma rdo ra me ri /
NK026(la)001:5948: mtha' rgyas gru bzhi lcags ri phyogs mdog bya'o //
NK026(la)001:5949: a bco brgyad po kun bzang yab yum bco brgyad du bsgom /
NK026(la)001:5950: bum par rdzas blug la dbus su dgod /
NK026(la)001:5951: de'i chu kun bzang yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems su bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:5952: gzhan yang rgya bod kyi bla ma brgyud pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rten dgod do //
NK026(la)001:5953: zhes gsungs pa'i don 'og tu rgyas par 'byung bas rgyas bshad kyi lag len de'i skabs su ston /
NK026(la)001:5955: de'i shar du 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon dbus mthing khar
NK026(la)001:5956: rigs lnga bskyed pa'i dbus kyi mi bskyod pa yab
NK026(la)001:5957: yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang sems su bsam pa'am
NK026(la)001:5958: / yang na 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa byas la bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor sgom /
NK026(la)001:5959: thod pa mtshan ldan du byang sems 'o bur sbyar ba dgod pa bdud rtsir bsgrub /
NK026(la)001:5960: ces gsungs pa'i don gong du yo byad bshams pa'i skabs su bstan pa ltar /
NK026(la)001:5961: tshogs chen gyi dbang la 'jug khar 'khor lo rtsibs
NK026(la)001:5962: bzhi pa'i dkyil 'khor bshams pa dang che mchog khro
NK026(la)001:5963: mkhar gyi tshul du lam tsam bsgrubs te /
NK026(la)001:5964: gsang dbang thun mong ba bskur zin na'ang thun mong
NK026(la)001:5965: ma yin pa'i dbang gong ma'i byin rlabs slad kyis
NK026(la)001:5966: bya dgos pas bdud rtsi kha gaso'o //
NK026(la)001:5968: nub tu tshe yi dkyil 'khor rtsibs bzhi ser /
NK026(la)001:5969: lte ba dmar por tshe yi 'brang rgyas bsham /
NK026(la)001:5970: gzhan yang mchod gtor so ma dang tshogs kyi yo byad bsham mo //
NK026(la)001:5971: zhes gsungs pa'i don dkyil 'khor chen po'i nub phyogs
NK026(la)001:5972: su stegs kyi khar tshe'i dkyil 'khor lte ba dmar
NK026(la)001:5974: de'i dbus su rin po che'i bum pa rdzas ldan g.yas su mar me /
NK026(la)001:5975: g.yon du gong gi yo byad bshams pa'i skabs kyi tshe 'brang bzhag /
NK026(la)001:5976: gzhan yang g.yas su tshe ril /
NK026(la)001:5978: tshe dpag med kyi mchog gtor zlum po 'dab bzhis bskor ba sman raka nyer spyod sogs kyang bsham /
NK026(la)001:5979: gzhan yang dkyil 'khor gyi mchod gtor tshogs ba skang gi yo byad rnams kyang rgya cher bsham mo //
NK026(la)001:5983: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni thog mar cha gsum btang /
NK026(la)001:5984: rdo rjes tshul phyag dang gral phyag nas bzung mtshams gcod sogs sngon 'gro'i rim pa dang /
NK026(la)001:5985: dngos gzhi rgyud lung gi zhi khro'i las byang 'dzab khang dbye ba dang 'dzab /
NK026(la)001:5989: dkyil 'khor du rig pa'i me tog dor ba sogs thams cad snga ma ltar rgyas par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:5990: bye brag gsang dbang gi byin rlabs kyi rdzas bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor sgrub pa ni /
NK026(la)001:5992: de nas badz+ra tsakra zhes pas mdun du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i shar du bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:5994: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:5995: byang du karma he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:5996: dbus su badz+ra he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:5997: de'i steng du thugs byang chub sems la yum khro mo gnam zhal ma dbu dgu /
NK026(la)001:6000: de yang dbu dgu ni ye shes dgu /
NK026(la)001:6001: phyag bco brgyad dbang po drug /
NK026(la)001:6003: rnam shes drug ste khams bco brgyad kyi rang bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:6004: zhabs bzhi ni rnam shes bzhis rigs bzhi ste he ru ka mnan pa'o //
NK026(la)001:6005: de'i steng du thugs byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin che mchog he ru ka dbu dgu /
NK026(la)001:6008: dbu dgu he ru ka dgu /
NK026(la)001:6009: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje rtse dgus dung dmar dkrug pa /
NK026(la)001:6010: g.yas brgyad kyis koo r+ai sogs brgyad /
NK026(la)001:6011: g.yon brgyad kyis sing+ha sogs brgyad /
NK026(la)001:6012: zhabs brgyad rnam shes tshogs brgyad khro mo'i dbu brgyad mnan pa /
NK026(la)001:6013: gnam zhal ma'i dbu gong ma'i zhal e gru gsum du yab kyi rdo rje bcug par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:6015: badz+ra tsakra zhes brjod pas bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor de
NK026(la)001:6016: nyid 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi par gyur pa'i shar du
NK026(la)001:6017: bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum smug dkar dmar ba'i
NK026(la)001:6018: zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum 'khor lo rgyu
NK026(la)001:6019: zhags khyung khra / g.yon gsum thod khrag zhags pa mi mgo 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:6020: yum bud+d+ha khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril pa /
NK026(la)001:6021: lhor rat+na he ru ka yab yum ser sngo dmar
NK026(la)001:6022: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rin chen
NK026(la)001:6024: g.yon gsum b+han dmar rgyu zhags ri rab bsnams pa /
NK026(la)001:6025: yum rat+na khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK026(la)001:6026: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka yab yum dmar dkar
NK026(la)001:6027: sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum pad+ma
NK026(la)001:6029: g.yon gsum b+han dmar thong gshol 'jig rten 'degs pa /
NK026(la)001:6030: yum pad+ma khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK026(la)001:6031: byang du karma he ru ka yab yum ljang dkar
NK026(la)001:6032: dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rgya
NK026(la)001:6034: g.yon gsum b+han dmar thong gshol zhags pa 'dzin /
NK026(la)001:6035: yum las kyi khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK026(la)001:6036: dbus su badz+ra he ru ka yab yum mthing dkar
NK026(la)001:6037: dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo
NK026(la)001:6039: g.yon gsum zhags pa lcags sgrog thong gshol can yum
NK026(la)001:6040: badz+ra kro d+hi dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba
NK026(la)001:6041: / de'i steng du thugs byang chub kyi sems las
NK026(la)001:6042: khro mo gnam zhal ma ye shes dgu dang ldan
NK026(la)001:6044: dbus zhal mthing ba e gru gsum gyi rnam pa can gyen du gdengs pa /
NK026(la)001:6045: g.yas zhal bzhi ljang dmar mthing ser zhal g.yas su 'khor ba /
NK026(la)001:6046: g.yon zhal bzhi dmar ljang dkar dmar ba g.yon nas 'khor ba /
NK026(la)001:6049: rnam shes drug ste khams bco brgyad kyi rang bzhin phyag bco brgyad /
NK026(la)001:6050: rnam shes bzhi'i rang bzhin zhabs bzhis he ru ka rigs bzhi'i dbu mnan pa /
NK026(la)001:6051: de'i steng du thugs byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dpal che mchog he ru ka dbu dgu /
NK026(la)001:6054: de yang dbu dgu ni rgyud lung gi he ru
NK026(la)001:6055: ka dgu'i rangabazhina gyi dbus zhal brtsegs ma gsum mthing
NK026(la)001:6057: g.yon zhal gsum dmar ba 'og gi gnam zhal ma
NK026(la)001:6058: dang steng gi che mchog gnyis ka phyag mtshan mthun
NK026(la)001:6059: par phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje rtse dgus dung
NK026(la)001:6060: dmar dkrugs pa / g.yas brgyad na goo r+ai la sogs pa'i khro mo brgyad /
NK026(la)001:6061: g.yon brgyad na sid+ha ma la sogs pa'i phra men brgyad /
NK026(la)001:6062: rnam shes tshogs brgyad dag pa'i zhabs brgyad kyis khro mo gnam zhal ma'i dbu brgyad mnan pa /
NK026(la)001:6063: yum gyi zhal dbus mar gsang rdor bcug pa'o //
NK026(la)001:6065: de ltar gsal ba dang phyag g.yas gnyis pa khro
NK026(la)001:6066: mo go r+ai dkar mo zhing dbyug pa bsnams pa
NK026(la)001:6067: de g.yab cing / badz+ra a yu pa la zhes
NK026(la)001:6068: bzlas pa'i rkyen gyis yab yum gnyis bsgul bskyod phrin
NK026(la)001:6069: las mdzad pas dgyes pa'i rol pa chen po sku
NK026(la)001:6070: nyams su bstar zhing yum gyi zhal du gsang ba'i
NK026(la)001:6071: rdo rje 'tshir zhing 'khyil ba dang byang sems 'bab
NK026(la)001:6072: cing lha thams cad sbyor ba mdzad pa'i mkha' gsang
NK026(la)001:6073: las byang sems yum gyi mkha' babs pa bdud rtsi'i
NK026(la)001:6074: dkyil 'khor thams cad mer gyis khengs te rigs bzhi
NK026(la)001:6075: he ru ka sogs kyi spyan phyed nub tsam du
NK026(la)001:6076: gyur pa de dag mkha' la babs pas thams cad
NK026(la)001:6077: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du gyur pa de
NK026(la)001:6081: tshar 'dus pas che mchog de nyid dbu nyer gcig phyag zhe gnyis par gyur te /
NK026(la)001:6082: sa nyer gcig non pa'i dbu nyer gcig ni 'di lta ste /
NK026(la)001:6083: rtsa zhal dang sku mdog mthing nag /
NK026(la)001:6084: g.yas zhal gsum ser dmar ljang /
NK026(la)001:6085: g.yon gsum dmar sngo ljang ba ste 'khor zhal bdun bsgrigs /
NK026(la)001:6088: g.yon gnyis mthing dkar ba ste 'khor zhal lnga bsgrigs /
NK026(la)001:6091: g.yon gnyis dmar dkar te 'khor zhal lnga bsgrigs /
NK026(la)001:6095: steng zhal dmar po'i steng rta dbu ljang gu rta skad sgrog pa /
NK026(la)001:6096: phyag zhe gnyis kyis lha zhi ba sangs rgyas zhe gnyis bsnams pa /
NK026(la)001:6097: zhabs brgyad kyis khro mo'i dbu brgyad 'khor zhal du gnas pa dang sbyor zhing /
NK026(la)001:6098: dbus zhal dang gsang rdor sbyor ba'o //
NK026(la)001:6100: 'phags pa rnams kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK026(la)001:6102: slar 'dus pas che mchog de nyid dbu stong phyag
NK026(la)001:6103: stong spyan stong stong gsum gyi stong chen po dang
NK026(la)001:6104: ldan pas badz+ra badz+ra zhes pa'i sgra bsgrags pas /
NK026(la)001:6105: 'jig rten gyi lha chen po dang /
NK026(la)001:6107: gnod sbyin la sogs pa thams cad bred nas dngangs
NK026(la)001:6108: shing mgrin gcig tu bdag cag 'bangs su mchi zer
NK026(la)001:6110: de las skad cig gi che mchog he ru ka
NK026(la)001:6111: de nyid sku mdog smug nag smug dkar dmar ba'i
NK026(la)001:6112: zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje g.yon
NK026(la)001:6113: gsum b+han dmar bsnams par gyur /
NK026(la)001:6115: de las khro bo che mchog smug nag tu bskyed
NK026(la)001:6116: pa'am lcogs na badz+ra he ru ka'i steng du rgyu'i
NK026(la)001:6117: che mchog zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'am /
NK026(la)001:6118: 'bras bu'i zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK026(la)001:6119: dbang mchog gi dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa dang 'di rnams gang mos su bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:6121: de nas che mchog zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang
NK026(la)001:6122: yum khro mkhar gyi rnam par bzhugs par mos te
NK026(la)001:6123: / a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:6124: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:6126: yab yum dgyes par rol pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK026(la)001:6127: rgyud dkyil 'khor gyi thod par babs par bsam mo
NK026(la)001:6128: // skabs 'dir rtsa bar badz+ra rat+na na re /
NK026(la)001:6129: byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK026(la)001:6130: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK026(la)001:6131: kun tu tshim par byed pa'i mchog /
NK026(la)001:6132: dkar dmar 'dres pa'i byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:6133: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK026(la)001:6135: bo d+hi tsit+ta gu h+ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum gis bskur gsung ngo //
NK026(la)001:6139: sh+r+ai ma h+aa su ka bo d+hi badz+ra h+aum ho am /
NK026(la)001:6140: zhes bzlas la gsang dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:6141: bskur thabs logs na yod do //
NK026(la)001:6143: chos kun sgyu mar dbang bskur nas //
NK026(la)001:6144: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK026(la)001:6145: rdzas dang tshig dang gang zag dang //
NK026(la)001:6146: kun rdzob dbang de ma thob kyang //
NK026(la)001:6147: chos la sems kyi dbang thob nas //
NK026(la)001:6148: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK026(la)001:6149: srin gsum dbang chen thams cad kun //
NK026(la)001:6150: de yang dbang mchog bskur bar 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:6151: bla med dbang de thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:6152: a ho ma h+aa su kha hoh zab mo dbang gsum rdzogs pa dang //
NK026(la)001:6153: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK026(la)001:6154: kun tu tshim par byed pa'i ro //
NK026(la)001:6155: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:6156: bu mchog de yi lce la bzhag /
NK026(la)001:6157: gnyis med don dam byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:6158: bu mchog de yi snying la bzhag /
NK026(la)001:6159: brten pa'i ye shes dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:6160: ces gsungs pa 'og gi dbang dngos kyi dus bskur tshig 'dir len pa yin /
NK026(la)001:6161: de nas slob ma rnams khrus nas bton /
NK026(la)001:6163: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu byas la /
NK026(la)001:6164: bla mas thugs bskyed phog rjes 'dir dbang gong ma
NK026(la)001:6165: gsum las thog mar gsang dbang bskur bar byed pa
NK026(la)001:6166: ni / zhes mtshams sbyor rgyas bsdus ci rigs byas la rtsa bar /
NK026(la)001:6167: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:6168: 'dir zab pa'i dbang gsum bstan par bya ste /
