NK026(la)001:10501: de'ang phrin las la thogs pa med cing snang grags thams cad sgyu mar mkhyen pas /
NK026(la)001:10502: dregs pa can bdud kyis bar mi chod cing mngon
NK026(la)001:10503: par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa lags par gda'
NK026(la)001:10504: zhing / des bla ma chen po glan bsod nams
NK026(la)001:10505: rgyal po la yang gdams pa la sogs pa mang
NK026(la)001:10506: du phul nas khong gi zhabs spyi bor len cing
NK026(la)001:10507: zhing / / dam tshig rin po che la gces
NK026(la)001:10508: spras mdzad pa bla ma dam pa rnams sangs rgyas
NK026(la)001:10509: rnams dang mi gnyis par 'khur ba la lags par
NK026(la)001:10510: zhing / / gda' / de ni yang dag par
NK026(la)001:10511: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nas da ltar gyi bla ma
NK026(la)001:10512: chen po chos kyi spyan mig can /
NK026(la)001:10513: yar 'khums su tha mal gyi sems med par grub
NK026(la)001:10514: thob kyi bka' srol chen po gangs kyi thigs pa
NK026(la)001:10515: lta bur bzang za ra tshags su brgyud pa'i brgyud
NK026(la)001:10516: khungs dang gtad rgya'i man ngag ste /
NK026(la)001:10517: tha mal dgongs pa mdo'i lag cha tshes bya ba mdo la gces pa'i cha gcig lags so //
NK026(la)001:10518: lha rje glan chen po'i zhal nas gsungs pa +thii //
NK026(la)001:10520: bla ma chen po bsod rgyal des kho rang gi
NK026(la)001:10521: yab kyis sna drangs pa'i mkhas btsun thams cad la
NK026(la)001:10522: thug / bka' dang rgyu 'bras kyi chos mtha' dag la mkhas shing /
NK026(la)001:10523: skye ba snga ma la shes pa'i rgyud sbyangs /
NK026(la)001:10524: yi dam gyi lhas dngos su dbang bskur nas /
NK026(la)001:10525: dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis lung bstan pa /
NK026(la)001:10526: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa thugs su chud pa /
NK026(la)001:10527: phrin las ji ltar spyod kyang bar chad kyis mi
NK026(la)001:10528: tshugs shing mkhas btsun mang po 'dus par gyur par
NK026(la)001:10529: gda' / des dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge la /
NK026(la)001:10530: de'ang mkhas pa phul du gyur cing rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan /
NK026(la)001:10531: ting nge 'dzin gyi drod dang ldan pa /
NK026(la)001:10532: dge bshes sngags pa kun gyis bkur ba'i 'os su gyur pa lags /
NK026(la)001:10533: des glan sh+aakya dpal la gnang /
NK026(la)001:10534: de'ang gdams pa'i mdzod lta sgom dam tshig gsum 'dzin
NK026(la)001:10535: cing dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa bla ma'i phyag
NK026(la)001:10537: khyad par mdo dbang zur lugs /
NK026(la)001:10540: zhang lugs thams cad gsal bar mnga' ba lags par gda' /
NK026(la)001:10541: des bla ma glan bsod nams mgon po la gnang /
NK026(la)001:10542: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi mnga' bdag tu gyur cing shes bya thogs med du mkhyen /
NK026(la)001:10543: o rgyan pad+mas lung bstan pa bzhin bsam yas pe
NK026(la)001:10544: kar gling nas zab chos shog ril bco lnga byung
NK026(la)001:10545: / bla ma sman lung dbus pa la phul /
NK026(la)001:10546: snyigs ma'i dus su'ang mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan 'gro don mdzad pa zhig lags /
NK026(la)001:10547: yang glan rdor 'od kyis nye ston sangs rgyas 'bum /
NK026(la)001:10549: des glan bsod nams mgon po la gdams pa gtad rgya dang bcas pa gnang ngo //
NK026(la)001:10550: des bla ma bzhi la gnang stee /
NK026(la)001:10551: bla ma rin po che 'bro ston bsam grub rdo
NK026(la)001:10552: rje sngags gsar rnying bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi grub pa
NK026(la)001:10553: thob / rig pa'i gnas lnga mkhyen pa dang gcig /
NK026(la)001:10554: bla ma nyang ston dpal ldan rdo rje rgyud lung rnams kyi phyag bzhes dang /
NK026(la)001:10557: rnam 'joms dkar po la grub pa thob pa dang gnyis /
NK026(la)001:10558: bla ma zi ston sh+aakya bzang po /
NK026(la)001:10560: phrin las shar ba la grub pa thob /
NK026(la)001:10561: mgon po stag zhon dang lha mos las ci bsgo byed pa khas blangs pa dang gsum /
NK026(la)001:10562: shangs mad'i bla ma grags she ba mkhas grub mang
NK026(la)001:10563: po la gtugs shing gshin rje gshed a kro nyin
NK026(la)001:10564: khri mtshan khri brgya mchod stong tshogs /
NK026(la)001:10565: rdzogs bstod lo sum cu lhag tu grub pa dang bzhi la mdo dbang bskur bar gda' /
NK026(la)001:10566: de'i tha mas zur chos kyi seng ge la gtad rgya dang bcas gnang ba'i tshul ni /
NK026(la)001:10567: jo mo slob dpon sras las /
NK026(la)001:10568: bdag sh+aaka 'byung gis cung tsam rig cing mos pa bgyis /
NK026(la)001:10569: kha cig 'di la ci rigs gsung yang dag snang sbyangs bas rig go //
NK026(la)001:10570: bka' dbang bskur zhus pa mi bdog /
NK026(la)001:10571: gnyis pa shang sa gur zhogs bla ma dpal ldan
NK026(la)001:10572: pa bgres pas sngags spyi la mkhas par gda' bas
NK026(la)001:10573: bdag sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi mdo'i dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:10574: glan gyi phur pa man ngag drug pa dang bcas pa /
NK026(la)001:10575: dbang sgrub brgya go gnyis zhal phye nas theg mdo'i gtad rgya ni ma gsan gda' lags /
NK026(la)001:10576: dang po rta nag mda' ba bla ma bsam 'grub nas /
NK026(la)001:10578: na rag dong sprug dbang sgrub /
NK026(la)001:10579: yang dag gzhan don dang me gcig rnams gsan gda' bas zhus nas thob /
NK026(la)001:10580: gtad rgya gsan pa ma grub gda' bas glan bla
NK026(la)001:10581: ma bsod nams mgon po'i phyi tshar gyi slob ma
NK026(la)001:10582: gsum pa bla ma gye khang sh+aakya bzang po des
NK026(la)001:10583: mdo dbang mdzad pa ni med na'ang /
NK026(la)001:10584: bla ma bsam 'grub rdo rje ba la mdo yongs
NK026(la)001:10585: rdzogs kyi phyag bzhes bstan cing bka' thob tsam dang
NK026(la)001:10586: / mdo yongs rdzogs kyi gtad rgya gtad cing gnang bas bka' drin che go bcad /
NK026(la)001:10587: khong med na ni bka' chad par 'dug /
NK026(la)001:10588: da sngags rnying ma'i bstan pa 'di nga rgad po
NK026(la)001:10589: ci la thug kyang dar rgyas su byed gsung mdzad
NK026(la)001:10590: do // dpal rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK026(la)001:10593: chos skyong mkha' 'gro zhal gzigs dang /
NK026(la)001:10594: grub rtags ni du ma bdog go //
NK026(la)001:10595: bla ma bsam 'grub pa des bdag zur h+aam sh+aakya
NK026(la)001:10596: 'byung gnas dang sring cig zur mo dge 'dun 'bum
NK026(la)001:10597: la gtad rgya dang bcas nas gnang ngo //
NK026(la)001:10598: bdag smyon pa'i chol dang rmi nyams la ston pa
NK026(la)001:10599: sh+aakya thub pa ba lang spyod na khri brtsigs pa'i
NK026(la)001:10601: badz+ra he ru ka mdze thod bsnams pa 'jigs pa zhig snang /
NK026(la)001:10604: pad+ma he ru bkrag mdangs gsal /
NK026(la)001:10605: karma he ru sna tshogs pad gda' /
NK026(la)001:10606: zhi dang rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro chos skyong ni /
NK026(la)001:10607: mi dang mi min nam mkha'i lus can gang du'ang rdzu zhing 'phrul ston gyi gda' lags /
NK026(la)001:10608: lha bdud 'dam kha ma nor ba gal che he /
NK026(la)001:10609: shing pho 'brug gi lo yang dben dgon pa ru bla ma rin po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas la /
NK026(la)001:10610: shan+ti ba las mdo khyad par dang yongs rdzogs kyi dbang /
NK026(la)001:10613: man ngag lag len gtad rgya dang bcas pa yongs su rdzogs par zhus so //
NK026(la)001:10614: 'dus pa mdo'i gtad rgya'i snyan brgyud kun la med pa'i man ngag khyad par can rdzogs so //
NK026(la)001:10615: 'di yan zur thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aaka 'byung gi gsung ngo //
NK026(la)001:10616: de nas zur thams cad mkhyen pa lcam sring gis
NK026(la)001:10617: ri sbug tu lang gro sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal
NK026(la)001:10618: po la gnang / des chu dbar nyi sbug tu brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang la gnang /
NK026(la)001:10619: des mnga' ris dbu rtse ba mkhas grub chen po
NK026(la)001:10620: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan la chu dbar nyi
NK026(la)001:10621: sbug tu 'brug lo zla ba bcu pa'i tshes brgyad
NK026(la)001:10622: nas hor zla bcu gcig pa'i tshes lnga'i bar du
NK026(la)001:10623: gnang / rje btsun de nyid kyi gdung sras mnga'
NK026(la)001:10624: ris kyi pan+di ta chen po pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo
NK026(la)001:10625: gnang / rje dang / gcung rig sngags 'chang ba'i
NK026(la)001:10626: 'khor los sgyur ba chen po legs ldan bdud 'joms
NK026(la)001:10627: rdo rje gnyis gtso bor gyur pa'i rigs sras bdun
NK026(la)001:10628: dang sngags btsun gyi 'dus pa brgya nyi shu tsam
NK026(la)001:10629: la mnga' ris glo bo ma thang du legs par
NK026(la)001:10630: stsal bas de dag thams cad kyis kyang bstan pa
NK026(la)001:10631: phyogs mthar spel bar mdzad cing /
NK026(la)001:10632: khyad par rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen pos dbus
NK026(la)001:10633: gtsang mnga' ris dwags kong lho brag dang bcas pa
NK026(la)001:10634: rnams zhabs kyis bcags te smin grol gyi dga' ston
NK026(la)001:10635: phyogs brgyar spel zhing mdo dbang gi 'chad nyan kyang
NK026(la)001:10636: lan mang du mdzad pa las /
NK026(la)001:10637: nyug gi rgyal khang du thams cad mkhyen pa mkhyen
NK026(la)001:10638: brtse'i dbang phyug khu dbon gyis gsol ba btab ste
NK026(la)001:10639: 'dus pa mdo'i smin grol gyi gdams pa gnang zhing
NK026(la)001:10640: / rig 'dzin rjes skyi ston tshe ring dbang po yang rjes su bzung /
NK026(la)001:10641: dam pa des pho brang bsam 'grub rtse'i spel dkar
NK026(la)001:10642: du rig 'dzin gyi 'dus pa rgya mtsho la mdo
NK026(la)001:10644: bla chen bres gshongs pa chos rgyal rdo rje rjes su bzung /
NK026(la)001:10645: skabs der kho bo'i yongs 'dzin blo mchog rig pa'i
NK026(la)001:10646: rdo rje de nyid sngar nas mdo dbang brgyud tshul
NK026(la)001:10648: rig 'dzin rje brgyud par bzhugs pa 'di 'jam mgon
NK026(la)001:10649: rdo rje 'chang bka' 'gyur ba chen po mgon po
NK026(la)001:10650: bsod nams mchog ldan gyi bkas bskul te gtsang stod
NK026(la)001:10651: bres kyi ri khrod du bla chen chos rgyal rdo
NK026(la)001:10653: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa 'di nyid mkhas grub rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sar bzhugs nges kyang /
NK026(la)001:10654: kho bo cag dag sngon chad chos kyi 'brel ba sogs zhu ma myong yang /
NK026(la)001:10655: kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen pa
NK026(la)001:10656: blo bzang rgya mtsho'i sdes snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa
NK026(la)001:10657: rin po che mchog tu gces par 'dzin pa'i thugs
NK026(la)001:10658: rje dang phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab par brten
NK026(la)001:10659: / bdag la zhus shig ces bka'i gnang bas mtshams sbyar te /
NK026(la)001:10660: bdag gis kyang bla ma dam pa 'di nyid bsten
NK026(la)001:10661: nas mnyes pa gsum gyis mnyes par byas te thog
NK026(la)001:10662: mar 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor chen por smin byed
NK026(la)001:10663: kyi dbang khrid gtad rgya phyag bzhes dang bcas pa
NK026(la)001:10664: legs par nos pa nas bzung mi phyed pa'i dad
NK026(la)001:10666: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro tshe gsum sogs bka' ma /
NK026(la)001:10667: nyang dang chos dbang gtso bor gyur pa'i gter chos
NK026(la)001:10668: sogs dam pa'i chos kyi bka' drin mang du nos
NK026(la)001:10670: de nas slob mas phyag bya thal mo sbyar la /
NK026(la)001:10673: kye ma kye ma hoh zhes gdung ba'i gsung phyungs la /
NK026(la)001:10674: kye kye dkyil 'khor dang sgrub rdzas dpon slob rnams
NK026(la)001:10675: gcig la gcig blta zhing gcig sems gcig la zhugs
NK026(la)001:10676: pas 'bral mi phod par gdung bas phan na lus
NK026(la)001:10677: dang srog kyang gtong phod pa la las kyi dbang
NK026(la)001:10678: gis zhing so sor 'phangs kyang lhan cig tu 'dzom
NK026(la)001:10680: rtag tu phan pa'i thabs 'di don che bar dgongs 'tshal te /
NK026(la)001:10681: de yang sngon rgyal ba rigs lngas lha gnod sbyin
NK026(la)001:10682: srin po mi'i rigs can lnga la ri m+aa la
NK026(la)001:10683: ya'i rtser sangs rgyas ston pa la mi phyed pa'i
NK026(la)001:10684: dad pa bskyed / bstan pa'i khur bzung /
NK026(la)001:10685: chos srid gsum kun tu dar bar mdzad /
NK026(la)001:10686: nag po'i phyogs kun bsnubs pa'i slad du gdung tshig nyer gsum smras pa ltar /
NK026(la)001:10687: khyed rnams kyis kyang bla ma brgyud pa'i rnam thar bzang po bskyang 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:10689: bu rnams rang rang gi lhar bskyed la 'dzab bzlas /
NK026(la)001:10691: me tog phog pa'i lhar bskyed de /
NK026(la)001:10693: yang na spyi 'dzab gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK026(la)001:10696: gtso bo'i nga rgyal gyis theg dgu lus la tshang bar dgod /
NK026(la)001:10698: lugs gzhan du lus la yig 'bru dgod pa sogs 'dug mod kyang /
NK026(la)001:10699: 'dir ni dbang gi dus su rtsa bar /
NK026(la)001:10700: dpal che mchog gi sku la gtsug tor rgyal mtshan
NK026(la)001:10701: rtse mo la gser gyi tog stong gi rdzogs pa
NK026(la)001:10702: chen po dang / sku dang sku'i rgyan la rdzogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:10703: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor gyis gdan gyi 'og nor bu rin po che'i gdan gyi steng na /
NK026(la)001:10705: rtse gsum gyi brag gtams pa la /
NK026(la)001:10709: ri rab kyi kha mu tig cal dang /
NK026(la)001:10710: skar ma gar+b+ha'i 'od 'khrigs pa'i nor bu'i 'od 'bar brag la /
NK026(la)001:10714: lha mi yang 'khor ba gzugs med pa'i khams dang /
NK026(la)001:10715: keng rus kyi ri rab dang /
NK026(la)001:10716: gzugs khams zhing chen gyi sa dang /
NK026(la)001:10717: 'dod khams kyi chags pa thams cad khrag gi rgya mtsho mngon par mthong zhing /
NK026(la)001:10718: phyag rgya rnam par spro ba'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK026(la)001:10720: rang nyid che mchog dbu nyer gcig par gsal btab pa'i rdo rje brag chen gyi gdan nas /
NK026(la)001:10721: gtsug tor gyi rtse mo'i bar la theg dgu de ltar tshang bar bshad pas /
NK026(la)001:10722: che mchog dbu nyer gcig pa'i nga rgyal bzung bas
NK026(la)001:10723: theg dgu lus la tshang bar bkod pa 'grub bo
NK026(la)001:10724: // de'i ngang las yig brgya bzla /
NK026(la)001:10729: sngar bsgrubs pa'i zhi dkyil de bla mas bzung la /
NK026(la)001:10731: bzhi pa zhi dkyil bsgrub pa dgongs 'dus bteg pa ni /
NK026(la)001:10732: snga rabs kyi phyag bzhes su tshogs chen dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:10733: gyi dbus steng na bzhugs pa'i zhi dkyil rdo rje
NK026(la)001:10734: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po de nyid 'degs srol
NK026(la)001:10737: yug gtad rgya'i dkyil 'khor zhes bshad pas /
NK026(la)001:10738: yug ni dar ram ras yug la tshom bu bcu
NK026(la)001:10739: gsum bkod pa de yin pas de la dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:10740: gyi mtshan gzhi dang tha snyad med la /
NK026(la)001:10741: de skabs kyi gtad rgya'i dkyil 'khor de zhi dkyil la ngos bzung zhing /
NK026(la)001:10742: de lta bu'i zhi dkyil yang gong du zhi dkyil chung ngu zhig gsar du bris nas bkod nas /
NK026(la)001:10743: zhi ba'i las gzhung gi dus bsgrubs pa de 'di'i skabs kyi dbang rdzas su dmigs pa yin pas /
NK026(la)001:10744: des na zhi dkyil de nyid bteg pa dbang bskur dgos shing /
NK026(la)001:10747: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK026(la)001:10748: srid gsum dbang can thams cad chos //
NK026(la)001:10749: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:10750: rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams ngag bshad //
NK026(la)001:10752: slob ma'i spyi bo mgrin pa snying gar gtug go //
NK026(la)001:10754: dkyil 'khor lag tu gtad la mgo bos gtug /
NK026(la)001:10756: dbang rtags phyag mtshan snying gi thad du reg /
NK026(la)001:10757: ces kyang gsungs pas de ltar bya /
NK026(la)001:10759: dpon slob gnyis kas dkyil 'khor dgongs 'dus dbang rtags dang bcas pa la gus pa cher bya /
NK026(la)001:10760: glegs bam dbang chen zhes bya ba //
NK026(la)001:10761: theg dgu spyi yi bod lung thob //
NK026(la)001:10762: rgyal po dzahltara byin rlabs gnad //
NK026(la)001:10765: de nas bu rnams spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir zhing khams bstan pa ni /
NK026(la)001:10767: 'dod pa'i skyon spangs skye la dbang byed pa //
NK026(la)001:10768: steng phyogs khro bo chen po h+aum k+aa ra //
NK026(la)001:10769: ma byin len spangs yo byad dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10770: shar phyogs khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal //
NK026(la)001:10771: srog gcod skyon spangs tshe la dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10772: lho phyogs khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed //
NK026(la)001:10773: phra ma'i skyon spangs chos la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10774: nub phyogs khro bo chen po rta mgrin dpal //
NK026(la)001:10775: ngag rtsub skyon spangs las la dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10776: byang phyogs khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK026(la)001:10777: log par lta spangs ye shes dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10778: shar lho khro bo chen po dbyug sngon can //
NK026(la)001:10779: rdzun gyi skyon spangs mos la dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10780: lho nub khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon //
NK026(la)001:10781: ngag 'khyal skyon spangs sems la dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10782: nub byang khro bo chen po 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK026(la)001:10783: gnod sems skyon spangs rdzu 'phrul dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10784: byang shar khro bo chen po khams gsum rgyal //
NK026(la)001:10785: brnab sems skyon spangs smon lam dbang mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:10786: 'og phyogs khro bo chen po stobs po che'o //
NK026(la)001:10787: rgyu dge ba bcu thun mong gi lam 'bras bu
NK026(la)001:10788: sa bcu'am dbang bcu mchog gi lam 'bras khro bo
NK026(la)001:10789: bcu'am phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas so //
NK026(la)001:10790: de nas gom pa bcu gnyis 'dug pa dang /
NK026(la)001:10793: sa dang po gsum nyan rang byang sems kyi lam la /
NK026(la)001:10794: bla ma slob dpon mched grogs rdzas gnyen longs spyod rdzogs skus 'khrid /
NK026(la)001:10795: bskyed nas sgom lam kri yog sa gnyis gsum lnga drug bdun brgyad dgu rnams /
NK026(la)001:10796: bla ma slob dpon mched grogs rdzas dgra mnyen longs spyod rdzogs skus 'khrid /
NK026(la)001:10797: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi mthar lam sa bcu nas bla
NK026(la)001:10798: ma slob dpon mched grogs rdzas dgra gnyen chos sku
NK026(la)001:10799: dbyer med mngon par byang chub skus 'khrid /
NK026(la)001:10800: bcu gsum pa gtad rgya ni /
NK026(la)001:10801: bla ma kun tu bzang pos khrid par mos pas /
NK026(la)001:10802: zhes gsungs pa'i don lnga pa /
NK026(la)001:10803: nga ni bcu gsum gyi bsrang bstod mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:10806: nga ni thabs kyi mnyan pa mkhan //
NK026(la)001:10807: 'khor ba'i chu bo mtha' med las //
NK026(la)001:10808: srid gsum bsgral ba'i dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10810: nga ni thabs kyi mig mkhan te //
NK026(la)001:10811: 'jig rten long ba dpag med rnams //
NK026(la)001:10812: ling tog bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10814: nga ni thabs kyi sman pa ste //
NK026(la)001:10815: grong khyer gsum gyi nad pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:10816: gcong nad sel bar dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10818: nga ni thabs kyi sa mkhan te //
NK026(la)001:10819: 'gro ba lam log lam stor rnams //
NK026(la)001:10820: ma nor 'khrid par dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10822: nga ni thugs rje'i spyan ras mkhan //
NK026(la)001:10824: thams cad skyob par dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10826: nga ni rdo rje rdzong chen te //
NK026(la)001:10827: 'khor ba'i g.yul chen dmag dpung las //
NK026(la)001:10830: nga ni thabs kyi tshong dpon te //
NK026(la)001:10831: 'dod pa rgya mtshos mi ngoms rnams //
NK026(la)001:10832: gter chen 'byin par dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10834: nga ni thabs kyi sgron ma ste //
NK026(la)001:10835: mun nag smag tu 'khyams pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:10836: mun pa bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10838: nga ni yid bzhin nor bu ste //
NK026(la)001:10839: sems can bde bas 'phongs pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:10840: yid bzhin skong bar dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10842: nga ni bka' yi lde mig ste //
NK026(la)001:10843: bka' sgrom tha ram gsang ba rnams //
NK026(la)001:10844: rnam par 'byed par dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10846: nga ni bka' yi 'grel pa ste //
NK026(la)001:10847: gsung gi glegs bam zab mo rnams //
NK026(la)001:10848: nges par 'grol bar dam bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:10850: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol 'dir //
NK026(la)001:10851: skal ldan gang zhig su zhugs pa //
NK026(la)001:10853: nges par 'char gyis brtson par gyis //
NK026(la)001:10854: de nyid sems kyi me long ste //
NK026(la)001:10855: mngon sum gsal bar rtogs ma thag /
NK026(la)001:10856: 'gro ba'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK026(la)001:10857: rdo rje gsang chen mchod mchog rnams //
NK026(la)001:10858: 'dir sgros gsal bar bshad sbyar bas //
NK026(la)001:10859: lha dang mi yi rig 'dzin las //
NK026(la)001:10860: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:10861: lha mi'i 'jig rten thams cad kyis //
NK026(la)001:10862: mun pa'i gdung ba kun bsal nas //
NK026(la)001:10864: da ni bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la 'bral mi phod pa'i dad pa bskyed /
NK026(la)001:10865: stor ba rnyed pa lta bu'i dga' spro bya /
NK026(la)001:10866: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi bdag por gyur te zhes spro ba bskyed /
NK026(la)001:10868: dpon slob thugs gcig pa'i gdung sems mos gus phyung la /
NK026(la)001:10869: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing yun du bzhugs pa'i
NK026(la)001:10870: sku tshe phrin las byin gyis brlab pa'i gsal gdab
NK026(la)001:10872: bla ma'i gdan khri la spyi bos btud la bla mas /
NK026(la)001:10873: ci phyir gdung ba'i mun par zhugs //
NK026(la)001:10874: thub pa mya ngan 'das gsungs pa //
NK026(la)001:10875: de ni nam mkha'i sku mnga' ba //
NK026(la)001:10878: de skad sprul pa'i sgra phyungs pas //
NK026(la)001:10879: sngon du byung ba'i rigs can rnams //
NK026(la)001:10880: lus btud shin tu gus byas nas //
NK026(la)001:10882: deyanga pus btsugs thal sbyar te //
NK026(la)001:10883: ston pa 'di yi rjes zlos bya'o //
NK026(la)001:10884: zhes gsungs pas 'di'i rjes zlos bya ste /
NK026(la)001:10886: mtshan mo mun nag sprin rum nas //
NK026(la)001:10887: glog 'gyur bar snang ston lta bur //
NK026(la)001:10888: thog ma tha ma med pa yi //
NK026(la)001:10889: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid du //
NK026(la)001:10890: byung ba'i skyes bu don grub khyod //
NK026(la)001:10891: dam pa rnams kyi gsang 'dzin cing //
NK026(la)001:10892: gsang ba pa yi bdag por grags //
NK026(la)001:10894: de nas slob mas phyag byas te bu rnams mnga' gsol ba'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:10895: bstan pa 'dzin pa'i slob dpon dang rgyal thebs /
NK026(la)001:10896: bstan pa skyong ba'i rgyal po dang btsun mo /
NK026(la)001:10897: bstan pa bsrung ba'i rig 'dzin dang gtso mo rnams /
NK026(la)001:10898: rgyal ba lnga ltar khri dang rdor dril byin /
NK026(la)001:10899: las kyi rdo rje'am mngag gzhug dang /
NK026(la)001:10900: yon bdag ni sems dpa' dang khro bo ltar gdan dang stegs la /
NK026(la)001:10901: 'chad mkhan la 'khor lo dang dung gtad /
NK026(la)001:10902: las mkhan la rgya gram dang rnga ral gri /
NK026(la)001:10904: phal pa nyan pa dang sgom pa dag la thub pa drug ltar pad+ma'i gdan gding ba /
NK026(la)001:10906: de kun kyang so so rang rig gi dbang rtags
NK026(la)001:10907: dang bcas pa dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs ltar rgyan
NK026(la)001:10908: gyis brjid pa la lha'i nga rgyal bya'o //
NK026(la)001:10909: de la tshe dang bkra shis kyi rdzas dang byin can gyi rdzas gsar la /
NK026(la)001:10911: zhes gsungs pa bgegs gtor +aahh+aum gis byin gyis brlabs bden brdar dang bcas te phyir btang la /
NK026(la)001:10912: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:10913: ces sogs khro bo'i drag sngags bzla zhing yungs thun sogs kyis bgegs bskrad de /
NK026(la)001:10915: bla ma re'i gsham mam brgyud pa'i mtshams su gsol 'debs mchod pa bya zhing bstim /
NK026(la)001:10918: ces gsungs pa'i don ni dper na /
NK026(la)001:10919: chos sku kun tu bzang po la gsol ba 'debs so //
NK026(la)001:10920: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:10922: drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar dang /
NK026(la)001:10924: rgyal ba dgongs brgyud bla mar gsol ba 'debs so //
NK026(la)001:10925: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:10927: rig 'dzin brda' brgyud bla mar gsol ba 'debs so //
NK026(la)001:10928: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod byin gyis gang zag snyan
NK026(la)001:10929: brgyud bla mar gsol ba phyi nang gsang byin gyis
NK026(la)001:10930: ces brjod cing gsol ba btab pas rig 'dzin brgyud
NK026(la)001:10931: pa rnams byon nas slob ma rnams la thim par
NK026(la)001:10932: bsam zhing / rdo rje'i slob ma 'di rnams la
NK026(la)001:10933: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad stsal
NK026(la)001:10934: bsam zhing / du gsol / zhes sogs kyi smon lam gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:10936: bkra shis ni slob ma rnams la me tog 'thor zhing /
NK026(la)001:10938: chos sku kun bzang longs sku rigs lnga dang //
NK026(la)001:10939: sprul sku rigs gsum yang sprul dga' rab sogs //
NK026(la)001:10940: ye shes sku mchog rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud //
NK026(la)001:10941: rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:10942: grags ldan mchog skyong klu rgyal 'jog po dang //
NK026(la)001:10943: gnod sbyin srin po li tsa dri med sogs //
NK026(la)001:10944: thugs rje gdung gsob rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud //
NK026(la)001:10945: rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud pa'i rgya gar mkhas grub lo pan brgyud pa dang //
NK026(la)001:10946: bstan pa'i srog shing bod kyi brgyud pa sogs //
NK026(la)001:10947: dbang phyug rdo rje gang zag snyan khung brgyud //
NK026(la)001:10948: gang zag snyan khung brgyud pa'i ces pas brgyud pa'i bla ma re re nas bya'o //
NK026(la)001:10949: de nas mdo 'di 'byung ba'i dus brjod ni /
NK026(la)001:10951: de kho na nyid nges pa'i theg pa chen po 'di gnas skabs gnyis dang bcur 'byung ste /
NK026(la)001:10952: gang rmongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10953: gang 'jig rten gyi sgron ma bkod pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10954: gang gi nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10955: snying po byang chub tu nges pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10956: gang rmongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10957: gang 'jig rten gyi sgron ma bkod pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10958: gang gi nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10959: snying po byang chub tu nges pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10960: dgos pa nges par 'grel ba na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10961: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dus la bab pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10962: byin gyis rlabs kyis snang ba na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10963: brgyud pa thabs kyis grags pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10964: gang gi ched du mdzad pa na yang 'byung //
NK026(la)001:10965: lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10966: las rgyud yongs su gcod pa na yang 'byung /
NK026(la)001:10967: dgongs pa rnam par 'gro ba na yang 'byung ngo //
NK026(la)001:10968: de dag ni thams cad kyi thams cad nas thams cad kun tu yongs su rnam par snang ngo //
NK026(la)001:10972: dri ba dang po'i rtog pa yongs su chad pa de bzhin du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:10974: de nas dpon slob thams cad bkra shis dang tshe rdzas la sogs pa la rol /
NK026(la)001:10975: dal zhing skabs yod la spro na gtad rgya gsang mtshan ma skabs 'dir yang bsgrags la /
NK026(la)001:10976: zhes gsungs kyang gong du song ba nges 'thus par snang /
NK026(la)001:10978: slob mas phyug dang yon phul ba bka' drin che'o zhes brjod //
NK026(la)001:10980: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngosa la /
NK026(la)001:10981: phyogs dus thams cad du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK026(la)001:10982: dang zhing khams 'dzin skyong bsrung ba la 'bad par
NK026(la)001:10983: bya ba'i phyir / gtad rgya rnam pa lnga bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:10984: bla ma bka' rdzogs pa'i slob ma rgyal tshab gcig /
NK026(la)001:10985: rgya dang gcig gdul bya rjes su 'dzin pa bstan
NK026(la)001:10986: pa dgongs 'dus kyi rgya dang gnyis sgrub rdzas me
NK026(la)001:10987: tog yul lugs kyi bca' na thang 'bul ba'i rgya
NK026(la)001:10988: dang gsum / bka'i gnyer gtad chos kyi bdag por mnga' gsol ba'i rgya dang bzhi /
NK026(la)001:10989: zhu ba po rang gi zhi ba'i gzhung mchod tshogs
NK026(la)001:10990: 'bul ba'i rgya dang lnga po ci nus kyis bsgrub
NK026(la)001:10991: par khas blangs dam bcas la 'bad pas bsgrub par
NK026(la)001:10992: bya'o // 'di dag bsgrub par khas mi len cing
NK026(la)001:10993: chos rku thabs su 'dod pa dag ni bzung bar
NK026(la)001:10994: bya ba'i yul ma yin pas zang zing gis phan
NK026(la)001:10995: gdags la smon lam rnam par dag pa btab pa
NK026(la)001:10996: rjes su phyis nas bzung bar bya'o //
NK026(la)001:10998: zhes gsungs pas gong du zhi dkyil sogs bris yod na bsdu zhing /
NK026(la)001:10999: dar yug me tog gi tshom bu can de nyid kyang bla ma'i phyogs su bsdu ba yin /
NK026(la)001:11001: las rjes mi mngon par byas la dga' ston la rol bar bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11002: zhes gsungs pa ltar tshogs 'khor sogs la rol lo //
NK026(la)001:11003: des gtad rgya'i cho ga grub bo //
NK026(la)001:11004: skabs 'dir mdo dgon legs ldan gyi dbang bskur bya ba skabs su babs par snang zhing /
NK026(la)001:11005: de yang gtsang shod pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi chog khrigs ltar mdzad 'dug pas /
NK026(la)001:11006: zur du byed pa'i tshes lha'i sta gon sogs 'dug
NK026(la)001:11007: pa dbang chog rang gi dkyus ltar byas pas 'thus
NK026(la)001:11008: / 'dir gzhung de la brten te cho ga ma
NK026(la)001:11009: tshang ba rnams kha bskang zhing mi dgos pa rnams
NK026(la)001:11010: dor te bri bar byas na 'thad par mthong bas
NK026(la)001:11011: / / des na lag len 'di ltar bya ba rigs par snang ste /
NK026(la)001:11014: rjes gsum gyi dang po ni /
NK026(la)001:11015: stegs bu bdud rtsis rkyang nul bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:11016: +aahh+aum ma h+aa man+dala la sid+d+hi ku ru h+aum /
NK026(la)001:11018: de nas las thig gdab pa ni sgo rdzogs spyi ltar la /
NK026(la)001:11019: lte bar chos 'byung gru gsum lnga sgroms shong ba'i zlum thig gis bskor /
NK026(la)001:11020: de'i phyir zlum thig gcig bskor ba thod mkhar gyis /
NK026(la)001:11021: de'i mthar btson khang bcu drug gis zlum thig /
NK026(la)001:11022: de'i mthar cha phran gcig rnams bskor /
NK026(la)001:11026: de'i phyir dur khrod rdo ra me ri sogs kyi cha dabye'o //
NK026(la)001:11027: bla mas thun mtshams kyi lha'i nga rgyal gyis las
NK026(la)001:11028: thig gi steng lha gnas rnams su khrag gi thig
NK026(la)001:11029: le bkod la / de'i steng 'bru nag gi tshom bu bkod cing /
NK026(la)001:11030: 'og nas 'byung ba'i lha so so'i snying po brjod pas mgon po 'khor bcas bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:11031: dbang bskur byin rlabs sngon du 'gro bas spyan 'dren mchod bstod bsdus pa dang /
NK026(la)001:11034: lha yi ded dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:11035: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK026(la)001:11036: dur khrod bdag po sgrol ba'i ging /
NK026(la)001:11037: khro bo'i rgyal po khyod la bstod //
NK026(la)001:11039: drag po sku lnga rgyal ba'i bka' sdod mchog /
NK026(la)001:11040: ye shes lnga ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i 'khor //
NK026(la)001:11041: phrin las bdud 'dul dgra bgegs kun gyi gshed //
NK026(la)001:11042: legs ldan 'khor dang bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:11043: legs ldan 'khor bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:11044: khyed la mchod pa bya ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11045: slob ma rjes su bzung bya'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11047: sta gon la ni gnas par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11048: de bzhin bagyi'o de bzhin mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11049: h+aum badz+ra u tish+tha'i sngags rgyas nam mkhar bteg cing mchod bstod bsdus pa byas la bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:11050: bar 'dir bum pa dang slob ma sta gon bshad
NK026(la)001:11051: pas dngos sta tha dad kyi tshe de ltar yin
NK026(la)001:11052: kyang / 'dir dngos sta sbrel ba 'jug pa bde
NK026(la)001:11053: bas de'i phyir bum pa yang dngos gzhi'i sgrub mchod
NK026(la)001:11054: kyi skabs su bsgrubs pas 'thus pas /
NK026(la)001:11056: dbus su chos 'byung rtse mo shar bstan gyi phyogs
NK026(la)001:11057: bzhir chos 'byung bzhi rtse mo nang bstan mthing kha
NK026(la)001:11058: dang / gzhi thams cad khrag khyams de'i mthar thod
NK026(la)001:11059: phreng btson khang bcu drug le tshe bcas pa dmar
NK026(la)001:11060: dang / nag / de'i mthar cha phran la thod ra /
NK026(la)001:11063: rtsig pa ni sar stag gi thod rtsig /
NK026(la)001:11068: 'obs khung gzhi dmar po la phyogs mtshams brgyad du gru gsum rtse phyir bstan mthing kha re re'o //
NK026(la)001:11069: de dag la mngon rtogs ltar lha mtshan dgod do //
NK026(la)001:11070: de ltar dkyil 'khor bris zin nas /
NK026(la)001:11071: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi'i khar rnam rgyal bum
NK026(la)001:11072: pa rdzas ldan dar nag gi mgul chings dang bcas
NK026(la)001:11073: pa kha rgyan gyi gseb tu gtso bo'i tsakli dang
NK026(la)001:11074: bcas pa bsham / dbang gzhung du las bum gsungs
NK026(la)001:11075: kyang 'dir las bum yod bzhin pa yin pas mi
NK026(la)001:11076: bcas pa bsham / dgos so // de'i mdun du
NK026(la)001:11077: sgrub gtor ni ka p+aa lar gru gsum phyi dmar
NK026(la)001:11078: nang nag pa 'khor mdun du yum la zla gam
NK026(la)001:11080: nang 'khor bzhi la gru gsum bzhi /
NK026(la)001:11083: sgo ma bzhi rnams la zur gsum chung ba grangs dang mnyam pa mtheb kyus bskor ba /
NK026(la)001:11092: la dus bran pa dar nag btsugs dang /
NK026(la)001:11093: mchod gtor de bas chung ba gong ltar ram yang na gru gsum mdun du yum /
NK026(la)001:11094: 'khor gyi grangs mtheb skyus bskor ba gong du bsad pa'i mthun rdzas kyis bran pa'ang bsham /
NK026(la)001:11095: phyi mchod dang sman raka tshogs kyi 'khor lo dang bcas pa yang rgya cher bkod /
NK026(la)001:11096: dbang rdzas la sta gon gyi chas /
NK026(la)001:11114: tsa ma ra ni deng sang mi rkang gi gling bu bris pa 'dra 'dug mod /
NK026(la)001:11116: phyag mtshan drag po tsa ma ra /
NK026(la)001:11117: dam can gnas nas 'bod pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11118: zhes pa'i tshig gis 'khrul gzhi byas pa 'dra zhing /
NK026(la)001:11119: kho bos brtags na 'dus pa chen po'i bsnyen dbang gi dus su /
NK026(la)001:11120: rnga nyi ma'i steng du h+aum gi 'phro 'du las bskyed cing /
NK026(la)001:11121: badz+ra tsa ma ra dza m+aa ra ya h+aum gis byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:11123: dpal gyi phyag rgya ye shes tsa ma ra //
NK026(la)001:11125: gzhung gzhan las rnga yab kyi skad dod du tsa ma ra 'dzug tshul yang snang bas /
NK026(la)001:11126: 'dir yang rnga ni drag po'i phyag mtshan du bsdus kyang chog pas /
NK026(la)001:11127: phyag mtshan drag po tsa ma ra //
NK026(la)001:11129: dam can gnas nas 'bod pa ni shin tu 'brel chags par snang ngo snyam /
NK026(la)001:11130: de ltar min na rkang dung la tsa ma ra
NK026(la)001:11131: yin tshul gyi shes byed kyang smra dgos par snang
NK026(la)001:11132: bas dpyad dgos / 'on kyang bdag ni 'dus pa
NK026(la)001:11133: chen po'i bsnyen dbang gi rjes su 'brangs te tsa
NK026(la)001:11134: ma ra rnga kho nar ngos 'dzin par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11137: ri rab gling bzhi rgya gram gyis mtshan pa /
NK026(la)001:11139: mda' gzhu rnams kyang bsag par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11140: de nas bsgrub mchod bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:11141: 'dir ye shes kyi mgon po yin pas bdag mdun
NK026(la)001:11142: bum gsum mgon po kho na bgyis pas chog par
NK026(la)001:11143: snang yang / 'dir 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:11144: dang 'brel ba'i dbang gis gong du zhi khro'i phrin
NK026(la)001:11145: las bgyis pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas bzhin pa yin
NK026(la)001:11146: snang yang / pas / khro bo'i tshogs byin rlabs kyi gong du mgon po'i sgrub mchod bya ste /
NK026(la)001:11147: bla ma che mchog he ru ka'i nga rgyal la gnas pas khyab bo //
NK026(la)001:11148: de lta bu'i nga rgyal gyis thog mar mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK026(la)001:11149: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa rnams tshogs
NK026(la)001:11150: chen gyi grub mchod kyi sngon 'gro'i skabs ltar byin
NK026(la)001:11151: gyis brlab / de nas dkyil 'khor bum pa sgrub
NK026(la)001:11152: gtor gsum las rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor rten brten
NK026(la)001:11154: bum pa yang phyi mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bum pa
NK026(la)001:11155: la nang dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal yas khang du
NK026(la)001:11157: sgrub gtor yang gtor snod b+h+r+aum las dur khrod kyi
NK026(la)001:11158: gzhal yas khang du gtor ma mgon po gtso 'khor
NK026(la)001:11160: tshig gcig gis mdun bskyed bum pa gtor ma gsum
NK026(la)001:11161: gyi rten dang brten pa thams cad gsal la ma
NK026(la)001:11163: de yang deng sang mdo mgon kho na mdzad par
NK026(la)001:11164: snang yang dbang rdzas sogs dang dkyil 'khor gyi babs
NK026(la)001:11165: la brtags na rgyud mgon 'thad ces rig 'dzin 'gyur
NK026(la)001:11166: med rdo rje gsung pa bzhin don la gnas shing
NK026(la)001:11167: ngo bo gcig phyir mi 'gal la /
NK026(la)001:11168: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i gsan yig tu rig 'dzin legs ldan zhabs las rgyud mgon dang /
NK026(la)001:11169: mdo mgon gnyis gsan pa'i mdo mgon ljang sngon drag
NK026(la)001:11170: por ngos bzung ba don la gnas pas deng sang
NK026(la)001:11171: zhal gcig phyag gnyis par mdo mgon dang /
NK026(la)001:11172: zhal gsum phyag drug par rgyud mgon zer ba yang dpyad par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11173: mngon rtogs gsar du bris pa ni 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:11176: stong pa'i ngang las dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal yas
NK026(la)001:11177: khang chen po gru bzhi sgo bzhi rgyan rta babs
NK026(la)001:11178: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK026(la)001:11182: byang phyogs bya'i thod pa las grub pa'i rtsig pa dang /
NK026(la)001:11184: rgyu rlon snying dang glo ba'i 'phyang 'phrul sogs d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK026(la)001:11187: zhing gi rgyal mtshan dang ba dan 'phyar ba /
NK026(la)001:11188: zhing chen gyi pags pa'i thog dang bla bre /
NK026(la)001:11189: 'og gzhi thams cad khrag mtshor gyur pa'i lte bar chos 'byung la sgrom /
NK026(la)001:11191: khrag khyams thod mkhar gyis bcad pa /
NK026(la)001:11192: phyi rol tu 'obs khung brgyad dur khrod chen po
NK026(la)001:11193: rdorje'i ra gur ye shes kyi me 'bar ba dang
NK026(la)001:11194: bcas pa'i dbus su rdo rje brag chen pad+ma nyi
NK026(la)001:11196: rang gi thugs ka nas h+aum 'phros te yongs su gyur pa las /
NK026(la)001:11197: dpal ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa /
NK026(la)001:11198: sku mdog dang dbus zhal ljang nag brjid pa /
NK026(la)001:11201: phyag drug gi g.yas kyi dang pos skyes bu gsal
NK026(la)001:11202: shing la brgyus pa'i ti ra'i dbyug pa beng gi
NK026(la)001:11204: bar pa rdo rje gsor zhing 'phyar ba /
NK026(la)001:11205: tha mas gnam lcags kyi phur pa bsgril ba /
NK026(la)001:11206: g.yon gyi dang po dung chen du srid pa gsum
NK026(la)001:11207: gyi sems can gyi snying dang rak+tasa gang ba gsol
NK026(la)001:11208: ba / bar pa na shak+ti'i mdun rnon /
NK026(la)001:11209: tha mas sbrul nag gi zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK026(la)001:11210: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum du bzhugs pa /
NK026(la)001:11211: zhing chen dang glang chen gyi pags pas stod g.yogs shing /
NK026(la)001:11212: stag lpags kyi sham thabs la sbrul gyi ska rags bcings pa /
NK026(la)001:11213: thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang rlon pa'i do shal sbrul rigs lnga'i rgyan /
NK026(la)001:11214: thal zhag rak+ta'i mtshan ma can /
NK026(la)001:11215: ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'i steng na bya khyung lding zhing /
NK026(la)001:11216: sta zur la seng ge gnyis 'khrab pa /
NK026(la)001:11217: rtsib logs la 'phar ba dang dred mo 'khyug la /
NK026(la)001:11219: de'i g.yon du nye gnas ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai
NK026(la)001:11220: ma ljang nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis sbrul zhags dang
NK026(la)001:11222: zhing g.yang dang stag sham can /
NK026(la)001:11223: g.yas su las kyi mgon po mthing nag gcer bu 'jigs tshul can gri thod 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:11224: zhabs gnyis dor stabs bam ro'i khar bgrad pa'o //
NK026(la)001:11225: shar gyi lcags mkhar du khro bo badz+ra ging ka ra sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs tshul can /
NK026(la)001:11226: g.yas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bskor zhing g.yon thod khrag
NK026(la)001:11227: 'dzin pa gri thogs ging chen bcu gsum sogs 'khor
NK026(la)001:11229: lho'i gru gsum du gnod sbyin zangs mdog rgyal po
NK026(la)001:11230: dmar nag 'jigs pa mi lpags kyi g.yang gzhi gsol
NK026(la)001:11231: ba / g.yas gser gyi ral gri /
NK026(la)001:11233: yum bse gdong zangs gri can sogs 'khor du mas bskor ba /
NK026(la)001:11234: nub tu srin po r+aa hu la smug nag mgo dgu bya rog gi zhal dang bcu yod pa /
NK026(la)001:11235: lus kun mig gis gang zhig sku smad dug sbrul du 'khyil ba /
NK026(la)001:11236: phyag gnyis kyi g.yas pa thog gi 'khor lo bskor ba /
NK026(la)001:11237: g.yon pa chu srin gyi zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK026(la)001:11238: gza' gdong dregs pa'i 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK026(la)001:11239: byang du ma mo re ma ti mthing nag skem zhing sgeg la gtum pa spyi bor zla tshes /
NK026(la)001:11241: snyan cha seng ge sbrul nag dril bus brgyan pa /
NK026(la)001:11242: zhing gi stod g.yogs re lde'i sham thabs sogs ma mo'i rgyan dang chas thams cad kyis spras pa /
NK026(la)001:11243: g.yas khram shing dang g.yon nad rkyal 'dzin pa drel rta la zhon pa'o //
NK026(la)001:11244: btson khang bcu drug tu goo r+ai la sogs pa'i gnas kyi khro mo brgyad dang /
NK026(la)001:11245: sing ha ma la sogs pa'i yul gyi phra men
NK026(la)001:11246: brgyad rang rang gi rgyan cha lugs dang ldan pa'o
NK026(la)001:11247: // gru chad bzhir shar lhor skam ma /
NK026(la)001:11248: lho nub tu shin tu skam ma /
NK026(la)001:11249: nub byang du ra ros ma /
NK026(la)001:11250: byang shar du khrag 'thung ma bzhi rngams khro chags pa'i nyams can no //
NK026(la)001:11251: khrag khyams la shar du srin mo dmar ser g.yag gdong can la sogs pa drug /
NK026(la)001:11252: lhor zhi ba dmar mo dom mgo can la sogs pa drug /
NK026(la)001:11253: nub tu dga' byed dmar mo bya rgod mgo la sogs pa drug /
NK026(la)001:11254: byang du gsod byed ma ljang nag spyang gdong can la sogs pa drug ste /
NK026(la)001:11255: dbang phyug ma nyer bzhi po yang rang rang gi rgyan chas phyag mtshan dang ldan pa'o //
NK026(la)001:11256: shar sgor khu byug gdong nag mo lcags kyu can /
NK026(la)001:11257: lho sgor ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren ma /
NK026(la)001:11258: nub sgor seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:11259: byang sgor skye ka'i mgo can ljang nag dril bu 'khrol ba'o //
NK026(la)001:11260: phyi rol gyi 'obs khung rnams su rnag dang chu ser dang /
NK026(la)001:11261: khrag dang sha chen dang bshang gci rkang dang klad pa klad rgya rnams kyis gang ba'i nang du /
NK026(la)001:11263: sbrang ma dang sbrang rgod dang /
NK026(la)001:11266: sdig pa dang sdom la sogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:11267: gzhan yang kam ka ru rtse rkang ldag dang /
NK026(la)001:11268: khrag 'thung mchu dmar kha skyen dang /
NK026(la)001:11278: 'phar ba rkang sdeb la sogs pa gcan gzan gdug pa'i tshogs rnams dang /
NK026(la)001:11279: gzhan yang gshog pa can gyis nam mkha' gang ba /
NK026(la)001:11280: sder mo can gyis sa gzhi gang ba /
NK026(la)001:11281: ro langs dang 'dre srin yi tshogs dang /
NK026(la)001:11284: ma mo bye ba'i tshogs kyis bskor bar gyur /
NK026(la)001:11285: bum gtor dkyil 'khor dang bcas par dmigs la sh+au nya t+aa sogs ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:11286: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab bo //
NK026(la)001:11287: dbang 'di ga dang 'brel ba'i rtsar mchod ces pa zhig snang yang /
NK026(la)001:11288: ha cang gi khrigs legs pa mi snang zhing /
NK026(la)001:11289: kho bos nub dgon lugs mdo mgon gyi bka' gtad lung dang bcas thob pa'i /
NK026(la)001:11290: las gzhung gi phrin las nub dgon lugs rgyas bsdus 'tshams par snang zhing /
NK026(la)001:11291: de'i mgo bor mgon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i mngon rtogs kyang 'dug pas /
NK026(la)001:11292: da lta ma dgos kyang 'og tu lugs de ga'i rjes gnang gi dus su dgos pa dang /
NK026(la)001:11293: dbang gi dus ma gtogs rgyun gyi bskang gsol de
NK026(la)001:11294: nyid 'khyer bde bas gzhung ltar bris pa ni 'di
NK026(la)001:11295: ltar / bskang rdzas byin brlab ni /
NK026(la)001:11297: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da lis bsang /
NK026(la)001:11299: stong pa'i ngang las a las ye shes kyi ka
NK026(la)001:11300: p+aa la yangs shing rgya che ba rnams kyi nang
NK026(la)001:11301: du dgra bgegs ma lus pa bsgral ba las byung
NK026(la)001:11309: gzhan yang h+aum zhu ba las byung ba'i mkha' lding /
NK026(la)001:11316: dpal gyi zhal zas la sogs pa mdor na mgon
NK026(la)001:11317: po 'khor dang bcas pa mnyes par byed pa'i bskang
NK026(la)001:11318: rdzas bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK026(la)001:11319: yul sa dang nam mkha' bar snang thams cad khyab pa /
NK026(la)001:11320: dus 'khor ba ji srid ma stongs kyi bar du gnas pa /
NK026(la)001:11321: ngo bo bzang zhing rgya che ba /
NK026(la)001:11322: bkod pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK026(la)001:11323: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i rnam par sprul pa
NK026(la)001:11324: las byung ba'i mchod pa'i yo byad bsam gyis mi
NK026(la)001:11325: khyab pa dang ldan par gyur /
NK026(la)001:11326: ar+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar brjod cing rol mo byed /
NK026(la)001:11327: de nas sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin gyis brlabs la bskang ba bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11329: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:11330: bskal pa grangs med 'das pa'i sngon rol tu //
NK026(la)001:11331: mtha' yas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyang //
NK026(la)001:11332: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don mdzad gdug pa 'dul //
NK026(la)001:11333: mgon po spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal 'dud //
NK026(la)001:11334: bde ba'i 'byung gnas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11335: bar chad sel phyir des bstan cho ga bri //
NK026(la)001:11336: su zhig bsnyen sgrub bzhi la rtag tu gnas pa des /
NK026(la)001:11337: bdag dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:11338: gnas dben par sha chen dang snying chen la sogs
NK026(la)001:11339: pa sha khrag sna tshogs dang 'bru sna tshogs dang
NK026(la)001:11344: gtor ma b+han+d+ha'am snod bzang por bsham /
NK026(la)001:11345: gtor ma'i dbus su lha bshos nag po gru gsum pa bzhag /
NK026(la)001:11346: spyan gzigs dkor cha sna tshogs bsham /
NK026(la)001:11347: sman raka dang thun mong gi mchod pa bsham /
NK026(la)001:11348: ma h+aa k+aa la'i bris sku dgram /
NK026(la)001:11349: de nas bdag nyid che mchog he ru ka'am /
NK026(la)001:11350: rdo rje gzhon nu gang rung du bsgom /
NK026(la)001:11351: kro d+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:11352: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:11353: zhes pas bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal chen por gsal ba'i mdun du ke man+dala b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:11354: kem las kem rus kyi ri rab /
NK026(la)001:11355: pags pa'i gur dang bla bre /
NK026(la)001:11360: tshil bu'i gad pa dang ldan pa'i dbus su ru
NK026(la)001:11361: tra man+da la zhes pas lcags mkhar nag po gru
NK026(la)001:11362: gsum 'bar ba'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK026(la)001:11363: h+aum mthing nag las 'od zer phar 'phros /
NK026(la)001:11364: bstan pa la gnod pa'i dgra bgegs tshar bcad /
NK026(la)001:11365: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las dpal ye shes kyi mgon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK026(la)001:11366: g.yas pa tsan dan gyi beng chen nam mkha' la 'phyar ba /
NK026(la)001:11367: g.yon pa bdud kyi khrag gis bkang ba'i thod pa 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:11368: dar ber sngo khra brjid pa sku la gsol ba /
NK026(la)001:11369: gser ska rin po che 'bar ba sked la bcings pa /
NK026(la)001:11373: mdun na mi nag po nam mkha' la 'o dod 'bod pa /
NK026(la)001:11374: steng na nam mkha' lding sprul pa'i tshogs dpag tu med pa /
NK026(la)001:11375: dpung zur g.yas g.yon na se nga ge ral pa gsig pa /
NK026(la)001:11376: rtsib logs g.yas g.yon na 'phar ba lag sdeb dang dred mo rkang sdeb byed pa /
NK026(la)001:11377: zhabs long bu gnyis na stag nang rgyal mo 'khrugs pa /
NK026(la)001:11378: nye gnas ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma dang gnyis su med par rol pa /
NK026(la)001:11379: nag po chen po stong dang sha za bye ba 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK026(la)001:11380: de'i thugs ka nas 'od zer dpag tu med pa phrom phrom 'phros pas /
NK026(la)001:11381: bstan pa la gnod pa'i dgra bgegs tshar bcad /
NK026(la)001:11382: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK026(la)001:11383: spyir sangs rgyas bstan pa dar ba /
NK026(la)001:11385: sems can thams cad la bde skyid 'byung ba /
NK026(la)001:11386: khyad par bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor dang bcas pa dang /
NK026(la)001:11387: lus dang grib ma ltar 'grogs te bsrung ba dang /
NK026(la)001:11389: sba ba'i phyir du rang bzhin gyi gnas nas gnas 'di ru spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:11390: gu gul dang tshil chen gyi dud pa rgyun mi chad par bya ste /
NK026(la)001:11392: bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i sngags sbrel la bzlas so //
NK026(la)001:11393: b+hur gur ma h+aa pad+ma rde 'bur tsi 'bur /
NK026(la)001:11394: byi ge byi ma na s+ye /
NK026(la)001:11395: e ho sho mo kro d+ha h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:11397: b+hu d+hu ku rna a pra rna 'bu tsi kyi
NK026(la)001:11398: byi ma na s+ye ba sho ma kro d+ha h+aum
NK026(la)001:11400: b+hu tu ku tu i tsi kyi phyi u tsu ma kro d+ha h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:11403: re re la bsnyen pa 'bum 'bum bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11405: lang+ka yul gyi grong brdal gyi //
NK026(la)001:11406: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK026(la)001:11407: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK026(la)001:11408: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK026(la)001:11409: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK026(la)001:11410: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:11411: gsang ba sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:11412: ming gis dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa //
NK026(la)001:11413: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:11414: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK026(la)001:11415: nye gnas kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma //
NK026(la)001:11416: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK026(la)001:11417: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs dang //
NK026(la)001:11418: slas dang byi mo bra mo'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11419: 'dus pa chen po'i rnal 'byor tshogs bcas rnams //
NK026(la)001:11420: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:11421: ga na pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra ma
NK026(la)001:11422: h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma
NK026(la)001:11423: ya s+t+wam / a kar+sha ya e h+ye hi sh+r+ai
NK026(la)001:11424: ma h+aa k+aa la h+aum dzah e a ra l+li
NK026(la)001:11425: ya s+t+wam / hrim hrim / rdo rje brag chen gtams pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11426: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen khri //
NK026(la)001:11427: bam chen bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK026(la)001:11428: rab 'jigs dpa' bo 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:11429: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na ba ti /
NK026(la)001:11430: ma h+aa yak+sha pa ta li /
NK026(la)001:11431: dzahh+aum pam hoh sa pa ri w+aa ra pad+ma mu dra sa ma ha s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:11432: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul bzlog cing //
NK026(la)001:11433: lha dmag dkar po'i dbugs 'byin pa //
NK026(la)001:11434: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas la //
NK026(la)001:11435: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK026(la)001:11436: bsod nams gzi byin 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:11437: ye shes tshogs chen 'phags la spyod pa rlabs chen
NK026(la)001:11438: 'phags la pha rol phyin bcu 'phags la sgrib pa
NK026(la)001:11439: rnam gnyis spangs la bdag med gnyis med rtogs la
NK026(la)001:11440: ston pas lung bstan thob la sngon gyi rgyal ba
NK026(la)001:11442: drang srong rig 'dzin rnams dang smon lam gcig /
NK026(la)001:11443: lha srin sde brgyad rnams dang mthu rtsal gcig /
NK026(la)001:11444: tshogs kyi bdag po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:11445: stong gsum 'adi'am stong gsum gzhan dag na //
NK026(la)001:11446: la du la phug la sogs yid bzhin zas //
NK026(la)001:11447: thang skyes chu skyes la sogs longs spyod rkyen //
NK026(la)001:11448: 'chi med bdud rtsi la sogs dam tshig chu //
NK026(la)001:11449: rim gsum mchod pas tshogs bdag mnyes gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:11450: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na pa ti /
NK026(la)001:11451: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK026(la)001:11452: sa pa ri w+aa ra ba ling+ta i dam grih+na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11453: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11454: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11457: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11458: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11459: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11463: ma h+aa su kha hoh rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyod //
NK026(la)001:11464: rdo rje can du gcig nges na //
NK026(la)001:11465: gsang ba gsum dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11466: mi phyed rdo rjee dam tshig sbyin //
NK026(la)001:11467: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig 'di //
NK026(la)001:11468: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK026(la)001:11470: grub nas 'jig pa'i dus med do //
NK026(la)001:11471: +aahh+aum badz+ra a mri ta a hi h+ai sa ma
NK026(la)001:11472: ya h+aum h+r+ai th+aah gsang ba gsum gyi dam pa
NK026(la)001:11473: rnams // khyed kyis rab tu bslus gyur na //
NK026(la)001:11474: de kun khros nas khrag chen po //
NK026(la)001:11475: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung /
NK026(la)001:11477: na ra kan te b+ha ra hri da ye /
NK026(la)001:11481: a mri to te kan nar bu tsa ra bu /
NK026(la)001:11482: rdo rje dri yi bdud rtsi mchog /
NK026(la)001:11483: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar //
NK026(la)001:11484: bsre ba'i mchog ste srog gi snying //
NK026(la)001:11485: snying dang snying gi spun du bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11486: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya a /
NK026(la)001:11487: bdag gis lan gsum blangs byas te //
NK026(la)001:11488: tshogs bdag la yang lan gsum sbyin //
NK026(la)001:11489: ma h+aa mtsho gling sgrub gnas su //
NK026(la)001:11490: rdo rje srin po'i spyan snga ru //
NK026(la)001:11491: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11492: dam tshig gnyan la khyed ma 'da' //
NK026(la)001:11493: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:11495: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu po che //
NK026(la)001:11496: bar snang khams su rgyu ba la //
NK026(la)001:11497: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK026(la)001:11498: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ni //
NK026(la)001:11499: rdo rje'i ming gi dbang bskur ba //
NK026(la)001:11500: mngags byed ces kyang btags pa ste //
NK026(la)001:11501: tshogs kyi bdag po chen por grags //
NK026(la)001:11502: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu bo che //
NK026(la)001:11503: 'ching byed rdo rje phreng ba can //
NK026(la)001:11504: bdag gis bsnyen cing mchod pa las //
NK026(la)001:11505: gzhung dang 'gal ba bzod par gsol //
NK026(la)001:11506: phrin las snyan snyun gsol ba ni //
NK026(la)001:11507: lha yi dgra lha chen por gsol btab nas //
NK026(la)001:11508: rnal 'byor yongs kyi pho nyar zhal 'ches shing //
NK026(la)001:11509: lha min dmag tshogs 'dul ba'i thugs dam can //
NK026(la)001:11510: bdag gis bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod /
NK026(la)001:11511: dam nyams dgra bo myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11512: rdo rje brag chen gdan steng nas //
NK026(la)001:11513: bsnyen pa'i tshul gyis bka' sdod pa //
NK026(la)001:11514: tsan dan dbyug pa sngon po yis //
NK026(la)001:11515: khams gsum rdul du rlog mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:11516: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK026(la)001:11517: bdag ni dgra bgeg tshogs dang g.yul 'gyed na //
NK026(la)001:11518: yun gyi mgo dang dpang du khyed gsol gyi //
NK026(la)001:11519: log 'dren dgra bgegs rdul du brlag pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11520: bdag gi rgyal kha 'phel bar mdzad du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11521: dam tshig dbang gis lus dang grib ma bzhin //
NK026(la)001:11522: 'grogs te bdag dang 'khor tshogs bsrung du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11523: dam nyams dgra bgegs myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11524: tshogs bdag khyod kyi 'khor tshogs kyis //
NK026(la)001:11525: bka' nyan rnams kyis bdag la khram btab na //
NK026(la)001:11526: khram kha phyes shing bar chad bzlog tu gsol //
NK026(la)001:11527: tshe dang rdzu 'phrul mthu dang mngon shes dang //
NK026(la)001:11528: rigs brgyud longs spyod chos kyi dngos grub gsol //
NK026(la)001:11529: snying nas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11530: rdo rje slob dpon smod pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11531: dam tshig gnyan po 'bral byed dang //
NK026(la)001:11532: sgrub la bar chad byed pa'i dgra //
NK026(la)001:11533: sod cig choms shing bsgral du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11535: rus pa klad pa nang khrol zo //
NK026(la)001:11536: bdun brgyud rtsad nas bcad par gyis //
NK026(la)001:11537: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ya ma ma sarba sha trum /
NK026(la)001:11539: ma dza me ta bam sam mam sa /
NK026(la)001:11545: i dam ba li na gri h+na gri h+na /
NK026(la)001:11549: b+hi bi to sa ma ya a te kra ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:11550: dbang gi dus bum pa'i gzungs thag blangs te gong gi bsnyen sgrub bzhi sbrel gyi sngags bzla zhing /
NK026(la)001:11551: bum nang gi lhar 'od zer spro bsdu bdud rtsi dbab pa sogs spyi ltar dang /
NK026(la)001:11552: rten gtor dang mdun bskyed la yang thugs brgyud bskul ba'i dmigs pa bya'o //
NK026(la)001:11553: rgyun gyi bskang gsol dkyus bzhin ma gtogs 'dir bzlas pa bya mi dgos so //
NK026(la)001:11554: hoh dpal ma h+aa k+aa la tshogs kyi bdag po
NK026(la)001:11555: 'dus pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pho mo'i tshogs dang
NK026(la)001:11557: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi 'khor rnams bsrung bar zhal gyis bzhes nas /
NK026(la)001:11558: lha mi mang pos lha'i dgra lha chen por mnga' gsol te /
NK026(la)001:11559: lha ma yin gyi g.yul bzlog cing /
NK026(la)001:11560: glang po che sna yon btul ba dang /
NK026(la)001:11561: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu rdul du brlag ste /
NK026(la)001:11562: bgegs kyi rgyal po byi na ya ga ji ltar btul ba dang /
NK026(la)001:11563: seng ge bzang btsan rgyal lta ba log ste /
NK026(la)001:11564: dge slong ma'i bdud du gyur te /
NK026(la)001:11565: nyang sha mi go chas mgon po rtse gcig tu bsgrubs te /
NK026(la)001:11566: lha ma yin gyi bu mo nam mkha'i glog ma
NK026(la)001:11567: sprin gyi lha ru gyur pa rdul du brlag ste
NK026(la)001:11568: / phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi dgra
NK026(la)001:11569: bgegs 'dul bar zhal gyis bzhes pa de bzhin du
NK026(la)001:11570: / / bdag cag bka' dang dam la mos pa
NK026(la)001:11571: rnams kyis rtse gcig tu bsten te mchod cing bsgrubs
NK026(la)001:11572: / / nas / thugs dam rgyud bskul bas bstan
NK026(la)001:11573: pa bshig pa'i dgra bgegs che ge mo 'di lo
NK026(la)001:11574: grangs dang zhag grangs su ma bzhag par rtags dang
NK026(la)001:11576: phan zhing gso ba'i cho ga byas na yang smon lam yid bzhin du 'grub ste /
NK026(la)001:11577: bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par smon no //
NK026(la)001:11578: mgon po khyod mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK026(la)001:11579: phyogs dang dus kun thams cad du //
NK026(la)001:11580: sems can legs don 'byor ba la //
NK026(la)001:11581: bgegs kyi rnam pa kun med shog /
NK026(la)001:11582: rta dang ba lang nor dang 'bru //
NK026(la)001:11583: bu tsha pha ma gnyen bshes rnams //
NK026(la)001:11584: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK026(la)001:11585: thams cad 'byor ba ldan par shog /
NK026(la)001:11586: dgra bos nyes byed med 'gyur zhing //
NK026(la)001:11587: nad dang mu ge kun med shog /
NK026(la)001:11588: rgyal po dge zhing des pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:11589: chos kyi yul 'khor skyong bar shog /
NK026(la)001:11590: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK026(la)001:11591: phyogs bcu kun tu dar ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11592: myur du sems can thams cad kyang //
NK026(la)001:11593: chos kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK026(la)001:11594: dge ba thams cad spyad sngo zhing //
NK026(la)001:11595: mgon po khyod mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK026(la)001:11596: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:11597: longs spyod rnam gnyis rdzogs par smon //
NK026(la)001:11598: bdag cag byang chub mchog thob nas //
NK026(la)001:11602: gtor ma byang shar du bskyal lo //
NK026(la)001:11603: tshogs bdag rgyun gyi yi dam rdzogs so //
NK026(la)001:11605: dpal mgon nag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:11607: nyams na sgrub rtags mi 'byung bas /
NK026(la)001:11608: bskang ba'i cho ga bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:11613: rgyud lugs kyi gtor ma chen po /
NK026(la)001:11637: dam rdzas sna tshogs tshang bar bsags la /
NK026(la)001:11638: mchod cing bskang ba 'di skad do //
NK026(la)001:11640: bdag ni rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK026(la)001:11641: bdag ni rnal 'byor thugs dam can //
NK026(la)001:11642: dam la gnas shing lha la 'phreng //
NK026(la)001:11643: khyod kyi srung ma mthu rtsal can /
NK026(la)001:11644: hoh dgongs shig ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11645: dgongs shig legs ldan nag po'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11646: sngon tshe dpal gyi spyan snga ru //
NK026(la)001:11647: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11648: phyag na rdo rje'i spyan snga ru //
NK026(la)001:11649: bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11650: khyed kyi thugs dam gnyan po 'di //
NK026(la)001:11651: da lta rnal 'byor rjes bskul na //
NK026(la)001:11652: bsgrub cing bskul zhing gshegs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:11653: ma h+aa k+aa la gnas 'dir spyon //
NK026(la)001:11654: chos skyong chen po gnas 'dir lha chen dpal 'bar
NK026(la)001:11655: legs ldan nag po rnal 'byor dgra lha rig 'dzin
NK026(la)001:11656: srung ma sring gcig lha mo gsang ba'i yum dang
NK026(la)001:11659: bos so mgon po snyan ma sra //
NK026(la)001:11660: bos so chos skyong snyan ma sra //
NK026(la)001:11661: bos so bdud rgyal snyan ma sra //
NK026(la)001:11662: g.yab bo legs ldan spyan ma rtul //
NK026(la)001:11663: bsten no mgon po rgyang ma ring //
NK026(la)001:11664: bsgrub bo mgon po gang ma g.yel //
NK026(la)001:11665: bskur ro mgon po 'phrang ma dog /
NK026(la)001:11666: rbad do legs ldan mthu ma chung //
NK026(la)001:11667: bskul lo mgon po bang ma bul //
NK026(la)001:11668: do nub dam skyong gnas 'dir spyon //
NK026(la)001:11669: do nub cha dang khrims la dga' //
NK026(la)001:11670: grogs po bya'o gzhung ma ngan //
NK026(la)001:11671: mdza' bo bya 'o ro ma dor //
NK026(la)001:11672: mna' tho bsten no phrag ma dog /
NK026(la)001:11673: rje bor bya'o dbang ma che //
NK026(la)001:11674: bran ltar bskul lo rgyud ma ngan //
NK026(la)001:11675: sring cig lha mo da tshur spyon //
NK026(la)001:11676: sring ltar bsten no dbang ma che //
NK026(la)001:11677: sring ltar bsten no tshul ma ngan //
NK026(la)001:11678: gzungs ltar bsten no phrag ma dog /
NK026(la)001:11679: 'khol ltar bsten no snying ma ring //
NK026(la)001:11680: khyed dam tshig gnyan la mi sems na //
NK026(la)001:11681: dang po'i chad pa 'di min nam //
NK026(la)001:11682: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11683: dkon mchog dbu 'phang bstod pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11684: rnal 'byor dgra lha bya ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11685: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs bsgral ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11686: dam tshig gnyan po bsrung ba dang //
NK026(la)001:11687: dam tshig 'da' bar ma chad do //
NK026(la)001:11688: bstan pa bsrung bar ma byas sam //
NK026(la)001:11689: dam las ma g.yel da tshur spyon //
NK026(la)001:11690: bcol ba'i las 'di ma byas na //
NK026(la)001:11691: dang po'i chang las mna' yang zos //
NK026(la)001:11692: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i bka' yang bslus //
NK026(la)001:11693: rnal 'byor bdag gi yid kyang chad //
NK026(la)001:11694: dang po'i chad las mna' zos na //
NK026(la)001:11695: dam tshig nyams kyi chad pa yod //
NK026(la)001:11696: bka' yi smod pas sdigs par mchi'o //
NK026(la)001:11697: de yi dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK026(la)001:11698: bskul nas ma rings las 'di mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11699: thugs dam gnyan po bdag bskang ngo //
NK026(la)001:11701: khyed kyang dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK026(la)001:11703: de tsam mtshang nas ma brgal na //
NK026(la)001:11704: mi shes snyam nas snyoms las byed //
NK026(la)001:11706: nyon dang mgon po thod phreng can //
NK026(la)001:11707: nyon dang chos skyong nag po tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11708: nyon cig sring cig re ma ti //
NK026(la)001:11709: rgyal bas bka' la mi bden med //
NK026(la)001:11710: zab mo'i don la mi sems med //
NK026(la)001:11711: zas dang skom la mi chags med //
NK026(la)001:11712: do nub khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK026(la)001:11713: do nub nyams chag ma lus bskang //
NK026(la)001:11714: do nub zhig ral ma lus bskang //
NK026(la)001:11715: do nub lha la bshags par bgyi //
NK026(la)001:11716: do nub lha la sems 'khon sbyong //
NK026(la)001:11717: do nub mnyes pa'i zas shig 'dren //
NK026(la)001:11718: do nub bza' ba'i gzhung zhig byed //
NK026(la)001:11719: do nub byas pa'i lan cig ldon //
NK026(la)001:11720: do nub barngana pa'i gtang rag gtong //
NK026(la)001:11721: do nub phyi ma'i zhu skyems 'dren //
NK026(la)001:11723: bskang ngo khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK026(la)001:11724: bshags so dam tshig so ru bshags //
NK026(la)001:11726: ma h+aa k+aa la tshur gson dang //
NK026(la)001:11727: dpal ldan mgon po tshur gson dang //
NK026(la)001:11728: legs ldan nag po tshur gson dang //
NK026(la)001:11729: khyod kyi thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK026(la)001:11730: thams cad gyur pa'i pany+tsa dang //
NK026(la)001:11732: sha khrag 'khyil ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK026(la)001:11733: snang gsal 'od kyi zhun mar dang //
NK026(la)001:11734: sha chen spos kyi dud sprin dang //
NK026(la)001:11735: tshogs kyi zhal zas mang po dang //
NK026(la)001:11736: mgon lug nag po spyi dkar dang //
NK026(la)001:11737: bya mo nag po gser mig dang //
NK026(la)001:11738: mchod pa'i brten pa'i dam rdzas kyis //
NK026(la)001:11739: chos skyong rnams kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK026(la)001:11740: brten pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11741: mda' bya rgod ma sku yi rten //
NK026(la)001:11742: chos kyi sku yis thugs rak+ta rnam gsum gsung gi rten //
NK026(la)001:11743: gsung gi rten gyis thugs tsit+ta rnam gsum thugs kyi rten //
NK026(la)001:11744: thugs kyi rten gyis thugs gnas gsum nag po phyi yi rten //
NK026(la)001:11745: phyi yi rten gyis thugs bya nag rgyal mtshan nang
NK026(la)001:11746: gi rten nang gi rten gyis thugs gri thod snying
NK026(la)001:11748: gsang ba'i rten gyis thugs 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11749: g.yab dar nag pos thugs dam tshig gnyan po bsre ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11750: bdud rtsi sman gyis thugs rak+ta skom du 'thung ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11751: dmar chen ar+g+hasa thugs mnyes byed skom du 'thung ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11752: su ra chang gis thugs rtag tu mi 'bral 'grogs pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11753: gta' gtor chen pos rgyun du phrin las bcol ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11754: rgyun gyi gtor mas thugs rbad pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11755: khyi nag snying gis thugs gsang ba'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11756: tsit+ta snying gis thugs bsgral ba'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11757: lug nag snying gis thugs bskang ba'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11758: lug nag spyi dkar thugs dgyes pa'i dam rdzas yin
NK026(la)001:11759: mkha' lding nag pos thugs sring mo'i dam rdzas yin
NK026(la)001:11760: pa'i phyir // nal bu'i rgyal mtshan thugs 'dun pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11761: mi rkang gling bus thugs m+aam sa zas su za ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11762: sha chen bdun rtsis thugs shangs kyi dbang po tshim mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11763: gsur chen dud pas thugs ljags kyi dbang po tshim mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11764: bshos bu dmar nag thugs spyan gyi dbang po tshim mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11765: tshil chen mar mes thugs snyan gyi dbang po tshim mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11766: rol mo sgra yis thugs mthun pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11767: gos nag zhwa nag thugs mchod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11768: nya sha la phug la dus thugs sgrub pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11769: sngags dang phyag rgyas thugs dgyes shing dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11770: tshogs dang gtor mas thugs nag po chen po'i thugs
NK026(la)001:11771: chos skyong mgon po'i thugs dpal ldan chen po'i thugs
NK026(la)001:11772: legs ldan nag po'i thugs lha yi dmag dpon thugs
NK026(la)001:11773: rigs bzhi mgon po'i thugs sprul pa'i mgon po'i las
NK026(la)001:11774: kyi mgon po'i phyag brnyan mgon po'i pho nya mgon
NK026(la)001:11775: po'i phyogs skyong mgon po'i gtsug tor dkar mo sku
NK026(la)001:11776: yi yum // sku yi yum gyi thugs a ra pa tsa gsung gi yum //
NK026(la)001:11777: gsung gi yum gyi thugs yak+sha pa te thugs kyi yum //
NK026(la)001:11778: thugs kyi yum yi thugs li sa d+ho da yon tan yum //
NK026(la)001:11779: yon tan yum gyi thugs byi ta ra ni las kyi yum //
NK026(la)001:11780: las kyi yum gyi thugs ka pur ka ni pho nya yum //
NK026(la)001:11781: pho nya'i yum gyi thugs dkar sha ma ni mgyogs byed yum //
NK026(la)001:11782: mgyogs byed ma yi thugs dur khrod ma bdun thugs klu mo bsrung bzhi rnams dang ni //
NK026(la)001:11783: dur khrod bdag mo gru 'degs bzhi rnams dang //
NK026(la)001:11784: srin mo chen mo nyi shu brgyad kyi thugs ma h+aa k+aa la'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK026(la)001:11785: tshogs bdag mgon po 'khor dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:11786: yang dag srung mar dam bcas shing //
NK026(la)001:11787: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:11788: legs ldan nag po bdud kyi rje //
NK026(la)001:11789: gsang mtshan rdo rje ro langs te //
NK026(la)001:11790: nye gnas kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma //
NK026(la)001:11791: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11792: gnod sbyin sde bzhi thugs dam can //
NK026(la)001:11793: kro d+ha khro bo ging gi tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11794: yak+sha gnod sbyin dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11795: rak+sha srin po rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11796: tsit+ta za byed ma mo'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11797: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11798: bka' sdod las mkhan bshan pa ni //
NK026(la)001:11799: nag po gri gug thod khrag 'thung //
NK026(la)001:11800: khyod ni bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK026(la)001:11801: dam nyams dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:11802: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK026(la)001:11803: bstan pa'i dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK026(la)001:11804: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la rak+mo kro ti shwa
NK026(la)001:11805: r+ai nag mo ting lam ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa
NK026(la)001:11806: hi / rak+ta tsit+ta go ro tsa na kem ni
NK026(la)001:11807: ri ti ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha
NK026(la)001:11809: kro d+ha yak+sha rak+sha tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:11811: hoh dpal ma h+aa k+aa la rig 'dzin gyi srog shing /
NK026(la)001:11815: chos skyong yongs kyi rje bo /
NK026(la)001:11816: srin po bya'i gshog pa can /
NK026(la)001:11817: ljang nag chen po phyag na tsan+dana gyi beng chen
NK026(la)001:11818: bsnams nas byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi phyir 'brang zhing
NK026(la)001:11819: / lho phyogs gshin rje'i sna 'dren pa /
NK026(la)001:11820: tshogs bdag chen po bzhi'i mnga' bdag /
NK026(la)001:11822: mgon po nag po'i tshogs la dbang bsgyur ba khyed
NK026(la)001:11823: dam rdzas kyi gtor ma chen po'i 'di bzhes la
NK026(la)001:11824: / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung ba'i phrin las rgya chen po mdzad du gsol /
NK026(la)001:11825: zhes pa la sogs pa gang 'dod pa'i smon lam gdab /
NK026(la)001:11826: tshogs 'bul sman raka gtor mar sbreng /
NK026(la)001:11827: mgon po legs ldan gyi bshags pa'i yig chung ngo //
NK026(la)001:11829: dpal chen rdo rje srin po'i lha tshogs dang //
NK026(la)001:11830: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:11831: gsang sngags theg chen bslab pa'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK026(la)001:11832: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK026(la)001:11833: thun bzhi'i rnal 'byor bsgom par khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11834: tha mal las la yengs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK026(la)001:11835: bde gshegs thugs rgyud bskul bar khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11836: don med long gtam smra ba mthong lo gnyis med ye shes sgom par khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11837: chags sdang rtogs pa'i dbang gyur phyi nang gsang rten 'dzugs par khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11838: dgongs pa'i dam rdzas ma tshogs dgyes pa'i mchod gtor 'bul bar khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11839: snyoms las le lor gyur pa man ngag sbas nas bsgrub par khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11840: gsang gtam khrom du bsgrags pa gsung gi bka' bzhin bsgrub par khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11841: gzu lum ras chod gyur pa dam rdzas phud kyi mchod par khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11842: 'bags btsog nyer pas gyur pa dam tshig gtsang mar bsrung bar khas blangs nas /
NK026(la)001:11843: nyams chag sgrib snyon gos pa mnyes pa'i gtor ma gtong bar khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11844: gtor tshogs 'byor ba chung ba rak+ta'i mchod pa gtor bar khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11845: mchod pa dus su ma thongs las bzhi gtor mas bskul bar khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11846: thugs dam dus su ma skong mnyes pa'i gtang rag gtong bar khas blangs nas //
NK026(la)001:11847: tshogs gtor 'byor ba chung ba gzhan yang bshags pa gnyan po 'bul pa ni //
NK026(la)001:11848: bdag cag rnal 'byor mched dang lcam dral gyi //
NK026(la)001:11849: ma h+aa k+aa la'i dkyil 'khor sgor zhugs nas //
NK026(la)001:11850: 'da' daka'i dam tshig gnyan po bsrung rgyu la //
NK026(la)001:11851: bsnyen sgrub dus 'das phud gtor chag pa dang //
NK026(la)001:11852: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig nyams pa kun //
NK026(la)001:11853: rdo rje srin po dur khrod tshogs la bshags //
NK026(la)001:11854: las mgon nag po 'khor dang bcas la bshags //
NK026(la)001:11855: bstan srung mthu yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11856: gtor ma rten dang dam rdzas gtad bzung nas //
NK026(la)001:11857: dus bzhir phud dang nang nub mchod rgyu la //
NK026(la)001:11858: mchod pa'i 'byor tshogs chung ste sku ma mnyes //
NK026(la)001:11859: sku yi dam tshig nyams pa mthol bzlas brjod sngags sogs long gtam bar du bcug /
NK026(la)001:11860: nag po'i srog snying gnad nas ma bskul te //
NK026(la)001:11861: bzlas brjod sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa kun //
NK026(la)001:11862: lha chen 'khor dang bcas la mthol yi dam rtse gcig gzhung bzhin sgom rgyu la //
NK026(la)001:11863: ting 'dzin rtse gcig mi gsal nag po bskyed //
NK026(la)001:11864: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa mthol dar nag ba dan rak+ta dam rdzas tshogs //
NK026(la)001:11865: brten rdzas ma tshang yan lag dam tshig rnams //
NK026(la)001:11866: nag po 'khor dang bcas la mthol dus gsum dpal mgon khyed kyi spyan snga ru //
NK026(la)001:11867: khas blangs nongs pa shor ba mthol dam tshig zhig
NK026(la)001:11868: ral gyur pa phrin las gong 'og nor 'chol gsang
NK026(la)001:11869: sngags 'chol bar shor ba rang don dri mas gos
NK026(la)001:11870: pa nyams len gzhung dang 'gal ba thugs dang 'gal
NK026(la)001:11871: ba ci mchis mthol lo bshags //
NK026(la)001:11872: mthol bshags bzod pa dam pa bzhes mdzod las //
NK026(la)001:11873: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:11874: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:11876: bskang bshags gtso bor bya zhing phrin las bcol lo //
NK026(la)001:11879: bzhengs shig chos kyi dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK026(la)001:11880: spyod cig yum gyi mkha' la spyod //
NK026(la)001:11881: gshegs shig sems can don la gshegs //
NK026(la)001:11882: lha chen dpal 'bar gshegs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:11883: chos skyong mgon po nag po la //
NK026(la)001:11884: dkon mchog gsum gyi mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11885: khrims kyi cha lugs gsum dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:11887: dus gsum sangs rgyas mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11888: sku yi cha byad gsum dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:11889: chos skyong rigs gsum mgon pos mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11890: brjid pa'i gzi mdangs gsum dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:11891: chos skyong khro bo rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11892: zhal gyi khro gnyer gsum dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:11893: chos skyong lha chen brgyad kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11894: dbu skra kham nag thor tshugs can //
NK026(la)001:11895: chos skyong klu chen brgyad kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11896: yan lag sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan //
NK026(la)001:11897: chos skyong sa bdag rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11898: na bza' mthing ber nag po gsol //
NK026(la)001:11899: chos skyong zhing skyong rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11900: phyag na tsan+dana bing chen bsnams //
NK026(la)001:11901: chos skyong mgon po nag po ni //
NK026(la)001:11902: srid pa gsum la mnga' mdzad phyir //
NK026(la)001:11903: sku yi lte ba zur gsum zab //
NK026(la)001:11904: chos skyong gza' chen brgyad kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11905: brjid pa'i smin ma glog ltar 'khyug /
NK026(la)001:11906: chos skyong rgyu skar rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11907: sku smad rme ba'i dum bus brgyan //
NK026(la)001:11908: chos skyong sde brgyad yongs kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11909: cha sgra drag po gsum dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:11910: chos skyong yi dwags rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11911: rin chen 'bar ba'i thod tshar can //
NK026(la)001:11912: chos skyong gshin rje rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11913: spyan nas bskal ba'i me chen 'bar //
NK026(la)001:11914: zhal nas bskal pa'i chu chen 'bab //
NK026(la)001:11915: shangs nas bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshub //
NK026(la)001:11916: chos skyong ma mo rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11917: chags chen rak+ta'i thig les brgyan //
NK026(la)001:11918: chos skyong ging chen rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11919: zhag gi zo ris brjid pas brgyan //
NK026(la)001:11920: chos skyong pho nya rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11921: lhag pa'i thal chen tshom bus brgyan //
NK026(la)001:11922: chos skyong srin po rnams kyis mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:11923: thod rlon phreng ba'i do shal can //
NK026(la)001:11924: lha chen mgon por mnga' gsol lo //
NK026(la)001:11925: mgon po'i thugs dam rten la chos //
NK026(la)001:11926: mgon po'i yid chags dkor la mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11927: mgon po'i phrin las dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK026(la)001:11928: mgon po'i thugs dam rgyud bskul lo //
NK026(la)001:11929: ma sring gnyan gyi thugs gtsug tor dkar mo sku yi yum //
NK026(la)001:11931: rdo rje sgeg mo thugs kyi yum //
NK026(la)001:11932: lam bo d+ha ra yon tan yum //
NK026(la)001:11933: byi da ra ni las kyi yum //
NK026(la)001:11934: u tsu ma ni 'od kyi yum //
NK026(la)001:11935: kar+sha ma ni phrin las yum //
NK026(la)001:11936: kam ka mo ni pho nya mo //
NK026(la)001:11937: lha chen mgon po thugs dam can //
NK026(la)001:11938: dmar gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK026(la)001:11939: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i bka' srung mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11940: gtsug lag khang gi bdag po mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11941: bdud 'dul yongs kyi dmag dpon mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11942: gzugs can dgra yi gshed ma mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11943: gzugs med bgegs kyi bya ra mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11944: bdag cag rig 'dzin srog shing mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11945: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dgra lha mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11946: dug gsum nad kyi sman pa mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11947: bdag gi bsam pa 'grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11954: sha chen dang snying gis brten /
NK026(la)001:11955: khyad par gyi gtor mas rgyun du mchod /
NK026(la)001:11958: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK026(la)001:11959: yang dag gsang ba'i sku zhig byung ba ni //
NK026(la)001:11960: mthing nag mi bsrun 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i sku //
NK026(la)001:11961: nyid kyi sku mdog mthing nag chen po la //
NK026(la)001:11962: dbu skra kham nag thor tshugs gcig tu 'khyil //
NK026(la)001:11963: thabs dang shes rab nyi zlas dbu la brgyan //
NK026(la)001:11964: smin ma nag po khro gnyer brjid pa'i zhal //
NK026(la)001:11965: spyan bzlog zhal bsgrad mche ba rno gtsigs nas //
NK026(la)001:11966: dam nyams log par lta ba'i snying rtsa gcod //
NK026(la)001:11967: spyan nas me 'bar shangs nas 'tshub ma ldang //
NK026(la)001:11968: phyag gnyis thabs dang shes rab zung 'brel ba //
NK026(la)001:11969: g.yas pa'i phyag na tsan+dana beng chen bsnams //
NK026(la)001:11970: rab tu gsor zhing log 'dren gdug pa 'dul //
NK026(la)001:11971: g.yon pa'i phyag na par bu dku la brten //
NK026(la)001:11972: dar ber sngo khra brjid pa sku la gsol //
NK026(la)001:11973: gser ske rin chen 'bar ba sked la bcings //
NK026(la)001:11974: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum bsgrad pa'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:11975: ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK026(la)001:11976: pho nya sprul pa'i tshogs ni skar ltar 'khrugs //
NK026(la)001:11977: bstan pa bshig pa'i dam nyams rdul du rlog /
NK026(la)001:11978: sdig can las ngan 'khor ba'i sems can 'dis //
NK026(la)001:11979: bstan pa bshig cing dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod //
NK026(la)001:11980: dben gnas 'joms shing gtsug lag dkor khang bshig /
NK026(la)001:11981: rdo rje slob dpon sku la dgra byed pa //
NK026(la)001:11982: bsgral ba'i zhing du dam nyams 'di 'gyur bas //
NK026(la)001:11983: pha rol 'joms pa'i stobs kyis myur du sgrol //
NK026(la)001:11984: rgyal ba'i spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas ltar //
NK026(la)001:11985: bcol ba'i las rnams myur du grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:11987: sh+aa sa na +aa pa h+aa ri ni /
NK026(la)001:11988: e sha a pany+tsi ma k+aa +aa yam /
NK026(la)001:11989: i dam rat+na tra y+aa ya a pa k+aa ri
NK026(la)001:11990: ni ya di pra t+ai dz+ny+aa sma ri sa ta
NK026(la)001:11991: d+aa / i dam dush+ta na kha kha /
NK026(la)001:12001: sha sa m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:12004: nag po stong gi tshogs dang /
NK026(la)001:12006: ma mo bye ba 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK026(la)001:12012: dug gsum nad kyi sman pa /
NK026(la)001:12013: gtsug lag khang gi bdag po /
NK026(la)001:12017: tshe dang dbang phyug spel cig /
NK026(la)001:12018: dpal dang grags pa sgrubs shig /
NK026(la)001:12025: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu bya ba'i bar sngar bzhin la /
NK026(la)001:12026: bla mas thugs bskyed phog ste /
