NK026(la)001:12027: sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK026(la)001:12028: de'i phyir du lam sgrub pa'i bar chad zhi ba dang /
NK026(la)001:12029: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag tu bsgrub par bya
NK026(la)001:12030: ba'i phyir bstan srung mgon po'i dbang bskur ba gsan
NK026(la)001:12031: te / sems can gyi don rgya chen po bgyid
NK026(la)001:12032: snyam pa byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa
NK026(la)001:12036: rin chen chos kyang dkon la rtag tu 'tshe ba mang //
NK026(la)001:12038: 'tshe ba las skyob par byed pa dam pa chos
NK026(la)001:12039: skyong ba'i srung ma zhig la nges par brten dgos
NK026(la)001:12040: shing / de la yang 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa gnyis las /
NK026(la)001:12041: 'jig rten pa rnams kyis thun mong gi bar chad
NK026(la)001:12042: sel zhing dngos grub phra mo ster bar nus srid
NK026(la)001:12043: kyang / khong cag rnams kyang 'khor ba las ma
NK026(la)001:12044: 'das pa'i phyir bdud bzhi'i bar chod sel mi nus
NK026(la)001:12045: kyang / shing / 'jig rten las 'das pa rnams
NK026(la)001:12046: ni ngo bo dkyil 'khor gyi khyab bdag dang tha
NK026(la)001:12047: kyang / shing / mi dad cing / rnam pa
NK026(la)001:12048: gdul bya gdug pa can rnams 'dul bar bya ba'i
NK026(la)001:12049: phyir bka' sdod kyi tshul bzung ste /
NK026(la)001:12050: dge 'dun dkon mchog gi rang bzhin du bzhugs pa yin pas /
NK026(la)001:12051: de'i phyir bsten pas bar chod mtha' dag sel zhing
NK026(la)001:12052: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag tu 'grub par nus
NK026(la)001:12053: pa yin pas bsten dgos shing /
NK026(la)001:12054: de lta bu la yang thog mar dbang dang rjes
NK026(la)001:12055: gnang bka' gtad sogs kyi sgo nas slob ma dang
NK026(la)001:12056: chos skyong ngo sprod dgos pas da lam de'i skabs
NK026(la)001:12058: de la yang gang las byung ba'i brgyud pa dang /
NK026(la)001:12059: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i gdams pa gnyis las /
NK026(la)001:12061: sngon bskal pa dpag tu med pa 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba /
NK026(la)001:12062: bskal pa kun dga' zhes bya ba la zhing khams
NK026(la)001:12063: mngon par dga' bar sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa zhes
NK026(la)001:12065: bstan pa de la rab tu byung ba'i dge slong
NK026(la)001:12066: thub dka' gzhon nu zhes bya bas theg pa chen
NK026(la)001:12067: po'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus /
NK026(la)001:12068: dge slong thar pa nag po dang dan 'phags zhes bya ba gnyis kyi sngags lam nos pa las /
NK026(la)001:12069: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK026(la)001:12070: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK026(la)001:12071: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK026(la)001:12074: thar pa nag pos tshig las gol te lta ba log nas sbyor sgrol log par spyad par brten /
NK026(la)001:12075: bla ma dang mched dan 'phags kyi dam las 'gal te /
NK026(la)001:12076: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu dmyal ba yi dwags ce spyang /
NK026(la)001:12080: sha sbrang la sogs pa'i rim gyis brgyud pa'i mthar rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bus /
NK026(la)001:12081: yul lang+ka pu rir smad 'tshong ma'i bur gyur te /
NK026(la)001:12082: de yang thal ka mgo gsum lag pa drug /
NK026(la)001:12083: mchu sder bya gshog can 'jigs su rung bar gyur te /
NK026(la)001:12084: ma shi ba'i ro dang lhan du dur khrod du
NK026(la)001:12085: bskyal bar ma'i sha zos shing lus brtas nas pho
NK026(la)001:12086: thams cad bsad pa'i sha khrag la longs spyod cing
NK026(la)001:12087: / mo thams cad la sbyor ba byas rdzu 'phrul dang mngon shes phra mo yang grub ste /
NK026(la)001:12088: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad ma rungs par byas /
NK026(la)001:12089: mtsho ko ka thang dmar gyi do /
NK026(la)001:12090: ri bo ma la ya drag shul can gyi rtser gnas te /
NK026(la)001:12091: dur khrod kyi ma mo dang /
NK026(la)001:12092: dbang mo sogs dregs pa can thams cad kyi dpon du gyur pa'i tshe /
NK026(la)001:12093: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad yul dang 'phrad
NK026(la)001:12094: pa'i thugs rje skyes te bka' bgros te thub dka'
NK026(la)001:12095: gzhon nu rdo rje sems dpar sangs rgyas pa dang
NK026(la)001:12096: / dan 'phags phyag na rdo rjer gyur pa gnyis
NK026(la)001:12097: 'dul bar bskos te thabs la mkhas pa'i cho 'phrul
NK026(la)001:12098: du mas btul bar gyur to //
NK026(la)001:12099: khyad par du yang bsgral nas zhal du gsol te
NK026(la)001:12100: bsnams nas bton pa la phyag na rdo rjes dbang
NK026(la)001:12101: bskur zhing / ming yang phyi ltar na bstan srung legs ldan nag po /
NK026(la)001:12102: nang ltar na dur khrod sgrol ging /
NK026(la)001:12103: gsang ba ltar na sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal por btags /
NK026(la)001:12104: sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs /
NK026(la)001:12105: bskal ba de'i phyi ma la 'og phyogs kyi 'jig
NK026(la)001:12106: rten gyi khams thal bas khebs pa zhes bya bar
NK026(la)001:12107: / de bzhin gshegs pa thal ba'i dbang po'i dbyangs
NK026(la)001:12108: zhes bya bar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par
NK026(la)001:12109: lung bstan pa sogs rgyas par na mdo dgongs pa
NK026(la)001:12111: 'dir skye brgyud mdo tsam bshad pa lags /
NK026(la)001:12112: de lta bu'i bstan srung dbang po 'di nyid kyi
NK026(la)001:12113: chos skor rgya gar gyi pan grub rig 'dzin rnams
NK026(la)001:12114: las brgyud de / bod yul gyi ljongs 'dir gnubs
NK026(la)001:12115: chen lo ts+aa ba sangs rgyas ye shes rin po
NK026(la)001:12117: rim bzhin brgyud de 'ongs pa las kho bos khyab
NK026(la)001:12118: bdag sman lung pa chen po'i zhabs drung du gtor
NK026(la)001:12119: ba'i bka' gtad tsam las zhu ma thub kyang /
NK026(la)001:12120: slad kyis gtsang shod pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan pa'i
NK026(la)001:12121: chog khrigs steng nas dbang bskur ba rig 'dzin 'gyur
NK026(la)001:12122: med rdo rje las nos shing /
NK026(la)001:12123: zur stod lugs kyi dbang bzhi byin rlabs kyi tshul
NK026(la)001:12124: du len pa mthar gtor ma'i bka' gtad dang bcas
NK026(la)001:12125: pa / la stod brag dkar ba mkhan chen byams
NK026(la)001:12126: pas rin chen chos 'phel las nos pas brgyud tshul
NK026(la)001:12127: mi nub par bya ba'i phyir rim par 'bul ba
NK026(la)001:12128: skabs su bab pa yin pas /
NK026(la)001:12129: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i gdams pa dngos la gnyis te /
NK026(la)001:12131: slob ma'i bgyi 'os gnyis las dang po lhag chad med par grub khul yin /
NK026(la)001:12132: gnyis pa la da res dngos sta sbrel nas bya
NK026(la)001:12133: ba la thog mar sta gon gyi chos rnams zhu
NK026(la)001:12135: zhes mtshams sbyor la dbang dngos ni gtsang shod pa'i rtsa bar /
NK026(la)001:12136: slob ma khrus byas man+dala phul //
NK026(la)001:12137: gral la rim par 'khod pa yis //
NK026(la)001:12138: gsol ba 'di skad gdab par bya //
NK026(la)001:12140: snyim pa me tog dang bcas te gsol ba btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum mdzod /
NK026(la)001:12141: hoh rang bzhin 'du 'bral med pa'i lha //
NK026(la)001:12142: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog tu //
NK026(la)001:12143: bdag kyang mnyam par smra ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12144: byin rlabs rab tu bzhugs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:12147: kun rdzob sems bskyed kyi don du /
NK026(la)001:12148: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK026(la)001:12149: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK026(la)001:12150: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK026(la)001:12151: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK026(la)001:12152: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed kyi slad du /
NK026(la)001:12153: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK026(la)001:12154: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK026(la)001:12155: zhes sogs kyi sems lnga bskyed do //
NK026(la)001:12157: sems gnyis ldan la gsang don sbyin //
NK026(la)001:12160: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK026(la)001:12161: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK026(la)001:12162: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK026(la)001:12163: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK026(la)001:12164: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:12165: sus kyang ma bcings bcings med de //
NK026(la)001:12166: bcings par bya ba yod ma yin //
NK026(la)001:12167: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yi //
NK026(la)001:12168: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa 'dor //
NK026(la)001:12169: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK026(la)001:12170: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK026(la)001:12171: khyod la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK026(la)001:12172: zhes brjod cing don dkrol lo //
NK026(la)001:12173: slar yang gsol ba btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod //
NK026(la)001:12174: he ru ka dpal khyod la 'dud //
NK026(la)001:12175: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK026(la)001:12176: de yi dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK026(la)001:12177: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song zhing //
NK026(la)001:12178: theg chen khang par 'jug pa dang //
NK026(la)001:12179: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK026(la)001:12182: de nas rdo rje slob ma yi //
NK026(la)001:12183: tshe sba bgegs bskrad sgrib pa phral //
NK026(la)001:12184: lha bskyed go bgo lus srung bya //
NK026(la)001:12186: bi shwa badz+ra sngags kyis bskrad //
NK026(la)001:12187: lag sor rlabs phral bden stobs sbyangs //
NK026(la)001:12188: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyi don ni /
NK026(la)001:12189: gong du tshogs chen gyi slob ma sta gon skabs ltar bya la /
NK026(la)001:12190: tshe sba ba'i dus kyi +aa yur h+aum dzah +aa yu dz+ny+aa na b+hin+d+hu b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:12192: gzhan ma lus srung gi bar sngar ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:12194: rtsa ba'i sngags kyis mgon por bskyed //
NK026(la)001:12195: go bgo lus bsrung bka' nan bcings //
NK026(la)001:12197: b+hur kar ti h+aum phata las slob ma skad cig
NK026(la)001:12198: gis dpal ye shes kyi mgon po zhal gcig phyag
NK026(la)001:12199: gnyis phyag g.yas tsan+dana gyi beng chen dang g.yon thod
NK026(la)001:12200: khrag bsnams pa / dar ber sngo khra'i 'jol ber
NK026(la)001:12201: gser skad hor lhwam can ye shes kyi me 'bar
NK026(la)001:12202: ba'i dbus na bzhugs par bskyed pa'i spyi bor las
NK026(la)001:12203: 'khor lo dkar po gyis mtshan pa /
NK026(la)001:12204: mgrin par +aahls pad+ma dmar po +aahs mtshan pa /
NK026(la)001:12205: thugs kar h+aum las rdo rje sngon po h+aum gis
NK026(la)001:12206: mtshan par gyur ba'i yig 'bru gsum po sku gsung
NK026(la)001:12207: thugs rdo rje'i lha dkar dmar mthing ba /
NK026(la)001:12208: rdo rje pad+ma 'khor lo 'dzin pa'i skur gyur par mos mdzod /
NK026(la)001:12209: ces dri bzang gi chus gnas gsum du thig le yas mar lan gsum bkod cing /
NK026(la)001:12210: +aahh+aum lugs 'byung gnyis kyi bar du lugs ldog gcig ste lan gsum brjod do //
NK026(la)001:12212: de nas srung skud gsum sgril la //
NK026(la)001:12213: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'ii sngags kyis gdab //
NK026(la)001:12214: dpung par bcings pas lus dag bya //
NK026(la)001:12215: zhes gsungs pa'i don srung skud las bum gyi chus bsang /
NK026(la)001:12217: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li ha na
NK026(la)001:12218: ha na h+aum phata kyis gdab cing 'khyil ba'i rang
NK026(la)001:12219: bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa pho'i g.yon dang /
NK026(la)001:12221: mdung steng dri bzang gi chus brlan cing rdo rje
NK026(la)001:12222: rgya gram du bzhag pa ni lus kyi bar chad
NK026(la)001:12225: man+dala rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan //
NK026(la)001:12226: so shing dor te ltas brtag go //
NK026(la)001:12228: so shing dor ba'i ras bris pad 'dab bzhi pa
NK026(la)001:12229: h+aum tram h+r+aih+aahsa rigs lnga'i rang bzhin du byin gyis
NK026(la)001:12230: brlab / so shing bum chus bsang /
NK026(la)001:12231: badz+ra dzi ha sam b+ha ra d+ha ni h+aum gis byin gyis brlabs pa slob mar sbyin /
NK026(la)001:12232: bshad pas brda' dkrol te sngags gong mas dkyil 'khor du dor te ltas brtag pa spyi ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:12235: tsan+dana nam ni dri chu la //
NK026(la)001:12236: sngags btab khrus bshal khong du btung //
NK026(la)001:12237: zhes gsungs pa ltar dri bzang gi khyor chu /
NK026(la)001:12238: +aahbig+h+nan+ta krita a mri tu kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:12239: ces byin gyis brlabs pa'i chu sbyin cing /
NK026(la)001:12240: h+r+aihbi shud+d+ha sarba d+harma sarba p+aa pam ni tsa s+ya
NK026(la)001:12241: sam sho d+ha nisarba bi kalpana a pa na ye
NK026(la)001:12242: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes sbyin pas kha bshal /
NK026(la)001:12243: khong du btung ba yid kyi sgrib sbyong ngo //
NK026(la)001:12245: d+hi dang ha yis basngagasa pa yi //
NK026(la)001:12246: ku sha sngon po gnyis sbyin la //
NK026(la)001:12247: sngags dang stan bya rmi lam brtag /
NK026(la)001:12248: dri zhing ngan na bzlog par bya //
NK026(la)001:12249: zhes gsungs pas dngos sta tha dad yin na slob
NK026(la)001:12250: ma'i grangs dang mnyam pa'i ku sha che chung gnyis
NK026(la)001:12251: dgos shing sbrel skabs 'dir ku sha che chung gcig
NK026(la)001:12252: bum chus bsang / d+hi has byin gyis brlabs la
NK026(la)001:12253: gtad de nyal lugs sogs bshad pa spyi ltar ro
NK026(la)001:12255: de nas gegs brgyad bshad kyang rung //
NK026(la)001:12256: zhes gsungs pa spro na sgo 'byed phyag rdor skabs ltar bshad do //
NK026(la)001:12257: sbrel ba'i tshe ma bshad kyang 'thus /
NK026(la)001:12259: de nas thig tshon byin brlabs te //
NK026(la)001:12260: legs ldan dkyil 'khor gzhung bzhin bri //
NK026(la)001:12261: las gzhung bsrang la bsgrub cing mchod //
NK026(la)001:12262: ces gsungs pa sta gon zhag gis bar du chod
NK026(la)001:12263: na skabs 'dir bya dgos kyang da lam gong du
NK026(la)001:12267: slob ma khrus byas man+dala phul //
NK026(la)001:12268: zhes gsungs pa'i dngos gzhi'i 'jug pa'i don du man+dala phul /
NK026(la)001:12270: de nas gsol ba gdab pa ni //
NK026(la)001:12272: snyim pa me tog dang bcas te 'jug pa'i don
NK026(la)001:12273: du gsol ba gdab pa'i rjes zlos lan gsum bya
NK026(la)001:12274: ste / dpal mgon legs ldan nag po yi //
NK026(la)001:12275: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:12277: dpa' bos thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK026(la)001:12278: lan gsum bla mas lan btab pa //
NK026(la)001:12279: legs ldan nag pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:12281: las dang bsam pa thams cad 'grub //
NK026(la)001:12282: bla med theg chen 'bras bu thob //
NK026(la)001:12283: gnas skabs bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12289: bu khyod su yin ci la dga' //
NK026(la)001:12291: bdag ni las mchog skal par ldan //
NK026(la)001:12293: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' spyad nas ni //
NK026(la)001:12294: 'gro ba thams cad bsgral bar nus //
NK026(la)001:12296: a kham w+ai ra h+aum zhes mig dar bcings /
NK026(la)001:12297: a kham wa ra h+aum zhes me tog gi phreng ba gtad /
NK026(la)001:12299: bla ma dang mdun bskyed gtso bo'i thugs ka nas
NK026(la)001:12300: khro bo sbrul pa spros te bgegs bskrad par mos
NK026(la)001:12302: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata /
NK026(la)001:12303: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12311: zhes pa 'dug pa lhar bskyod cing gnas gsum byin
NK026(la)001:12312: gyis brlab pa'i don yin pa dngos sta tha dad
NK026(la)001:12313: kyi tshe gong bzhin 'dir blang ngo //
NK026(la)001:12314: sbrel ba'i tshe gong mas go chod /
NK026(la)001:12317: ye shes mgon po'i dkyil 'khor mchog gsum rtsa gsum
NK026(la)001:12318: kun 'dus kyi drung du mkha' khyab kyi 'gro ba
NK026(la)001:12321: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK026(la)001:12323: dngos sta tha dad tshe sngar byang chub sems gnyis bskyed phyir /
NK026(la)001:12326: sbrel ma'i tshe gong gi 'thus par sems /
NK026(la)001:12327: sdom bzung dngos 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:12329: rdo rje chos dbyings kun gyi gtso /
NK026(la)001:12330: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK026(la)001:12331: bde ba mchog gi dam pa ste //
NK026(la)001:12332: sems can don dang phrin las bsgrub //
NK026(la)001:12333: sangs rgyas yon tan 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12334: dam tshig dam pa bsrung bar bgyi //
NK026(la)001:12335: chos kun rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK026(la)001:12336: bdag kyang rang bzhin dag pa nas //
NK026(la)001:12337: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK026(la)001:12339: sems can 'byams klas ma lus rnams //
NK026(la)001:12340: mchog nyid bsgrub par bgyis pas na //
NK026(la)001:12341: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cing //
NK026(la)001:12342: slar yang ldog par mi bgyid do //
NK026(la)001:12343: bcom ldan thams cad mchog gi bdag lags te //
NK026(la)001:12344: mchog nyid bsgrub phyir rdo rje blang bar bgyi //
NK026(la)001:12345: rdo rje rgyal por khyod zhugs pas //
NK026(la)001:12346: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ste //
NK026(la)001:12347: rdo rje dam tshig mchog nyid ni //
NK026(la)001:12348: phun sum tshogs par sgrub lags pas //
NK026(la)001:12349: bdag la dus 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:12350: lan gsum bla mas bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK026(la)001:12351: 'di ni rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK026(la)001:12352: sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig yin //
NK026(la)001:12353: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK026(la)001:12354: rtag tu 'bral bar ma byed cig /
NK026(la)001:12355: de ltar khyod kyis rtag tu spyod //
NK026(la)001:12356: dri bzang gi chu nan sbyin pas /
NK026(la)001:12357: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK026(la)001:12358: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK026(la)001:12359: sangs rgyas kun khros khrag chen po //
NK026(la)001:12360: snying nas drangs te 'thung bar byed //
NK026(la)001:12361: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12363: de lta bas na bu khyod kyis //
NK026(la)001:12364: dam tshig 'di ni bsrung bar bgyis //
NK026(la)001:12365: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub ni //
NK026(la)001:12367: pany+tsa a mri ta u tsit+ta a mri ta tha tha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12369: de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyi //
NK026(la)001:12370: phyag na rdo rje nga yin gyi //
NK026(la)001:12371: nga yis ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK026(la)001:12372: khyod kyis de ltar bya dgos so //
NK026(la)001:12374: dkyil 'khor la me tog 'dor zhing 'di'i rjes zlos bya /
NK026(la)001:12376: sngon tshe gong nas bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK026(la)001:12377: bdag gi nye gnas gang lags pa //
NK026(la)001:12378: las 'phro thugs rje ldan pa'i lha //
NK026(la)001:12379: da lta nyid du 'bab gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:12382: slar yang me tog de nyid spyi bor bzhag cing /
NK026(la)001:12383: pra ti gri h+na swa mi mam sat+wa ma h+aa ba la /
NK026(la)001:12384: rdo rje che ge zhes gsang mtshan 'dogs pa'am rnying pa dran par byas pas kyang 'thus /
NK026(la)001:12385: ye shes dbab pa'i don du gsol ba btab pa'i rjes zlos bya /
NK026(la)001:12386: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma thams cad kyis byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK026(la)001:12387: dpal he ru ka bdag la dbab tu gsol //
NK026(la)001:12390: stong pa'i ngang las mgon po zhal gsum phyag drug pa 'khor bcas mngon rtogs ltar bskyed /
NK026(la)001:12393: bla ma la mos gus byas pa'i rkyen gyis /
NK026(la)001:12394: bla ma dang mdun bskyed kyi thugs ka dang rang
NK026(la)001:12395: bzhin gyi gnas nas kyang ye shes mgon po 'khor
NK026(la)001:12396: dang bcas pa spyan drangs te thim par bsam zhing
NK026(la)001:12397: / tshil chen gu gul sogs kyi dud pa dang /
NK026(la)001:12398: rkang gling thod rnga rol mo'i sgra chen por bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:12399: spyan 'dren gyi tshigs bcad las gzhung ltar brjod pa'i mthar /
NK026(la)001:12400: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12401: mgon po'i rtsa sngags rnams dang /
NK026(la)001:12402: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wa na ma h+aa ka
NK026(la)001:12403: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK026(la)001:12406: zhes brjod pa'i mthar gnas gsum du rdo rje bzhag la /
NK026(la)001:12407: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK026(la)001:12410: mig thur ram rdo rje thogs te /
NK026(la)001:12411: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK026(la)001:12412: thur mas ling tog bsal ba ltar //
NK026(la)001:12413: bu khyod kyi ni mi shes pa'i //
NK026(la)001:12414: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK026(la)001:12415: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK026(la)001:12419: ni ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:12420: mum ni ye nas rang sangs rgyas //
NK026(la)001:12421: h+aum ni rtsa ba byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:12422: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa //
NK026(la)001:12423: ha zhes mthong ba yongs su dag /
NK026(la)001:12424: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs mthong bar byed //
NK026(la)001:12425: pho brang dbus na thod mkhar lnga //
NK026(la)001:12426: dkyil na sgrol ging yab yum ste //
NK026(la)001:12427: khro bo gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK026(la)001:12428: ma mo rim par phyogs bzhir gnas //
NK026(la)001:12429: btson khang srin mo bcu drug dang //
NK026(la)001:12430: de mtha' thod pa'i phreng bas bskor //
NK026(la)001:12431: gru chad bzhi la gru 'degs bzhi //
NK026(la)001:12432: bar khyams khrag mtsho dbang mo dang //
NK026(la)001:12433: sgo bzhir sgo ma chen mo bzhi //
NK026(la)001:12434: de dag mtha' ni 'obs mkhar brgyad //
NK026(la)001:12435: kun gyi phyi nang sha za dang //
NK026(la)001:12436: gnod sbyin 'dre srin ro langs dang //
NK026(la)001:12437: bya gcan ce spyang mang pos bskor //
NK026(la)001:12438: sha khrag rus pa ri dang mtsho //
NK026(la)001:12439: dur khrod gnas chen 'jigs par bstan //
NK026(la)001:12440: zhes mgon po 'khor bcas kyi lha ngo bstan cing rgyas par don rtags kyang bkrol la bshad do //
NK026(la)001:12443: man+dala phul la dbang nyid zhu //
NK026(la)001:12444: zhes gsungs pas dbang dngos gzhi'i bum dbang gi don du man+dala phul /
NK026(la)001:12445: gsol ba btab rjes zlos byas te /
NK026(la)001:12446: dbyings ni ye shes gtso mchog yin //
NK026(la)001:12447: rdo rje dam pa mchog 'dzin pa //
NK026(la)001:12448: khyod ni dam tshig gtso lags kyis //
NK026(la)001:12449: dbang phyug rgyal por dbang bskur cig /
NK026(la)001:12452: rin po che yi dbang 'di ni //
NK026(la)001:12453: sangs rgyas kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK026(la)001:12454: gsang gsum gnas las byung ba yi //
NK026(la)001:12455: rdo rje'i dbang bskur chen po sbyin //
NK026(la)001:12458: dbang rdzas lnga dang slob ma la //
NK026(la)001:12459: rigs lnga'i rab gnas tshul bzhin bya //
NK026(la)001:12460: don lnga'i rtog pa so sor bskyed //
NK026(la)001:12462: slob ma las bum gyi chus bsang sbyang /
NK026(la)001:12463: stog pa'i ngang las mi bskyod he ru ka sngon
NK026(la)001:12464: po zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdor dril 'dzin pa yum
NK026(la)001:12465: dang bcas pa'i gnas gsum du +aahh+aum las 'od zer
NK026(la)001:12466: 'phros / rang 'dra'i ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK026(la)001:12467: bum pa mgon po 'khor bcas su gsal ba mi
NK026(la)001:12468: bskyod pa'i rang bzhin can gyis bum dbang bskur zhing
NK026(la)001:12469: 'phros / / mkha' dbyings rnam dag bum pa na //
NK026(la)001:12470: dpal ldan mgon po'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs //
NK026(la)001:12471: gnyis med byang chub sems rtags chus //
NK026(la)001:12472: byin rlabs mthu yi dbang thob shog /
NK026(la)001:12473: b+hur kar ma h+aa k+aa la kro d+ha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12474: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri trag mo he /
NK026(la)001:12478: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK026(la)001:12479: ha he phata b+h+yoh ru lu ru lu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12484: karma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12485: a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12486: zhes mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtugs te dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:12488: mi bskyod pa'i sgo nas chu dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12489: zhe sdang gi dri ma dag /
NK026(la)001:12490: rnam par shes pa'i phung po gnas gyur /
NK026(la)001:12491: stong nyid ye shes mngon du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12492: slob ma dang dbang rdzas dbu rgyan bsang sbyang /
NK026(la)001:12493: stong pa'i ngang las rin 'byung he ru ka zhal
NK026(la)001:12494: gcig phyag gnyis rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin
NK026(la)001:12495: pa yum dang bcas pa'i gnas gsum du +aahh+aum /
NK026(la)001:12496: de las 'od zer 'phros rang 'dra'i ye shes pa
NK026(la)001:12497: dzahh+aum bam hoh dbang rdzas kyi lha 'od du zhu
NK026(la)001:12498: nas rin po che'i cod pan du gyur /
NK026(la)001:12500: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan mchog /
NK026(la)001:12501: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK026(la)001:12502: sangs rgyas rin chen las byung ba'i //
NK026(la)001:12503: dbu rgyan mchog gis dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:12504: rat+na mu ku ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12505: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi sgo nas cod pan gyi dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12506: nga rgyal gyi dri ma dag /
NK026(la)001:12508: mnyam nyid ye shes mngon du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12509: slob ma dang rdo rje bsang sbyang /
NK026(la)001:12510: stong pa'i ngang las snang mtha' he ru ka dmar
NK026(la)001:12511: po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa yum dang bcas
NK026(la)001:12514: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hoh dbang rdzas
NK026(la)001:12515: kyi snang mtha' 'od du zhu nas rdo rjer gyur
NK026(la)001:12516: pa lag pa g.yas su gtad de /
NK026(la)001:12517: chos kun rdo rje'i mtshan nyid du //
NK026(la)001:12518: rdo rje la'ang mtshan nyid med //
NK026(la)001:12519: rdo rje lta bu'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK026(la)001:12520: chos kun rdo rje lta bur ltos //
NK026(la)001:12522: 'od dpag med kyi sgo nas rdo rje'i dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12525: sor rtog ye shes mngon du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12526: slob ma dang dril bu bsang sbyang /
NK026(la)001:12527: stong pa'i ngang las don grub he ru ka ljang
NK026(la)001:12528: gu ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa yum dang
NK026(la)001:12531: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hoh dbang rdzas
NK026(la)001:12532: kyi don grub 'od du zhu nas dril bur gyur
NK026(la)001:12534: 'di ni sangs rgyas gsung dbyangs nyid //
NK026(la)001:12535: ye shes sems dpa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK026(la)001:12536: rdo rje sems dpa' dka' thub dam //
NK026(la)001:12537: rtag tu khyod kyis bcang bar gyis //
NK026(la)001:12538: badz+ra g+han+de ah don yod grub pa'i sgo nas dril bu'i dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12539: phrag dog gi dri ma dag /
NK026(la)001:12540: 'du byed kyi phung po gnas gyur /
NK026(la)001:12541: bya grub ye shes mngon du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12542: slob ma dang dbang rdzas rdor dril zung bsang sbyang /
NK026(la)001:12543: stong pa'i ngang las rnam snang he ru ka dkar
NK026(la)001:12544: po 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa yum dang
NK026(la)001:12546: de las 'od zer 'phros rang 'dra'i ye shes pa
NK026(la)001:12547: dzahh+aum bam hoh dbang rdzas kyi rnam snang 'od du
NK026(la)001:12548: zhu ba rdor dril zung du gyur pa spyi bor
NK026(la)001:12549: dkrol te / yang dag bla med dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:12550: mtshan drangs rdo rje'i ming btags pa //
NK026(la)001:12551: sngags 'chang ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK026(la)001:12552: rig 'dzin zhing du grags gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:12553: gsang mtshan dran du gzhug cing /
NK026(la)001:12554: badz+ra n+aa ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12555: rnam snang gi sgo nas ming gi dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12556: gti mug gi dri ma dag /
NK026(la)001:12557: gzugs kyi phung po gnas gyur /
NK026(la)001:12558: me long ye shes mngon du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12559: de ltar bskyed pa rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du bum dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12561: lam bskyed rim sgom pa la dbang /
NK026(la)001:12562: 'bras bu sprul sku thob pa'i nus ldan du bskyed pa yin /
NK026(la)001:12564: gnyis pa gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba //
NK026(la)001:12565: man+dala phul la gsol ba gdab //
NK026(la)001:12566: ces gsungs pa'i don gsang dbang gi yon du man+dala phul /
NK026(la)001:12567: gsol btab kyi rjes zlos ni /
NK026(la)001:12568: slob dpon khyod ni dgongs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:12569: legs ldan nag po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:12570: gsang ba mchog gi dbang bskur ba //
NK026(la)001:12571: deng 'dir bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:12573: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor lha tshogs snyoms par zhugs
NK026(la)001:12574: pa'i dga' ba'i sgras phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa
NK026(la)001:12575: thams cad spyan drangs zhal du zhugs /
NK026(la)001:12576: rjes chags kyi mes 'od du zhu ba gsang rdzas
NK026(la)001:12577: dang 'dres par phab pa slob ma la sbyin te
NK026(la)001:12578: / dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa'i //
NK026(la)001:12579: yab yum gnyis med bde ba'i don //
NK026(la)001:12580: byang chub sems kyi thig le 'dis //
NK026(la)001:12581: bde chen rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK026(la)001:12582: a ho ma h+aa su ka bo d+hi tsit+ta a /
NK026(la)001:12583: zhes rtsa rlung gi snod rung du byas te lus thams cad bde stong gis khyab par mos /
NK026(la)001:12584: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du gsang dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12586: lam rdzogs rim sgom pa la dbang /
NK026(la)001:12587: 'bras bu longs sku thob pa'i nus ldan du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12589: gsum pa man+dala phul la 'di skad zhu //
NK026(la)001:12590: zhes gsungs pa'i don gsum pa'i yon du man+dala phul la gsol btab ni /
NK026(la)001:12591: khyod ni dam tshig kun gyi gtso //
NK026(la)001:12592: rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:12593: sems can don sgrub phrin las kyi //
NK026(la)001:12594: thugs rjes mnyam sbyor grub par mdzad //
NK026(la)001:12596: slob ma mgon por gsal ba kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma'i rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12597: nye gnas kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma //
NK026(la)001:12598: mtshan ldan sgeg cing mdzes pa mo //
NK026(la)001:12599: lhan cig skyes dga' bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12600: lha mo 'di dang rol par gyis //
NK026(la)001:12601: zhes gtad pa las mgon po yab kyi gsang gnas rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa dang /
NK026(la)001:12602: yum gyi mkha' pad+ma 'dab brgyad as mtshan pa snyoms
NK026(la)001:12603: par zhugs pas byang sems yas babs kyi dga' bzhi
NK026(la)001:12605: h+aum zhes yum gyi dmar cha dang lhan cig par
NK026(la)001:12606: drangs pas mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi nyams su myong
NK026(la)001:12607: zhing bde stong gi ngang la bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:12608: phyag rgya b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor du shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12610: lam pho nya sgom pa la dbang /
NK026(la)001:12611: 'bras bu chos sku thob pa'i nus ldan du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12616: bzhi pa'i yon tan man+dala phul /
NK026(la)001:12618: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa bskyed //
NK026(la)001:12619: rdo rje chos dbyings kun gyi gtso //
NK026(la)001:12620: mi gnas chags pa chen po las //
NK026(la)001:12621: ma lus 'byung gnas bdag la stsol //
NK026(la)001:12623: tshig dbang gi ngo sprod pa ni /
NK026(la)001:12624: gsang ba gsang chen rab gsang ba //
NK026(la)001:12625: rang gi sems kyi me long ltos //
NK026(la)001:12626: mthong bas de bzhin nyid du 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:12627: gzhan min rang byung de kho na'o //
NK026(la)001:12628: zhes brjod la ka dag gi ngang du mnyam par bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:12629: don dam gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bzhi pa thob /
NK026(la)001:12630: sgo gsum gyi dri ma dag /
NK026(la)001:12631: lam blo 'das rdzogs pa chen po sgom pa la dbang /
NK026(la)001:12632: 'bras bu ngo bo nyid sku thob pa'i skal ldan du byas pa'o //
NK026(la)001:12635: de nas drag po'i rjes gnang ni //
NK026(la)001:12636: lcags khang dmigs rten byas pa'i mthar //
NK026(la)001:12637: drag po'i rdzas rnams dgram par bya //
NK026(la)001:12638: mgon po 'khor bcas bskyed bstim bskul //
NK026(la)001:12639: yon tan brjod la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:12640: bsnyen bsgrub rim pa'i sngags brjod cing //
NK026(la)001:12641: man ngag thams cad rdzogs par sbyin //
NK026(la)001:12642: zhes gsungs pa'i don deng sang phyag bzhes su sgrol dbang mdzad pa las gzhan mi 'dug kyang /
NK026(la)001:12643: kho bo'i yongs 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rjes lcags khang
NK026(la)001:12644: bskyed pa ni sgrub gtor lhar bskyed pa'i don du
NK026(la)001:12645: snang bas / nub dgon lugs bzhin 'dir gtor dbang
NK026(la)001:12646: bskur na gzhung don dang mthun par snang bas de
NK026(la)001:12647: ltar gyis shig ces bka' stsal pa don la gnas
NK026(la)001:12648: par shes shing yid ches pas skabs 'dir nub dgon
NK026(la)001:12649: lugs zur stod lugs pa'i phyag bzhes bzhin dbang bzhi
NK026(la)001:12650: byin rlabs kyi tshul du bskur ba ni /
NK026(la)001:12651: mnyam med nub dgon po'i thugs sras byams pa blo
NK026(la)001:12652: gros rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i yig cha'i steng nas
NK026(la)001:12653: bdag gis nos pas yi ge de nyid las btus
NK026(la)001:12659: lnga pa yan lag bdun pa rnams sngon 'gror gsungs pas /
NK026(la)001:12660: bye brag tu bskur na lnga ga nges par dgos kyang /
NK026(la)001:12661: 'dir sbrel ba'i dbang gis man+dala gsol btab kyis 'thus
NK026(la)001:12662: par snang bas bka' gtad kyi don du man+dala phul
NK026(la)001:12663: / gsol btab 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum bya ste /
NK026(la)001:12664: dpa' bo chen po dgongs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:12665: bdag cag skal ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:12667: rgyal ba'i sras su bzung du gsol //
NK026(la)001:12671: sku gsung thugs kyi rjes gnang /
NK026(la)001:12674: me tog sbyin pa ste lnga las /
NK026(la)001:12675: dang po yi dam lha'i dbang ni dmigs pa 'di bzhin du mdzod /
NK026(la)001:12676: slob dpon dpal che mchog tu gsal ba'i thugs ka nas h+aum 'phros /
NK026(la)001:12677: khyod rang rnams kyi snying gar thim pas lus thams cad bsregs /
NK026(la)001:12678: rnam shes h+aum du gyur pa las /
NK026(la)001:12679: skad cig dpal chen po zhal gsum phyag drug pa'am zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i bskyed rim phog ste /
NK026(la)001:12680: tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor nas khro bo'i gtor ma
NK026(la)001:12681: blangs te gtor ma de nyid dpal chen po khrag
NK026(la)001:12682: 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad du gsal ba slob ma'i
NK026(la)001:12683: mgor bzhag pas / lha rnams kyi sbyor mtshams nas
NK026(la)001:12684: byung ba'i byang sems spyi bor thim pas smin mtshams
NK026(la)001:12685: yan chad gang bum dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12689: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob /
NK026(la)001:12690: lus thams cad la khyab pas dbang bzhi pa thob par mos mdzod /
NK026(la)001:12691: ces gtor ma mgo bor bzhag ste /
NK026(la)001:12694: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK026(la)001:12695: zhes sogs nas tshang bar brjod pa'am /
NK026(la)001:12697: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK026(la)001:12698: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po //
NK026(la)001:12699: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK026(la)001:12700: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh zhes brjod
NK026(la)001:12701: cing dbang bskur ba ni yi dam lha'i dbang ngo
NK026(la)001:12702: // gnyis pa sku gsung thugs kyi rjes gnang bya ba'i dang po ni /
NK026(la)001:12703: slob ma dpal chen por gsal ba gnas 'gyur te /
NK026(la)001:12704: dur khrod kyi dbus su mgon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa mngon rtogs ltar bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:12705: slob dpon dpal chen du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros /
NK026(la)001:12706: lho nub srin yul lang+ka pu ri ri bo ma
NK026(la)001:12707: la ya'i rtse mo nas mgon po 'khor bcas kyi
NK026(la)001:12708: sku dpag tu med pa byon nas slob bu'i lus
NK026(la)001:12710: b+hur kur ta'i sngags dang spos rol bya'o //
NK026(la)001:12712: yang bla ma'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros /
NK026(la)001:12713: mgon po'i gsung gi byin rlabs thams cad yig 'bru
NK026(la)001:12714: h+aum dang ru dmar nag gi rnam par spyan drangs
NK026(la)001:12715: te / mgrin par thim par bsam la sngags dang spos rol gong ltar bya'o //
NK026(la)001:12717: yang bla ma'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros /
NK026(la)001:12718: mgon po'i thugs kyi byin rlabs thams cad beng dang
NK026(la)001:12719: gri gug rtse gsum thod khrag sogs kyi rnam par
NK026(la)001:12720: spyan drangs te / snying gar thim par bsam la sngags dang spos rol gong bzhin bya'o //
NK026(la)001:12721: des gnyis pa sku gsung thugs kyi rjes gnang grub /
NK026(la)001:12722: gsum pa bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK026(la)001:12723: gtor ma bla ma'i phyag tu bzhes te gong du
NK026(la)001:12724: lhar bsgrubs zin pa de nyid sngar yod gsal 'debs
NK026(la)001:12725: kyi tshul du lcags mkhar gyi rten dang brten pa
NK026(la)001:12726: mgon po 'khor bcas su tshig gis gsal btab la
NK026(la)001:12727: / skabs 'dir mgon po ljang sngon zhal gsum phyag
NK026(la)001:12728: drug pa ltar bskyed cing nub mgon lugs zur du
NK026(la)001:12729: byed na mgon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa ltar
NK026(la)001:12730: / ro // ma h+aa k+aa la ga na pa
NK026(la)001:12731: ti sa pa ri w+aa ra ma h+aa ka ru
NK026(la)001:12732: ni k+aa dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:12733: a kar+sha ya e h+ye hi sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa
NK026(la)001:12734: la h+aum dzah e a ra li hrim hrim zhes
NK026(la)001:12735: spyan drangs / dzahh+aum bam hohs bstim /
NK026(la)001:12736: pad+ma mu dra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:12739: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na ba ti ma
NK026(la)001:12740: h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye sa pa ri
NK026(la)001:12741: w+aa ra ba lim i dam gri h+na kha kha
NK026(la)001:12742: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi ma h+aa ba lin+ta kh+aa hi
NK026(la)001:12743: / ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:12745: ma h+aa ba su kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:12746: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:12747: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:12751: ma h+aa su kha hoh rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyod //
NK026(la)001:12752: rdo rje can du gcig nges can //
NK026(la)001:12753: gsang ba gsum dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12754: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig sbyin //
NK026(la)001:12755: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig 'di //
NK026(la)001:12756: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas phyung //
NK026(la)001:12758: grub nas 'jig pa'i dus med do //
NK026(la)001:12760: de nas gtor ma mgon por gsal ba'i steng gi
NK026(la)001:12761: cha la bla ma brgyud pa rnams gsal btab ste
NK026(la)001:12762: mgon por bka' bsgo bar bsam la /
NK026(la)001:12763: bla ma brgyud pa'i gshar btab pa ni /
NK026(la)001:12764: dang po nub dgon lugs kyi byin rlabs 'di ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK026(la)001:12765: chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK026(la)001:12766: longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga /
NK026(la)001:12767: sprul sku ye shes kyi mgon po sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po /
NK026(la)001:12769: skal ldan rgyal po dzah slob dpon s+thi ram ti /
NK026(la)001:12771: bal po ba su d+ha ra /
NK026(la)001:12773: sna chung chos kyi seng ge /
NK026(la)001:12774: mthu stobs byi bu log po /
NK026(la)001:12775: bshos bu rdo rje seng ge /
NK026(la)001:12776: skyes mchog zhang ston bkra shis /
NK026(la)001:12777: mkhas pa glan ston jo bzung /
NK026(la)001:12778: glan ston d+ha na dkar skya /
NK026(la)001:12781: zur bla ma sh+aakya seng ge /
NK026(la)001:12782: zur bla ma seng ge dpal /
NK026(la)001:12783: rdo rje gling pa byang chub rin chen /
NK026(la)001:12784: chos rje bsod nams blo rgyal /
NK026(la)001:12785: mkhas grub chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12787: se ston chen po rin chen rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12788: spyan tshab mgon po zla ba /
NK026(la)001:12789: mnyam med nub dgon pa chen po byams pa chos rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po /
NK026(la)001:12790: thugs sras byams pa blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12791: ngam ring mkhan chen byams pa bzang po /
NK026(la)001:12792: thugs sras sprul sku sh+aakya rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12793: mtshungs med bla ma byams pa rin chen chos 'phel gyi bar du byon pa dang /
NK026(la)001:12795: chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK026(la)001:12796: longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga /
NK026(la)001:12797: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje /
NK026(la)001:12798: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dza /
NK026(la)001:12817: bar ston blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12824: zur tshos stong la bde legs rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12825: se ston chen po rin chen rgyal mtshan /
NK026(la)001:12828: byams pa rin chen rdo rje /
NK026(la)001:12829: skyi ston tshe ring dbang po /
NK026(la)001:12830: zur chen ngag dbang phun tshogs /
NK026(la)001:12831: rig 'dzin chen po 'gyur med rdo rje'i bar du byon pa dang /
NK026(la)001:12832: khyab bdag sman lung pa chen po blo mchog rig
NK026(la)001:12833: pa'i rdo rje sogs rtsa brgyud kyi dpal ldan bla
NK026(la)001:12834: ma dam pa de rnams kyi bka' dang dam tshig
NK026(la)001:12835: gi rim pa las ma 'da' bar bdag gi slob
NK026(la)001:12838: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi go 'phong thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK026(la)001:12839: zhes sngags dang spos rol bcas te slob ma rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:12840: bzhi pa sngags kyi bzlas lung ni /
NK026(la)001:12841: slob dpon che mchog tu gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum las sngags phreng byung ba zhal nas thon /
NK026(la)001:12842: slob ma mgon por gsal ba'i zhal du zhugs lte ba nas thon /
NK026(la)001:12843: slob dpon yi dam du gsal ba'i lte bar zhugs
NK026(la)001:12844: nas 'khor ba las 'od zer gri gug la sogs
NK026(la)001:12845: pa phyir 'phros nas dgra bgegs bsgral bar bsam la
NK026(la)001:12846: / phreng ba la 'dzin du bcug nas sngags 'di rnams kyi rjes zlos lan gsum byar gzhug go //
NK026(la)001:12847: b+hur kur ma h+aa pad+ma rde 'bur tsi 'bur byi
NK026(la)001:12848: gi bye ma na s+ye e sho ma kro d+ha
NK026(la)001:12849: h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:12850: b+hu tu kun a kra na 'bu tsi kyi bye
NK026(la)001:12851: ma na se kha sho ma kro d+ha h+aum h+aum
NK026(la)001:12853: b+hur tu kur tu i tsi khyi byi u tsusma kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:12856: mdo dbang gi bsdus don zur lugs su /
NK026(la)001:12857: chos skyong gtor dbang zhes pa /
NK026(la)001:12859: sarba sid+d+ha pha la h+aum +aah zhes so //
NK026(la)001:12861: sngags mthar sarba sid+d+hi pha la h+aum +aa yang sbyor /
NK026(la)001:12862: lnga pa me tog sbyin pa ni /
NK026(la)001:12863: slob mas bla ma la me tog 'thor zhing 'di'i rjes zlos bya /
NK026(la)001:12864: mgon po bdag gis bzung lags kyis //
NK026(la)001:12865: bdag la 'go bar mdzad du gsol //
NK026(la)001:12867: slob dpon gyis me tog slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK026(la)001:12868: mgon po 'di la stsal lags kyis //
NK026(la)001:12871: des dngos gzhi'i cho ga grub bo //
NK026(la)001:12872: de dag gi rim pa ni /
NK026(la)001:12873: se ston rgya mkhar ba dang nub dgon pa'i lugs
NK026(la)001:12874: bzhin du dbang bzhi'i byin rlabs bka' gtad gtor dbang
NK026(la)001:12877: 'brub khung du zan ling bshams pa la rak+ta bran te dgug gzhug spyi ltar byas la /
NK026(la)001:12878: slob ma'i lag tu gri gug gtad de /
NK026(la)001:12879: sangs rgyas kun gyi ral gri che //
NK026(la)001:12881: dgra bgegs gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12882: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK026(la)001:12883: badz+ra khang+ga a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:12884: zhes gtad la ling+gara bsnun no //
NK026(la)001:12885: ti ras mtshan pa'i beng chen gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12886: ti ra'i beng chen gsal shing 'di //
NK026(la)001:12887: srid gsum dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12888: gdug pa rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12889: de ring khyod la ti ra d+ha ka dz+wa la a zhes ling+gara bsnun no //
NK026(la)001:12892: dug lnga dbyings su bsgral ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12893: sdig can lnga phung bshig pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12894: de ring khyod la badz+ra a b+hi ling+gara bsnun no //
NK026(la)001:12896: drag po gnam lcags phur pa 'di //
NK026(la)001:12897: dbyings la ye shes shar ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12898: zhing bcu gnas su bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12899: de ring khyod la badz+ra k+ai la ya a b+hi ling+gara btab bo //
NK026(la)001:12901: thod rlon gdug pa'i khrag gis bkang //
NK026(la)001:12902: 'khor ba dong nas sprug pa dang //
NK026(la)001:12903: dam nyams snying khrag btung ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12904: de ring khyod la ka p+aa la rak+ta a b+hi ling+gara gtig go //
NK026(la)001:12905: shak+ti ste mdung so'i nang rma bya'i sgro chun gyis bkang ba'i 'phang mdung gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12906: mdung rnon g.yang gzhi'i ru mtshon 'di //
NK026(la)001:12907: bdud kyi g.yul las rgyal ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12908: rbad dbral snying gzer gdab pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12909: de ring khyod la badz+ra shu la a b+hi ling+gara brdeg go //
NK026(la)001:12912: 'khor ba'i gnas nas drang ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12913: bla srog yar ba bsdam pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12914: de ring khyod la n+aa ga p+aa sha a b+hi ling+ga 'ching ngo //
NK026(la)001:12916: chos sku yon tan mchog mnga' ba'i //
NK026(la)001:12917: phyag mtshan drag po tsa ma ra //
NK026(la)001:12918: dam can gnas nas 'bod pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12919: de ring khyod la badz+ra tsa ma ra a b+hi zhes brdung ngo //
NK026(la)001:12921: legs ldan khro rgyal thugs ka nas /
NK026(la)001:12922: tsar sha pa ni mtshon cha mchog /
NK026(la)001:12923: yungs kar rgyal po sha ri ram //
NK026(la)001:12924: de ring khyod la badz+ra pe ta li rak+sha a b+hi ling+ga brab bo //
NK026(la)001:12925: gu gul sor mer sbyar te gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12926: gu gul sbyar ba'i rdzas mchog 'dis //
NK026(la)001:12927: dgra bo lha dang dbye ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12928: bgegs rnams myos dang bskrad pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12929: de ring khyod la ma ku ta la pra ta la b+hi zhes ling+gara bdug go //
NK026(la)001:12930: ri rab gleng gzhi rgya gram gyis mtshon pa mnan pa'i phyir gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12931: ri rab gling bzhi rgya gram 'dis //
NK026(la)001:12932: rtog pa'i zug rngu gzhil ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12933: gdug pa can rnams mnan pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12934: de ring khyod la bi shwa badz+ra sum e bam ma ya a b+hi ling+ga mnan no //
NK026(la)001:12935: me hom sbar ba sbyin sreg gi phyir du gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12937: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i bag chags dang //
NK026(la)001:12938: dgra bgegs thams cad bsreg pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12939: de ring khyod la badz+ra dz+wa la ram a b+hi mda' gzhu gtad la /
NK026(la)001:12940: thabs shes chags sdang mda' gzhu dang //
NK026(la)001:12941: drag po thun dang rdzas 'di yis //
NK026(la)001:12942: dgra bgegs rdul du brlag bya'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:12943: de ring khyod la badz+ra tik+na khat+ga a b+hi zhes
NK026(la)001:12944: ling+gara bsnun te bsgral la bdud rtsis bran te gtor
NK026(la)001:12946: de nas zhabs la spyi bos gtugs //
NK026(la)001:12947: yon mchog dbul zhing gtang rag btang //
NK026(la)001:12948: tshogs kyi mchod pas mnyes par bya //
NK026(la)001:12949: lhag brtan gshegs bsdu lus bsrung bsngo //
NK026(la)001:12950: dza gad rdzas kyi bkra shis gsol //
NK026(la)001:12951: zhes gsungs pa ltar gtang rag gi man+dala dbul zhing /
NK026(la)001:12952: dam tshig bsdus te bran du khas blangs pa sogs spyi ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:12955: mchod gtor bsgul te sman raka bran la bstab pa nub dgon lugs 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:12957: dpal ldan mgon po nag po ni //
NK026(la)001:12958: mthing nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK026(la)001:12959: khyod kyi gsang ba'i mnga' gsol ba //
NK026(la)001:12960: ro langs rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK026(la)001:12961: gsang ba'i mtshan du grags pa can //
NK026(la)001:12962: bskal pa bzang po'i yab yum du //
NK026(la)001:12963: rnal 'byor yongs kyi mgon po ste //
NK026(la)001:12964: dge bsnyen legs ldan nag po lags //
NK026(la)001:12965: gang dag chos pa rnams kyi shing //
NK026(la)001:12966: rnal 'byor srung mar khas blangs te //
NK026(la)001:12968: sa brgyad non pa'i sems dpa' mchog /
NK026(la)001:12969: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:12970: bskal pa phyi mar lung yang bstan //
NK026(la)001:12972: thal bas khebs pa'i zhing zhes par //
NK026(la)001:12973: rdzogs sangs rgyas su lung yang bstan //
NK026(la)001:12974: khyod kyi mthu dang rtsal gyi su //
NK026(la)001:12975: bdud dang srin po la sogs 'dul //
NK026(la)001:12976: dgra bgegs ma lus thal bar rlog /
NK026(la)001:12977: bstan srung khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:12979: dpal ldan mgon po nag po khyod //
NK026(la)001:12980: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK026(la)001:12981: phrin las thams cad grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:12982: khyod kyi bka' yi 'khor gnas pa'i //
NK026(la)001:12983: chos skyong srung ma thams cad kyang //
NK026(la)001:12984: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK026(la)001:12985: bdag dang rnal 'byor sgrub kun gyi //
NK026(la)001:12986: dkon mchog phyogs su gtogs pa yi //
NK026(la)001:12987: gnod byed thams cad bzlog pa dang //
NK026(la)001:12988: dus ma yin par 'chi ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12989: bkra mi shis pa sna tshogs rnams //
NK026(la)001:12990: de dag khyod kyi bzlog tu gsol //
NK026(la)001:12991: bdag gi don rnams grub pa dang //
NK026(la)001:12992: dgra bgegs gtan du gzhom du gsol //
NK026(la)001:12993: yid kyang rtag tu bde ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12994: longs spyod phun tshogs ldan par shog /
NK026(la)001:12995: sh+aakya seng ge'i spyan snga ru //
NK026(la)001:12996: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK026(la)001:12997: bde gshegs bstan pa khyod nyid kyis //
NK026(la)001:12998: bsrung zhing rgyas par bya ba dang //
NK026(la)001:12999: nad dang rims dang dug rnams dang //
NK026(la)001:13000: chu dang mkha' 'gro rkun po dang //
NK026(la)001:13001: dus ma yin par 'chi ba dang //
NK026(la)001:13002: bkra mi shis pa thams cad rnams //
NK026(la)001:13003: de dag khyed kyis bzlog tu gsol //
NK026(la)001:13004: rnal 'byor pa yi las rnams mdzod //
NK026(la)001:13006: b+hur kur ti sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK026(la)001:13008: sngags mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i sngags btags te dbul /
NK026(la)001:13009: bstod pa gong du song bas 'thus /
NK026(la)001:13011: rdul tshon dang sgrub gtor bum pa'i ye shes pa gshegs /
NK026(la)001:13012: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu /
NK026(la)001:13014: de yang 'dir gong du smos pa ltar /
NK026(la)001:13015: gtsang shod pa'i dbang byang dang /
NK026(la)001:13016: nub dgon lugs kyi rjes gnang bka' gtad gnyis ka bsdoms te /
NK026(la)001:13017: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang gi mtha' rten du bsgrigs pa yin pas /
NK026(la)001:13018: lugs gnyis ka'i rgyun ma chad par bsdebs yod pas
NK026(la)001:13019: gnyis ka thob pa'i go chod nges su yod la
NK026(la)001:13020: / mdo dbang dang ma 'brel tshe dbang dang rjes
NK026(la)001:13021: gnang gang 'thad so so'i lugs bzhin bskur dgos pas
NK026(la)001:13022: / / dbang chog so sor yod pa ltar bya /
NK026(la)001:13023: 'di lta bu'i dbang dang rjes gnang thob phyin cad
NK026(la)001:13024: nyer dgu dang bcu bzhi sogs kyi dus gtor dang
NK026(la)001:13025: rgyun gtor ma chag par bya dgos shing /
NK026(la)001:13026: khyad par khyab bdag sman lung pa chen po'i gsung rgyun bzhin /
NK026(la)001:13027: gtor bsngo chung ngu 'di spyir mdo dbang thob pa dang /
NK026(la)001:13028: khyad par chos skyong 'di'i dbang bskur rjes gnang thob
NK026(la)001:13029: pa rnams kyis chag med du bya ba'i rgyun yod
NK026(la)001:13030: pas 'di ltar / gtor ma gang 'byor bdud rtsis bran la /
NK026(la)001:13032: +aahh+aum gis bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs te /
NK026(la)001:13033: chos skyong 'khor bcas byon te rol par bsam la /
NK026(la)001:13035: lang+ka'i yul gyi grong brdal gyi //
NK026(la)001:13036: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK026(la)001:13037: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK026(la)001:13038: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo la //
NK026(la)001:13039: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK026(la)001:13040: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas ni //
NK026(la)001:13041: gsang sngags 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:13042: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13043: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:13044: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK026(la)001:13045: nye gnas kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma //
NK026(la)001:13046: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK026(la)001:13047: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs pa //
NK026(la)001:13049: pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:13050: 'dir gshegs mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK026(la)001:13051: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK026(la)001:13052: bdag gis bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:13053: hoh tshogs kyi bdag po ma h+aa k+aa la legs
NK026(la)001:13054: ldan nag po 'dus pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pho
NK026(la)001:13055: mo 'khor dang bcas pa'i zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa
NK026(la)001:13058: ma h+aa ba lin+ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:13059: ma h+aa sarba pu dza kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:13061: dus gtor gyi tshe gong du bshad pa'i mchod phrin rnams bya /
NK026(la)001:13062: khyad par mdo dbang gi tshe nub re bzhin mchod phrin rgyas par re bya /
NK026(la)001:13063: bstab pa dang bcas thun gtor re yang 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:13064: de dag gis bka' srung mgon po'i dbang dang rjes
NK026(la)001:13065: gnang gi rim pa rnams legs par bstan zin to
NK026(la)001:13066: // dam can gyi bskang gso ni /
NK026(la)001:13067: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud kyi srung ma
NK026(la)001:13068: chen po rdo rje legs pa mchod par 'dod pas
NK026(la)001:13069: / mchod gtor gyi rim pa gang 'byor bzang du bsham la /
NK026(la)001:13070: ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus /
NK026(la)001:13071: +aahh+aum gis bdud rtsir byin gyis brlab la bsngo zhing /
NK026(la)001:13072: mdun du dam can 'khor bcas skad cig gis byon
NK026(la)001:13073: te gtor ma gsol bar bsam la 'di skad do
NK026(la)001:13075: sum cu rtsa gsum dga' ldan lha yul gyi //
NK026(la)001:13076: rnam pa rgyal ba'i khang bzang chen po nas //
NK026(la)001:13077: gdod nas ma skyes rang byung dag pa'i lha //
NK026(la)001:13078: mnyam nyid rig pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:13079: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa la //
NK026(la)001:13080: bstan pa bsrung zhing legs nyes stangs 'dzin pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13081: dge bsnyen chen po rdo rje legs pa ste //
NK026(la)001:13082: 'jig rten skyong ba khyod la khyod ni yab yum dmu bdud tshogs pa'i sras //
NK026(la)001:13083: bden tshig btsugs pas sangs rgyas chos dang mjal //
NK026(la)001:13084: lha min kun la dbang sgyur thugs dam can //
NK026(la)001:13085: dmu bdud dkar po khyod la chos med mna' zan dam nyams kun gyi gshed //
NK026(la)001:13086: skye bo'i dgra lha dgra bo'i gshed ma ste //
NK026(la)001:13087: gzhan gyis ma bcol nyid kyis zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13088: legs nyes stangs 'dzin khyod la don dam nges pa'i bden pa ma mthong yang //
NK026(la)001:13089: skyes mchog khyad par can gyi gang zag gis //
NK026(la)001:13090: dbang bskur ming btags bstan pa'i gnyer gtad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13091: chos skyong srung ma khyod la rang gi las dang rdzu 'phrul bsod nams kyis //
NK026(la)001:13092: lho yi 'dzam gling khyab par rgyu na yang //
NK026(la)001:13093: khyad par bzhugs sa bod yul dbus kyi dpal //
NK026(la)001:13094: yul lha gnyan po khyod la sngon tshe thog mar rang gi bag chags sad //
NK026(la)001:13095: smon lam dam bca' nyid kyi ming smos pas //
NK026(la)001:13096: bla bod mdo gtsang bgrod pa'i sna 'dren mdzad //
NK026(la)001:13097: tshong dpon chen po khyod la skye bo 'thab rtsod g.yul chen 'gyed pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:13098: gang gis khyod la gsol mchod byas pa na //
NK026(la)001:13099: dmag gi ru bzlog pha rol dpung 'joms pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13100: dmag dpon chen po khyod la 'jig rten 'di na mthu chen 'ga' mchis kyang //
NK026(la)001:13101: bcol ba'i las rnams myur du mi bsgrub ste //
NK026(la)001:13102: khyod kyi gang gis mchod cing bsten pa na //
NK026(la)001:13103: myur du sgrub byed khyod la 'khor ba'i gnas na lha srin gzhan bsten na //
NK026(la)001:13104: dgra nyid bsad cing bdag la gnod pa 'byung //
NK026(la)001:13105: khyod ni gang dang 'brel ba rtag tu skyong //
NK026(la)001:13106: yun du grogs mdzad khyod la 'jig rten 'di na ma tshogs gzhan bsten na //
NK026(la)001:13107: zug rngu rags shing rtog pa rab tu che //
NK026(la)001:13108: khyod ni mi nag skye bos bsgrubs na yang //
NK026(la)001:13109: mthu dbang ster byed khyod la khyod ni gsang sngags nang gi dam tshig can //
NK026(la)001:13110: bdag ni dam srung dam tshig gnyan por bsrung //
NK026(la)001:13111: mnyam por don gyi sid+d+hi re ba na //
NK026(la)001:13112: don dam mtshungs pa'i lha la las kyi dbang gis ra yi sha la dgyes //
NK026(la)001:13113: ra sha ra tshil rtag tu zas su za //
NK026(la)001:13114: ra yi pags pa nyid kyang na bzar gsol //
NK026(la)001:13115: skyes bu rdzu 'phrul can la spyir na khyod kyi yon tan sprul pa ni //
NK026(la)001:13116: gcig tu ma nges gnas skabs mthar thug kyang //
NK026(la)001:13117: bka' dang dam tshig bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13118: gtsug lag khang skyong khyod la dad pa'i sems kyi gdung ba'i shugs phyungs te //
NK026(la)001:13119: gus pa'i dang bas lus ngag sems btud nas //
NK026(la)001:13120: yon tan ri rab rdul las cha tsam zhig /
NK026(la)001:13121: dang ba'i dad pas gus pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:13122: ces rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas bstod pa'o //
NK026(la)001:13123: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po'i bka' srung du mngags te /
NK026(la)001:13124: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas te se nas rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan la bskur ba'o //
NK026(la)001:13125: de nas mtha' rten tshe dbang ni /
NK026(la)001:13126: spyir sgyu 'phrul tshe dbang rgyas par snang bas /
NK026(la)001:13127: 'dir gzhung don ltar mdo tsam yi ger bkod pa
NK026(la)001:13128: ni dkyil 'khor chen po'i mchod gtor tshogs skong rnams
NK026(la)001:13130: rgyud lung gi phrin las dang 'dzab sogs zhi khro'i cho ga tshogs kyi bar grub rjes /
NK026(la)001:13132: de nas tshe yi dkyil 'khor gyi bum pa b+h+r+aum
NK026(la)001:13133: gyi 'phro 'du las gzhal yang khang gdan dang bcas
NK026(la)001:13134: pa'i dbus su / +aam b+y+aam las tshe dpag med yab yum tshe rten can /
NK026(la)001:13135: shar du rnam snang bgrang phreng /
NK026(la)001:13137: nub tu mi bskyod pa rin chen /
NK026(la)001:13138: byang du don grub zla tshes kyis kha brgyan pa /
NK026(la)001:13139: g.yas pa rang rtags 'dzin cing thams cad dkar po'o //
NK026(la)001:13140: sems dpa' man chad g.yon rin po che'i snod 'dzin pa'o //
NK026(la)001:13142: mnga' ris kyi pan+di ta chen po pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje'i gsung bzhin bkod pa ni 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:13143: tshe bum la las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing /
NK026(la)001:13146: stong pa'i ngang las tshe'i bum pa b+h+r+aum las 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK026(la)001:13147: phyi bum pa la nang gzhal yas khang gru bzhi
NK026(la)001:13148: sgo bzhi pa'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa
NK026(la)001:13149: de'i dbus su rma bya brgyad bsnol gyis bteg pa'i
NK026(la)001:13150: rin po che'i khri dang pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan
NK026(la)001:13152: rtsibs bzhir mo tram h+aum +aahrnamasa su gyur /
NK026(la)001:13155: 'phro 'du yongs su gyur pa las dbus su bcom
NK026(la)001:13156: ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa yab
NK026(la)001:13157: yum sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK026(la)001:13158: / mnyam gzhag gi steng na rin po che'i bum pa 'chi med bdud rtsis gang ba 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:13159: zhabs gnyis rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa'i pang
NK026(la)001:13160: na yum na bza' dkar mo g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon
NK026(la)001:13161: rin po che'i bum pa yab kyi snyan g.yas pa'i
NK026(la)001:13162: thad du 'dzin pa zhabs gnyis yab kyi sked la
NK026(la)001:13163: 'khril ba / yab yum gnyis ka dar dang rin po che'i rgyan du mas spras pa'i skur gyur /
NK026(la)001:13164: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor
NK026(la)001:13165: lo dang g.yon bgrang phreng gis kha brgyan pa'i tshe
NK026(la)001:13166: bum 'dzin pa / lhor rin 'byung dkar po g.yas
NK026(la)001:13167: rin po che dang g.yon nor rkyal gyis kha brgyan
NK026(la)001:13169: nub tu mi bskyod pa dkar po g.yas rdo rje
NK026(la)001:13170: dang g.yon rin po ches kha brgyan pa'i tshe bum
NK026(la)001:13171: 'dzin pa / byang du don grub dkar po g.yas
NK026(la)001:13172: rgya gram dang g.yon zla tshes kyis kha brgyan pa'i
NK026(la)001:13174: de dag thams cad kyang rang 'od kyi yum dang bcas par bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:13176: de nas sa ma ya dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK026(la)001:13177: ces gsungs pas rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK026(la)001:13178: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes so //
NK026(la)001:13183: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:13186: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru
NK026(la)001:13187: ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK026(la)001:13188: ma ya s+t+wam / zhes nam mkhar spyan drangs te rig pa'i me tog 'dor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:13189: ye shes rgyal po'i sku gsung thugs //
NK026(la)001:13190: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK026(la)001:13191: de ring du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK026(la)001:13192: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK026(la)001:13195: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes rig pa'i me tog dor la /
NK026(la)001:13197: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:13201: kri t+ya nush+tha na sogs phyag rgyar bcas te dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:13202: sarba ta th+aa ka ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:13203: de bzhin du w+aa ka badz+ra /
NK026(la)001:13204: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:13205: zhes sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab bo //
NK026(la)001:13207: bde bar gshegs so sogs kyis mchod /
NK026(la)001:13208: bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+tasa mchod /
NK026(la)001:13209: sbyor sgrol dang ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK026(la)001:13210: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod la /
NK026(la)001:13212: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK026(la)001:13215: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:13217: +aahh+aum su ra ha u pa b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:13218: ka ma la m+aa la badz+ra a mri ta ha
NK026(la)001:13219: ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga wan dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK026(la)001:13220: a la la hoh ma h+aa ba ling+ta kha kha
NK026(la)001:13223: dzahh+aum bam hoh ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK026(la)001:13224: ma h+aa sa ma ya ma h+aa rak+ta /
NK026(la)001:13226: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK026(la)001:13227: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK026(la)001:13229: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:13231: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:13232: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK026(la)001:13233: a nu r+aa ga ya ham /
NK026(la)001:13234: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13235: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phatah sam ha ra na h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13236: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:13238: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK026(la)001:13239: zhes sogs lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis mchod la //
NK026(la)001:13240: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK026(la)001:13242: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar gyis bstod de /
NK026(la)001:13244: hohbacoma ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa
NK026(la)001:13245: 'khor dang bcas pa la dngos grub tu gsol ba
NK026(la)001:13246: ni / khyed kyi sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan
NK026(la)001:13247: skye shi med pa tshe'i dngos grub sngon gyi thugs
NK026(la)001:13248: dam las ma 'da' bar da lta nyid du stsal
NK026(la)001:13249: ni / du gsol / de nas snying gar tshe rten bskyed la a yus mnan /
NK026(la)001:13251: bum nang gi lha'i thugs kar nyi zla'i ga'u'i nang
NK026(la)001:13252: du zla gam dmar po sgo gcig pa'i dbus su
NK026(la)001:13253: rang gzhan gyi tshe'i ngo bo yi ge a dkar
NK026(la)001:13254: la 'tsher ba / dmar la dwangs pa /
NK026(la)001:13256: a yu h+aum dzah a yu dz+ny+aa na b+hin+d+hu b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:13257: badz+ra a yu she h+aum a /
NK026(la)001:13258: zhes brjod pas a 'od du zhu ba las tshe'i
NK026(la)001:13259: rang bzhin bdud rtsi mu tig dkar po dri ma
NK026(la)001:13260: med pa dkar la dmar cha yod pa ga'u kha
NK026(la)001:13261: sbyor lhung lhung gang bar bsam /
NK026(la)001:13262: h+aum badz+ra zhes pas ga'u'i steng 'og nas rdo rje
NK026(la)001:13263: rgya gram dang ye shes kyi me 'bar bar gyur
NK026(la)001:13265: rdo rje rgya gram gyi steng 'og gi rwa rnams
NK026(la)001:13266: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyis bsdams par bsam mo
NK026(la)001:13268: phyag rgya'i sor mo phye bas badz+ra mu ka hos dkyil 'khor gyi lha mang po 'phros /
NK026(la)001:13271: zhes gsungs pa'i sngags gong ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:13276: bstim pa ni bshad ma thag pa ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:13278: b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzahdzahh+aum bam hoh brgya
NK026(la)001:13279: stong bzlas nas tshe dpag med yab yum mang po
NK026(la)001:13280: spros / khams gsum gyi tshe bsdus pas gtso bo'i
NK026(la)001:13281: zhal nas rang yang tshe dpag med yab yum du
NK026(la)001:13282: gsal ba'i thugs kar lud tshe rten la thim par
NK026(la)001:13283: spros / bsam / a yu h+aum dzahs bsrung bstim bya ba gong ltar ro //
NK026(la)001:13284: rigs bzhi la spro bsdu bya ba'i dmigs pa gong gi rigs 'gres sbyar ba dang /
NK026(la)001:13286: b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK026(la)001:13287: s+w+aa b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam
NK026(la)001:13288: hoh h+aum b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum
NK026(la)001:13289: bam hoh h+aa b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah
NK026(la)001:13291: de nas rang gi snying gar tshe rten bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:13292: zhes gsungs pa ni gong ltar nyi zla'i ga'u'i nang
NK026(la)001:13293: du zla gam sgo gcig gi nang du a bskyed
NK026(la)001:13295: a yu h+aum dzah zhes pa yang gong ltar /
NK026(la)001:13296: a yu h+aum dzah a yu r+dz+ny+aa na bin+d+hu b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:13297: badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah zhes bzlas pas bum pa'i lha 'od du zhu /
NK026(la)001:13298: rang gi snying ga'i tshe rten la thim pas lus 'od phung las +aahh+aum du gyur /
NK026(la)001:13300: h+aum yang mi dmigs par bsam ste /
NK026(la)001:13302: cis kyang mi 'gyur mi shigs pa'i //
NK026(la)001:13303: stong pa'i go cha bla na med //
NK026(la)001:13304: mtshan ma'i spyod yul kun bcom nas //
NK026(la)001:13305: thams cad kun las rgyal bar gnas //
NK026(la)001:13306: ma byung mi gnas 'dus ma byas //
NK026(la)001:13307: chos kyi dbyings su tshe sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:13308: sangs rgyas kyis kyang gzigs mi 'gyur //
NK026(la)001:13309: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a ti tish+tha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13311: 'di ni tshe stong pa nyid du sba ba ste zab gnad do //
NK026(la)001:13313: de nas rang rdo rje sems dpar bskyed la go bgo /
NK026(la)001:13315: zhes gsungs pa ni tshe stong nyid du sbas pa
NK026(la)001:13316: de rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam par langs te go
NK026(la)001:13317: bgo ba dang lus bsrung ba dang dbang gi skabs
NK026(la)001:13318: ltar ro // mgo bo'i gnas lngar dbang bskur ba'i phyag rgya byas te /
NK026(la)001:13319: pad+ma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aam /
NK026(la)001:13320: bud+d+ha k+aa la sha a b+hi shin+tsa /
NK026(la)001:13321: rat+na k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK026(la)001:13322: badz+ra k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13323: karma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK026(la)001:13325: tshe dbang du gyur cig sogs bya /
NK026(la)001:13327: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13328: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13329: myur du tshe dpag tu med pa'i go 'phang thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13330: zhes sgyu 'phrul tshe chog las byung ngo //
NK026(la)001:13333: de nas bum par khro bo'i lha dbus su pad+ma he ru ka sogs dmar po bskyed /
NK026(la)001:13336: hoh bcom ldan 'das pad+ma he ru ka sogs dngos grub gong ltar blang /
NK026(la)001:13338: slar yang bum nang du khro bo'i gzhal yas khang
NK026(la)001:13339: gsal ba'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar
NK026(la)001:13340: pad nyi bdud bzhi'i gdan gyi steng du h+r+aihm yongs
NK026(la)001:13342: khro bo rta mgrin pad+ma he ru ka yab yum
NK026(la)001:13343: sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis khro tshul
NK026(la)001:13344: dang ldan pa / g.yas pa sna tshogs rdo rje
NK026(la)001:13345: dang g.yon pa ka p+aa la 'chi med kyi bdud
NK026(la)001:13346: rtsis gang ba thugs kar steng 'og tu 'dzin pas
NK026(la)001:13348: zhabs g.yas brkyang ba'i gar stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK026(la)001:13349: yum rdo rje phag mo gri gug thod pa 'dzin
NK026(la)001:13350: pa dang gnyis su med par 'khril pa'i 'khor du
NK026(la)001:13354: lcags sgrog ma ste gsang yum bzhi sogs 'khor dpag
NK026(la)001:13355: tu med pas bskor ba thams cad kyang dar dang
NK026(la)001:13356: rin po che rus pa'i rgyan drug gis brgyan cing
NK026(la)001:13357: dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan pa dang bcas par
NK026(la)001:13358: bsam la / badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK026(la)001:13359: e h+ye hi a na ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hohs spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:13360: ram badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum //
NK026(la)001:13361: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:13362: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:13363: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK026(la)001:13364: de nyid du na bdag la stsol //
NK026(la)001:13365: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK026(la)001:13366: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma hoh badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK026(la)001:13367: ces rig pa'i me tog dor la /
NK026(la)001:13369: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par byas /
NK026(la)001:13370: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:13371: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab bo //
NK026(la)001:13372: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK026(la)001:13373: zhes kha bsgyur te chu gnyis /
NK026(la)001:13379: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin rnams kyis gong bzhin mchod la /
NK026(la)001:13381: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK026(la)001:13383: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho'i bar gyis bstod la /
NK026(la)001:13384: hoh bcom ldan 'das pad+ma he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:13385: khyed kyi sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan skye shi
NK026(la)001:13386: med pa tshe'i dngos grub sngon gyi thugs dam las
NK026(la)001:13387: ma 'da' bar da lta nyid du stsal du gsol
NK026(la)001:13389: bi shwa badz+ra sa spro bsdu zhes pa ni /
NK026(la)001:13390: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la
NK026(la)001:13391: man+da la phata phata phata ha la ha la ha
NK026(la)001:13392: la h+aum / zhes khro bo'i sprul pa spros /
NK026(la)001:13396: badz+ra a yu she dza h+aum a /
NK026(la)001:13397: zhes pas lha mo tsan+da li dkar po phyag bzhi ma /
NK026(la)001:13398: g.yas pa gnyis na rdo rje dang lcags kyu /
NK026(la)001:13399: g.yon pa gnyis na rin po che dang zhags pa can 'phros pas tshe bsdus /
NK026(la)001:13400: gtso bo'i thugs kar zhi ba dang 'dra ba'i tshe rten bsgoms pa la thim /
NK026(la)001:13401: gong ltar rgya gram gyis bsdoms pa dang /
NK026(la)001:13403: yang bi shwa badz+ra sogs kyis khro bo spros /
NK026(la)001:13404: b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK026(la)001:13405: h+aum b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam
NK026(la)001:13406: hoh tram b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum
NK026(la)001:13407: bam hoh h+r+aihb+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah dzahh+aum
NK026(la)001:13408: bam hoh h+aa b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzah
NK026(la)001:13409: dzahh+aum bam hohs khams gsum gyi tshe bsdus bstim pas
NK026(la)001:13410: bum pa'i bar zhes gsungs pa snga ma zhi ba
NK026(la)001:13411: ltar rang yang rta mgrin yab yum gsal ba'i snying
NK026(la)001:13412: khar tshe rten bskyed la a yu she h+aum dzah
NK026(la)001:13414: badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzahzhesa lha rnams 'od du zhu /
NK026(la)001:13415: bdud rtsi yi ge +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa lngar gyur /
NK026(la)001:13416: a yur+dz+ny+aa na h+aum dzahsogasa brjod pas /
NK026(la)001:13421: h+aa dpral bar thim pas lus yig 'bru lngar gyur /
NK026(la)001:13422: de dag kyang mi dmigs par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:13425: zhes gsungs pa zhi khro'i tshogs skong rnams bya'o //
NK026(la)001:13427: zhag du byed kyang de ltar byed do //
NK026(la)001:13428: de nas nub tha ma la tshe nas la 'brang rgyas zla gam byas /
NK026(la)001:13429: bum pa'i g.yon du bzhag ces gsungs pa ni sgrub
NK026(la)001:13430: pa'i dbang du byas te thog mar gong ltar sgrub
NK026(la)001:13431: pa'i dus tshe 'brang gi bum pa'i kha bcad la
NK026(la)001:13432: bsgrub / dbang bskur khar tshe 'brang ste zla gam
NK026(la)001:13433: de nyid g.yon du 'jog par gsungs pa yin kyang
NK026(la)001:13434: 'dir tshe sgrub la sgrub mchod zhag sbrel bya long
NK026(la)001:13435: mi yong bas gong ltar bshams pas 'thus shing /
NK026(la)001:13436: de mtshungs zhag gi bar du chod na 'di man
NK026(la)001:13437: chod dbang gi bya ba la 'jig pa'i nyen byed
NK026(la)001:13441: zhes gsungs kyang gong du song ma thag yin pas mi dgos so //
NK026(la)001:13443: bum pa'i g.yas su mar me bzhag /
NK026(la)001:13444: ces gsungs pa la mar me /
NK026(la)001:13445: rma byas bteg pa'i rin po che'i khri pad+ma dang
NK026(la)001:13446: zla ba'i gdan la h+aum m+aum las rdo rje tshe
NK026(la)001:13447: dpag med sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK026(la)001:13448: pa mnyam gzhag gi steng na rin po che'i bum
NK026(la)001:13449: pa rdo rjes mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:13450: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK026(la)001:13451: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma dmar mo rdo rje dang bum pa 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK026(la)001:13452: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis spras pa'i skur gyur par bsgom mo //
NK026(la)001:13454: 'brang rgyas la dbus su tshe dpag med yab yum /
NK026(la)001:13455: h+aum bzhi las shar du rgyal mtshan mchog dkar mo dpal be'u lcags kyu can /
NK026(la)001:13456: lhor rin chen gter ldan ma sngon mo bum pa zhags pa can /
NK026(la)001:13457: nub tu dbang sgyur dpal ldan ma dmar mo pad+ma lcags sgrog can /
NK026(la)001:13458: byang du mi zad mdzod ldan ma ljang gu za ma tog dril bu can bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:13460: zla gam gyi 'brang rgyas mi dmigs te stong pa'i
NK026(la)001:13461: ngang las 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya
NK026(la)001:13462: brgyad bsnol gyis bteg pa'i rin po che'i khri pad
NK026(la)001:13463: zla'i gdan la / +aamhp+y+aam las 'phro 'dus pa las
NK026(la)001:13464: mgon po tshe dpag med sku mdog dmar po zhal
NK026(la)001:13465: gcig phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi steng na rin po
NK026(la)001:13466: che'i bum pa bdud rtsis gang ba 'dzin pa /
NK026(la)001:13467: zhabs gnyis rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa'i pang
NK026(la)001:13468: na yum gos dkar mo pad+ma dang bum pa 'dzin
NK026(la)001:13469: pas 'khril ba / yab yum gnyis ka dar dang
NK026(la)001:13470: rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i rtsibs bzhir dzahh+aum
NK026(la)001:13471: bam hohls shar du rgyal mtshan mchog dkar mo dpal
NK026(la)001:13473: lhor rin chen gter ldan ma sngon mo bum pa zhags pa can /
NK026(la)001:13474: nub tu dbang bsgyur dpal ldan ma dmar mo pad+ma dang lcags sgrog /
NK026(la)001:13475: byang du mi zad mdzod ldan ma ljang gu za ma tog dang dril bu can du bsam /
NK026(la)001:13476: tshe ril rnams rta mgrin dmar po khro tshul g.yas
NK026(la)001:13477: sna tshogs rdo rje dang g.yon thod pa bdud rtsis
NK026(la)001:13478: gang ba 'dzin pa yum dang bcas pa g.yas brkyang
NK026(la)001:13479: gi gar gyis rol bar bsam la /
NK026(la)001:13483: badz+ra sa ma h+aum dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK026(la)001:13484: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wa na ma h+aa k+aa
NK026(la)001:13485: ru ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK026(la)001:13489: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:13490: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs /
NK026(la)001:13495: tsan+da li'i 'dzab kyi spro bsdus tshe bsdu bsrung bya /
NK026(la)001:13499: badz+ra a yu she dza h+aum a /
NK026(la)001:13500: zhes lha mo tsan+da li spro ba nas khams gsum
NK026(la)001:13501: gyi tshe bsdus bstim pa'i bar gong gi khro bo'i
NK026(la)001:13506: rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal
NK026(la)001:13507: ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK026(la)001:13508: dang / sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi dge 'dun gyi
NK026(la)001:13509: khyad par du bcom ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag
NK026(la)001:13510: tu med pa'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK026(la)001:13511: dang / dang / gsang sngags dang gzungs sngags rnams
NK026(la)001:13512: kyi bka' dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma
NK026(la)001:13513: rnams kyi bka' bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis
NK026(la)001:13514: bdag cag rnams kyi tshe ma mo dang byad ma
NK026(la)001:13515: gshin rje la sogs pa'i lha srin sde brgyad dang
NK026(la)001:13516: dang / dang / / bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad
NK026(la)001:13517: cu la sogs pa su gang gi lag na gnas
NK026(la)001:13520: a yu h+aum dzah a yur+dz+ny+aa na ban+d+hu b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:13521: badz+ra a yu she h+aum a /
NK026(la)001:13524: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:13525: dkar mo mgyogs ma zhi byed 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:13526: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:13527: rdo rje tshe mchog gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK026(la)001:13528: mgyogs ma rnams kyis tshe khug la //
NK026(la)001:13529: byin chen rnams kyis byin phob cig /
NK026(la)001:13530: sa ma ya de wi ang+ku sha dza dzahh+aum /
NK026(la)001:13532: lho phyogs dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK026(la)001:13533: sngon mo drag shul 'od zer stong 'phro'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:13534: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK026(la)001:13535: rin chen tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK026(la)001:13536: mgyogs ma rnams kyi byin chen rnams kyi sa ma ya de wi p+aa sha h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13537: nub phyogs pad+ma r+aa ga'i zhing khams nas //
NK026(la)001:13538: dmar mo dbang sgyur 'od zer 'phro ba'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:13539: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i pad+ma tshe mchog 'gugs
NK026(la)001:13540: pa'i mgyogs ma byin chen rnams sa ma ya de
NK026(la)001:13542: byang phyogs rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK026(la)001:13543: ljang gu phrin las 'od zer 'phro ba'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:13544: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs las kyi tshe mchog 'gugs
NK026(la)001:13545: pa'i mgyogs ma rnams kyi byin chen rnams kyi sa
NK026(la)001:13546: ma ya de wi g+han+de ho hoh zhes brjod cing
NK026(la)001:13547: re re zhing sngags brgya rtsa dang bstim srung gong
NK026(la)001:13548: ltar bya'o // de nas pad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha
NK026(la)001:13549: ha ya g+r+ai wa hu lu hu lu h+aum dz+wa
NK026(la)001:13551: ces pas rta mgrin dmar po g.yas ral gri g.yon zhags pa can du ma spros /
NK026(la)001:13552: tshe bkug par bsam zhing sngags gong ma bzlas /
NK026(la)001:13553: de nas bdag nyid pad+ma he ru ka lte ba
NK026(la)001:13554: man chad khrag mtshor nub pa dmar dkar sngo ba'i
NK026(la)001:13555: zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i dang po gnyis na bud+d+ha
NK026(la)001:13557: bar pa gnyis na rat+na he ru ka yab yum /
NK026(la)001:13558: tha ma gnyis na karma he ru ka yab yum mo //
NK026(la)001:13559: de nas thal mo brdeb cing /
NK026(la)001:13560: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:13561: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:13562: ces mang du bzlas pas lha dang lha ma yin gyi tshogs bsgral nas tshe bsdu /
NK026(la)001:13563: de bzhin rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:13564: rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:13566: rat+na he ru kas mi dang byol song /
NK026(la)001:13567: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:13568: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:13570: karma he ru kas yi dwags dang dmyal ba'i tshe
NK026(la)001:13571: srog ste a yu h+aum dzahs 'od nag por bdag
NK026(la)001:13573: mchog phur gcig pad+ma 'dus par bskyed la k+aa ya
NK026(la)001:13574: badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab
NK026(la)001:13575: / bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13576: zhes pa mang du bzlas shing 'od nag po de
NK026(la)001:13577: la gtad de dril bas he ru ka drag po
NK026(la)001:13578: spyod pa'i byang sems phur pa la thim /
NK026(la)001:13579: phur pa byang sems kyi rang bzhin du dkar ldem
NK026(la)001:13580: sdem 'dug pa btab pas 'od nag po de bdud
NK026(la)001:13581: rtsir dkar ltem gyis gyur te /
NK026(la)001:13582: a yu h+aum dzahzhesa brjod pas 'brang rgyas kyi tshe dpag med la bsdu'o //
NK026(la)001:13583: de yan chod bdag don sgrub mchod kyi rim pa'o //
NK026(la)001:13584: de nas slob ma rnams bos te khrus bya /
NK026(la)001:13585: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK026(la)001:13586: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu bya /
NK026(la)001:13587: bla mas thugs bskyed phog rjes /
NK026(la)001:13588: 'dir bcom ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag med kyi
NK026(la)001:13589: dbang la brgyud pa sum ldan rig 'dzin gyi tshogs
NK026(la)001:13590: las brgyud de 'ongs pa'i mgon po tshe dpag med
NK026(la)001:13591: kyi dbang mtha' rten gyi tshul du bskur ba byed
NK026(la)001:13592: pa yin / de la slob dpon gyi bgyi bar
NK026(la)001:13593: 'os pa bum par tshe dpag med zhi khro rim
NK026(la)001:13594: bzhin bskyed pa sogs legs par grub /
NK026(la)001:13595: slob ma'i ngo skal du gyur pa la tshe dbang gi yon du man+dala phul /
NK026(la)001:13596: gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK026(la)001:13597: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgya la //
NK026(la)001:13598: mchog sbyin ji ltar stsal ba ltar //
NK026(la)001:13599: bdag kyang skyob pa'i don gyi phyir //
NK026(la)001:13600: nam mkha'i rdo rje deng bdag stsol //
NK026(la)001:13603: de nas mtshams bshags byin dbab bya //
NK026(la)001:13608: ye nas rnam dag chos skur dag pa la //
NK026(la)001:13609: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK026(la)001:13610: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK026(la)001:13611: de bzlog don du rgyal ba'i bka' nos te //
NK026(la)001:13612: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK026(la)001:13613: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK026(la)001:13614: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK026(la)001:13615: thugs rje che mnga' khyod la bzod par gsol //
