NK026(la)001:13619: stong pa'i ngang las rma bya brgyad bsnol gyis bteg
NK026(la)001:13620: pa'i rin po che'i khri pad+ma dang zla ba'i steng
NK026(la)001:13621: du sems kyi ngo bo +aamhp+y+aam las mgon po tshe
NK026(la)001:13622: dpag med sku mdog dmar po mnyam gzhag gi steng
NK026(la)001:13623: na rin po che'i bum pa 'chi med tshe'i bdud
NK026(la)001:13625: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can /
NK026(la)001:13626: yum gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon tshe bum 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK026(la)001:13627: thugs kar rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' dang bcas pa /
NK026(la)001:13628: gzhan yang snod thams cad bde ba can gyi zhing khams /
NK026(la)001:13629: bcud kyi sems can skye 'gro bdag gzhan gyi phung
NK026(la)001:13630: khams skye mched snang srid thams cad tshe dpag med
NK026(la)001:13631: du gsal ba / bdag gi thugs ka'i tshe dpag
NK026(la)001:13632: med kyi thugs srog las kyang 'od zer 'phros pas
NK026(la)001:13633: rang bzhan dang mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor bla ma phyogs
NK026(la)001:13634: bcu'i zhing khams thams cad nas tshe dpag med kyi
NK026(la)001:13635: lha tshogs sprin 'thibs pa ltar byon te /
NK026(la)001:13636: khyed rang rnams la thim pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK026(la)001:13637: spos dang rol mo bcas te gong gi gzungs kyi mthar /
NK026(la)001:13638: a be sha ya a a /
NK026(la)001:13644: slar yang khyed rang rnams tshe dpag med yab yum
NK026(la)001:13645: du gsal ba'i snying khar nyi zla'i ga'u'i nang du
NK026(la)001:13646: zla gam dmar po sgo gcig pa'i dbus su tshe'i
NK026(la)001:13647: ngo bo yi ge a dkar la 'tsher ba /
NK026(la)001:13649: snum la 'dril ba zhig gsal btab pa ni /
NK026(la)001:13650: snyig gar tshe rten bskyed pa'o //
NK026(la)001:13653: mi gsum gyi tshe rdzas re re bteg la bum pa blangs la /
NK026(la)001:13654: zhes gsungs pa thog mar bla mas bum dbang bskur ba ni /
NK026(la)001:13656: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK026(la)001:13657: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel //
NK026(la)001:13658: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' bas //
NK026(la)001:13659: mnyam nyid sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:13660: zhes brjod pas bum pa'i lha rnams kyi sku las mang po byung nas bdag gi spyi bor thim /
NK026(la)001:13661: klad pa sku rdo rjer gyur par bsam zhing k+aa ya sid+d+hi dang /
NK026(la)001:13663: bum pa'i mar spyi bor byug /
NK026(la)001:13664: ces gsungs pa bum chu spyi bor blug cing ngag tu blud do //
NK026(la)001:13667: 'brang rgyas kyi lha la dmigs te /
NK026(la)001:13669: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i gsung //
NK026(la)001:13670: gsung rab dam pa yi ge med //
NK026(la)001:13671: brjod du med cing spros bral ba //
NK026(la)001:13672: rdo rje gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:13673: zhes brjod pas tshe 'brang gi lha rnams kyi mgrin pa nas +aamhmanga po byung nas lce la thim //
NK026(la)001:13674: lce gsung rdo rje gyur par bsam la /
NK026(la)001:13677: gsung gi sid+d+hi thob par brda sprad /
NK026(la)001:13678: mar me'i lha la dmigs te mar me snying gar gtug cing /
NK026(la)001:13679: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i thugs //
NK026(la)001:13680: chags med ye shes gnyis mkhyen pa //
NK026(la)001:13681: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi //
NK026(la)001:13682: rdo rje thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK026(la)001:13683: zhes brjod pas mar me'i lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs las h+aum mang po byung nas snying la thim /
NK026(la)001:13684: yid thugs rdo rjer gyur par bsam la /
NK026(la)001:13688: thugs kyi sid+d+hi thob par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:13690: nub phyogs byams ldan dbang gi zhing khams nas //
NK026(la)001:13691: bcom ldan mgon po ye shes tshe dpag med //
NK026(la)001:13692: thugs kyi dpal be zla gsang ga'u nas //
NK026(la)001:13693: rnal 'byor byang sems a yu dmar po de //
NK026(la)001:13694: rtse gcig bdag gis bsgrubs pa'i tshe lags kyis //
NK026(la)001:13695: byin gyis brlab cing dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK026(la)001:13696: a yu h+aum dzah a yur+dz+ny+aa na b+hin+d+hu b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:13697: badz+ra a yu she h+aum dzahsogasa kyi sngags dang bcas bum pa /
NK026(la)001:13699: mar me ste tshe rdzas gsum po snying gar bteg cing bstim pa dang /
NK026(la)001:13700: smon lam zhi ba ltar bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:13702: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13703: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13704: tshe dpag tu med pa'i go 'phang thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13707: de nas dbang rdzas rnams rim par thogs la /
NK026(la)001:13708: zhes gsungs pa slar yang bum pa spyi bor /
NK026(la)001:13710: mar me snying gar gtug cing //
NK026(la)001:13711: a yu dmar po rdo rje 'chang gi tshe //
NK026(la)001:13712: gzhan gyis mi 'phrog khams gsum kun las rgyal //
NK026(la)001:13713: rang gi byang sems gdod nas skye shi med //
NK026(la)001:13714: mi 'gyur tshe yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK026(la)001:13715: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu h+ya a yu dz+ny+aa na bin+d+hu b+h+r+aum /
NK026(la)001:13716: badz+ra a yu she dz+ny+aa na swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:13717: bum pa'i lha rnams 'od du zhu nas slob ma la thim par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:13718: de nas slob dpon gyi me tog 'thor zhing /
NK026(la)001:13722: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13723: skye med kyi ye shes su gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13724: 'chi med kyi bdud rtsir gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13725: mi 'gyur ba'i g.yung drung du gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13726: mi shigs pa'i rdo rjer gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13727: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan du gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13728: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa'i skal pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:13729: ces bum chu hub re blud pas tshe'i rang bzhin
NK026(la)001:13730: mi shigs pa'i g.yung drung snying gi dkyil du bstim
NK026(la)001:13731: mo // de nas tshe sba ba ni /
NK026(la)001:13732: gnas rnams su rdo rje rgya gram gyis rgyas btab tshul dang bcas te /
NK026(la)001:13733: h+r+aih byang chub sems kyi a yu dmar po 'di //
NK026(la)001:13734: chos nyid skye med dbyings su sbas nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:13735: de la phyag rgya bdun gyis btab par bya //
NK026(la)001:13736: dang po sku gsung thugs kyi rgya //
NK026(la)001:13737: gnyis pa rdo rje rgya gram rgya //
NK026(la)001:13738: gsum pa zla gam dbang gi rgya //
NK026(la)001:13739: bzhi pa rta mchog dbang gi rgya //
NK026(la)001:13740: lnga pa gar mkhan mchog gi rgya //
NK026(la)001:13741: drug pa gser gyi zor ba'i rgya //
NK026(la)001:13742: bdun pa chos kyi dbyings kyi rgya //
NK026(la)001:13743: rgya bdun rim pas btab pa la //
NK026(la)001:13746: tshe chog 'di'i dbu zhabs kyi dka' gnas thams cad
NK026(la)001:13747: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan yab sras kyi bzhed
NK026(la)001:13748: gzhung ltar bkrol ba yin kyang /
NK026(la)001:13749: skabs 'dir khams lugs su legs bshad 'di lta bu snang ste /
NK026(la)001:13750: rang nyid tshe dpag med yab yum du gsal ba'i
NK026(la)001:13751: yab kyi thugs kar rdo rje rgya gram gyi gur
NK026(la)001:13752: khang / de'i nang du nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor gyi gur khang /
NK026(la)001:13753: de'i nang du 'khor lo dkar po gyis 'khrigs pa'i gur /
NK026(la)001:13754: de'i nang du pad+ma dmar po +aahs 'khrigs pa'i gur /
NK026(la)001:13755: de'i nang du rdo rje sngon po h+aum gis 'khrigs
NK026(la)001:13756: pa'i gur rnams kyis dang po sku gsung thugs kyi
NK026(la)001:13757: rgya dang / gnyis pa rdo rje rgya gram gyi rgya /
NK026(la)001:13758: gsum pa zla gam dbang gi rgya rnams tshang /
NK026(la)001:13759: de'i nang du 'od zer dkar po /
NK026(la)001:13762: dmar po +aamh ljang gu h+aa rnams kyis 'khrigs pa'i gur /
NK026(la)001:13763: de'i nang du gser 'khor rtsibs brgyad pa /
NK026(la)001:13764: rtsibs mchan brgyad la gser gyi zor ba so phyir
NK026(la)001:13765: bstan brgyad yong ba yu ba la tram gis mtshan
NK026(la)001:13767: de'i nang du pad nyi'i gdan la h+r+aihdamara zung las
NK026(la)001:13768: rta mgrin yab yum rta mgo ljang khu rta skad
NK026(la)001:13769: 'tsher ba me dpung gi dbus na bzhugs pa /
NK026(la)001:13770: de'i thugs kar bkrag mdangs kyi ngo bo 'od phung dkar po mtshon gang tsam /
NK026(la)001:13771: de'i nang du rnam shes kyi ngo bo h+aum dmar ser /
NK026(la)001:13772: de'i zhabs kyu'i nang du tshe'i ngo bo a dkar po /
NK026(la)001:13773: a de'i dpung pa g.yas kyi nang du srog gi sa bon n+ri dkar ljang /
NK026(la)001:13774: dpung pa g.yon du rang rang gi ming yig dang po /
NK026(la)001:13775: de gnyis kyi bar du bla'i ngo bo yu dmar ser //
NK026(la)001:13776: de rnams kyi steng du dkar po /
NK026(la)001:13781: de'i phyir sngags phreng gis bskor ba rnams rta mchog gi rgya /
NK026(la)001:13784: chos kyi dbyings kyi rgya rnams tshang bar bshad pas spros pa'i yan lag tu bsgoms kyang legs so //
NK026(la)001:13785: de nas tshe 'brang dang tshe ril gyi ye shes pa gshegs /
NK026(la)001:13786: dam tshig pa bdud rtsir zhu bar bsam ste /
NK026(la)001:13788: thams cad la rdzas dbang bkye la dngos grub tu rol bar bya'o //
NK026(la)001:13789: de nas gsol byang ste tshe chang blangs la /
NK026(la)001:13790: ltar dkar la 'tsher ba yab kyi dbang //
NK026(la)001:13791: +aahltara dmar la dwangs pa yum gyi dbang //
NK026(la)001:13792: h+aum ltar smug la 'dril ba byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:13793: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:13795: gnas gsum so sor gtug cing /
NK026(la)001:13797: wa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13798: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsita badz+ra swa b+h+aa l+aa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK026(la)001:13799: tshe ril tshe chang sogs 'brim zhing rol te /
NK026(la)001:13800: smon lam btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos bya ste /
NK026(la)001:13802: bdag cag dpon slob lcam dral 'dir tshogs shing 'dus
NK026(la)001:13803: pa rnams la sku mi 'gyur ba tshe'i dngos grub
NK026(la)001:13806: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub da lta nyid du stsal du gsol lo //
NK026(la)001:13807: a la la hoh zhes brjod cing las mkhan gyis bla ma dang /
NK026(la)001:13808: thams cad la drangs te rol /
NK026(la)001:13809: tshe chog 'di kha shin tu mtshar zhing go dka' bar 'dug pa /
NK026(la)001:13810: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi gsung bzhin pan
NK026(la)001:13811: chen pad+ma dbang rgyal gyis zin bris mdzad pa'i sgyu
NK026(la)001:13812: 'phrul tshe dbang gi cho ga las kha 'gengs rnams
NK026(la)001:13813: btus shing / legs bshad de dang ma 'phrad na
NK026(la)001:13814: cho ga phal cher chad pa las 'os mi 'dug
NK026(la)001:13815: btus shing / pas / 'di nyid yid brtan du rung zhing dkon par shes dgos la /
NK026(la)001:13816: 'on kyang sgyu 'phrul tshe dbang dngos zur na yod pas /
NK026(la)001:13817: 'dis sgyu 'phrul tshe dbang gi go mi chod pas /
NK026(la)001:13818: dbye ba phyed par byed dgos so //
NK026(la)001:13820: 'di yan gyis tshe dbang gi rim pa grub bo //
NK026(la)001:13821: de nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK026(la)001:13822: spyir snga 'gyur gyi bka' brgyad sogs las thugs rten mar me dgod par gsungs shing /
NK026(la)001:13823: de mtshungs yang dag gi skabs kyang me dgu dang
NK026(la)001:13824: me gcig sogs sgrub rten du mar me dgod par
NK026(la)001:13825: gsungs pa ltar / 'dir yang dngos grub kyi skabs
NK026(la)001:13826: 'dir rab tu khro bo'i lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i
NK026(la)001:13827: mar me dkyil 'khor gyi lha gnas so sor bkod
NK026(la)001:13828: gsungs pa ltar / cing / de ltar min kyang dbus su che mchog dang /
NK026(la)001:13830: badz+ra he ru ka ste gtso bo gsum thun mong du mar me gcig dgod /
NK026(la)001:13831: rtsibs brgyad kyi shar rtsibs la rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13832: shar lhor lung gi he ru ka bzhi thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13833: glo 'bur gyi gru chad la gnas kyi khro mo brgyad thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13834: khyams dang po la yul gyi phra men brgyad thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13835: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i khyams la spor ma brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13836: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams la dbang mo nyer brgyad thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13837: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams la mkha' 'gro so gnyis thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13838: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams la ma bdun sring bzhi thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13839: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams la ging chen bco brgyad thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13840: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams la khro bo khro mo drug cu thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13841: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams la pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13842: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams la ma mo drug cu thun mong du gcig /
NK026(la)001:13843: dkyil 'khor bcu pa la mi dgos /
NK026(la)001:13844: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams su rig 'dzin bla ma rnams la thun mong du gcig rnams bkod /
NK026(la)001:13845: de mtshungs dngos grub kyi zhal zas dkar gsum mngar
NK026(la)001:13846: gsum sbyar ba'i 'brang rgyas chen mo mar gyis byugs
NK026(la)001:13847: pa gcig la dpa' 'bar bcu bzhi yang btsugs /
NK026(la)001:13848: de'i mthar dmigs kyis bsal ba'i dngos grub kyi rdzas ma h+aa m+aam sa /
NK026(la)001:13849: rdo rje ka ta ri ste sha skam smug rlon pa sogs sna tshogs dang /
NK026(la)001:13850: m+aam sa g.yu mdog ces khur ba skam rlon gyi rigs /
NK026(la)001:13851: dza gad dam rdo rje shugs te chang bzang po la bu ram btab pa /
NK026(la)001:13853: gal phyi zhes pra ldum btsos pa /
NK026(la)001:13855: 'jam des zhes bur mar yin pas /
NK026(la)001:13856: bur ma bsgar mas kyang rung /
NK026(la)001:13860: rdo rje kun tu rgyu lan tsh+wa /
NK026(la)001:13861: gzhan yang g.yas bldag dang zas sna bza' bca' btung ba'i dngos po sna tshogs /
NK026(la)001:13862: 'jig rten na longs spyad du rung ba'i dngos po
NK026(la)001:13863: sna tshogs dngos grub kyi rdzas 'byor bshoms su bsham
NK026(la)001:13864: mo // bla ma la la dag dpal 'bar gyi
NK026(la)001:13865: gsal shing 'brang rgyas tsam la brten nas dngos grub
NK026(la)001:13866: len pa ni mi rigs te /
NK026(la)001:13867: zur lugs dang khams lugs gnyis ka la pho brang
NK026(la)001:13868: gi mar me 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs su
NK026(la)001:13874: brtan rjes gsal shing gi mar me ste dpal 'bar la spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:13876: dngos grub bskul te slob mar bstim par gsungs pa'i gzhung don ma go ba'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:13880: cho ga de dag tshar ba dang /
NK026(la)001:13881: de nas 'bras dngos grub blang ba'i rim pa ni /
NK026(la)001:13882: thog mar 'byung po blta nyan tshar bcad pa'i phyir khro bo bcu'i mtshams drag tu bcad /
NK026(la)001:13883: lha dang 'khon spyang ba'i phyir bshags pa bya /
NK026(la)001:13884: 'gro don mthar dbyung ba'i phyir dam bca' blangs /
NK026(la)001:13885: rang nyid gzi brjid bskyed pa'i phyir byin dbab /
NK026(la)001:13886: ces gsungs pa'i don khro bo bcu'i mtshams gcod ni
NK026(la)001:13887: khro mtshams kyi khro bo bcu rnams gsal btab ste
NK026(la)001:13889: dbang mchog sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:13890: nga ni dkyil 'khor las byed kyis //
NK026(la)001:13891: phyogs skyong bcu po mnan pa dang //
NK026(la)001:13892: 'khor gyi gdon tshogs ma lus kun //
NK026(la)001:13893: dus gsum sangs rgyas bka' byung gis //
NK026(la)001:13895: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13897: ces sogs khro bo bcu'i sngags kyis mtshams bcad /
NK026(la)001:13900: dam bca' ni rgyas par spro na //
NK026(la)001:13901: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK026(la)001:13904: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK026(la)001:13905: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK026(la)001:13906: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK026(la)001:13907: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK026(la)001:13909: byin 'bebs kyang rgyas par spro na /
NK026(la)001:13910: gong du dkyil 'khor bris zin nas bya ba'i byin 'bebs rgyas pa /
NK026(la)001:13912: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK026(la)001:13915: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK026(la)001:13918: mdzod gcig ces dpal phreng dam pa las byung ba ltar bya /
NK026(la)001:13921: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:13922: rang bzhin gnas nas sku bskyod de //
NK026(la)001:13923: mkhyen pa'i gnas mchog 'dir gshegs nas //
NK026(la)001:13924: brtse bas byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK026(la)001:13927: spos dang rol mor bcas te 'di skad do //
NK026(la)001:13929: rigs lnga'i dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:13931: nga ni dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK026(la)001:13932: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rab bskor zhing //
NK026(la)001:13934: nyid kyi bka' bzhin spyan 'dren na //
NK026(la)001:13935: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:13936: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma gshegs na //
NK026(la)001:13937: sgrub mchog dngos grub ma stsal na //
NK026(la)001:13938: sku gsung thugs dang 'gal bar mchis //
NK026(la)001:13939: dam tshig mchog la dgongs nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:13940: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:13943: sku yi 'khor lo rab bud+d+ha khrag 'thung 'khor nyid
NK026(la)001:13944: kyi bka' bzhin spyan dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs dam
NK026(la)001:13945: tshig tshul bzhin ma sgrub mchog dngos grub ma sku
NK026(la)001:13946: gsung thugs dang 'gal dam tshig mchog la dgongs sku
NK026(la)001:13948: nga ni dpal ldan rin chen 'chang //
NK026(la)001:13949: yon tan 'khor lo rab rat+na khrag 'thung 'khor nyid
NK026(la)001:13950: kyi bka' bzhin dam tshig tshul bzhin dam tshig tshul
NK026(la)001:13951: bzhin sgrub mchog dngos grub sku gsung thugs dang dam
NK026(la)001:13952: tshig mchog la yon tan dngos grub stsal h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13954: pad+ma'i 'khor lo rab pad+ma khrag 'thung 'khor nyid kyi
NK026(la)001:13955: dam tshig dam tshig sgrub mchog sku gsung dam tshig
NK026(la)001:13956: mchog la gsung gi dngos grub h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13958: las kyi 'khor lo karma khrag 'thung 'khor nyid kyi
NK026(la)001:13959: dam tshig dam tshig sgrub mchog sku gsung dam tshig
NK026(la)001:13960: mchog la las kyi dngos grub stsal zhes brjod do
NK026(la)001:13961: // dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK026(la)001:13962: nam mkha'i mtha' klas chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab //
NK026(la)001:13963: ma chags spyan mnga' ma sgrib ye shes gsal //
NK026(la)001:13964: kun nas kun tu dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:13965: rdo rje'i zhag kyang tshang lags so //
NK026(la)001:13966: bzlas brjod grangs kyang tshang lags so //
NK026(la)001:13967: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus 'di lags //
NK026(la)001:13968: 'gro ba mang po bdag gis bsgral //
NK026(la)001:13969: bla med byang chub bdag gis bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:13970: mthu chen mthu rtsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK026(la)001:13971: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK026(la)001:13972: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:13973: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK026(la)001:13974: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:13975: thugs rje khro dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:13976: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK026(la)001:13977: da lta nyid du bdag la stsol //
NK026(la)001:13978: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:13979: mnyam pa'i don la ma skyes gnyis med phyir //
NK026(la)001:13980: dngos grub stsal dang gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK026(la)001:13981: rig dang ma rig sgyu ma'i khyad par gyis //
NK026(la)001:13982: sgyu ma'i spyod yul mnyam par ma grub cing //
NK026(la)001:13983: rgyal ba'i dgongs spyod klong du ma gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:13984: log rtog srin po'i zhes pa ma zlog na //
NK026(la)001:13985: mkhyen rab ting 'dzin dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:13986: chags pa'i nad kyis gdungs pa'i sdug bsngal la //
NK026(la)001:13987: bdud dang srin po zhe sdang glo bur gyis //
NK026(la)001:13988: sgyu ma'i lus srog tshe la bar gcod na //
NK026(la)001:13989: khro rgyal mthu yis zil gyis mnan pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:13990: rdzu 'phrul lam mchog dngos grub gsung rab rgya mtsho'i bdud rtsi'i char phab nas //
NK026(la)001:13991: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas rmongs pa la //
NK026(la)001:13992: shes shing rtogs pa'i shes rab mi ldan na //
NK026(la)001:13993: shes bya thogs med dngos grub 'bad pas btsal ba'i dus gsum dge bshes de //
NK026(la)001:13994: srid la phan 'dogs ston pa'i dpal mgon lags //
NK026(la)001:13995: drin la lan ldon gang lags ma 'tshal na //
NK026(la)001:13996: sems kyi me long dngos grub rnam rtog zhen pa'i bag chags stug po yis //
NK026(la)001:13997: dus gsum chos la mun pa'i rdzas ltar sgribs //
NK026(la)001:13998: dus gsum dge bshes drin la lan slan phyir //
NK026(la)001:13999: dus la rmongs pa'i sems can lan bgyid nas //
NK026(la)001:14000: mngon shes drug gi dngos grub rgyu drug rim gyis drang ba'i don slad du //
NK026(la)001:14001: khams gsum ma lus khyab par 'gro ba'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14002: sems kyi gdos su bdag gi lus mchis na /
NK026(la)001:14003: thogs med rkang mgyogs dngos grub log rtog mang pos shes rgyud g.yengs pa yis //
NK026(la)001:14004: ston pas gsungs pa'i bka' rgyud ji snyed pa //
NK026(la)001:14005: don dang yi ge brjod med ma bsam na //
NK026(la)001:14006: mi brjed gzungs kyi dngos grub ngang nyid rnam rtog las kyi dbang gyur cing //
NK026(la)001:14007: sdug bsngal mang pos bcings pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK026(la)001:14008: 'dul thabs mang pos 'gro ba'i don bgyid kyis //
NK026(la)001:14009: rnam bzhi las kyi dngos grub rang gi rnam rtog las kyi dbang gyur zhing //
NK026(la)001:14010: blang dor med pa'i don la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:14011: so so'i blo la ji ltar 'thad pa bzhin //
NK026(la)001:14012: mthun 'jug thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul lags kyis //
NK026(la)001:14013: sen yog pra yi dngos grub dug gsum zhen pas 'khor ba'i gcong gting nas //
NK026(la)001:14014: 'tsho byed sman pa'i rgyal pos bcos su gsol //
NK026(la)001:14015: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub dam pa ste //
NK026(la)001:14016: dur khrod rdzas la brten nas bdag la stsol //
NK026(la)001:14017: skya reng dang po'i dngos grub dus la bab //
NK026(la)001:14018: khrag 'thung 'khor bcas dngos grub dbab tu gsol //
NK026(la)001:14019: khams gsum dregs pa ma lus 'tshal bar gyis //
NK026(la)001:14020: bcom ldan dpal chen dngos grub ye shes thabs kyi 'gro don kun bgyis kyis //
NK026(la)001:14021: khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub dur khrod rol pas khams gsum dbang sdud kyis //
NK026(la)001:14022: phra men brgyad kyi dngos grub phrin las rnam bzhis 'gro don sdud lags kyis //
NK026(la)001:14023: khro bo bcu yi dngos grub sprul pa mang pos sems can kun 'dul phyir //
NK026(la)001:14024: yang sprul nying sprul dngos grub ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14026: de nas rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14028: chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung bas //
NK026(la)001:14029: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:14030: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:14031: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum ye shes 'bar ma brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14032: goo r+ai khro mo brgyad kyi chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14033: sid+ha phra men brgyad kyi tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14034: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi yi 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod rol pa nas //
NK026(la)001:14035: spor ma gsang yum tshogs bcas dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14036: dbang phyug ma sring tshogs kyi dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14037: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis phrin las myur mgyogs chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14038: ma bdun sring bzhi'i tshogs kyi sgrol byed rab tu 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14039: rdo rje ging chen bco brgyad zhe sdang 'bab thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14040: khro rgyal srin po'i tshogs kyi ci bgyi'i bka' nyan tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14041: pho nya sder mo'i tshogs kyi las rnams yongs su grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14042: ye shes ma mo'i tshogs kyi sdom pa'i sa la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK026(la)001:14043: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang tshogs kyi gnas mchog yang dag don gyi 'og min nas //
NK026(la)001:14044: rgyal ba kun bzang yab yum 'og min dbang phyug chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK026(la)001:14045: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK026(la)001:14046: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs lnga yab yum bcas //
NK026(la)001:14047: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi lha klu gnod sbyin so so'i gnas mchog nas //
NK026(la)001:14048: bcom ldan rigs gsum mgon po'i u rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14049: rdor sems sprul pa dga' rab rdo rje dang //
NK026(la)001:14050: rgyal po'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron la //
NK026(la)001:14051: rdor sems gsang ba'i bdag po dngos byon nas //
NK026(la)001:14052: dbang bzhi rdzogs bskur rtog tshogs lha ngo 'phrod //
NK026(la)001:14053: dbang rtags chags shing me long rnam gnyis sbyin //
NK026(la)001:14054: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:14055: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:14056: rgya bod gnyis kyi so mtshams su //
NK026(la)001:14057: ma ga d+ha yi brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14058: u rgyan rgyal po d+harma k+aa ya ni //
NK026(la)001:14059: klu yi rgyal po'i bu mo yis //
NK026(la)001:14060: dga' rab rdo rje spyan drangs nas //
NK026(la)001:14061: tshom bu stong gi dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:14062: khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:14063: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir rgya gar za hor yul gyi mtshams //
NK026(la)001:14065: rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi dang //
NK026(la)001:14066: sras mo ni lan+d+ha ra gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14067: tshom bu lnga yi dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:14068: khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:14069: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir rgya gar sid+ha gnyis kyi mtshams //
NK026(la)001:14070: g.yu mtsho gling dgu'i brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14071: sid+ha u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK026(la)001:14072: sras mo go ma de wi gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14073: tshom bu lnga bcu'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:14074: brgya phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK026(la)001:14075: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir rgya gar yul dbus ma ga d+ha /
NK026(la)001:14076: wa ra na si'i gnas dag tu //
NK026(la)001:14077: dge slong nyin byed seng ge dang //
NK026(la)001:14078: srin po'i bu mo na shi gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14079: tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:14080: 'khor ni lnga brgya sangs rgyas te //
NK026(la)001:14081: de yi dngos grub rgya gar bal po'i so mtshams su //
NK026(la)001:14082: dge slong so kya de wa dang //
NK026(la)001:14083: lha mo bkra shis dngos grub gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14084: tshom bu bcu pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:14085: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir rgya dang bal po yul gyi mtshams //
NK026(la)001:14086: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14088: bal mo bza' yi sh+aakya gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14089: tshom bu lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK026(la)001:14090: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir rgya gar stag gzig yul gyi mtshams //
NK026(la)001:14091: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14092: slob dpon s+thi ra ma ti dang //
NK026(la)001:14093: bu mo ga ga sid+d+hi gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14094: ji ltar bsgrub cing brten pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14095: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir bod dang zhang zhung yul gyi mtshams //
NK026(la)001:14096: gangs dkar ti se'i brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14097: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba dang //
NK026(la)001:14098: lha mo dmar mo chos 'tshol gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14099: ji ltar bsgrub cing brten pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14100: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir mon bod gnyis kyi so mtshams su //
NK026(la)001:14101: spa gro stag tshang seng ge phug /
NK026(la)001:14102: slob dpon nam mkha'i snying po dang //
NK026(la)001:14103: shel dkar bza' yi mtsho rgyal gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14104: ji ltar bsgrub cing brten pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14105: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir bod khams dan+tiga brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:14106: slob dpon rgyal ba blo gros dang //
NK026(la)001:14107: lha mo sum bza' ser mo gnyis //
NK026(la)001:14108: ji ltar bsgrub cing brten pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14109: de yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:14110: bod yul gtsang gi g.yas ru phyogs //
NK026(la)001:14111: nyug gi rdo rje sgrom bu ru //
NK026(la)001:14112: gnubs ban sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK026(la)001:14113: rang byung thig le nyag gcig don //
NK026(la)001:14114: zla ba dgu yis sems nyid grol //
NK026(la)001:14115: dngos po'i gnas lugs gtan la phebs //
NK026(la)001:14116: ji ltar bsgrub cing brten pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14117: de yis dngos grub khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho ni //
NK026(la)001:14118: thugs sras nang nas mchog tu gyur //
NK026(la)001:14119: sprul pa mang po zhal gzigs pas /
NK026(la)001:14120: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub brnyes //
NK026(la)001:14121: de yi dngos grub sgrub gnas phyag sham dgon pa ru //
NK026(la)001:14122: so ni ye shes dbang phyug gis //
NK026(la)001:14123: chos nyid don dam thugs su chud //
NK026(la)001:14124: rdzogs chen lta ba'i bka' yang babs //
NK026(la)001:14125: de yi dngos grub shol yag sdings kyi gnas mchog tu //
NK026(la)001:14126: dbang bzhi chu bo'i bka' babs pas //
NK026(la)001:14127: sru ni legs pa'i sgron ma yis //
NK026(la)001:14128: dge mched bco lnga'i slob bu smin //
NK026(la)001:14129: de yi dngos grub de dag nang nas zhu yi rus //
NK026(la)001:14130: bsod nams sh+aakya zhes su grags //
NK026(la)001:14131: de yi dngos grub bod yul gtsang gi ru logs phyogs //
NK026(la)001:14132: 'ug pa lung gi yang dben du //
NK026(la)001:14134: bka' lung rgyud dang man ngag la //
NK026(la)001:14135: phul byung shes bya ma lus mkhyen //
NK026(la)001:14136: de yi dngos grub g.yas ru rgya bo'i dben gnas su //
NK026(la)001:14137: zur chung shes rab grags pa ni //
NK026(la)001:14138: lta dgongs rtse mo phul du gyur //
NK026(la)001:14139: snang grags sgyu mar mkhyen pa yi //
NK026(la)001:14140: skal ldan gdul bya smin grol mdzad //
NK026(la)001:14141: de yi dngos grub g.yas ru chu dbar li thung du //
NK026(la)001:14142: glan ston sh+aakya bzang po ni //
NK026(la)001:14144: phrin las spyod la thogs pa med //
NK026(la)001:14145: de yi dngos grub shangs kyi nya tshal khang stod du //
NK026(la)001:14146: lha rje sh+aakya byang chub ni //
NK026(la)001:14147: rdzogs chen lta ba'i phul du byung //
NK026(la)001:14148: shes bya thogs med ma lus mkhyen //
NK026(la)001:14149: de yi dngos grub 'og gdong lha rje 'gar zhes grags //
NK026(la)001:14150: ye shes mkha' 'gros byin brlabs pa //
NK026(la)001:14151: zag med bde ba'i nyams dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:14152: de yi dngos grub 'chums kyi 'chad dgon gnas mchog tu //
NK026(la)001:14153: sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:14154: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab mnga' //
NK026(la)001:14155: dbang gi chu bo'i bka' rnams rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:14156: de yi dngos grub shar ri rgya gar gling chung du //
NK026(la)001:14157: mkhas pa glan ban rdo rje 'od //
NK026(la)001:14158: gsang bdag zhal gzigs dus gsum mkhyen //
NK026(la)001:14160: de yi dngos grub dam chos 'byung gnas sha ri mor //
NK026(la)001:14161: glan ston brtson 'grus ye shes ni //
NK026(la)001:14162: gdul bya yang dag sa la 'god //
NK026(la)001:14164: de yi dngos grub gung thang dpal gyi dgon po ru //
NK026(la)001:14165: mkhas pa bsod nams rgyal po yis //
NK026(la)001:14166: dbang gis 'gro ba du ma smin //
NK026(la)001:14167: de yi dngos grub sprul sku lha rje lha 'bum gyis //
NK026(la)001:14168: drag pos gdul bya mang po smin //
NK026(la)001:14169: de yi dngos grub glan ston chos kyi seng ge ni //
NK026(la)001:14170: ting 'dzin dgongs pa'i drod dang ldan //
NK026(la)001:14171: de yi dngos grub rdza lung dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK026(la)001:14172: dbang bzhi rdzogs pa sangs rgyas dpal //
NK026(la)001:14174: de yi dngos grub gnas mchog gung thang yang dben du //
NK026(la)001:14175: glan ston bsod nams mgon po ni //
NK026(la)001:14176: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dbang bka' babs //
NK026(la)001:14177: dbang mchog chu bos smin grol mdzad //
NK026(la)001:14178: de yi dngos grub dben gnas bye ma seng ge ru //
NK026(la)001:14179: chos bdag 'bro ston rdo rje ni //
NK026(la)001:14180: rgyud lung man ngag kun la mkhas //
NK026(la)001:14181: de yi dngos grub bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun ya dben du //
NK026(la)001:14183: kun mkhyen 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK026(la)001:14184: de yi dngos grub re sbug dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK026(la)001:14185: lang gro tshe dbang rgyal po ni //
NK026(la)001:14186: mthu stobs dbang phyug sprul sku'i gar //
NK026(la)001:14187: de yi dngos grub dben gnas chu dbar nyi sbug tu //
NK026(la)001:14188: brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang ni //
NK026(la)001:14190: de yi dngos grub glo bo ma thang chos sdings su //
NK026(la)001:14191: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan ni //
NK026(la)001:14192: mkha' grub kun gyi yang rtser so na //
NK026(la)001:14193: de yi dngos grub grub pa'i gnas mchog chu bo rir //
NK026(la)001:14194: rig 'dzin legs ldan rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK026(la)001:14195: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i mnga' bdag mchog /
NK026(la)001:14196: de yi dngos grub brag dmar chos lung dgon pa ru //
NK026(la)001:14197: skyi ston tshe ring dbang po ni //
NK026(la)001:14198: bka' gter chos kyi rgyal srid 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:14199: de yi dngos grub gtsang stod bres kyi ri khrod du //
NK026(la)001:14200: bla chen chos rgyal rdo rje dpal //
NK026(la)001:14201: mdo sgyu'i smon grol srog shing 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:14202: de yi dngos grub sman lung dam pa'i gdan sa ru //
NK026(la)001:14203: nyang ston blo mchog rdo rje ni //
NK026(la)001:14204: gnas lnga rig pa'i rdo rje 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:14205: de yi dngos grub thub bstan rdo rje brag dgon du //
NK026(la)001:14206: lha btsun pad+ma phrin las nyid //
NK026(la)001:14207: bka' gter bstan pa'i ring lugs spel //
NK026(la)001:14208: de yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK026(la)001:14210: ye shes lha yi dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:14211: gsal shing gi ni ri mo la //
NK026(la)001:14212: spyan drangs mchod dang bzlas pa dang //
NK026(la)001:14213: bstod dang smon 'jug bsdu ba drug /
NK026(la)001:14214: ces pas don drug gi dang po /
NK026(la)001:14215: 'brang rgyas la gsal shing mtho dman rim pa bcu bzhi bya //
NK026(la)001:14216: de nas pho brang dpal gyi mar me bkod pa de 'dus pa'i lha tshogs su bskyed /
NK026(la)001:14217: dbang bskur byin brlab snyan gsan dbab /
NK026(la)001:14218: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs nyid spyan drangs bstim /
NK026(la)001:14220: dkyil 'khor gyi mar me rnams 'dus pa chen po'i
NK026(la)001:14221: lha tshogs bcom ldan 'das che mchog he ru ka
NK026(la)001:14224: rgyud kyi he ru ka yab yum bzhi /
NK026(la)001:14225: lung gi he ru ka yab yum bzhi /
NK026(la)001:14233: khro bo khro mo drug cu /
NK026(la)001:14234: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu /
NK026(la)001:14236: rig 'dzin bla ma rnams sku mdog phyag mtshan rnams pa ji lta bar gsal bar gyur /
NK026(la)001:14237: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs phyag rgyar bcas te dbang bskur /
NK026(la)001:14238: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab //
NK026(la)001:14239: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu
NK026(la)001:14240: ba'i phyag rgya se gol dang bcas te snyan gsan
NK026(la)001:14241: dbab / ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14242: e h+ye hi a na ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:14243: dzahh+aum bam hoh k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14245: rten la spyan drangs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:14246: bla mas lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK026(la)001:14247: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14248: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwo r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14249: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK026(la)001:14250: ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa r+ai
NK026(la)001:14251: h+aum / badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:14252: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14253: badz+ra am gu sha dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14254: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14255: zhes pas dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi mar me las
NK026(la)001:14256: gsal shing ste dpal 'bar dang po la me sbar
NK026(la)001:14257: bas 'od dang sprul par bcas nas mar me'i lha
NK026(la)001:14258: gtso bo gsum dpal 'bar dang po'i rtse mor byon
NK026(la)001:14259: par bsam la / gnyis pa mchod pa ni /
NK026(la)001:14260: bdud rtsi rak+ta gtor ma gsum rtsa sngags kyis dbul /
NK026(la)001:14261: zhes gsungs pas sngags gong ma gsum gyi mthar ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:14262: ma h+aa ba lin+ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:14264: zhes 'bul zhing gsal shing la sman raka sbran /
NK026(la)001:14267: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dang //
NK026(la)001:14268: dbang mchog he ru yab yum dang //
NK026(la)001:14269: badz+ra he ru yab yum dang //
NK026(la)001:14270: gtso bo rnams kyi thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14271: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK026(la)001:14272: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK026(la)001:14274: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskang //
NK026(la)001:14275: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:14276: de nas gong gi sngags rnams dang //
NK026(la)001:14277: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14281: bcom ldan che mchog he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:14282: bla med yum chen khro mo'i rgyal //
NK026(la)001:14283: mthing nag sku yis bdud bzhi 'dul //
NK026(la)001:14284: nyi shu rtsa gcig sa rnams gnon //
NK026(la)001:14285: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon sangs rgyas //
NK026(la)001:14286: zhabs brgyad ting 'dzin dbyings su sbyor //
NK026(la)001:14287: rgyan rnams ma lus sku la rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:14288: khro rgyal sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14289: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:14290: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad de //
NK026(la)001:14291: stong pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs //
NK026(la)001:14292: mthing nag dgyes pa chen po'i sku //
NK026(la)001:14293: zhabs brgyad ru tra pho mo mnan //
NK026(la)001:14296: rdo rjee rigs mchog bdud 'dul gtso //
NK026(la)001:14297: gdug pa thams kyis btul nas ni //
NK026(la)001:14298: bdud rigs rdul du rlog mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:14299: dpa' chen sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14300: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14301: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14303: hoh bcom ldan 'das che mchog yab yum dang /
NK026(la)001:14305: dpal chen yab yum la sogs pa rnams la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14306: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir
NK026(la)001:14307: tshogs pa rnams la shes bya la thogs pa med
NK026(la)001:14308: pa'i shes rab / mi brjed pa'i gzungs /
NK026(la)001:14317: 'khor dang longs spyod pa sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK026(la)001:14318: myur du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK026(la)001:14320: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah gsum gyis dang po 'od dang sprul pa /
NK026(la)001:14322: gsum pa sku 'od du zhu nas rang la thim
NK026(la)001:14323: pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi
NK026(la)001:14324: brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:14326: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah'i sngags dang pos lha de rnams kyi 'od dang sprul pa /
NK026(la)001:14327: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahzhesa gnyis pas gsung yig 'bru rang sngags kyi rnam pa /
NK026(la)001:14328: ang+ku sha gsum pas sku yongs rdzogs 'od du zhu
NK026(la)001:14329: nas dpon slob thams cad la thim pas sku gsung
NK026(la)001:14330: thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi brjid dang ldan
NK026(la)001:14331: par bsam 'og ma kun la yang 'agre'o //
NK026(la)001:14333: de nas rim pa gnyis pa rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi'i dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14334: pho brang gi mar me nas rigs bzhi lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs te /
NK026(la)001:14335: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14336: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14337: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14338: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14339: ang+ku sha dzahzhesa lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK026(la)001:14340: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14341: zhes pas mar me gnyis pa las spyan drangs shing
NK026(la)001:14342: dpal 'bar gnyis pa la me sbar bas rtser byon
NK026(la)001:14344: bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+ta gsum so so'i sngags mthar gong bzhin dbul /
NK026(la)001:14346: rigs bzhi he ru ka yi thugs //
NK026(la)001:14347: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14348: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen tshur
NK026(la)001:14350: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14351: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14352: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14353: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14354: he ru ka yab yum bzhi'i sngags la ru lu re re dang /
NK026(la)001:14355: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na re re gdags so //
NK026(la)001:14358: chos dbyings dag pa sangs rgyas yul nas bzhengs //
NK026(la)001:14359: nyon mongs gnas nas sems can don kun mdzad //
NK026(la)001:14360: thugs rjes byang chub gnas su 'god mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:14361: bcom ldan dpal chen bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:14362: kro d+hi shwa r+ai ra bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14363: phun sum tshogs 'dzin yon tan mchog gi sku //
NK026(la)001:14364: lha mang tshogs kyis kun nas rnam bstod cing //
NK026(la)001:14365: rngam pa'i zhal du dug gsum 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:14366: bcom ldan dpal chen rat+na he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:14367: kro d+hi shwa r+air bcas la gsung mchog chos kyi sku ni kun khyab cing //
NK026(la)001:14368: sa dang bar snang khams la gnas pa dag /
NK026(la)001:14369: byang chub sems la rab tu 'god mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:14370: bcom ldan dpal chen pad+ma he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:14371: kro d+hi shwa r+air bcas la nan tan drag shul spyod pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK026(la)001:14372: thabs mkhas thugs rje chen po'i drag shul gyis //
NK026(la)001:14373: rgyud drug sems can ma lus kun sgrol ba //
NK026(la)001:14374: bcom ldan dpal chen karma he ru ka //
NK026(la)001:14375: kro d+hi shwa r+air bcas la lnga pa smon lam ni /
NK026(la)001:14376: hoh bcom ldan 'das rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14377: bdag rnal 'byor pa dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir tshogs
NK026(la)001:14378: pa rnams la shes bya la thogs pa med pa'i
NK026(la)001:14379: shes rab / mi brjed pa'i gzungs /
NK026(la)001:14388: 'khor dang longs spyod la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK026(la)001:14390: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah lan gsum gyis dang pos 'od dang sprul pa /
NK026(la)001:14392: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas thim pa sogs gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14393: de nas gsum pa lung gi he ru ka bzhi lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK026(la)001:14394: badz+ra rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14395: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14396: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14397: sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14398: sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14399: ru lu gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14400: gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14401: ru lu yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14402: yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14403: ru lu mar me gsum pa las dpal 'bar gsum pa'i mar me sbar bas rtser byon /
NK026(la)001:14405: bdud rtsi gtor mar rak+ta rnams sngags mthar gong bzhin dbul /
NK026(la)001:14407: lung gi he ru ka yi thugs //
NK026(la)001:14408: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14409: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14410: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos gsum pa 'dzab ni /
NK026(la)001:14411: gong gi snying po bzlas so //
NK026(la)001:14414: sbyor ba dam tshig gsang ba sgrol ba'i dbyings //
NK026(la)001:14415: log lta myong byed skye gnas reg bya 'joms //
NK026(la)001:14416: ga na nyams pa ta na mtshan ma sgrol //
NK026(la)001:14417: lung gi khro rgyal tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14419: hoh bcom ldan 'das lung gi he ru ka yab yum tshogs la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14420: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir tshogs pa rnams la /
NK026(la)001:14421: shes bya la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14422: drug pa ang+ku sha lan gsum gyis bsdu ba yang gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14423: bzhi pa la khro mo brgyad lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK026(la)001:14432: zhes goo r+ai brgyad kyi sngags dang /
NK026(la)001:14433: badz+ra +aang+ku sha dzah ru lu mar me bzhi pa
NK026(la)001:14434: las gsal shing gi me bzhi pa sbar zhing spyan
NK026(la)001:14435: drangs / bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+ta rang sngags kyi mthar btags la dbul /
NK026(la)001:14436: goo r+ai brgyad kyi thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14437: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14438: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14439: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos badz+ra goo r+ai ha sogs
NK026(la)001:14441: goo r+ai la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //
NK026(la)001:14442: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK026(la)001:14443: sku mdog phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK026(la)001:14444: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14445: khro mo brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14446: bdag cag rnal 'byor sogs gong bzhin 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14447: ang+ku shas bsdu ba yang gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14448: lnga pa la phra men brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi spyan drangs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:14450: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14451: badz+ra sing+ga la mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14452: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14453: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14455: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14456: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14457: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah badz+ra a mu kh+aa h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14459: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hoh zhes so
NK026(la)001:14460: so'i sngags dang lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas badz+ra amng+ku
NK026(la)001:14462: mar me lnga pa las gsal shing lnga pa spar /
NK026(la)001:14463: ru lu badz+ra sid+ha mu kha he /
NK026(la)001:14464: sogs rang sngags mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14465: sid+ha phra men brgyad rnams dang /
NK026(la)001:14466: sgo ma bzhi yi thugs zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru
NK026(la)001:14467: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od
NK026(la)001:14468: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs tshur 'dus bdag la dngos
NK026(la)001:14469: rang sngags dang ru lu gu h+ya bzlas /
NK026(la)001:14472: sing+ha phra men chen mo brgyad rnams ni /
NK026(la)001:14473: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK026(la)001:14474: rnam sprul las kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:14475: sid+ha phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK026(la)001:14476: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams ni //
NK026(la)001:14477: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:14478: shar lhor nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrung //
NK026(la)001:14479: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la phyag smon lam ni /
NK026(la)001:14480: phra men brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14481: bdag cag rnal 'byor sogs snga ma bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14482: ang+ku shas bsdu ba yang gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14483: drug pa spor ma brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK026(la)001:14484: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata /
NK026(la)001:14486: sh+r+ai badz+ra mud+ga ra mu kha shwa ra y+aa na
NK026(la)001:14487: ma sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra ya y+aa
NK026(la)001:14488: na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ga pra dz+wa la
NK026(la)001:14489: ya y+aa na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+di pra dz+wa la
NK026(la)001:14490: ya y+aa na mah badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahs spyan drangs
NK026(la)001:14491: / mar me drug pa las gsal shing drug pa spar /
NK026(la)001:14492: rang sngags kyi mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i sngags btags te mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14494: spor byed chen mo brgyad rnams dang /
NK026(la)001:14495: gsang yum bzhi yi thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14496: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14497: gu h+yu dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14498: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos a rag+mo h+aum re dang
NK026(la)001:14503: chos dbyings rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK026(la)001:14504: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK026(la)001:14505: srid gsum zhing du sbyor ba'i g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK026(la)001:14506: spor byed chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14507: bar khyams de yi shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK026(la)001:14508: dgyes pa bskyed pa gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK026(la)001:14509: gnyis med rol pas byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK026(la)001:14510: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag smon lam ni
NK026(la)001:14511: hoh spor ma chen mo brgyad dang gsang ba'i yum
NK026(la)001:14512: chen bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs
NK026(la)001:14513: 'gre / ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14515: dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14529: badz+ra ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:14530: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:14534: badz+ra ma h+aa m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:14542: badz+ra bum pa k+aa la ma b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:14543: badz+ra lam bo d+ha ra b+h+yo /
NK026(la)001:14544: ru lu ru lu badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahs spyan drangs shing /
NK026(la)001:14545: mar me bdun pa las dpal 'bar bdun pa spar /
NK026(la)001:14546: rang sngags mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14548: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad kyi thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14549: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14550: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14551: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos rtsa sngags nyer brgyad dang
NK026(la)001:14552: ru lu spel te bzlas so //
NK026(la)001:14555: ming sring la sogs dbang phyung nyi shu brgyad //
NK026(la)001:14556: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK026(la)001:14557: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK026(la)001:14558: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14560: dbang phyug nyer brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs dang /
NK026(la)001:14561: ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14562: brgyad pa la mkha' 'gro so gnyis lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14564: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahs mar me brgyad pa las gsal shing brgyad pa'i me spar /
NK026(la)001:14565: rang sngags mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14567: mkha' 'gro so gnyis thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14568: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od zer 'phros /
NK026(la)001:14569: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs tshur 'dus bdag la dngos e a ra li h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14573: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK026(la)001:14574: 'dod rgur sgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK026(la)001:14575: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:14576: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14578: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14579: ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14580: dgu pa la ma bdun sring mo bzhi lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14581: ma ma d+h+aa tu h+aum bdun dang /
NK026(la)001:14583: ru lu badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahs mar me dgu pa
NK026(la)001:14584: las dpal 'bar dgu pa la me spar zhing spyan
NK026(la)001:14585: drangs / rang sngags mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14587: ma bdun sring bzhi'i thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14588: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14589: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14590: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos ma ma d+h+aa tu h+aum
NK026(la)001:14595: 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:14596: phyi 'khor bsrung zhing nang 'khor skyong bar mdzad //
NK026(la)001:14597: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK026(la)001:14598: bgegs srung ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14600: ma bdun sring mo bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14601: ang+ku shas bsdu ba yang gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14602: bcu pa la ging bco brgyad lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14603: ging+ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14604: ru lu badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahs mar me bcu pa las gsal shing bcu pa la me spar zhing /
NK026(la)001:14605: rang sngags mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14607: ging chen ging lcam thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14608: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14609: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14610: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos ging+ka ra dang ru lu
NK026(la)001:14613: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK026(la)001:14614: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK026(la)001:14615: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK026(la)001:14616: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14618: ging chen bco brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14619: ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14620: bcu gcig pa la steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14622: ru luh badz+ra ung+ku sha dzahs mar me bcu gcig
NK026(la)001:14623: pa las dpal 'bar bcu gcig pa la me spar
NK026(la)001:14624: zhing / sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14626: khro bo khro mo drug cu thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14627: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od
NK026(la)001:14628: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs tshur 'dus bdag la dngos
NK026(la)001:14630: ru lu gu h+ya spel lo //
NK026(la)001:14632: bcom ldan h+aum mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK026(la)001:14633: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK026(la)001:14634: 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK026(la)001:14635: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14637: khro bo khro mo drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14638: ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14639: bcu gnyis pa la phyogs bzhi'i pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14640: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14642: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh ang+ku sha dzahs spyan
NK026(la)001:14643: drangs shing mar me bcu gnyis pa las gsal shing
NK026(la)001:14644: bcu gnyis pa'i me spar zhing /
NK026(la)001:14645: rang sngags kyi mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa dbul /
NK026(la)001:14647: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu'i thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14648: zur brgyad dkyil 'khor nas 'bru snying po ru lu
NK026(la)001:14649: 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpa' chen
NK026(la)001:14650: thugs tshur 'dus bdag la dngos sngags de dag dang
NK026(la)001:14651: lu ru / gu h+ya spel lo //
NK026(la)001:14654: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yi //
NK026(la)001:14655: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med //
NK026(la)001:14656: ci bgyi'i bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:14657: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14659: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu'i tshogs la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14660: ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14661: bcu gsum pa 'og gi ma mo drug cu lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14663: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahs spyan drangs shing mar me bcu
NK026(la)001:14664: gsum pa las gsal shing bcu gsum pa'i me spar
NK026(la)001:14665: zhing / rang sngags kyi mthar sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod pa gsum dbul /
NK026(la)001:14667: ma mo drug cu'i thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14668: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14669: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros dpal chen thugs
NK026(la)001:14670: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub ma ma shwa ra
NK026(la)001:14671: h+aum / ru lu ru lu gu h+ya spel lo //
NK026(la)001:14674: stong khams yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK026(la)001:14675: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK026(la)001:14676: yum chen las la dbang ba'i ma mo che //
NK026(la)001:14677: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK026(la)001:14679: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14680: ang+ku shas bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK026(la)001:14681: de nas rim pa bcu bzhi pa la khro bo
NK026(la)001:14682: khro mo khra thabs dang rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang thams
NK026(la)001:14683: cad lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:14684: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14685: badz+ra yo gi gu ru sa ya dzah zhes mar
NK026(la)001:14686: me bcu bzhi pa las gsal shing bcu bzhi pa'i
NK026(la)001:14687: me spar ro // 'od dang bcas te gsal shing gi rtse la byon par bsam /
NK026(la)001:14689: rang sngags mthar ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:14690: ma h+aa ba lin+ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:14692: bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+ta dbul /
NK026(la)001:14694: man ngag mdo lung rgyud dang bcas pa yi //
NK026(la)001:14695: rig 'dzin bla ma rnams kyi thugs ka nas //
NK026(la)001:14696: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru snying po ru lu 'bru
NK026(la)001:14697: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od phar 'phros pas ni mchod
NK026(la)001:14698: pa phul // tshur 'dus bdag la dngos ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14699: badz+ra yo gi gu ru sa ma ya dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14700: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum /
NK026(la)001:14704: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK026(la)001:14705: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin gyi //
NK026(la)001:14706: rgya bod rig 'dzin grub thob tshogs la bstod //
NK026(la)001:14707: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsol cig /
NK026(la)001:14709: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi bla ma rnams la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs gong bzhin 'gre /
NK026(la)001:14711: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahlana gsum gyi dang por 'od dang sprul pa /
NK026(la)001:14713: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim /
NK026(la)001:14714: bdag sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:14716: slob ma rnams phyir khrus bya /
NK026(la)001:14717: gsungs kyang nang du las bum gyi chus khrus byas pas 'thus /
NK026(la)001:14718: nang du sleb pa dang 'brang rgyas re /
NK026(la)001:14720: dza gad re drangs te rol lo //
NK026(la)001:14721: de nas dngos grub kyi rdzas gzhan rnams kyang thams cad brims te rol lo //
NK026(la)001:14722: zhal zas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14723: h+r+aih zla gam zhal gyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:14724: rang rig ye shes mngon snang ba'i //
NK026(la)001:14725: 'dod yon gsang ba'i longs spyod rgyan //
NK026(la)001:14726: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:14727: hoh bdag cag dpon slob mched dang lcam dral rnams
NK026(la)001:14728: kyis rdo rje tshe gsol bas tshe dbang phun sum
NK026(la)001:14729: tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14730: ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14731: dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'dus par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14732: zla rgyas gsol bas tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14733: gal phyi gsol bas bsam pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14734: zla phrom gsol bas chos nyid zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14735: 'jam des gsol bas byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14736: zhal zas kha ba dang mngar ba dang skyur ba
NK026(la)001:14737: dang ro rnam pa sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro
NK026(la)001:14738: sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:14739: ces brjod pas dngos grub kyi zhal zas rnams la rim pas rol bar bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14740: de'ang dngos grub kyi lhag ma gsum la /
NK026(la)001:14741: yi dam lha'i skal ba bla ma /
NK026(la)001:14742: dkyil 'khor lha'i skal ba rgyal thebs /
NK026(la)001:14743: rig 'dzin rnams kyi skal ba slob ma thams cad la dagye'o //
NK026(la)001:14744: de nas dngos grub brtan par bya ba'i phyir 'di'i rjes zlos bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:14745: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK026(la)001:14746: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:14747: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub dam pa rnams //
NK026(la)001:14748: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK026(la)001:14749: k+aa ya w+aaka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK026(la)001:14751: kun gyis dam rdzas la me tog gtor ro //
NK026(la)001:14752: zhes gsungs par glan ston gyis /
NK026(la)001:14753: nas la rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas byas la
NK026(la)001:14754: dbang rdzas 'jug pa'i snod du blug pa'am rang gi
NK026(la)001:14755: khyim yin na mdzod phugs su dor /
NK026(la)001:14757: de nas mar me'i smon lam ni /
NK026(la)001:14758: kun gyi srin lag sbrel te /
NK026(la)001:14759: bla ma'i phyag g.yon gyis mar me bzung la /
NK026(la)001:14760: slob ma rnams kyis kyang mar me bzung ste /
NK026(la)001:14761: dbyangs snyan pos rjes zlos bya zhing /
NK026(la)001:14763: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:14764: snying po byang chub lam du zhugs pa yi //
NK026(la)001:14765: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen por mi ltung zhing //
NK026(la)001:14766: chags sdang gcong rong gnas su mi skye dang //
NK026(la)001:14767: log lta dmyal ba'i zangs khar rbab mi 'dril //
NK026(la)001:14768: 'khon 'dzin gcan gzan gdug pa'i skad mi thos //
NK026(la)001:14769: nyon mongs mtshon rtse gdug pa'i zer mi 'phog /
NK026(la)001:14770: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' drin che ba dang //
NK026(la)001:14771: srog gis sbrel ba'i mched dang lcam dral dang //
NK026(la)001:14772: gsum pa'i dbang gis sbrel ba'i rig ma gsum //
NK026(la)001:14773: skye ba 'di dang tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK026(la)001:14774: mi 'bral rtse gcig 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK026(la)001:14775: sa bcu khyad par rim gyis bgrod par shog /
NK026(la)001:14776: nam zhig tshe 'phos lus barje dus byung na //
NK026(la)001:14777: 'khor ba'i g.yang sar lan gcig lhung srid kyang //
NK026(la)001:14778: snang ba'i sgo 'byed zhun mar mdangs gsal 'dis //
NK026(la)001:14779: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cing //
NK026(la)001:14780: kun tu 'od kyi sa la rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK026(la)001:14781: pad+ma chen po'i sa la lhun gyis grub //
NK026(la)001:14782: 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14783: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis mdun bsus shig /
NK026(la)001:14784: yi dam lha yis rgyab nas srog brten cig /
NK026(la)001:14785: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis mtha' skyor cig /
NK026(la)001:14786: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis sna drongs shig /
NK026(la)001:14787: ma tshogs dbang mo rnams kyis rjes skyongs shig /
NK026(la)001:14788: lcang lo can gyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK026(la)001:14789: mi ldog pa yi sa la gnas nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:14790: rdo rje khro rgyal khyed kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK026(la)001:14791: rig 'dzin rnams dang dbyer med gyur nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:14792: bla med sku gsung thugs su 'grub par shog /
NK026(la)001:14793: de nas bla mas shar sgo nas /
NK026(la)001:14794: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du /
NK026(la)001:14795: zla gam zhal gyi gzhal yas khang bzhengs /
NK026(la)001:14796: dur khrod gsang ba'i dam rdzas rnams bkram /
NK026(la)001:14797: mar me ye shes kyi 'od phung /
NK026(la)001:14799: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:14800: dngos grub rnam gsum blangs pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK026(la)001:14801: bdag cag dpon slob mched dang lcam dral rnams tshe 'dir yang g.yang ba'i longs spyod ldan zhing /
NK026(la)001:14802: rdo rje tshe'i yon tan phun sum tshogs shing 'gro
NK026(la)001:14803: ba ma lus pa'i don byed pa'i mthu phun sum
NK026(la)001:14805: tshe 'phos lung barjesa kyang ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyun
NK026(la)001:14806: dang ma bral bar 'dren pas lung ston par gyur
NK026(la)001:14807: cig / rig 'dzin gyi go 'phang thob ste /
NK026(la)001:14809: sems dpa' brgyad kyi rgyab skyor /
NK026(la)001:14810: sems ma brgyad kyis mdun bsus /
NK026(la)001:14814: 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa non /
NK026(la)001:14815: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes chen
NK026(la)001:14816: pos bdag gzhan gyi don ma lus pa lhun gyis
NK026(la)001:14819: snum gyis kyang snying gar byug go //
NK026(la)001:14820: dkyil 'khor nas mar me blangs la /
NK026(la)001:14821: smon lam btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos kyang bya ste /
NK026(la)001:14823: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs rnams kyis mi gnas pa'i ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14824: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14825: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14826: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14827: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14828: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14829: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14830: dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14831: 'da' ka thugs kyi ye shes dang /
NK026(la)001:14832: thugs ye shes dgu'i dngos grub bdag cag rnams kyis thob bo //
NK026(la)001:14833: a la la hoh zhes brjod la kun la 'brim zhing snying khar gtug go //
NK026(la)001:14834: de nas bla mas dge ba rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba'i tshul yang rgyas par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14835: de ltar mar me'i smon lam grub nas skabs 'dir gtang rag gi yon dbul ba ni /
NK026(la)001:14836: rtsa bar gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK026(la)001:14837: glan ston bsod nams mgon po'i 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK026(la)001:14838: drin lan bsab pa'i phyir yon tan dbul te /
NK026(la)001:14840: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK026(la)001:14841: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:14842: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung las kyang /
NK026(la)001:14843: che ba rgyal srid dang yul 'khor /
NK026(la)001:14844: gces pa bu smad dang phyag rgya ma /
NK026(la)001:14849: yun du dad pa dang dam tshig /
NK026(la)001:14850: zhu khar sri zhu dang gus pa /
NK026(la)001:14851: mchog tu brtse sems dang gdung ba la sogs pa
NK026(la)001:14852: mnyes pa sna tshogs chu bo'i gzhung bzhin du dbul
NK026(la)001:14853: lo // zhes gsungs pa ltar gang 'byor dbul zhing gtang rag gi man+dala yang 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:14854: de nas dam tshig bsgrag pa ni /
NK026(la)001:14855: de ltar gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i smin byed
NK026(la)001:14856: kyi dbang zab mo legs par thob nas dam tshig
NK026(la)001:14857: dang sdom pa'i tshogs bskyang ba ni nges par gal
NK026(la)001:14858: che la / de la yang rgyas bshad bsam gyis mi khyab kyang mdor bsdu ba'i tshe /
NK026(la)001:14859: spyir bya spyod rnal 'byor bzhi so sor bye brag
NK026(la)001:14860: gi dam tshig dang sdom pa'i tshul bsrung tshul tha
NK026(la)001:14861: dad kyang / thun mong du rigs lnga spyi dang
NK026(la)001:14862: bye brag gi dam tshig rnams yin pas gsar rnying
NK026(la)001:14863: bka' gter gyi ring lugs rnams su rgyas par 'byung
NK026(la)001:14864: dad kyang / ba bzhin dang / gsar rnying thun
NK026(la)001:14865: mong gi sngags lam du zhugs pa rnams la rtsa
NK026(la)001:14866: ltung bcu bzhir grangs nges pa yongs grags ltar rtsa
NK026(la)001:14868: yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba ni mnga' ris pan+di
NK026(la)001:14869: ta chen po pad+ma dbang rgyal gyi sdom gsum rnam
NK026(la)001:14870: nges las / dbang dang dam tshig ma smin rig ma bsten //
NK026(la)001:14871: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus su lus ngag rtsod //
NK026(la)001:14872: ma gsungs rig mar rang stobs bdud rtsi len //
NK026(la)001:14873: snod ldan slob mar gsang sngags mi ston dang //
NK026(la)001:14874: dad ldan chos 'dri ba la chos gzhan ston //
NK026(la)001:14875: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad //
NK026(la)001:14876: rnal 'byor ye shes mi ldan sngags par rlom //
NK026(la)001:14877: snod min la bshad yan lag ltung ba brgyad //
NK026(la)001:14880: bsnyen sogs ma byas dbang rab las la 'jug /
NK026(la)001:14881: phyi chos mos la lus kyi phyag rgya bstan //
NK026(la)001:14882: sdom pa gnyis kyi bcas las dgos med 'da' //
NK026(la)001:14883: zhes sogs phra mo rnams kyang bsrung ngo //
NK026(la)001:14884: khyad par rang lugs snga 'gyur gyi ring srol la //
NK026(la)001:14885: rtsa ba bla ma'i sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig la dgu dgur phye bas nyi shu rtsa bdun /
NK026(la)001:14886: yan lag gi dam tshig nyi su rtsa lnga la /
NK026(la)001:14890: ngag 'khyal te khyad par du bya ba lnga /
NK026(la)001:14895: phrag dog ste dug lnga mi spang bar lam du 'khyer dgos pas mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga /
NK026(la)001:14900: byang sems rnams dang du blang zhing mi 'dor ba'i dam tshig lnga /
NK026(la)001:14904: dbang po lnga rnams lha ru shes par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga /
NK026(la)001:14909: las kyi rigs te bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga ste /
NK026(la)001:14910: dam tshig nyi shu rtsa lngar spang blang rnams thos
NK026(la)001:14911: bsam gyis sgro 'dogs chod par byas te bsgom pas
NK026(la)001:14913: don bsdu na sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK026(la)001:14914: de sogs dam tshig rnam gzhag mang gsungs pa //
NK026(la)001:14915: rtsa ba yan lag bcas 'dir ma 'dus med //
NK026(la)001:14916: mdor na rang lus rdo rje gsum shes na //
NK026(la)001:14917: sngags kyi dam tshi sa la 'bum sde 'dus //
NK026(la)001:14918: zhes gsungs pa ltar sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du
NK026(la)001:14919: shes pa mnyam rjes thams cad du bskyang na dam
NK026(la)001:14920: tshig nyams med du bsrung bar nus pa'i tha tshig
NK026(la)001:14921: go // de dag la nyams chag 'byung tshul ni /
NK026(la)001:14922: thos bsam ma byas pa'i skyon gyis ltung mtshams mi shes pa dang /
NK026(la)001:14923: bla ma lha sogs la mi gus pa dang /
NK026(la)001:14924: bag med par spyod pa dang /
NK026(la)001:14925: nyon mongs mang ba rnams ni ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi zhes bya ba yin la /
NK026(la)001:14926: de dag gi gnyen po mdo rgyud la thos bsam
NK026(la)001:14927: gyi sgro 'dogs dpyad de slob par 'os pa rnams
NK026(la)001:14929: kun la dag snang dang gus pa bskyed pa dang /
NK026(la)001:14930: rtag par dran bzhin shes bzhin gyi gnyen po bsten pa dang /
NK026(la)001:14931: rang rgyud la nyon mongs pa gang shugs che zhing
NK026(la)001:14932: rags pa de'i gnyen por 'bad pa drag pos bslab
NK026(la)001:14933: bo // gong gi ltung ba byung ba'i sgo bzhi'i steng du brjed nges che ba dang /
NK026(la)001:14934: dran pa mi gsal ba gnyis bsnan pas dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu drug ces bshad pa yin /
NK026(la)001:14935: rgyu de dag la brten nas dam tshig nyams ma
NK026(la)001:14936: nyams nyin mtshan dus drug tu rang rgyud la legs
NK026(la)001:14937: par brtags pas thun gyi drug cha las 'das na
NK026(la)001:14938: thun tshod las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14939: zhag gcig las 'das na 'gal ba zhes bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14940: zla ba gcig las 'das na nyams pa zhes bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14941: lo gcig las 'das na 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14942: lo gnyis las 'das na ral pa zhes bya'o //
NK026(la)001:14943: 'on kyang dri med bshags rgyud kyi gleng gzhi ltar
NK026(la)001:14944: sngags kyi dam tshig gser dngul gzhom pa bzhin gso
NK026(la)001:14946: gso tshul de yang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK026(la)001:14947: de yang snying thag pa nas 'gyod sems kyis bsags na gsor rung zhing /
NK026(la)001:14948: thun zhag zla ba lo sogs song rim gyi nyes pa lci ru 'gro la /
NK026(la)001:14949: lo gsum 'das par gyur na ni de dag kyang
NK026(la)001:14950: gsor mi rung bas tshe 'dir yid du mi 'ong
NK026(la)001:14951: ba'i sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyis nyam thag par byas
NK026(la)001:14952: te tshe 'di'i snang ba nub ma thag tu rdo
NK026(la)001:14953: rje'i dmyal ba zhes nam yang thon par mi 'gyur
NK026(la)001:14954: ba'i gnas der sdug bsngal mi bzad pa nyams su
NK026(la)001:14956: de lta bas na dam tshig gso ba'i tshul gal che bas /
NK026(la)001:14957: de yang o rgyan chen pos gsang sngags lam rim du /
NK026(la)001:14958: mnyam rjes bza' bcang bsrung ba'i dam lnga dbog /
NK026(la)001:14960: dang po bum dbang 'khor bcas thob pa'i mnyam gzhag gi dam tshig tu bskyed rim sgom pa /
NK026(la)001:14961: rjes thob kyi dam tshig lha dang mi 'bral zhing lus ngag tha mal du mi 'khrul ba /
NK026(la)001:14962: bza' ba'i dam tshig sha lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga la rol pa /
NK026(la)001:14963: bcang ba'i dam tshig rdo rje dril bu /
NK026(la)001:14964: bsrung ba'i dam tshig snod bcud lha dang gzhal yas
NK026(la)001:14965: khang du shes pa dang mi 'bral ba rnams 'das
NK026(la)001:14968: ral par gyur na dbang gang thob pa'i lha re
NK026(la)001:14969: re la bsnyen pa sum khri drug stong bzlas pas
NK026(la)001:14970: gaso'o // bum dbang gi steng du gsang dbang gi
NK026(la)001:14971: mnyam gzhag gi dam tshig tu gtum mo sgom pa
NK026(la)001:14972: gaso'o // / rjes thob kyi dam tshig tu tsan+da li'i nyams len dang mi 'bral ba /
NK026(la)001:14973: bza' ba'i dam tshig tu zas thams cad ye shes
NK026(la)001:14974: kyi bdud rtsi ru byin gyis brlabs nas rol pa
NK026(la)001:14975: / bcang ba'i dam tshig rlung kha sbyor nyer gcig re zhag re la chag med du bsgom pa /
NK026(la)001:14976: bsrung ba'i dam tshig khams kun+da mi nyams par byed
NK026(la)001:14977: pa rnams sngar bzhin 'das nyams 'gal ral du gyur
NK026(la)001:14978: pa la sngon du chad las kyis sbyang zhing /
NK026(la)001:14979: de rjes slar dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dbang bskyar nas len pas gaso'o //
NK026(la)001:14980: bum gsang gi steng shes rab ye shes kyi dbang
NK026(la)001:14981: nos pa'i mnyam gzhag gi dam tshig dngos dang ye
NK026(la)001:14982: shes kyi phyag rgya bsten pa /
NK026(la)001:14983: rjes thob kyi dam tshig tu bde chen gyi nyams dang mi 'bral bar bya ba /
NK026(la)001:14984: bza' ba'i dam tshig zas thams cad snyoms 'jug gi tshul du rol pa /
NK026(la)001:14985: bcang ba'i dam tshig khams dwangs ma mi nyams par byed pa /
NK026(la)001:14986: bsrung ba'i dam tshig dngos sam ye shes kyi mu
NK026(la)001:14987: dra bsten pa rnams la 'das nyams 'gal ral du
NK026(la)001:14988: gyur pa dang / dbang bzhi pa'i mnyam gzhag gi
NK026(la)001:14989: dam tshig tu zung 'jug gnyis med du bsgom pa
NK026(la)001:14990: gyur pa dang / / rjes thob kyi dam tshig
NK026(la)001:14991: tu rjes gcod thams cad zung 'jug gi ngo bor
NK026(la)001:14992: gyur pa dang / / lta ba / bza' ba'i dam tshig chos nyid la chos nyid rol pa /
NK026(la)001:14993: bcang ba'i dam tshig chos thams cad gnyis med kyi don la rtag par gnas pa /
NK026(la)001:14994: bsrung ba'i dam tshig gnyis med ye shes chen po
NK026(la)001:14995: las mi 'da' ba rnams las 'das nyams 'gal ral
NK026(la)001:14998: 'pho med kyi tshul khrims yang dag par bsrung ba dang /
NK026(la)001:14999: rdzogs pa'i rim pa sgom pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15000: rang byin gyis brlab pa sogs la nan tan du
NK026(la)001:15001: byas pa rnams bye brag tu gso ba'i tshul lo
NK026(la)001:15002: // spyir de dag la gong du bshad pa ltar
NK026(la)001:15003: thun tshod la 'das pa de ma thag tu gsor
NK026(la)001:15004: // rung / zhag las 'gal na tshogs kyi 'khor lo brgya phrag la sogs btang bas gso /
NK026(la)001:15005: zla ba gcig las nyams na rang la gang yod
NK026(la)001:15006: kyi bdog pa'i dngos po thams cad kyis bskang la
NK026(la)001:15007: gso / lo gcig las 'das na bu dang chung
NK026(la)001:15008: ma dang nor gyi dbyig ste gces pa rnams kyang
NK026(la)001:15009: gso / btang la gso / lo gnyis las ral
NK026(la)001:15010: na rang gi srog kyang 'phangs pa med par gtong
NK026(la)001:15011: gso / btang la gso / dgos shing / gzhan
NK026(la)001:15012: yang snying po rgyan las gsungs pa ltar tshogs zhing
NK026(la)001:15014: badz+ra b+han+d+ha gra tha sogs phral ba'i sngags rgya dang /
NK026(la)001:15016: gtum mo'i me dmigs kyis bsreg pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15017: lta bas mi dmigs par sgom pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15018: lam dus su thun bzhi'am drug tu dbang blang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15019: 'dus pa'i tshogs dbus su mi 'chab par zhu ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15020: rten khyad par can gyi drung du skad gsang mthon pos smreng ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15022: sku gsung thugs kyi rten bzhengs pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15023: za byed mkha' 'gro'i rnal 'byor sogs kyis me la sbyang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15024: phyi nang gsang ba'i gtor ma gtong ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15025: gsang sngags bzla zhing bsam gtan sgom pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15026: mi phyugs kyi srog skyob pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15027: rgyal ba'i gsung rab klog pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15028: bla ma'i drung ngam rang nyid kyis dkyil 'khor bzhengs la bdag 'jug blang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15029: yig brgya dus bzang la bzla ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15030: phung po gsum pa'i mdo 'don pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15031: rdor sems sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste dpal gsang ba'i snying po dang /
NK026(la)001:15032: sgyu 'phrul bla ma sogs las gsungs pa'i phra thig gi rnal 'byor sgom pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15033: glang chen rab 'bogs kyi rgyud las gsungs pa'i rnal 'byor spyi khrus sam /
NK026(la)001:15034: na raka dong sprugs kyi sgrub mchod rgyud 'don sogs
NK026(la)001:15035: bshags pa'i thabs sna tshogs kyis nyes ltung dang zhag
NK026(la)001:15036: tu mi 'grogs pas gso zhing slar bsrung ngo //
NK026(la)001:15037: de ltar dam tshig de dag kyang nyams pa med
NK026(la)001:15038: par bsrung zhing lam la spyod pa dag ni myur
NK026(la)001:15039: na tshe 'dir 'ja' lus 'od phung chen por yongs
NK026(la)001:15040: su grol ba'am / 'chi khar bar do sangs rgyas
NK026(la)001:15041: kyi go 'phang mngon du byed pa'i mchog gi dngos
NK026(la)001:15042: su grol ba'am / grub dang / grub chen brgyad
NK026(la)001:15043: dang dbang phyug gi yon tan brgyad sogs thun mong
NK026(la)001:15045: ring mtha' yang skye ba bcu drug nas 'brang bu mngon du byed de /
NK026(la)001:15046: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK026(la)001:15047: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK026(la)001:15049: mdor na mthar thug gi gnas skabs su /
NK026(la)001:15051: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK026(la)001:15052: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK026(la)001:15053: byas la mi sogs tshogs gyur te //
NK026(la)001:15054: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK026(la)001:15056: rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i dkon mchog 'grel du /
NK026(la)001:15057: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig dang ldan na nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK026(la)001:15058: 'dod pa lnga la spyad pa'i skyon gyis mi gos shing /
NK026(la)001:15059: nyan thos dang byang chub sems dpa'i gzhung du grags
NK026(la)001:15060: pa'i tshul khrims dang sdom pa thams cad kyang 'dus
NK026(la)001:15061: shing phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ro //
NK026(la)001:15062: zhes gsungs pas nyon mongs pa byol nyog tu spyod
NK026(la)001:15063: par ma gsungs pas dam tshig dang sdom pa ldan
NK026(la)001:15064: pa gnang bkag gi mtshams shes pa rnams kyis thabs
NK026(la)001:15065: la mkhas pas spyad kyang nyes pas gos par mi
NK026(la)001:15067: mdor na de ltar gdams pa rnams rdo rje'i slob
NK026(la)001:15068: ma khyed rnams kyis yang dag par bya dgos so
NK026(la)001:15069: // glan ston gyis mdo'i dbang byang dang /
NK026(la)001:15070: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang byang g.yung ston gyis mdzad pa las /
NK026(la)001:15071: bla ma'i zhabs slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK026(la)001:15072: de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyi //
NK026(la)001:15073: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin pas //
NK026(la)001:15074: nga yis ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK026(la)001:15075: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK026(la)001:15076: zhes gsungs pa ltar zhabs sam phyag slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:15077: slob bus de'i lan du 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum bya ste /
NK026(la)001:15078: bla ma rdo rje rgyal po la //
NK026(la)001:15079: dad mos gus pa'i sems ldan pas //
NK026(la)001:15080: bka' yi ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK026(la)001:15081: lus ngag yid gsum gnyer gyis blang //
NK026(la)001:15085: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyang spro na bya'o //
NK026(la)001:15087: 'dir dbang bsab pa'i cho ga bya'o //
NK026(la)001:15089: de'i tshul ni g.yung ston chen po'i dbang byang las 'di ltar /
NK026(la)001:15090: dbang phyug gi mdun du dbang bco brgyad kyi dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa rnams bsags la /
NK026(la)001:15091: zhes gsungs pas bum dbang nas tshe dbang bar gyis
NK026(la)001:15092: dbang rdzas thams cad tshang bar mdun du bsags pa'am
NK026(la)001:15093: / yang na dbang rdzas thams cad gnas khang der yod pas 'thus /
NK026(la)001:15095: dbang phyug kun tu bzang por gsal ba'i thugs ka'i
NK026(la)001:15096: h+aum las 'od 'phros pas dbang rdzas rnams rim pas
