NK026(la)001:15097: sngar rab tu gnas pa'i lhar gsal btab la /
NK026(la)001:15098: zhes gsungs pas dper na dbu rgyan rin chen 'byung
NK026(la)001:15099: ldan du bskyed pa lta bu rnams slar yang lha
NK026(la)001:15102: h+aum zhes dbang phyug gis bskur gnas rnams su rang rang gi dbang rdzas gtugs pas /
NK026(la)001:15103: 'od du zhu nas rang rang gi mtshungs ldan gyis
NK026(la)001:15104: rgyu la bstim pas sngar bas kyang nus pa cher
NK026(la)001:15106: zhes gsungs pa dper na dbu rgyan rin 'byung gi
NK026(la)001:15107: rab gnas can de bskur gnas spyi bor gtugs pas
NK026(la)001:15108: 'od du zhu nas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu rnam par
NK026(la)001:15109: shes pas tshogs brgyad la bstim pas ye shes lnga'i
NK026(la)001:15110: nus pa skyes par bsam pa lta bus mtshon par
NK026(la)001:15111: nus la / rgyas par sgyu 'phrul dbang byang du blta'o //
NK026(la)001:15113: dbang rdzas thams cad kyi rab gnas bsgrub zin pa dang /
NK026(la)001:15114: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros te /
NK026(la)001:15115: sngar dbang po'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i mdun gyi nam
NK026(la)001:15116: mkha'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'od du zhu
NK026(la)001:15117: nas dbang phyug la thim pas 'od dang ldan par
NK026(la)001:15118: bsam mo // zhes gsungs pa ltar bya ba ni
NK026(la)001:15119: zab gnad gzhan nas ches khyad par du 'phags pa
NK026(la)001:15120: dbang nyams pa gso ba'i tshul lo //
NK026(la)001:15121: de ltar dngos gzhi'i cho ga rnams legs par grub nas /
NK026(la)001:15122: rjes kyi cho ga ston par byed pa la lnga ste /
NK026(la)001:15126: mchod bstod lhag chad bskang zhing bzod par gsol nas dkyil 'khor bsdu ba /
NK026(la)001:15127: bsngo smon bkra shis brjod cing dga' ston rol pa rnams so //
NK026(la)001:15128: de la dang po lhag ma ni /
NK026(la)001:15130: de nas lhag ma bsdus te /
NK026(la)001:15132: mar me btsugs nas dkyil 'khor nas gom pa bdun
NK026(la)001:15133: cu 'phags pa'i sar phrin las rnam bzhi gang byed
NK026(la)001:15134: pa'i man+dala bya / zhes gsungs pa bsdu na zhing
NK026(la)001:15135: lpags steng lhag ma bshams pa'i khar chos skyong gi
NK026(la)001:15136: gtor ma rnams kyang spags te sman raka bran /
NK026(la)001:15137: de'i steng du zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gsal 'debs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15139: bla mas rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor las mkhan gyis sgo ma bzhi man chad gsal gdab /
NK026(la)001:15140: ces gsungs kyang dpon slob thams cad kyi sngags tsam gyis dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams gsal gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15142: de nas badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs lhag ma'i mgron snyan gsan dbab /
NK026(la)001:15143: pad+ma'i phyag rgya bcas la lhag ma dang kha chu'i
NK026(la)001:15144: dam tshig la re ba rnams sngon gyi thugs dam
NK026(la)001:15145: las ma 'da' bar sgrub pa po bdag gi stong
NK026(la)001:15148: zhes thal mo lan gsum gdab /
NK026(la)001:15149: d+aa ki na'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs /
NK026(la)001:15150: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol tu khyung gshog gi phyag rgyas zil gyis mnan /
NK026(la)001:15151: rta gdong gi phyag rgyas dbang du sdud /
NK026(la)001:15155: ces gsungs pa'i don bla mas bdud rtsi hub gang bzhes te ya rkan rigs lnga /
NK026(la)001:15156: ma rkan yum lngar gsal ba'i sbyor mtshams kyi bdud
NK026(la)001:15157: rtsir bsam la lhag ma bshams pa la kha chu
NK026(la)001:15162: dpal chen rak+sha he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:15163: goo r+ai'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15164: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams gyis //
NK026(la)001:15165: go r+ai khro mo brgyad du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15166: srin mo chen mo brgyad rnams btul //
NK026(la)001:15167: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK026(la)001:15168: byang sems sa yi snying po yis //
NK026(la)001:15169: khro mo chen mo goo r+air sprul //
NK026(la)001:15170: srin mo chen mo ging thod btul //
NK026(la)001:15171: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK026(la)001:15172: rdo rje'i dam las bro bskyal te //
NK026(la)001:15173: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK026(la)001:15174: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK026(la)001:15175: rdo rje dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK026(la)001:15176: las kyi lhag ma 'di longs la //
NK026(la)001:15177: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK026(la)001:15178: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15179: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK026(la)001:15180: byang sems nam mkha'i snying po yis //
NK026(la)001:15181: khro mo chen mo tsoo r+air sprul //
NK026(la)001:15183: lhag ma byin nas rdo rje'i dam las gtan gyi
NK026(la)001:15184: bran du sngon gyi khas blangs rdo rje'i dam las
NK026(la)001:15185: las kyi lhag ma khas blangs dam bcas bcol ba'i
NK026(la)001:15186: las rnams phyi yi dkyil 'khor byang sems spyan ras
NK026(la)001:15187: gzigs dbang gis // khro mo chen mo phra mor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15188: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed btul //
NK026(la)001:15189: lhag ma byin nas rdo rje'i dam las gtan gyi
NK026(la)001:15190: bran du sngon gyi khas blangs rdo rje'i dam las
NK026(la)001:15191: las kyi lhag ma khas blangs dam bcas bcol ba'i
NK026(la)001:15192: las rnams phyi yi dkyil 'khor byang sems phyag na
NK026(la)001:15193: rdo rje yis khro mo chen mo beet+tara sprul //
NK026(la)001:15194: srin mo chen mo za byed btul //
NK026(la)001:15195: lhag ma byin nas rdo rje'i dam las gtan gyi
NK026(la)001:15196: bran du sngon gyi khas blangs rdo rje'i dam las
NK026(la)001:15197: las kyi lhag ma khas blangs dam bcas bcol ba'i
NK026(la)001:15198: las rnams phyi yi dkyil 'khor byang chub sems dpa'
NK026(la)001:15199: byams pa yis // khro mo chen mo puk+kara sprul //
NK026(la)001:15200: srin mo nang rol 'dren ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15201: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK026(la)001:15202: las kyi khas blangs bcol ba'i phyi yi byang sems
NK026(la)001:15204: khro mo chen mo g+hasmara sprul //
NK026(la)001:15205: srin mo chen mo rab 'jigs btul //
NK026(la)001:15207: gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i las kyi khas blangs
NK026(la)001:15208: bcol ba'i phyi yi byang sems kun tu bzang po
NK026(la)001:15209: yis // khro mo chen mo sme shar sprul //
NK026(la)001:15210: srin mo chen mo srog gcod btul //
NK026(la)001:15211: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK026(la)001:15212: las kyi khas blangs bcol ba'i phyi yi byang chub
NK026(la)001:15214: khro mo chen mo tsan+dara sprul //
NK026(la)001:15215: srin mo chen mo smyon ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15216: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i las kyi khas blangs bcol ba'i phyi yi h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15217: dpal chen rak+sha he ru ka /
NK026(la)001:15218: phra men tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15219: dpal chen he ru'i zhal bzhad pas //
NK026(la)001:15220: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad rnams kyis //
NK026(la)001:15221: sing ha phra men brgyad du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15222: srin mo mgo brnyan brgyad rnams btul //
NK026(la)001:15223: shar lho lha mo l+aa s+ye mas //
NK026(la)001:15224: khro mo chen mo seng mgor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15225: srin mo 'jigs byed seng mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:15226: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK026(la)001:15227: las kyi khas blangs bcol ba'i phyi yi lho phyogs
NK026(la)001:15229: phra men chen mo stag mgor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15230: srin mo za byed stag mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:15232: nub phyogs lha mo g+airti mas //
NK026(la)001:15233: phra men chen mo wa mgor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15234: srin mo len byed wa mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:15236: byang phyogs lha mo n+air+t+ya mas //
NK026(la)001:15237: phra men chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15238: srin mo ra ro khyi mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:15240: shar lho lha mo d+h+au pe mas //
NK026(la)001:15241: phra men chen mo rgod mgor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15242: srin mo bya rgod mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15244: lho nub lha mo me tog mas //
NK026(la)001:15245: phra men kang+ka'i mgo ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15246: srin mo kang+ka'i mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15248: nub byang lha mo mar me mas //
NK026(la)001:15249: phra men bya rog mgo ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15250: srin mo 'joms byed bya rog btul //
NK026(la)001:15252: byang shar lha mo dri chab mas //
NK026(la)001:15253: phra men hu lu mu kar sprul //
NK026(la)001:15254: srin po bskul byed 'ug mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:15257: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15258: sgo ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15259: tshad med sgo ma bzhi rnams kyis //
NK026(la)001:15260: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15261: shar gyi byams pa lcags kyu mas //
NK026(la)001:15262: sgo ma rta gdong lcags kyur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15263: srin mo rta yi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15265: lho yi snying rje zhags pa mas //
NK026(la)001:15266: sgo ma phag gdong zhags par sprul //
NK026(la)001:15267: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15269: nub kyi dga' ba lcags sgrog mas //
NK026(la)001:15270: sgo ma dred mgo lcags sgrog sprul //
NK026(la)001:15271: srin mo dred kyi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15273: byang gi btang snyoms dril bu mas //
NK026(la)001:15274: sgo ma chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15275: srin mo chen mo spyang mgo btul //
NK026(la)001:15278: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15279: spor ma'i tshogs kyis bskor nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:15280: dpal chen thugs rje sbyor ba las //
NK026(la)001:15281: thub drug yid chos brgyad po yis //
NK026(la)001:15282: spor ma chen mo brgyad du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15283: phyogs skyong brgyad kyi bu mo btul //
NK026(la)001:15284: kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15285: spor ma nyi zer zhags par sprul //
NK026(la)001:15286: 'bar ma nyi zer zhags pa btul //
NK026(la)001:15288: yi dwags thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15289: spor ma glog phreng 'dzin du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15290: 'bar ma chen mo glog phreng btul //
NK026(la)001:15292: mi yi thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15293: spor ma mdung thung 'phen du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15296: dmyal ba'i thubs pa gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15297: spor ma gshin rje ral grir sprul //
NK026(la)001:15298: 'bar ma gshin rje ral gri btul //
NK026(la)001:15300: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15301: spor ma dril 'khrol ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15304: lha min thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15305: spor ma skar mda' gdong du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15308: byol song thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15309: spor ma glag+sha sdeb tu sprul //
NK026(la)001:15310: 'bar ma ban glang sna tshogs btul //
NK026(la)001:15312: lha yi thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK026(la)001:15313: spor ma khyung thogs ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15314: 'bar ma gnod sbyin khyung thogs btul //
NK026(la)001:15317: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15318: gsang ba'i yum bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15319: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK026(la)001:15320: yi ge h+aum bzhi sprul byas nas //
NK026(la)001:15321: de las gsang ba'i yum bzhir sprul //
NK026(la)001:15322: de bzhis srin mo bzhi btul te //
NK026(la)001:15323: shar gyi bde ba za byed mas //
NK026(la)001:15324: srin mo za byed khrag 'thung btul //
NK026(la)001:15326: lho yi bde ba rmongs byed mas //
NK026(la)001:15327: srin mo chen mo rus 'cha' btul //
NK026(la)001:15329: nub kyi bde ba rgyas 'debs mas //
NK026(la)001:15330: srin mo dur khrod bdag mo btul //
NK026(la)001:15332: byang gi bde ba tshe 'phel mas //
NK026(la)001:15333: srin mo dur khrod bdag mo btul //
NK026(la)001:15336: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15337: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15338: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK026(la)001:15339: tshangs ma la sogs ye shes kyi //
NK026(la)001:15340: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis //
NK026(la)001:15341: las kyi dbang mo mgo brnyan tshogs //
NK026(la)001:15342: 'jig rten rnams kyi sring mo ste //
NK026(la)001:15343: lag na glo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK026(la)001:15344: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs su sbrul //
NK026(la)001:15345: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK026(la)001:15346: 'gal byed gnod pa'i tshogs rnams btul //
NK026(la)001:15349: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15350: mkha' 'gro tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15351: dpal chen sku yi 'od zer las //
NK026(la)001:15352: sems dpa' sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis //
NK026(la)001:15353: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sprul //
NK026(la)001:15354: srin mo sum cu rtsa gnyis btul //
NK026(la)001:15355: sems dpa' rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK026(la)001:15356: mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15357: srin mo chen mo dga' byed btul //
NK026(la)001:15359: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK026(la)001:15361: srin mo chen mo spor mo btul //
NK026(la)001:15363: sems dpa' rdo rje legs pa yis //
NK026(la)001:15364: mkha' 'gro gsor byed ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15365: srin mo chen mo gsod byed btul //
NK026(la)001:15367: sems dpa' rdo rje rin chen gyis //
NK026(la)001:15369: srin mo chen mo 'bar ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15371: sems dpa' rdo rje nyi ma yis //
NK026(la)001:15372: mkha' 'gro gzi brjid ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15373: srin mo chen mo gzi brjid btul //
NK026(la)001:15375: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK026(la)001:15376: mkha' 'gro bdud rtsi rgyal byed sprul //
NK026(la)001:15377: srin mo rgyal byed dbang ldan btul //
NK026(la)001:15379: sems dpa' rdo rje bzhad pa yis //
NK026(la)001:15381: srin mo chen mo 'joms ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15383: sems dpa' rdo rje chos rab kyis //
NK026(la)001:15384: mkha' 'gro chags byed ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15385: srin mo chen mo chags ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15387: sems dpa' rdo rje rnon po yis //
NK026(la)001:15388: mkha' 'gro chags bral ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15389: srin mo chen mo chags bral btul //
NK026(la)001:15391: sems dpa' rdo rje 'khor lo yis //
NK026(la)001:15393: srin mo chen mo 'khor lo btul //
NK026(la)001:15395: sems dpa' rdo rje smra ba yis //
NK026(la)001:15397: srin mo chen mo rgyas ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15399: sems dpa' rdo rje sna tshogs kyis //
NK026(la)001:15400: mkha' 'gro sna tshogs gzugs su sprul //
NK026(la)001:15401: srin mo chen mo sna tshogs btul //
NK026(la)001:15403: sems dpa' rdo rje go cha yis //
NK026(la)001:15404: mkha' 'gro chen mo bsrung mor sprul //
NK026(la)001:15405: srin mo chen mo ma srin btul //
NK026(la)001:15407: sems dpa' rdo rje mche ba yis //
NK026(la)001:15408: mkha' 'gro gnod sbyin ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15409: srin mo chen mo gnod sbyin btul //
NK026(la)001:15411: sems dpa' rdo rje khu tshur gyis //
NK026(la)001:15413: srin mo chen mo 'phrog ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15415: sems dpa' dpa' bar 'gro ba yis //
NK026(la)001:15416: mkha' 'gro bya rog gdong du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15417: srin mo chen mo mig 'byed btul //
NK026(la)001:15419: sems dpa' kun tu bzang po yis //
NK026(la)001:15421: srin mo chen mo 'jigs byed btul //
NK026(la)001:15423: sems dpa' zla 'od gzhon nu yis //
NK026(la)001:15425: srin mo chen mo mon thong btul //
NK026(la)001:15427: byang chub sems dpa' bzang skyong gis //
NK026(la)001:15428: mkha' 'gro bzhad gdong ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15429: srin mo bzhad kyi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15431: sems dpa' d+r+wa ba can 'od kyis //
NK026(la)001:15432: mkha' 'gro khyi mgo ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15433: srin mo khi yi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15435: sems dpa' rdo rje snying po yis //
NK026(la)001:15436: mkha' 'gro phag gdong ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15437: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15439: sems dpa' nam mkha' mdzod kyis ni //
NK026(la)001:15440: mkha' 'gro rnga mgo ma ru sbrul //
NK026(la)001:15441: srin mo rnga mo'i mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15443: sems dpa' 'od dpag med kyis ni //
NK026(la)001:15444: mkha' 'gro bong bu'i mgo ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15445: srin mo bong bu'i mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15447: sems dpa' ngan song kun sbyong gis //
NK026(la)001:15448: mkha' 'gro ra mgo ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15449: srin mo ra yi mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15451: sems dpa' rgyal ba ye shes kyis //
NK026(la)001:15452: mkha' 'gro byi ba'i mgo can sprul //
NK026(la)001:15453: srin mo byi ba'i mgo can btul //
NK026(la)001:15455: sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pas //
NK026(la)001:15456: mkha' 'gro keng rus ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15457: srin mo keng rus 'dzin ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15459: sems dpa' sbobs pa brtsegs pa yis //
NK026(la)001:15460: mkha' 'gro rus phreng can du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15461: srin mo rus pa'i phreng can btul //
NK026(la)001:15463: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa yis //
NK026(la)001:15464: mkha' 'gro bum sna ma ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15465: srin mo bum sna'i chung ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15467: sems dpa' ngan song kun 'dren gyis //
NK026(la)001:15469: gshin rje rnam 'joms chung ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15471: sems dpa' spos kyi glang po yis //
NK026(la)001:15472: mkha' 'gro da sha g+r+ai bar sprul //
NK026(la)001:15473: da sha g+r+ai ba'i chung ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15475: byang sems don yod grub pa yis //
NK026(la)001:15477: gnod sbyin 'bod sgrog chung ma btul //
NK026(la)001:15480: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15481: pho nya'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15482: 'od zer sum brgya drug cu la //
NK026(la)001:15483: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15484: shar du 'od zer dkar po las //
NK026(la)001:15485: dung gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15486: dri za'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK026(la)001:15488: lho ru 'od zer sngon po las //
NK026(la)001:15489: lcags kyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15490: gshin rje'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK026(la)001:15492: nub tu 'od zer dmar po las //
NK026(la)001:15493: zangs kyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15494: klu yi gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK026(la)001:15496: byang du 'od zer ljang gu las //
NK026(la)001:15497: g.yu yi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15498: gnod sbyin gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK026(la)001:15500: steng du 'od zer ser po las //
NK026(la)001:15501: gser gyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15502: ya bdud gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK026(la)001:15505: bse yi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15506: ma mo'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK026(la)001:15509: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15510: ging chen tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15511: dpal chen he ru ka bzhad pas /
NK026(la)001:15512: rdo rje ging chen bco brgyad sprul //
NK026(la)001:15513: gdon gyi rgyal po bco brgyad btul //
NK026(la)001:15516: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15517: ma bdun tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15518: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba yis //
NK026(la)001:15519: yi ge h+aum bdun spros pa las //
NK026(la)001:15520: gsang ba'i ma mo bdun du sprul //
NK026(la)001:15521: srin mo chen mo bdun po btul //
NK026(la)001:15524: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK026(la)001:15525: sring mo bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK026(la)001:15526: gling bzhi dbang sgyur chen mo yis //
NK026(la)001:15527: srin mo chen mo bzhi ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15528: bgegs kyi rgyal po bzhi po btul //
NK026(la)001:15531: bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod pas //
NK026(la)001:15532: dpal chen badz+ra he rur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15533: dbus kyi yi dwags dregs pa btul //
NK026(la)001:15535: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad kyis //
NK026(la)001:15536: dpal chen bud+d+ha he rur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15537: shar gyi dri za'i srin po btul //
NK026(la)001:15539: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gyis //
NK026(la)001:15540: dpal chen rat+na he rur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15541: lho yi gshin rje srin po btul //
NK026(la)001:15543: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas kyis //
NK026(la)001:15544: dpal chen pad+ma he rur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15545: nub kyi klu yi gdon tshogs btul //
NK026(la)001:15547: bcom ldan don yod grub pa yis //
NK026(la)001:15548: dpal chen karma he rur sprul //
NK026(la)001:15549: byang gi gnod sbyin srin po btul //
NK026(la)001:15551: rigs kyi yum chen lnga rnams kyis //
NK026(la)001:15552: khro moo chen mo lnga ru sprul //
NK026(la)001:15553: srin mo chen mo lnga rnams btul //
NK026(la)001:15554: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK026(la)001:15555: sngon gyi dam las ma g.yel bar //
NK026(la)001:15556: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK026(la)001:15557: thugs dam chen po ji bzhin du //
NK026(la)001:15558: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15560: chos skyong gi mchod gtor rnams kyang gtsang sar zhal nang du bstan te 'bul lo //
NK026(la)001:15562: lhag ma btang ste zhes gsungs pa grub nas /
NK026(la)001:15563: gnyis pa brtan ma bskyang ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15564: phyi rol tu bya bar gsungs pa spro na phyir bya /
NK026(la)001:15565: mi spro na sgrub khang nas kyang rung ste /
NK026(la)001:15566: snod rnams chang gis bshal te gcig tu bsdus pa'i
NK026(la)001:15567: khar dpal gyi gtor ma'i mtheb skyu bsdus te blug
NK026(la)001:15569: +aahh+aum gis byin gyis brlabs te btang ba'i tshul ni /
NK026(la)001:15572: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai ru ka h+aum a a a h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:15573: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen he ru ka yi 'khor /
NK026(la)001:15574: nag mo chen mo bzhin mi sdug gi bu mo bdud mo chen mo bzhi /
NK026(la)001:15575: dmar mo khro gnyer can gyi bu mo gnod sbyin ma chen mo bzhi /
NK026(la)001:15576: dkar mo bzhin bzang ma'i bu mo sman btsun ma chen mo bzhi /
NK026(la)001:15577: bod khams skyong ba'i brtan ma bcu gnyis 'khor zhing gi rdul snyed dang bcas pa /
NK026(la)001:15578: sngon gyi thugs dam las ma 'da' bar dpal chen po'i bka' yi pham phab blang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15579: sgrub pa po'i stong grogs la gshegs shig /
NK026(la)001:15580: d+aa ki ni h+aum dzah e a ral+li hrim hrimhh+aum /
NK026(la)001:15581: bka' yi tshogs dang bcas nyid du //
NK026(la)001:15582: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha' yi //
NK026(la)001:15583: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK026(la)001:15584: 'dir spyon dam skongs mchod pa bzhes //
NK026(la)001:15585: bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK026(la)001:15586: dpal ldan ha ri rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK026(la)001:15587: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK026(la)001:15588: 'brog chen 'khor 'dul rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso //
NK026(la)001:15589: bdud mo chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK026(la)001:15590: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs te //
NK026(la)001:15591: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:15592: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:15593: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK026(la)001:15594: 'dir byon dam skongs mchod pa bzhes //
NK026(la)001:15595: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15596: gangs dkar sha med rdo rje g.yu bun ma //
NK026(la)001:15597: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK026(la)001:15598: gser chen mkha' lding rdo rje rlung mo che //
NK026(la)001:15599: rma ri rab 'byams rdo rje drag mo rgyal //
NK026(la)001:15600: gnod sbyin chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK026(la)001:15601: sngon gyi thugs dam bran g.yog mang po'i lhab lhub
NK026(la)001:15602: mang po'i sil snyan mang po'i 'dir byon dam skongs
NK026(la)001:15603: bcol ba'i phrin las kong btsun de mo rdo rje
NK026(la)001:15604: bod khams skyong // btsan la la rol rdo rje sman cig ma //
NK026(la)001:15605: sman btsun ug chos rdo rje g.yar mo bsil //
NK026(la)001:15606: g.yu yi dril bu rdo rje zu le ma //
NK026(la)001:15607: sman btsun chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK026(la)001:15608: sngon gyi thugs dam bran g.yog mang po'i lhab lhub
NK026(la)001:15609: mang po'i sil snyan mang po'i 'dir byon dam skongs
NK026(la)001:15610: bcol ba'i phrin las slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis
NK026(la)001:15611: // a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK026(la)001:15612: rnam lnga zhing gi mchog bkram nas //
NK026(la)001:15613: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK026(la)001:15614: zhing chen bsgyel ba'i gdan steng du //
NK026(la)001:15615: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK026(la)001:15616: sgrub pa po yi grogs bya zhes //
NK026(la)001:15617: thar pa thob phyir ming yang btags //
NK026(la)001:15618: nad rnams thams cad bzlog pa dang //
NK026(la)001:15619: dgra bgegs thams cad 'dul ba dang //
NK026(la)001:15620: bsam pa thams cad sgrub bo zhes //
NK026(la)001:15621: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK026(la)001:15622: dam tshig dag la khyod ma 'da' //
NK026(la)001:15623: gal te dam las 'das gyur na //
NK026(la)001:15624: khro bo yak+sha me dbal gyis //
NK026(la)001:15625: snying gi dkyil nas khrag drangs nas //
NK026(la)001:15627: de bas thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK026(la)001:15628: 'dir byin dam skongs mchod pa bzhes //
NK026(la)001:15629: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15635: ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK026(la)001:15636: brtan ma chen mo bcu gnyis kyi zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:15637: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK026(la)001:15639: brtan ma chen mo bcu gnyis la phrin las su gsol ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15640: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gi sdang ba'i dgra thul /
NK026(la)001:15645: dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK026(la)001:15647: rgyal ba mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:15648: dam can thugs dam skongs gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:15649: pha ma la sogs 'gro drug la //
NK026(la)001:15650: tshad med gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK026(la)001:15651: longs spyod ldan zhing tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK026(la)001:15652: thams cad sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK026(la)001:15653: gsum pa las bzhi'i bro bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15654: gtong gzhong kha sbubs pa'i steng du rnal 'byor pa
NK026(la)001:15655: rnams lag g.yas steng du byas pa'i mdzub mo gnyis
NK026(la)001:15656: bsnol te sbrel ba bro ra zlum por byas la
NK026(la)001:15658: yam ram tsakra dz+wa la ram b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi
NK026(la)001:15659: shud+d+he badz+ra b+han+d+ha s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+dala ti ra bam
NK026(la)001:15660: / bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15662: 'dir dmigs pa rnams gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK026(la)001:15663: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang chog sgrol chen sangs rgyas
NK026(la)001:15664: rin chen gyis mdzad pa las 'di ltar gyis mdzad
NK026(la)001:15666: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dkar po zlum po 'khor lo dang /
NK026(la)001:15667: me dpung gis brgyan pa 'byams klas par gyur pa'i
NK026(la)001:15668: nang du bcud kyi sems can thams cad bud+d+ha khrag
NK026(la)001:15669: 'thung gi lha tshogs phyag na 'khor lo bsnams pa
NK026(la)001:15670: 'od dang sprul pa dkar po 'phro ba /
NK026(la)001:15671: phyogs bcu'i stong khams rdul phra mo snyed thon pas
NK026(la)001:15672: stong gsum khengs pas zhi ba'i las la thogs pa
NK026(la)001:15674: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:15676: yud tsam gyis ni zhi mdzad pa //
NK026(la)001:15677: zhi ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15679: s+t+wam b+ha ni s+t+wam b+ha ni h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15680: gri h+na pa ya gri h+na pa ya h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15682: b+ha ga wa na bid+y+aa r+aa dza h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:15683: hoh bcom ldan 'das bud+d+ha he ru ka 'kho dang
NK026(la)001:15684: bcas pa'i lha tshogs la phrin las snyan du gsol
NK026(la)001:15685: ba ni / bdag cag rnams kyi sdang ba'i dgra
NK026(la)001:15686: dang gnod pa'i bgegs dang ya ma dam sri la
NK026(la)001:15687: sogs pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad zhi
NK026(la)001:15689: sh+aan+tinga ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:15690: zhi ba'i gdul byar ma gyur pa rnams drag po'i bros tshar bcad pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15691: mathe'u chung sbrel ba'i bro ra gru gsum byas te /
NK026(la)001:15692: snod kyi 'jig rten mthing nag gru gsum me dpung dang rdo rjes brgyan par gyur /
NK026(la)001:15693: bcud kyi sems can badz+ra khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs
NK026(la)001:15694: phyag na rdo rje bsnams pa 'od dang sprul pa
NK026(la)001:15696: drag po'i las la thogs pa med par gyur /
NK026(la)001:15697: e yam dz+wa la ram b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he
NK026(la)001:15698: badz+ra b+han+d+ha s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma man+dala ti ra bam
NK026(la)001:15699: / badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15701: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:15703: thal ba'i rdul du brlag nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:15704: drag po'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15706: hoh bcom ldan 'das badz+ra he ru ka 'khor dang
NK026(la)001:15707: bcas pa rnams la phrin las su bcol ba ni
NK026(la)001:15708: / bdag cag rnams la sdang ba'i dgra /
NK026(la)001:15710: bsam sbyor ngan pa byed pa thams cad thal ba bzhin du brlag pa'i phrin las mdzad du gsol /
NK026(la)001:15711: rak+sha m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK026(la)001:15712: drag po'i gdul byar ma gyur pa rnams dbang gi bros dbang du bsdu ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15713: srin mdzub sbrel ba'i bro ra zla gam du byas la /
NK026(la)001:15714: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten zla gam dmar po dbang
NK026(la)001:15715: gi dkyil 'khor pad+ma dang me dpung gis mtshan pa
NK026(la)001:15716: / nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad pad+ma khrag
NK026(la)001:15717: 'thung gi lha tshogs phyag na pad+ma bsnams pa 'od
NK026(la)001:15718: dang sprul pa dmar nag 'phro ba /
NK026(la)001:15719: thams cad dbang du sdud pa'i las la thogs pa med par gyur /
NK026(la)001:15720: bam ram pad+ma dz+wa la ram b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi
NK026(la)001:15721: shud+d+he pad+ma b+han+d+ha s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na man+dala ti ra bam
NK026(la)001:15722: / pad+ma sh+ri he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15724: h+r+ai h+r+ai h+r+aih 'dod chags rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:15726: thams cad dbang du bsdus nas kyang //
NK026(la)001:15727: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK026(la)001:15729: hoh bcom ldan 'das pad+ma he ru ka 'khor dang
NK026(la)001:15730: bcas pa'i lha tshogs rnams la phrin las su gsol
NK026(la)001:15731: ba ni / bdag cag rnams la mi phan pa
NK026(la)001:15732: dang mi mdza' ba la sogs pa thams cad dbang
NK026(la)001:15734: p+aa sha ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:15735: de ltar thams cad dbang du bsdus nas rgyas pa'i bro bya ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15736: gung mo gnyis sbrel ba'i bro ra gru bzhir byas la /
NK026(la)001:15737: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten gru bzhi ser nag rgyas
NK026(la)001:15738: pa'i dkyil 'khor rin po che dang me dpung gis
NK026(la)001:15739: mtshan pa / nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad
NK026(la)001:15740: rat+na khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs phyag na rin po
NK026(la)001:15741: che bsnams pa 'od dang sprul pa ser nag 'bar
NK026(la)001:15742: ba chen po'i yon tan rgyas pa'i phrin las thogs
NK026(la)001:15744: mam ram rat+na dz+wa la ram b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi
NK026(la)001:15745: shud+d+he rat+na b+han+d+ha s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+dala ti ra bam
NK026(la)001:15746: / rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK026(la)001:15749: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK026(la)001:15751: dpal dang gzi brjid chen po rnams //
NK026(la)001:15752: yud tsam gyis ni rgyas 'gyur mdzod //
NK026(la)001:15754: hoh bcom ldan rat+na he ru ka 'khor dang bcas
NK026(la)001:15755: pa'i lha tshogs rnams la phrin las su gsol ba
NK026(la)001:15756: ni / rnal 'byor pa bdag cag rnams kyi tshe
NK026(la)001:15757: dang longs spyod dpal dang gzi brjid zla ba yar
NK026(la)001:15758: gyi ngo bzhin du 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i phrin las
NK026(la)001:15759: ni / mdzad du gsol / push+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK026(la)001:15761: de nas nam langs pa dang dkyil 'khor bsdus la /
NK026(la)001:15763: bzhi pa mchod bstod lhag chad bskang zhing bzod par gsol nas dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15764: dkyil 'khor chen po'i mchod pa rnams gsar du bshams shing /
NK026(la)001:15766: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK026(la)001:15767: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyi //
NK026(la)001:15768: zhes sogs nas bzung chu gnyis dang /
NK026(la)001:15769: bzhi bsnol gyis gtang rag gi tshul du mchod cing rol mo'i sgra rgya cher bya /
NK026(la)001:15771: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK026(la)001:15772: zhes sogs kyi zhi bstod dang /
NK026(la)001:15774: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK026(la)001:15775: zhes sogs kyi khro bstod bya /
NK026(la)001:15776: lhag chad bskang phyir yig brgya ci mang bzlas shing mthar /
NK026(la)001:15777: mgon po thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa khyed rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK026(la)001:15778: bdag cag las dang po pa'i gang zag gi dbang du gyur pas /
NK026(la)001:15779: dkyil 'khor chen po'i mchod sgrub ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK026(la)001:15780: dbang bskur ba'i las bgyis pa la 'gal 'khrul nongs
NK026(la)001:15781: pa'i tshogs ci mchis pa thams cad bzod par mdzad
NK026(la)001:15782: de / byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK026(la)001:15785: ma 'byor pa dang nyams pa dang //
NK026(la)001:15786: zhes sogs tshigs brgyad kyi sgo nas kyang bzod par gsol la /
NK026(la)001:15787: dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni g.yung ston chen po dang sgrol chen sangs rin gyis /
NK026(la)001:15788: badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol bar gsungs pa'i phyir na //
NK026(la)001:15789: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK026(la)001:15790: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK026(la)001:15791: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang /
NK026(la)001:15792: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK026(la)001:15794: lag len dang dmigs pa'i rim pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15798: dbang phyug gi rdo rje bsnams te shar sgo'i tshangs thig gi lam nas h+aum zhes brjod cing /
NK026(la)001:15799: dbus kyi gtso bo'i gnas kyi bar du bsdu /
NK026(la)001:15800: de bzhin du lho dang nub dang byang nas kyang ste /
NK026(la)001:15801: gzhal yas khang lha la bsdu /
NK026(la)001:15803: gtso bo thugs ka'i sa bon la bsdu /
NK026(la)001:15804: sa bon yang n+aa da la bsdus te /
NK026(la)001:15805: de yang me long la has btab pa bzhin du
NK026(la)001:15806: yal nas stong pa nyid kyi ngang la cung zhig
NK026(la)001:15807: bzhag / rdul tshon rnams bsdus la /
NK026(la)001:15808: chu bo chen po'am ri mthon po'i rtse la bskyal /
NK026(la)001:15810: bum chu don du gnyer ba yod na sbyin /
NK026(la)001:15811: med na mis mi 'gom pa'i sar dbo /
NK026(la)001:15812: rdzas dang yo byad rnams dben pa'i sar tshags bya'o //
NK026(la)001:15814: badz+ra muhbarjoda ma thag tu rdo rje slob dpon gyis
NK026(la)001:15815: rdo rje bsnams te rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor gong
NK026(la)001:15816: bzhin bsdu la rdzogs rim gyi dmigs pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15817: rdul tshon gyi ye shes pa gshegs /
NK026(la)001:15818: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu /
NK026(la)001:15819: bdag mdun bum gsum sgyu ma'i rol pa tsam du
NK026(la)001:15820: snang ba de nyid kyi gzhal yas khang rnams lha
NK026(la)001:15821: la bsdu / lha rnams kyang 'khor gtso bo la /
NK026(la)001:15822: gtso bo thugs srog h+aum la /
NK026(la)001:15830: n+aa da yang je phral yal te mthar mi dmigs ka dag chen po'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK026(la)001:15831: g.yung ston chen po'i gsung gong gi 'phros las /
NK026(la)001:15832: de ltar rtag pa'i mtha' bsal nas /
NK026(la)001:15833: slar yang chad pa'i mtha' bsal ba'i don du skad
NK026(la)001:15834: cig dran rdzogs su yi dam gang yin du rang
NK026(la)001:15839: yi dam gyi lha'i nga rgyal dang mi 'bral ba'i ngang nas mtshams phur sogs bsdu bar gsungs shing /
NK026(la)001:15841: chad pa'i mtha' bsal ba'i don du skad cig dran rdzogs su he ru kar gsal btab /
NK026(la)001:15842: ces gsungs pa legs par snang ste /
NK026(la)001:15843: stong nyid kyi ngang las chu las nya ldang ba'i
NK026(la)001:15844: tshul gyis rang nyid che mchog dbu nyer gcig phyag
NK026(la)001:15845: zhe gnyis pa'am / dbang mchog dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa'am /
NK026(la)001:15846: badz+ra he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug pa'am /
NK026(la)001:15847: rgyu'i he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'am /
NK026(la)001:15848: 'bras bu'i he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug pa sogs gang mos kyi rnam par blta'o //
NK026(la)001:15849: go bgo lus bsrung sogs mkhas grub se ston chen
NK026(la)001:15850: po rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi bzhed pa ltar legs
NK026(la)001:15851: te / de ltar rang nyid he ru kar gsal ba'i spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i ham /
NK026(la)001:15852: de las 'phros 'dus lus rdo rje'i go khrab kyis gtams par gyur /
NK026(la)001:15853: a tsan+d+ra man+da la ham s+pha ra na phata /
NK026(la)001:15855: rdo rje go cha'i rgyas dpral bar gtugs la /
NK026(la)001:15856: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha rak+sha /
NK026(la)001:15857: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin dang mi 'chi thal sbyor gnyis kyis gsang gnas su bzhengs /
NK026(la)001:15858: lte ba dang bcu drug mdor bcings /
NK026(la)001:15859: snying kha dang tshigs pa bdun par bcings /
NK026(la)001:15861: dpral ba dang ltag khung du bcings /
NK026(la)001:15862: spyi bor bzhengs pa'i tshul gyis bsrung bar byas /
NK026(la)001:15863: rdo rje khu tshur gyi mdzub mo gnyis khro bo
NK026(la)001:15864: de gnyis kyi rang bzhin gyis gnas de dag tu
NK026(la)001:15866: trum zhes lan drug gis gnas so sor phyag rgya bsnol te bsrung ngo //
NK026(la)001:15867: dar dkar pos gnas dgur mdud de bsrung bar bsam
NK026(la)001:15868: la lag gnyis spyi bor rtse sprad pa bsham bsdabs
NK026(la)001:15869: te badz+ra tu sh+ya hoh dbang bsnan pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15870: rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsam la rat+na mu ku ta tram tram tram tram tram /
NK026(la)001:15871: +aar+ya lam bo d+ha ra badz+ra d+r+ai sh+ya hoh de
NK026(la)001:15872: nas lha'i nga rgyal la gnas pas 'jug don rnams
NK026(la)001:15875: dug gsum gyi sbyin sreg bya /
NK026(la)001:15878: gtor ma tsho gsum du bcad pa'i dang po de
NK026(la)001:15879: chos kyi gtor ma zhes bya ste gter du sba
NK026(la)001:15880: / bar pa ye shes rol pa'i gtor ma zhes bya ste sbyin sreg bya /
NK026(la)001:15881: mtha' ma de thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor ma zhes
NK026(la)001:15882: bya ste las mkhan gyis mkha' 'gro chos skyong mchod
NK026(la)001:15883: / ces gsungs pa'i don ltar sbyin sreg bya ba'i dgongs pa yin nam snyam mo //
NK026(la)001:15885: dngos grub kyi gter sba ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15886: dpal gyi rtsar zhes gsungs pa dkyil 'khor gyi 'og
NK026(la)001:15887: gam yang na sgrub khang mdzod phugs gang bder dong
NK026(la)001:15888: zla gam brus la dmar por byug /
NK026(la)001:15889: sman raka gis chag chag gdab /
NK026(la)001:15890: b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang du bskyed la /
NK026(la)001:15891: de'i nang du sgrub gtor gyi dum bu dang /
NK026(la)001:15892: 'bru sman dar zab rin po che sna tshogs kyis bkang ba'i bum gter gzhug ste /
NK026(la)001:15896: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15897: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15898: bdud rtsi lnga yi gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15899: he ru ka yis mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15900: ye shes lnga yi don rtogs shog /
NK026(la)001:15901: ye shes lnga yis rgyab gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15902: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15903: dbyings phyug lnga yi gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15904: sha khrag rus pa'i gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15905: yum chen lnga yis mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15906: gsang ba'i mdzod dang 'phrad par shog /
NK026(la)001:15907: skye med dbyings kyis rgyas gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15908: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15909: khro mo brgyad kyi gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15910: rnam shes brgyad kyi gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15911: ma mo brgyad kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15912: gsang ba'i rdzas dang 'phrad par shog /
NK026(la)001:15913: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15914: phra men brgyad kyi gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15915: gsang ba'i dam rdzas gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15916: mgo brnyan rnams kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15918: rang rig ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15919: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15920: sgo ma bzhi yi gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15921: rnam thar bzhi yi gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15922: khro mo bzhi yis mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15923: bdud bzhi'i 'jigs las thar bar shog /
NK026(la)001:15924: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15925: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15926: dbang phyug ma yi gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15927: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15928: dam can rnams kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15929: bdud rtsi'i zas dang 'phrad par shog /
NK026(la)001:15930: rang rig ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15931: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK026(la)001:15932: khro bo bcu yi gter sbed do //
NK026(la)001:15933: dam rdzas rus pa'i gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15934: khrag 'thung rnams kyi mdun bsus nas //
NK026(la)001:15935: rdo rje'i gral dang 'phrad par shog /
NK026(la)001:15936: rang rig ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK026(la)001:15937: rdo rje slob dpon mched lcam gyis //
NK026(la)001:15938: dam rdzas gtor ma'i gter sbas pas //
NK026(la)001:15939: zag med gter la longs spyod cing //
NK026(la)001:15940: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dngos grub rnams //
NK026(la)001:15941: 'dod yon lnga yi longs spyod kyis //
NK026(la)001:15944: de nas phyi rol rgyal chen gyi tho'i rtsar /
NK026(la)001:15945: dkar gtor cha bzhi bsham la /
NK026(la)001:15946: byang nas rim pa bzhin gtor ma dang mchod pa lnga mtshan sngags kyi mthar btags te phul la /
NK026(la)001:15947: ri rgyal lhun po mtshan bzhis gong gi tho 'dzugs kyi skabs ltar bstod cing /
NK026(la)001:15948: ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol /
NK026(la)001:15950: phyogs skyong bcu'i tho yod kyang mchod gtor rnams rang sngags kyis phul la /
NK026(la)001:15951: dbang rdor gyis bstod de gshegs su gsol zhing tho bsgyel ba 'gre /
NK026(la)001:15952: mtshams phur bcu dang ye shes lha'i sgo byang gnyis la sku khrus gsol la dben sar bzhugs so //
NK026(la)001:15953: bar chad bgegs kyi sgo byang de la mchog phur
NK026(la)001:15954: dar gyi cod pan gcig tu bdud rtsi 'khyil bar
NK026(la)001:15955: bskyed / sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab la /
NK026(la)001:15956: sgo byang dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu bcug pa la phur pa de gdab /
NK026(la)001:15957: bdud rtsi thigs gcig blug nas byang chub kyi sems ma skyes bar du mi thar bar bsam mo //
NK026(la)001:15958: des las rjes bkra shis par 'gyur ro //
NK026(la)001:15959: zhes gsungs kyang thog mar sgo them du 'dogs pa'i dbang gis 'di ltar bshad pa yin la /
NK026(la)001:15960: 'dir gong du mnan zin pas 'di ltar bya mi dgos /
NK026(la)001:15961: lnga ba bsngo smon bkra shis brjod cing dga' ston la rol pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15966: zhes gsungs pas mdo rgyud dri ma med pa dang
NK026(la)001:15967: rang gzhung las ji ltar byung ba'i bsngo smon dang
NK026(la)001:15968: bkra shis kyi rim pa rgya cher bya zhing dga'
NK026(la)001:15969: ston bzang po la yang longs spyad par bya'o //
NK026(la)001:15970: rtsa bar gsal kha ma byung yang /
NK026(la)001:15971: glan ston gyis zhag gcig gnas bsrung /
NK026(la)001:15972: zhes pa shin tu 'thad pas zhag gcig gi bar
NK026(la)001:15973: dpon slob thams cad gzhan du mi 'gro bar zhi
NK026(la)001:15974: khro'i las byang yang gyer ba ni /
NK026(la)001:15975: slad nas sgrub pa byar rung ba'i dgos pa yod par gsung ngo //
NK026(la)001:15976: de nas rtsa ba'i sbyar byang bstan pa ni /
NK026(la)001:15977: mdo dbang rgya chen rgya mtsho lta bu las //
NK026(la)001:15978: bdag blo'i rnam dpyod ngang mchu lta bu'i blos //
NK026(la)001:15979: 'thor zhing du mar snang ba'i las khrigs rnams //
NK026(la)001:15980: gcig tu bsdebs pa'i dbang chog rin chen phreng //
NK026(la)001:15981: bgyis pa'i dge ba gang thob bsod nams kyis //
NK026(la)001:15982: khams gsum 'gro kun rdo rje 'dzin thob shog /
NK026(la)001:15983: ces pa mdo'i dbang chog rgya che zhing du mar
NK026(la)001:15984: snang yang phyag len cung zhig mi 'dra ba 'dug
NK026(la)001:15985: pas 'di ni zur hwam sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis de
NK026(la)001:15986: rnams kyi nang nas cho ga dbang bskur gyi phyag
NK026(la)001:15987: len mang du mdzad pa mthong ba dang /
NK026(la)001:15988: yang de nyid kyis khyod kyis mdo dbang chog khrigs
NK026(la)001:15989: bde ba zhig 'di ltar gyis gsungs pa'i bka' dang
NK026(la)001:15990: / bdag blo'i rnam dpyod kyis gu ru lugs su
NK026(la)001:15991: bltas pas chog pa dbang chog rin po che'i phreng
NK026(la)001:15993: chos smra ba'i dge sbyong gnyal pa bde legs pa
NK026(la)001:15994: zhes bya bas zur thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag len
NK026(la)001:15995: ji lta ba bzhin du g.yas ru yang dben du
NK026(la)001:15997: zhes yongs su rdzogs par bstan pa'i rim pa'o //
NK026(la)001:15999: dpal ldan tshogs gnyis yon tan sprin phung las //
NK026(la)001:16000: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i gru char legs phab ste //
NK026(la)001:16001: skal bzang gdul bya'i lo tog rgyas mdzad pa'i //
NK026(la)001:16002: rig 'dzin klu dbang tshogs la slar yang 'dud //
NK026(la)001:16003: rnam mang mdo rgyud dgongs don rgya mtsho'i 'jings //
NK026(la)001:16004: bdag blo'i skyogs kyis bcu bar nus min yang //
NK026(la)001:16005: yongs 'dzin gdengs can tshogs kyi bka' drin las //
NK026(la)001:16006: mdo dbang chos kyi rgya mtsho'i gting mtha' rnyed //
NK026(la)001:16007: sngon chad mkhas grub rig 'dzin bgrangs yas pas //
NK026(la)001:16008: mdo dbang smin grol chu gter 'di bsten nas //
NK026(la)001:16009: skal ldan gdul bya'i yid mtshor legs phab pas //
NK026(la)001:16010: snga 'gyur chos kyi rgya mtsho cher 'phel mod //
NK026(la)001:16011: 'on kyang me khyer nyi zla'i gral bsnyeg ltar //
NK026(la)001:16012: mi shes mngon rlom gyis dregs skye bo 'gas //
NK026(la)001:16013: ma rtogs log par rtog pa'i yur ba las //
NK026(la)001:16014: drangs te gzhung lugs chu bo rnam par dkrugs //
NK026(la)001:16015: de phyir yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i srol chen po'i //
NK026(la)001:16016: mdo dbang chos kyi nyi ma nub ri'i rtser //
NK026(la)001:16017: gzhol bar phyogs kyang kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i dbang //
NK026(la)001:16018: thugs rje'i nus pas thub bstan mkha' la bzung //
NK026(la)001:16019: khyad par grub mchog rje btsun mnga' ris pa'i //
NK026(la)001:16020: brgyud srol nges par grub brnyes zur lugs kyi //
NK026(la)001:16021: snyan brgyud ma nyams dbang gi chu bo'i rgyun //
NK026(la)001:16022: 'dzin skyong spel ba'i byed por bdag dbang bskur //
NK026(la)001:16023: 'on te skyes sbyangs blo gros cher phra yang //
NK026(la)001:16024: khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang dngos sman lung pa'i //
NK026(la)001:16025: drin las phyogs 'dir smra ba'i spobs pa ldan //
NK026(la)001:16026: de phyir tshul 'dir spro ba lhod ma gyur //
NK026(la)001:16027: de lta na yang sngon las bla gzugs kyis //
NK026(la)001:16028: rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzi'i khol por bdag gyur pas //
NK026(la)001:16029: zin med bstan pa 'dzin skyong yin no lo'i //
NK026(la)001:16030: bya mang g.yeng ba'i dbang gis yun ring lus //
NK026(la)001:16031: dam pa'i chos dang tshe 'di'i 'dun thabs gnyis //
NK026(la)001:16032: zong du bkram na tshe 'di don gnyer ba //
NK026(la)001:16033: gcig sems slob ma'i rgyud rengs tha rgod la //
NK026(la)001:16034: smin grol gdams pa'i char gyis ci zhig phan //
NK026(la)001:16035: 'di brtsams rang nyid ngal ba'i dge 'bras las //
NK026(la)001:16036: gzhan pa'i nying dgos yod par mi sems kyang //
NK026(la)001:16037: grangs med skye bar rjes bzung yongs 'dzin gyis //
NK026(la)001:16038: bka' stsal gser gyi cod pan gus pas blangs //
NK026(la)001:16039: ma nges snod ldan slob ma nyin skar tsam //
NK026(la)001:16040: 'byung bar srid dang mdo sngags zab don bcud //
NK026(la)001:16041: chos tshul mchog 'di nub par phangs pa'i phyir //
NK026(la)001:16042: snying stobs brtson pa'i lhag bsam dag pas bkod //
NK026(la)001:16043: 'khrul med yongs 'dzin ded dpon mchog bsten cing //
NK026(la)001:16044: mdo sgyu sems kyi rgya mtsho cher zhugs te //
NK026(la)001:16045: rnam dpyod brtson pa'i gru chags rab ldan pas //
NK026(la)001:16046: bsam 'phel dgos 'byung nor mchog bdag gis lon //
NK026(la)001:16047: lung rtogs snying po snga 'gyur chos kyi gzhung //
NK026(la)001:16048: smin grol dgos 'dod mchog ster yid bzhin dbang //
NK026(la)001:16049: mi zad re skong bstan 'gror mchod sbyin slad //
NK026(la)001:16050: thub bstan rgyal mtshan rtse mor bdag gis bkod //
NK026(la)001:16051: 'di ni skyabs mchog rnams kyi mchod sprin te //
NK026(la)001:16052: bstan pa pad+ma'i gnyen gyur nyin byed 'di //
NK026(la)001:16053: skal bzang mgron la bdud rtsi'i mchod sbyin 'di //
NK026(la)001:16054: thub bstan 'dzin skyong spel ba'ang 'di kho na //
NK026(la)001:16055: rig 'dzin grub pa'i tshogs kyi dga' ston 'di //
NK026(la)001:16056: bshes gnyen mkhas grub rnams kyi bzung bya 'di //
NK026(la)001:16057: sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi yi lam //
NK026(la)001:16058: thub bstan yongs rdzogs lus kyang 'di kho na //
NK026(la)001:16059: de phyir yid bzhin nor 'dra'i dam chos 'di //
NK026(la)001:16060: skyes chen bstan 'dzin yongs kyis legs bzung ste //
NK026(la)001:16061: 'chad nyan thos bsam sgom pa'i byi dor dang //
NK026(la)001:16062: bstan 'gror dge legs dgos 'dod stsol bar mdzod //
NK026(la)001:16063: 'di 'dra'i lam bzang dri med mchog rnyed nas //
NK026(la)001:16064: sna tshogs grub mtha'i 'jug sgo gzhan dag la //
NK026(la)001:16065: 'gram chu mi ldang lugs 'dir rab 'bad nas //
NK026(la)001:16066: rang gzhan don gnyis sgrub la 'bad par rigs //
NK026(la)001:16067: rnyed daka'i dal 'byor phun tshogs legs thob cing //
NK026(la)001:16068: 'khrul med bstan pa'i snying po 'dir zhugs nas //
NK026(la)001:16069: mthu gtad sel dang grong chog rnyed 'tshol la //
NK026(la)001:16070: 'phyan rnams gser gling stong log cis mi mtshungs //
NK026(la)001:16071: de phyir rigs rus skye bar snga 'gyur gyi //
NK026(la)001:16072: bstan 'dzin chos kyi khrir bzhugs skyes chen rnams //
NK026(la)001:16073: 'dus pa mdo yi smin grol mdzod 'di la //
NK026(la)001:16074: gces 'dzin skyong zhig spel bar gsol ba lags //
NK026(la)001:16075: sde snod gsum gyi rtsa ba rab brtan cing //
NK026(la)001:16076: phyi rgyud sde gsum yal 'dab khyon yangs pa //
NK026(la)001:16077: rnam gsum yo ga'i 'bras bu g.yur za ba'i //
NK026(la)001:16078: thub bstan dpag bsam ljon shing 'di bzung mdzod //
NK026(la)001:16079: smin grol nos pas mdo sngags lam srol shes //
NK026(la)001:16080: nyams su blangs pas grub gnyis 'dod rgur 'jo //
NK026(la)001:16081: nyan bshad bgyis pas lung rtogs chos kun 'dus //
NK026(la)001:16082: dam chos rgya mtsho'i gter 'di longs spyod mdzod //
NK026(la)001:16083: dge ba 'di yis rnam gsum srid par 'khyams pa'i 'gro //
NK026(la)001:16084: sdug bsngal gsum gyis 'ching ba las grol gdod ma'i mgon //
NK026(la)001:16085: khyab bdag kun bzang 'od phung chen por yongs grol te //
NK026(la)001:16086: phyogs dus kun tu dge legs dpal gyis 'tsho bar shog /
NK026(la)001:16087: khyad par sa gsum 'gro ba'i gtsug rgyan thams cad mkhyen //
NK026(la)001:16088: za hor rig 'dzin khyab bdag bla med rdo rje rtsal //
NK026(la)001:16089: ngag gi dbang phyug blo bzang rgya mtsho'i zhabs pad mchog /
NK026(la)001:16090: bskal pa rgya mtshor rdo rje'i khri la brtan gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:16091: bka' drin mnyam med zur chen chos dbyings rang grol rje //
NK026(la)001:16092: rdo rje 'chang dngos mgon po bsod nams mchog ldan zhabs //
NK026(la)001:16093: 'khor lo'i dbang phyug sman lung blo mchog rdo rje sogs //
NK026(la)001:16094: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa mchog tu rdzogs gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:16095: rgyal bstan ris med rnam dag mdo sngags bstan pa nyid //
NK026(la)001:16096: bshad dang sgrub pa'i sgo nas yun du gnas pa dang //
NK026(la)001:16097: de 'dzin skyes chen mkhas btsun grub pa 'dus sder bcas //
NK026(la)001:16098: 'phel rgyas rab brtan chos dang bkra shis 'phel bar shog /
NK026(la)001:16099: yangs pa'i rgyal khams chos bzhin skyong ba'i mi dbang rnams //
NK026(la)001:16100: byams pa'i stobs bzhin sa 'di rdzogs ldan ltar skyong bas //
NK026(la)001:16101: rgyal srid 'byor rgyas bde zhing lo legs gnod pa med //
NK026(la)001:16102: bstan la gus mchod 'gro rnams bde zhing chos spyod shog /
NK026(la)001:16103: bdag kyang tshe rabs kun tu dal 'byor lus thob cing //
NK026(la)001:16104: bstan la rab byung sdom pa gsum ldan chos bzhin spyod //
NK026(la)001:16105: smin grol gdams pas legs smin rim gnyis lam bsgoms te //
NK026(la)001:16106: zung 'jug kun bzang gdod ma'i mgon po'i sa thob shog /
NK026(la)001:16107: tshe 'di'i grags 'byor rnyed bkur chos brgyad rab spangs te //
NK026(la)001:16108: rgyal bas rab basngagasa dben pa'i ri ngogs nyams dga' bar //
NK026(la)001:16109: rang byung brag ri'i khang brtsegs lo ma'i 'dab gur can //
NK026(la)001:16110: mthong na dga' ba'i dka' thub nags tshal bsten par shog /
NK026(la)001:16111: der ni mi bsrun skye bo ngan rnams mi mthong zhing //
NK026(la)001:16112: dad gshin dkor rdzas rmi lam du yang mi myong bar //
NK026(la)001:16113: dka' thub zas dang ting 'dzin dga' bde'i dpal gyis 'tsho //
NK026(la)001:16114: gcig pur bsam gtan sogs pa'i skal bzang de thob shog /
NK026(la)001:16115: dngos brgyud pha ma lhag par bzang ngan 'brel thogs bcas //
NK026(la)001:16116: ma lus don yod 'og min tshogs chen dkyil 'khor du //
NK026(la)001:16117: tshom bu gcig par rig 'dzin grub pa'i sa thob nas //
NK026(la)001:16118: don gnyis lhun grub rdo rje theg pa'i lam bgrod shog /
NK026(la)001:16119: 'di brtsams ngal ba las byung dge ba de dag kyang //
NK026(la)001:16120: 'gro rnams thun mong byang chub mchog gi rgyur gyur te //
NK026(la)001:16121: gcig tu dkar ba'i dge 'bras bsod nams de yi mthus //
NK026(la)001:16122: spyi dang bye brag bstan 'gro'i sman yon 'di gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:16123: chos tshul 'di nyid 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phrin las gang //
NK026(la)001:16124: dpal ldan ye shes mgon po legs ldan nag po che //
NK026(la)001:16125: lcam dral bka' sdod pho nyar bcas pas gnyer mdzad de //
NK026(la)001:16126: bstan dang de 'dzin bsrung ba'i phrin las mchog sgrub mdzod //
NK026(la)001:16127: thub bstan lha lam tha gru yangs par snga 'gyur gyi //
NK026(la)001:16128: bka' gter nyi zla'i bgrod pa mchog gi rgyun bzang po'i //
NK026(la)001:16129: 'od snang de yis mtha' yas bstan 'gro'i bde legs kun //
NK026(la)001:16130: rmad byung dga' ston bzang pos yongs su khyab gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:16131: phun tshogs nyin mor byed pa'i dge legs rta bdun dbang //
NK026(la)001:16132: srid zhi'i mun sel phan bde'i pad tshal rab rgyas byed //
NK026(la)001:16133: skal bzang yid la mchog ster bkra shis bzang po de //
NK026(la)001:16134: rnam pa kun tu dge legs dpal 'bar bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:16135: rgyal ba sras bcas mkhyen brtse nus pa'i dpal las
NK026(la)001:16136: rab 'ongs rmad byung dam chos bkra shis g.yas su
NK026(la)001:16137: 'khyil ba'i dung // legs bshad mgrin par rab 'khyil
NK026(la)001:16138: bshes gnyen mkhas grub rnams kyis legs bus theg dgu'i
NK026(la)001:16139: chos sgra zab cing snyan pa yis //
NK026(la)001:16140: 'jig rten gsum du rab grags lhar bcas skye rgu'i
NK026(la)001:16141: tshogs kun yongs 'dus rdo rje theg pa'i chos kyi
NK026(la)001:16142: 'khor lo mchog / rab bskor phyogs dus gnas skabs
NK026(la)001:16143: kun tu dge legs dpal gyis yongs khyab bde skyid
NK026(la)001:16144: phun sum tshogs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:16145: de ltar 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi cho ga khrigs
NK026(la)001:16146: su byas pa dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs zhes
NK026(la)001:16148: khams gsum gyi bla ma srid pa gsum gyi 'dren
NK026(la)001:16149: mchog 'gro ba lha dang bcas pa'i skye rgu mtha'
NK026(la)001:16150: dag gi ma 'dris pa'i mdza' bshes chen po dkyil
NK026(la)001:16151: 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag nges pa don gyi rdo
NK026(la)001:16152: rje 'chang kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad
NK026(la)001:16153: mkhyen pa ngag gi dbang phyug blo bzang rgya mtsho'i
NK026(la)001:16154: sdes / bka' stsal gser gyi cod pan mchog gi
NK026(la)001:16155: dbang bskur zhing chog khrigs gsal ba zhig gyis shig
NK026(la)001:16156: ces rang lo nyer bzhi par mdo dbang thob pa'i
NK026(la)001:16157: nyer lnga'i lo la bka' gnang ba dang /
NK026(la)001:16158: rang lo nyer drug par slar yang khyab bdag sman
NK026(la)001:16159: lung pa chen por sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor
NK026(la)001:16160: du smin byed kyi dbang dang /
NK026(la)001:16161: mdo dbang gi phyag bzhes rnams la dogs gcod yig rnying gi lung sogs nos dus bka' las /
NK026(la)001:16162: rgyal dbang mchog gi zhabs drung nas bka' gnang ba
NK026(la)001:16163: ltar rgan po lnga pa'i lam du ma gyur pa'i
NK026(la)001:16164: gong du mdo dbang gi chog khrigs 'chad bde zhing
NK026(la)001:16165: sgroms bzang ba bka' ma'i bstan pa rin po che
NK026(la)001:16166: gso thub pa zhig cis kyang gyis zhes bla ma
NK026(la)001:16167: dam pa gnyis kyi bka' gnang ba ltar de lo
NK026(la)001:16168: nas mchod brjod tsam bris grub kyang /
NK026(la)001:16169: dgos med 'du 'dzi'i rnam g.yeng gi mal du btang
NK026(la)001:16170: snyoms kyi gnyid la yun ring por song ba na
NK026(la)001:16171: rang lo so gsums pa chu glang gi lo /
NK026(la)001:16172: byang gter phur pa rnam gsum gyi dbang chog cig
NK026(la)001:16173: bris pa rgyal dbang mchog gi spyan sngar bstar bas
NK026(la)001:16175: slar yang bka' stsal gyi me tog su wa r+na'i
NK026(la)001:16176: gnang skyes bzang po dang bcas spyi bor lhungs pa
NK026(la)001:16178: yos lor 'jig rten lha mi yan chod kyi shog bu brgya tsam bris pa las /
NK026(la)001:16179: sngar bzhin rnam g.yeng dang lo mtshams sogs kyi dbang las rtsom 'phror lus pa /
NK026(la)001:16180: rang lo so dgu pa sa lug don grub kyi
NK026(la)001:16181: lo sa ga zla ba'i dus chen nas nyan thos
NK026(la)001:16182: kyi theg pa'i 'jug sgo nas bzung bris pa lo
NK026(la)001:16183: de'i ston zla ra ba khrums kyi zla ba la
NK026(la)001:16184: babs pa'i tshe bza' shing gi 'bras bu dang /
NK026(la)001:16185: 'bru rnams kyang smin la rtsi bcud kyang rnam par
NK026(la)001:16186: rgyas pa'i dga' ston la skye rgu rnams longs su
NK026(la)001:16187: spyod pa'i dus / dkar phyogs dga' ba gsum pa
NK026(la)001:16188: res gza' dal 'gro dang rgyu skar gro bzhin can
NK026(la)001:16189: te sa gnyis nang 'phrad dngos grub kyi sbyor ba'i
NK026(la)001:16191: 'og min bla ma'i gdan sa thub bstan mi 'gyur
NK026(la)001:16192: rdo rje'i brag e wam gyi chos gra chen po'i
NK026(la)001:16193: gtsug lag khang du lha rigs kyi dge slong rdo
NK026(la)001:16194: rje 'dzin pa kun bzang pad+ma phrin las kyis legs
NK026(la)001:16195: par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni dol pa 'tsho
NK026(la)001:16196: byed dge slong sman mchog gi bgyis pa'i dge 'dis
NK026(la)001:16197: snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa rin po che phyogs dus
NK026(la)001:16198: gnas skabs thams cad du dar zhing rgyas la yun
NK026(la)001:16199: ring du gnas par gyur cig /
NK026(la)001:16200: sems can khams dang bsam pa'i khyad par nam yang zad med lha lam ngos //
NK026(la)001:16201: theg pa rim dgu'i mchog dman bar mtha' nyi zla gza' skar rab shar ba //
NK026(la)001:16202: go rim ji bzhin 'phyugs med legs bsgrigs khyab bdag drang srong rnga bo che //
NK026(la)001:16203: mdo dang rgyud sde rdzogs par ston mdzad kun tu bzang por mgos phyag 'tshal //
NK026(la)001:16204: dga' rab rdo rje rgyal po dzahl sogs /
NK026(la)001:16205: dag dang ma dag zhing gi pan grub kyi //
NK026(la)001:16206: thugs bcud chu klung rnam bzhi gcig 'dus mtsho //
NK026(la)001:16207: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes basngagasa bya'i yul //
NK026(la)001:16208: khu lung yab sras zur po che chung dang //
NK026(la)001:16209: gsang bdag sgro phug sgrol chen sh+aaka 'byung gi //
NK026(la)001:16210: lha rigs 'jam dbyangs rgyal mtshan bar byon pa //
NK026(la)001:16211: mdo dbang bla brgyud tshar du dngar rnams rgyal //
NK026(la)001:16212: khyad par snga 'gyur bka' gter mtha' dag gi //
NK026(la)001:16213: gdams pa'i bang mdzod rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa //
NK026(la)001:16214: legs ldan mthu yis bdud sde 'joms byed mtshon //
NK026(la)001:16215: rdo rje gdengs mdzad khyod zhabs gtsug na bsten //
NK026(la)001:16216: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug khu dbon gyi //
NK026(la)001:16217: bdag rkyen phrin las chos 'di'i srog mthud mkhan //
NK026(la)001:16218: skyi ston tshe ring dbang po bres pa rje //
NK026(la)001:16219: chos rgyal rdo rje'i rnam par thar la dad //
NK026(la)001:16220: pan chen bi ma la yi thugs rje'i gzugs //
NK026(la)001:16221: gdul bya'i don du mkhas grub zlos gar can //
NK026(la)001:16222: nyang ston blo mchog rdo rje rigs kun gyi //
NK026(la)001:16223: khyab bdag dang po'i mgon po las gzhan ci //
NK026(la)001:16224: sna nam rgod ldem yang srid bag chags mthus //
NK026(la)001:16225: theg dgu'i chos tshul sgo 'byed shing rta che //
NK026(la)001:16226: mchog sprul pad+ma phrin las rnam thar la //
NK026(la)001:16227: gzur gnas phal cher 'dud par gcig tu spro //
NK026(la)001:16228: g.yu 'brug rdzun zog phug steng gzhan phan blos //
NK026(la)001:16229: mang 'khrid gom bkod rgyun bral chu dong du //
NK026(la)001:16230: mthar srog dpral ba'i cho ga yid srubs kyi //
NK026(la)001:16231: stod smad bar du dar dang 'di mi 'dra //
NK026(la)001:16232: nges gsang ring lugs me lce srid rtse'i bar //
NK026(la)001:16233: bsnyeg bshul deng sang thal phung me stag tsam //
NK026(la)001:16234: sbar bar sgo gsum 'bad pa'i bsod nams kyi //
NK026(la)001:16235: phung po'i snod du stong gsum 'di yang chung //
NK026(la)001:16236: sngon dus rgyal blon lo pan chos phyir du //
NK026(la)001:16237: dka' spyad bsam tshe gsar rnying bstan 'dzin deng //
NK026(la)001:16238: phal cher chos brgyad 'khol por 'gran pa'i bang //
NK026(la)001:16239: yangs po'i gom stabs brel la mchi ma bku //
NK026(la)001:16240: la la mkhas btsun grags 'dod sgro gdugs bsgir //
NK026(la)001:16241: 'ga' zhig rngam rdig bzang rdzu'i mngal khur 'dzin //
NK026(la)001:16242: mang dag 'jig rten phal spyod dug rlangs bsten //
NK026(la)001:16243: kye hud snyigs dus rma bya'i tshul 'dis ci //
NK026(la)001:16244: tha snyad rtog ger sbyangs pa gzhon nu'i lus //
NK026(la)001:16245: shes bya'i pha mtha' gzhal ba'i gdong drug can //
NK026(la)001:16246: nges gsal glang po'i mche ba nyer phyung bas //
NK026(la)001:16247: gtan 'dun lang tsho dar lus skal dman mang //
NK026(la)001:16248: gcig tu mi zhen sna tshogs theg pa'i skas //
NK026(la)001:16249: rim par 'dzegs mtha' yi ge tshogs chen gyi //
NK026(la)001:16250: 'khor lo kun 'dus rigs bdag rdo rje 'chang //
NK026(la)001:16251: gzhan du mi sems rig rtsal bla na med //
NK026(la)001:16252: bgrang yas 'khor lo smin byed cho ga'i khrigs //
NK026(la)001:16253: zur lugs dgongs don mdzes rgyan rin chen phreng //
NK026(la)001:16254: rdo rje'i theg mchog bstan pa srid mtha'i bar //
NK026(la)001:16255: mi nub btsas su par gyi mchod sbyin 'dis //
NK026(la)001:16256: khri srong lde'u btsan bzhed phugs gangs ljongs su //
NK026(la)001:16257: mchod gnas sde gnyis bshad sgrub sa bon tshogs //
NK026(la)001:16258: bsod nams zhing sar bskyed bsring bde skyid 'bras //
NK026(la)001:16259: mnga' 'bangs yongs kyi dga' ston la spyod shog /
NK026(la)001:16260: don dam dge sbyong gos dkar ral yur can //
NK026(la)001:16261: gdul bya rjes 'dzin 'dod rnams sel med pa //
NK026(la)001:16262: dbang chu'i rgyun 'dis sgrib bkrus bzhed srol gyi //
NK026(la)001:16263: phrin las phyogs bral rna lung mdzes par shog /
NK026(la)001:16264: yid la kun tu dga' bskyed legs ldan dpyid //
NK026(la)001:16265: 'bod pa'i pho nyas nyer bkug sde bzhi'i dbyar //
NK026(la)001:16266: dar drag pho brang 'chi med mdun sa'i spun //
NK026(la)001:16267: 'jig rten gsum gyi rgyan du 'gyur bar shog /
NK026(la)001:16268: chos srid 'dzin par byed pa'i rkang sen zla //
NK026(la)001:16269: gnam sa bar med yid can cod pan du //
NK026(la)001:16270: cha 'phel dus kyi bdag po'i che ba yis //
NK026(la)001:16271: snang bas nyes tshogs smag rum mthar skrod shog /
NK026(la)001:16272: phyogs bral chos kyi sbyin pas sgo 'phar brgya //
NK026(la)001:16273: 'byed par gtogs rnams rang rig kun tu bzang //
NK026(la)001:16274: logs su mi 'tshol ye nas lhun grub pa //
NK026(la)001:16275: ngo 'phrod sku gsum zhing du grol bar shog /
NK026(la)001:16276: lha chen legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po dang //
NK026(la)001:16277: dpal mgon stag zhon mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul che //
NK026(la)001:16278: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i spyan sngar g.yar dam can //
NK026(la)001:16279: chos skyong srung mas rtag tu grogs byed shog /
NK026(la)001:16280: mkha' la rdo rje ra ba'i gur ma zhig /
NK026(la)001:16281: sa la dkyil 'khor chen po'i bkrag ma nyams //
NK026(la)001:16282: bar du sman raka mchod gtor ngad ma yal //
NK026(la)001:16283: lha sngags ye shes dpal 'bar bkra shis shog /
NK026(la)001:16284: theg pa rim dgu yongs su rdzogs pa 'dus pa mdo dbang chen mo /
NK026(la)001:16286: bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes /
NK026(la)001:16287: sog po dpal gyi ye shes gsum las yo ga
NK026(la)001:16288: gsum gyi chu bo gcig tu 'dres pa gnubs sangs
NK026(la)001:16289: rgyas ye shes rin po cher bka' babs pa dar
NK026(la)001:16291: 'gos chag dpal 'dzin sogs kyi 'jams yig sna tshogs
NK026(la)001:16292: la brten 'gro mang chos spong gi 'ching rgyar chud
NK026(la)001:16293: pa dang / dus dbang gis grub mtha' mtha' dag
NK026(la)001:16294: gal chung chos la byed pa'i dbang gis rim gyis
NK026(la)001:16296: g.yu 'brug rdo rje zer ba nas brgyud pa rgyun yod med the tshom gyi gzhi dang /
NK026(la)001:16297: khams phyogs nas dar ba tshor yang phyag len zhib
NK026(la)001:16298: rtsing gi khyad nas bstan pa dri bcas su gyur
NK026(la)001:16300: rig 'dzin yol mo ba chen pos /
NK026(la)001:16301: rdo rje bdud 'joms rgod kyi ldem 'phru can //
NK026(la)001:16302: kha mkhal 'jam dbyangs bla ma yeshesa khyung //
NK026(la)001:16303: sangs rgyas 'bar dang g.yung ston legs ldan rje //
NK026(la)001:16304: de sogs skye ba'i tha ma 'di lta ste //
NK026(la)001:16305: mkhyen pa'i chu gter shin tu rgya che zhing //
NK026(la)001:16306: brtse chen thugs rje'i rin chen 'dod rgu 'jo //
NK026(la)001:16307: mthu stobs nus pa'i chu srin yongs 'du'i mtsho //
NK026(la)001:16308: ngag gi dbang po dgung zla'i ma mar 'dud //
NK026(la)001:16309: ces skyes rabs kyi phreng ba tshar du dngar ba
NK026(la)001:16310: rig 'dzin mchog gi sprul skur sgrig rtsom gnang dgos
NK026(la)001:16312: glegs bam du 'god par mdzad pa bstan rgyun la
NK026(la)001:16313: bsam dga' ldan phun tshogs gling du par du brkos
NK026(la)001:16314: pa'i tshe / spar byang smon lam du za hor
NK026(la)001:16315: gyi sngags smyon zil gnon bzhad pa rtsal gyis lcags
NK026(la)001:16316: bya hor zla bdun pa'i yar tshes la sbyar ba'i
NK026(la)001:16317: yi ge la ni 'chams dpon dge slong ngag dbang
NK026(la)001:16318: dkon mchog gis bgyis pa sar+b+basmi dik+k+aa lo da ye
